amond Hands","No refunds after evaluation access is granted. Resets available at $75 for most models. Fast Track accounts cannot be reset.",{"splitMax":203,"schedule":1101,"processingTime":1102,"firstPayoutDays":24,"methods":1103},"Weekly","Via Rise payment provider",[208],{"newsTrading":26,"weekendHolding":110,"copyTrading":26,"expertAdvisors":26,"consistencyRule":1105,"notes":1106},"Sim-Funded accounts require 10 Active Trading Days where each day earns at least 23% of your best day's profit, with a minimum floor of $100–$200 depending on account size. No consistency rule during evaluations.","News trading allowed across all models. Weekend holding only permitted on Diamond Hands and LIVE Elite accounts. Copy trading and multi-account mirroring allowed post-LIVE Elite with approval. Algo trading permitted with compatible Rithmic platforms — no martingale, HFT, or scratch trades. 10-second rule prohibits entering and exiting a trade within 10 seconds. VPNs and masked connections banned — stable IP and verified location required. Position caps enforced per model (e.g. 2 minis/20 micros on 25K DTF, up to 24 minis/240 micros on 250K Fast Track). Breaching position limits results in instant disqualification and forfeited profits. Up to 20 active Sim-Funded accounts allowed, maximum 3 Fast Tracks. Fast Track has a 14-day hard calendar limit. OFAC-sanctioned countries blocked at all stages. All trades routed via Rithmic to regulated US exchanges.",{"platforms":1108,"instruments":1112},[303,907,302,1109,1110,1111],"R | Trader Pro","EdgeProX","Sierra Chart","Futures only — CME (Forex Futures, Crypto Futures incl. BTC/ETH, Index Futures incl. ES/NQ/YM/RTY, Interest Rates), CBOT (Agricultural incl. Corn/Wheat/Soybeans, Treasuries), COMEX (Gold, Silver, Copper, Platinum, Palladium), NYMEX (Crude Oil, Natural Gas, Gasoline, Heating Oil). Standard, mini, and micro contracts available. No stocks, spot forex, or CFDs.",{"trustpilotRating":388,"trustpilotCount":1114,"communitySize":1115,"notableFlags":1116},900,"16,000+ Discord members",[1117,1118,1119,1120,1121,1122],"3.8/5 Trustpilot with 900+ reviews (62% five-star, 24% one-star)","Not regulated or broker-backed during evaluation and Sim-Funded stages","LIVE Elite accounts funded through EdgeClear broker partnership","No published criteria for LIVE Elite account approval","Sim-Funded accounts are demo-based with payout eligibility","Mixed reviews — payout disputes and rule interpretation concerns on forums",{"website":1124},"https://elitetraderfunding.com",{"logo":1126},"/images/logos/elite-trader-logo.png",{"restrictedCountries":1128},[628,571,629,630,1129,573],"SO",{"hours":1131,"liveChat":110,"email":26,"discord":26},"Business hours (email ticket system)",{"tags":1133},[1134,1135,1136,326],"No Clear Path to Live Funding","Sim-Funded Accounts","High Ongoing Fees",[1124],"src/content/prop-firms/elite-trader-funding.json","ee532def75fe80ef","funded-elite",{"id":1140,"data":1142,"filePath":1239,"digest":1240},{"id":1143,"slug":1140,"name":1144,"status":16,"hqCountry":1145,"evaluation":1146,"pricing":1150,"payouts":1198,"rules":1203,"markets":1206,"trust":1209,"links":1219,"media":1221,"availability":1223,"support":1230,"custom":1232,"lastVerifiedAt":519,"lastUpdatedAt":519,"dataSources":1238},"d0000042-0000-0000-0000-000000000042","Funded Elite","LC",{"types":1147,"profitTargets":1148,"dailyDrawdown":25,"maxDrawdown":24,"minTradingDays":158,"scalingPlan":26},[21,22,155],{"phase1":1149,"phase2":25},12,{"challengeFees":1151,"resetFee":98,"refundPolicy":1197},[1152,1155,1157,1159,1161,1163,1165,1167,1170,1172,1174,1175,1177,1179,1181,1182,1185,1186,1188,1190,1192,1194,1195,1196],{"accountSize":1153,"fee":167,"model":22,"label":1154},7000,"Standard Challenge",{"accountSize":1156,"fee":350,"model":22,"label":1154},15000,{"accountSize":38,"fee":1158,"model":22,"label":1154},101,{"accountSize":42,"fee":1160,"model":22,"label":1154},152,{"accountSize":46,"fee":1162,"model":22,"label":1154},240,{"a