 only between your own accounts — no social platform mirroring. EAs and automated trading allowed on MT5 but HFT, latency arbitrage, hedging, and micro scalping banned. Martingale allowed but not with over-leveraging or shared EAs. Account sharing, account rolling, and IP sharing strictly forbidden. Switching accounts mid-challenge not allowed. Scalping allowed only with add-on (positions must be held 30+ seconds). Payments accepted via cards, PayPal, bank transfers, wire transfers, and crypto (max $500 via Confirmo.net). Registered in Saint Lucia. Broker connectivity through Purple Trading (CySEC-regulated). MT5 and TradeLocker restricted in US, Cuba, Iran, Iraq, Lebanon, Libya, North Korea, Syria, Somalia, Algeria, Crimea, Donetsk, and Luhansk regions.",{"platforms":1207,"instruments":1208},[115,215],"Forex (50-70+ pairs, 1:30 base, 1:50 or 1:100 with add-ons), Indices (10-15+, 1:30 base), Metals (5-10+, 1:30 base), Commodities (5-15+, 1:30 base), Crypto CFDs (10-30+, 1:30 base), Stock CFDs (100-150+, 1:30 base), Futures CFDs (50-100+). All leverage adjustable to 1:50 (+10% fee) or 1:100 (+20% fee).",{"trustpilotRating":1210,"trustpilotCount":1211,"communitySize":98,"notableFlags":1212},4.5,562,[1213,1214,1215,1216,1217,1218],"Registered in Saint Lucia","Not backed by a regulated broker directly","Broker connectivity through Purple Trading (CySEC-regulated EU broker)","4.5/5 Trustpilot with 562 reviews","Mixed public perception — favorable Trustpilot but payout complaints on other platforms","Restricted in US, Canada, and several other countries",{"website":1220},"https://fundedelite.com",{"logo":1222},"/images/logos/fundedlite.png",{"restrictedCountries":1224},[249,1225,1226,628,571,1227,1228,1229,629,630,1129],"CA","DZ","IQ","LB","LY",{"hours":1231,"liveChat":110,"email":26},"24/7 email support",{"tags":1233},[1234,1235,237,1236,1237],"Multiple Challenge Models","Customisable Add-Ons","Pay Later Model","300+ CFD Products",[1220],"src/content/prop-firms/funded-el