2329,"model":2324,"label":2317},425,"No refund on challenge fees. Monthly subscription model — pay 50% upfront, remaining 50% once funded. Account reset: $50 for 25K/50K accounts, $100 for all others.",{"splitMax":377,"schedule":2332,"processingTime":379,"firstPayoutDays":98,"methods":2333},"On demand (anytime)",[2334,207],"bank wire",{"newsTrading":26,"weekendHolding":98,"copyTrading":26,"expertAdvisors":26,"consistencyRule":2336,"notes":2337},"Three best other trading days must equal 80% or more of the largest day's net profit","Futures-only prop firm. News trading allowed during evaluation; funded traders must avoid trading 1 minute before/after major economic releases (FOMC, employment, inflation, GDP). Copy trading allowed only between accounts under the same name. High-frequency trading and trades under 10 seconds prohibited. Group/synchronized trading not allowed. Hedging across multiple funded accounts not allowed. Weekly trade execution must be at least 50% of average evaluation trades. Trailing drawdown stops at initial balance. No daily loss limits.",{"platforms":2339,"instruments":2356},[907,2340,1111,2341,2342,2343,2344,2345,2346,2347,2348,2349,2350,2351,2352,2353,2354,2355],"R|Trader Pro","ScalpTool","Volfix.net","Agena Trader","Bookmap","Jigsaw Trading","MultiCharts","Medved Trader","Track 'n Trade","Trade Navigator","MotiveWave","InsideEDGE Trader","Vetta","iTrader","Order Flow Trading","Photon Trade","Futures Markets: 50+ CME-listed products including Equity Indices, Commodities, Currencies, Interest Rates, Agricultural (micro and e-mini contracts, leverage scales with account size)",{"trustpilotRating":120,"trustpilotCount":2015,"communitySize":2358,"notableFlags":2359},"Private Discord (course subscribers only)",[2360,2361,2362,2363],"4.7/5 Trustpilot from 2,000+ reviews","No public Discord channel","Active Instagram and Twitter presence","Paid educational programs available",{"website":2365},"https://oneuptrader.com?ref=mmewyzh",{"logo":2367},"/i