-3 px-5 py-2.5 hover:bg-teal-50/50 transition-colors\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-6 text-xs font-black text-slate-400\">6.\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/apex-trader-funding-logo.png\" alt=\"Apex Trader Funding\" class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-md object-contain border border-slate-200 bg-white p-0.5 flex-shrink-0\" />\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-1 text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Apex Trader Funding\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500\">135,000\u003C/span>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-3 px-5 py-2.5 hover:bg-teal-50/50 transition-colors\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-6 text-xs font-black text-slate-400\">7.\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/instant-funding-logo-1.png\" alt=\"Instant Funding\" class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-md object-contain border border-slate-200 bg-white p-0.5 flex-shrink-0\" />\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-1 text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Instant Funding\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500\">90,500\u003C/span>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-3 px-5 py-2.5 hover:bg-teal-50/50 transition-colors\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-6 text-xs font-black text-slate-400\">8.\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-md bg-teal-500 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0\">\n        \u003Cspan class=\"text-[8px] font-black text-white\">EE\u003C/span>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-1 text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Equity Edge\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500\">90,500\u003C/span>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-3 px-5 py-2.5 hover:bg-teal-50/50 transition-colors\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-6 text-xs font-black text-slate-400\">9.\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/blueberry-funded-logo.png\" alt=\"Blueberry Funded\" class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-md object-contain border border-slate-200 bg-white p-0.5 flex-shrink-0\" />\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-1 text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Blueberry Funded\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500\">49,500\u003C/span>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-3 px-5 py-2.5 hover:bg-teal-50/50 transition-colors\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-6 text-xs font-black text-slate-400\">10.\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/alphacapital-1.png\" alt=\"Alpha Capital\" class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-md object-contain border border-slate-200 bg-white p-0.5 flex-shrink-0\" />\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-1 text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Alpha Capital\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500\">49,500\u003C/span>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n---\n\n## How to Choose The Best Prop Firms\n\nTo choose the best prop trading firm, you need to compare features that directly affect your chances of getting funded and earning payouts. Here are the key areas that matter:\n\n- **Challenges and Rules:** Look for firms with realistic profit targets (under 10%), clear drawdown limits, and flexible evaluation formats.\n- **Profit Splits and Scaling:** The best firms let you keep at least 80% of profits and offer account scaling based on performance.\n- **Fees and Spreads:** Lower challenge fees and tight spreads make it easier to pass evaluations and stay profitable.\n- **Trading Platforms:** Choose a firm that supports platforms like MT4, MT5, cTrader, or TradingView, depending on your preference.\n- **Market Access and Leverage:** More asset classes and leverage options give you greater flexibility in how you trade.\n- **Payouts:** Fast and consistent withdrawals, low minimums, and clear buffer zone rules help you access profits quickly.\n- **Support and Education:** Look for responsive support and clear trading guidelines, especially if you're new to prop trading.\n- **Transparency and Trust:** A good reputation, public reviews, and clear policies signal a firm you can rely on.\n\n---\n\n## How To Become A Prop Trader\n\nTo become a prop trader, you need to sign up with a proprietary trading firm, complete their evaluation process, and meet specific trading requirements. Most firms require traders to pass a challenge or evaluation phase before providing access to a funded account. Here's a step-by-step guide on how to get started:\n\n1. **Choose the right prop firm:** Research prop trading firms based on factors such as evaluation fees, profit splits, trading platforms, and the types of financial instruments they offer (forex, equities, futures, etc.). Select the firm that aligns with your trading style and objectives. We have specific pages for:\n   - [UK Prop Traders](/guides/uk)\n   - [Canadian Prop Traders](/guides/canada)\n   - [Indian Prop Traders](/guides/india)\n   - [Australian Prop Traders](/guides/australia)\n2. **Sign up and pay the evaluation fee:** Register with the firm and pay the fee to start the evaluation process or challenge. Fees will vary depending on the account size and the specific challenge you choose.\n3. **Complete the evaluation or challenge:** Follow the firm's guidelines during the challenge. You'll need to meet profit targets and avoid exceeding drawdown limits (maximum allowable losses). Challenges can vary in structure, with some requiring a single evaluation phase and others requiring two.\n4. **Pass the challenge to get funded:** Once you successfully complete the evaluation, the firm will provide a funded account. This account allows you to trade using the firm's capital.\n5. **Start trading and earn profits:** Begin trading with the firm's money, and share the profits based on the firm's profit split (e.g., 80% for you, 20% for the firm). Be sure to follow their risk management rules to maintain your funded account.\n6. **Scale your account:** Some firms offer scaling plans that allow you to increase your account size by consistently reaching profit targets. This can provide access to more capital over time, increasing your potential earnings.\n\nFollowing these steps can help you successfully become a prop trader, using the firm's capital to trade and keep a portion of the profits you generate.\n\n---\n\n## What Are The Risks Of Prop Trading?\n\nProp trading comes with several risks. One key risk is drawdown limits: prop firms impose strict daily or overall drawdown limits that, if breached, can result in disqualification. High-pressure evaluations also pose a challenge, where failing to meet profit targets can lead to the loss of entry fees without any payout. Additionally, some firms have restrictive rules, such as limiting trading styles or requiring strict risk management, which might not align with every trader's strategy. Market volatility is another factor, as even the most skilled traders can face significant losses in unpredictable market conditions. Finally, some prop firms lack transparency, so researching their reputation and rules is crucial before signing up.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Pros & Cons of Prop Trading\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Pros\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Use firm capital, limiting personal risk\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Keep up to 90% of profits\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Only risk the initial fee\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Access larger capital through scaling\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Max trading skills with mentoring\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Strict rules on drawdowns and profit targets\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Pressure to perform within deadlines\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Lose fees if the challenge isn't passed\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Some strategies may be restricted\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Market volatility makes goals tougher\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\nWe developed a guide on our [risk management](/risk-management) page to explore this area further for those new to the industry.\n\n---\n\n## FAQs\n\n### What is the best prop firm?\n\nDNA Funded is the best prop firm overall in 2026, with a top score of 97/100 in our testing. We evaluated over 28 prop firms firsthand using criteria like challenge rules, pricing, profit splits, platforms, and payout speed. In our 2026 prop firm testing, DNA Funded had the smoothest onboarding and account access, contributing to its high overall score.\n\nTo reduce upfront fees, use DNA Funded promo code PROPFIRMS25 for 25% off.\n\n### What is prop trading?\n\nProprietary trading (prop trading) allows traders to use virtual funds in financial markets like forex, shares, and commodities, after paying an initial evaluation fee. The aim is to meet specific profit targets to qualify for a funded account, where real money is provided by the prop firm. Profits are then shared between the trader and the firm, while any losses are covered by the prop company.\n\n### How many prop firms are forex brokers?\n\nMany prop firms have ties to CFD brokers and use them as their providers for pricing and spreads. For example, DNA Funded is backed by Eightcap Challenges, a regulated CFD broker. However, when you're doing the challenge, you're in a simulated environment rather than live trading, so the prop firm itself isn't acting as a broker. Only after you pass the challenge and get funded do you start trading in real markets, often through their broker partners.\n\nView our full list of [broker backed prop firms](/prop-firms).\n\n### Why use a prop firm rather than a real account?\n\nThe main advantage of using a prop firm over a real trading account is limiting personal financial risk. With a prop firm, you only risk the initial evaluation fee, while losses beyond that are covered by the firm. Once you qualify for a funded account, you receive a profit share without risking your own capital. Additionally, it's a great way to refine your trading strategies before committing to a live forex or CFD account with your own funds.\n\n### Which is the most trusted prop firm?\n\nThe most trusted prop firms are DNA Funded and IC Funded, based on key factors such as reliability, user reviews, and trading conditions. DNA Funded is backed by Eightcap Challenges, ensuring low fees and an 80% profit split. IC Funded offers tight spreads, low entry costs, and strong backing from IC Markets. Each firm is known for transparency and trader support.\n\nIt's important to understand how these firms make money prior to opening an account.\n\n### What prop firm pays the fastest?\n\nThe prop firms that offer the fastest payouts include DNA Funded, IC Funded, and Funded Trading Plus. DNA Funded allows traders to request profits as early as 14 days after their first trade, with flexible withdrawal options. IC Funded offers bi-weekly or on-demand withdrawals starting 14 days after the initial trade and has an outstanding crypto prop trading range. Funded Trading Plus also provides quick access to profits with instant funding and profit splits of up to 100%, making it another option for traders seeking fast payouts.\n\n### Which prop firm is better than FTMO?\n\nDNA Funded and IC Funded can be better options than FTMO, depending on what you're looking for. DNA Funded has lower fees starting at $49, an 80% – 90% profit split, and flexible challenge options. IC Funded, on the other hand, offers super-low spreads from 0 pips, strong ties to IC Markets, and popular platforms like MT4, MT5, and cTrader. Both firms offer lower costs and better trading conditions than FTMO, especially when it comes to forex prop trading.\n\n### What are the top prop trading firms with the highest profit splits?\n\nTop prop trading firms with the highest profit splits include Topstep, which offers up to 100% profit split on the first $10,000 earned and 90% after that. Funded Trading Plus provides profit splits that can go up to 100%, making it a strong option for traders.\n\nWhile high profit splits are appealing, it's crucial to also consider other factors such as challenge difficulty, fees, trading conditions, and customer support. Some firms with higher splits may have stricter rules or higher fees, so weigh the overall offering against your trading goals.\n\n---\n\n## How We Selected the Best Prop Firms for 2026\n\nTo find the best prop firms worldwide, we evaluated over 28 top prop trading firms, focusing on challenges, platform usability, payouts and targets, and cost structure. By personally testing each firm's challenges, platforms, and trading conditions, we narrowed the list to the 10 best prop firms based on essential metrics.\n\nOur comprehensive testing and analysis considered user experience, platform accessibility, and transparent fee structures, ensuring a balanced and realistic set of options for traders. Following our methodology allowed us to highlight firms offering the most achievable challenges and optimal profit-sharing terms, providing you with a clear, data-driven guide to selecting a prop trading firm that suits your needs.","src/content/blog/australia.md","bd266a94f64d62ed",{"html":4825,"metadata":4826},"\u003Ch2 id=\"what-are-the-best-prop-firms-in-2026\">What Are The Best Prop Firms In 2026?\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>Prop trading lets you trade with a firm’s capital, so you’re not risking your own money. In exchange, you split your profits with the firm. With more and more prop firms popping up, you now have options with lower entry fees and higher profit splits. We reviewed the best prop firms, focusing on things like low challenge fees, access to different markets, fair profit-sharing models, and transparent trading rules.\u003C/p>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"1-dna-funded--best-prop-firm-for-australian-traders\">1. DNA Funded — Best Prop Firm For Australian Traders\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>DNA Funded ranked 1st place in our list of the best prop firms, earning a top score of 97/100 for its low challenge fees from $49, flexible one- and two-step evaluations, and 80%–90% profit splits. Backed by DNA Markets, it offers tight spreads and uses the TradeLocker platform. You get access to over 800 markets including forex, stocks, and crypto, making it a strong option whether you’re just starting out or scaling up.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/dna-funded-logo.png\" alt=\"DNA Funded logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">DNA Funded\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">Best Prop Firm For Australian Traders\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">90%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Max DD\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">10%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Trustpilot\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">4.9 \u003Cspan class=\"text-amber-500\">★\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Ca href=\"/reviews/dna-funded\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-lg bg-teal-500 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-white hover:bg-teal-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n        Full Review →\n      \u003C/a>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose -mt-3 mb-6 rounded-xl border border-emerald-200 bg-emerald-50/80 px-5 py-3 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-3\">\n  \u003Ca href=\"https://partners.dnafunded.com/click?campaign_id=1&#x26;ref_id=30\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-emerald-500 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-emerald-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n    Visit DNA Funded\n  \u003C/a>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2.5\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4 text-emerald-600 flex-shrink-0\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M7 7h.01M7 3h5c.512 0 1.024.195 1.414.586l7 7a2 2 0 010 2.828l-7 7a2 2 0 01-2.828 0l-7-7A1.994 1.994 0 013 12V7a4 4 0 014-4z\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm text-emerald-700 font-semibold\">25% Off — Code:\u003C/span>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"font-mono font-bold text-xs bg-white border border-dashed border-emerald-300 px-3 py-1.5 rounded text-emerald-700 tracking-wide select-all\">PROPFIRMS25\u003C/span>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Pros &#x26; Cons\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Pros\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Fees from $49 and unique addons\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Low commission $5 roundturn\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Forex, crypto, stocks, and more\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>No MT4 or MT5\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Scaling plan TBC\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>No instant funding\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"why-dna-funded-is-1-best-prop-firm\">Why DNA Funded is #1 Best Prop Firm\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Based on our analysis of the top prop firms worldwide, we found DNA Funded to be the best prop firm overall with a score of 97/100.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>The Australian-based prop firm is backed by regulated broker DNA Markets (ASIC AFSL 514425), offering traders access to institutional-grade conditions like tight spreads, fast execution, and low trading costs. It stands out for its flexible one-step and two-step challenges, competitive fees, and profit splits of up to 90%.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>With TradeLocker integrated with TradingView, access to 800+ markets, and trading rule sets that align with forex broker compliance standards, DNA Funded offers the most complete setup we’ve tested.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Use PROPFIRMS25 to get 25% off challenge fees, making it cheaper to get started!\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"prop-challenges-and-accounts\">Prop Challenges and Accounts\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>DNA Funded offers three challenge types, catering to various trading styles:\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Single Helix (1-step challenge):\u003C/strong> Account sizes from $5,000 to $200,000. Fees start at $59, with a 10% profit target and no time limits, making it ideal for swing traders and those focused on longer-term strategies.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Double Helix (2-step challenge):\u003C/strong> Account sizes also range from $5,000 to $200,000, with fees starting at $49. Phase 1 requires a 10% profit target, while Phase 2 lowers it to 5%, with flexible trading days.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Rapid Challenge (1-step challenge):\u003C/strong> Designed for more experienced traders with account sizes ranging from $10,000 to $100,000, and fees from $99. This challenge requires a 5% profit target to be met within 10 days, with a stricter drawdown limit, making it suitable for scalpers or high-frequency traders.\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003Ctable>\u003Cthead>\u003Ctr>\u003Cth>DNA Funded Account Type\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Challenge Fees\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Account Sizes\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Early Payout (14→7 Days) Addon\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Profit Split Increase (80%→90%) Addon\u003C/th>\u003C/tr>\u003C/thead>\u003Ctbody>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>Single Helix (1 Step)\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$59 - $1,451\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>5K - 200K\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Yes\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>No\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>Double Helix (2 Step)\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$49 - $1,295\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>5K - 200K\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>No\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Yes\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>Pro Challenge\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$99 - $714\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>10K - 100K\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Yes\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Yes\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003C/tbody>\u003C/table>\n\u003Cp>After passing the evaluation process of your choosing, you will receive a certificate of recognition as funded traders do when completing the challenge firsthand.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"markets-and-leverage\">Markets and Leverage\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>DNA Funded provides access to over 800 forex, commodities, indices, stocks, and crypto markets (with restrictions on crypto in the Pro Challenge).\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Leverage varies by challenge type and asset. Forex is capped at 1:50 on Double Helix and 1:30 on Single Helix and Pro Challenge. Commodities and indices are fixed at 1:10, stocks at 1:5 following a recent reduction from 1:10, and crypto is 1:2 but only available on Single and Double Helix.\u003C/p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003Ctable>\u003Cthead>\u003Ctr>\u003Cth>Asset Class\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Single Helix\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Double Helix\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Pro Challenge\u003C/th>\u003C/tr>\u003C/thead>\u003Ctbody>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>Forex\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1:30\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1:50\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1:30\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>Commodities\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1:10\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1:10\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1:10\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>Indices\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1:10\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1:10\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1:10\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>Stocks\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1:5\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1:5\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1:5\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>Crypto\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1:2\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1:2\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Not Allowed\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003C/tbody>\u003C/table>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"trading-platforms\">Trading Platforms\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>All trading is done through \u003Cstrong>TradeLocker\u003C/strong>, which comes fully integrated with TradingView. This setup is ideal for manual traders who want advanced charting, one-click execution, and a clean web-based interface. However, automated trading and EAs are not supported.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>DNA Funded keeps its trading rules simple and in line with broker-backed standards. All accounts follow daily and overall drawdown limits based on the challenge type, and a daily profit cap of 40% now applies. This means you can only count up to 40% of your payout target in one trading day, which helps support steady, consistent trading.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Automated trading and expert advisors (EAs) are not allowed. You can copy trades between your own accounts, but not from others. News trading is allowed, but you’ll need to avoid opening or closing positions within 10 minutes of high-impact news. Weekend trading is also permitted.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"trust-and-community\">Trust and Community\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>DNA Funded is backed by DNA Markets, a well-known ASIC-regulated broker (AFSL 514425), ensuring tight spreads and reliable execution. While DNA Funded is still new, its connection to DNA Markets boosts its credibility hugely.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>The prop firm is also developing an active trading community through its Discord channel, offering a space for traders to connect and share insights.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"our-verdict-on-dna-funded\">Our Verdict on DNA Funded\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>DNA Funded is the best prop trading firm for 2026 even in the early stages of launch thanks to its flexible challenges, low fees, and an 80% – 90% profit share. Backed by DNA Markets, it provides reliable market access across forex, commodities, indices, stocks, and crypto. You can read our full evaluation on our \u003Ca href=\"/reviews/dna-funded\">DNA Funded review\u003C/a> page.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>With a user-friendly platform like TradeLocker and growing community support, DNA Funded is the best prop firm for both new and experienced traders looking for a new challenge to become a funded trader.\u003C/p>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"2-brightfunded--profit-share-scales-to-100\">2. BrightFunded — Profit Share Scales to 100%\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>BrightFunded earned our #2 spot with a score of 95/100, thanks to its industry-leading profit share that scales up to 100%, a well-structured two-step evaluation, and access to three top trading platforms. Based in the Netherlands, BrightFunded stands out for its transparent rules, wide market coverage, and a scaling plan with no cap — making it an excellent choice for Australian traders looking to grow their funded accounts over time.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/brightfunded-logo.png\" alt=\"BrightFunded logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">BrightFunded\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">Profit Share Scales to 100%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">100%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Max DD\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">10%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Trustpilot\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">4.7 \u003Cspan class=\"text-amber-500\">★\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Ca href=\"/reviews/brightfunded\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-lg bg-teal-500 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-white hover:bg-teal-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n        Full Review →\n      \u003C/a>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose -mt-3 mb-6 rounded-xl border border-emerald-200 bg-emerald-50/80 px-5 py-3 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-3\">\n  \u003Ca href=\"https://brightfunded.com?affiliateId=rsBbtrzYQSyr3RcHYHQT5w\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-emerald-500 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-emerald-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n    Visit BrightFunded\n  \u003C/a>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2.5\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4 text-emerald-600 flex-shrink-0\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M7 7h.01M7 3h5c.512 0 1.024.195 1.414.586l7 7a2 2 0 010 2.828l-7 7a2 2 0 01-2.828 0l-7-7A1.994 1.994 0 013 12V7a4 4 0 014-4z\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm text-emerald-700 font-semibold\">20% Off — Code:\u003C/span>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"font-mono font-bold text-xs bg-white border border-dashed border-emerald-300 px-3 py-1.5 rounded text-emerald-700 tracking-wide select-all\">PROPFIRMS20\u003C/span>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Pros &#x26; Cons\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Pros\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Profit share scales up to 100%\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Wide market access with forex, indices, crypto\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Unlimited scaling plan with no cap\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>No MT4 platform available\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>No instant funding option\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Minimal educational resources\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"more-about-brightfunded\">More About BrightFunded\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>BrightFunded scored 95/100 in our review for its strong combination of high payouts, flexible rules, and multiple platform choices. What sets it apart is the profit share that starts at 80% and scales all the way to 100% through their loyalty program — one of the highest in the industry.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>The firm runs a two-step evaluation with an 8% profit target in Phase 1 and 5% in Phase 2. The daily drawdown is capped at 5% and the maximum drawdown at 10%, with a minimum of 5 trading days required per phase. There are no maximum time limits, so you can trade at your own pace.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"challenge-fees-and-account-sizes\">Challenge Fees and Account Sizes\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>BrightFunded offers account sizes from $5,000 to $200,000, all through their two-phase evaluation:\u003C/p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003Ctable>\u003Cthead>\u003Ctr>\u003Cth>Account Size\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Challenge Fee\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Phase 1 Target\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Phase 2 Target\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Daily DD\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Max DD\u003C/th>\u003C/tr>\u003C/thead>\u003Ctbody>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>$5,000\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$55\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>8%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>5%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>5%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>10%\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>$10,000\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$95\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>8%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>5%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>5%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>10%\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>$25,000\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$195\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>8%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>5%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>5%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>10%\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>$50,000\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$295\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>8%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>5%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>5%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>10%\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>$100,000\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$495\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>8%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>5%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>5%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>10%\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>$200,000\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$975\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>8%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>5%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>5%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>10%\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003C/tbody>\u003C/table>\n\u003Cp>All challenge fees are refundable with the 100% Refund add-on (10% surcharge). BrightFunded also offers optional add-ons like bi-weekly or weekly payouts to customise your experience.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"markets-and-leverage-1\">Markets and Leverage\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>BrightFunded provides access to forex, indices, commodities, and crypto markets. Leverage varies by asset class:\u003C/p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003Ctable>\u003Cthead>\u003Ctr>\u003Cth>Asset Class\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Leverage\u003C/th>\u003C/tr>\u003C/thead>\u003Ctbody>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>Forex\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Up to 1:100\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>Indices\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Up to 1:20\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>Commodities\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Up to 1:20\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>Crypto\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Up to 1:5\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003C/tbody>\u003C/table>\n\u003Cp>The higher forex leverage at 1:100 is a notable advantage over many competitors, giving traders more flexibility to manage positions across currency pairs.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"trading-platforms-1\">Trading Platforms\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>BrightFunded supports three industry-leading platforms, catering to a range of trading styles:\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>MT5 (MetaTrader 5):\u003C/strong> The industry standard with expert advisor support, multi-asset capabilities, and advanced order types. Ideal for traders who rely on automated strategies.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>cTrader:\u003C/strong> Known for its clean interface, fast execution, and advanced charting. A favourite among manual traders and scalpers for its depth of market data and intuitive layout.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>DXTrade:\u003C/strong> A web-based platform offering TradingView-style charting with a simple, modern interface. Great for traders who prefer browser-based access without installing software.\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"trading-rules\">Trading Rules\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>News trading is unrestricted during the evaluation phase, with a 10-minute window restriction on funded accounts during major events. Weekend holding is allowed, and hedging is permitted within a single account. Expert advisors are supported on MT5. Copy trading from external sources is not allowed.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"trust-and-community-1\">Trust and Community\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>BrightFunded holds a \u003Cstrong>4.7/5 on Trustpilot\u003C/strong>, reflecting strong trader satisfaction. The firm has built an active community of over 16,000 members on Discord, providing a space for traders to share strategies, tips, and payout certificates. Customer support is available via live chat and email, with generally fast response times reported by users.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>BrightFunded regularly shares payout certificates from funded traders, adding transparency and credibility to their payout process.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"our-verdict-on-brightfunded\">Our Verdict on BrightFunded\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>BrightFunded is a standout prop firm for Australian traders who want to maximise their earnings through a profit share that scales to 100%. With three solid platforms, competitive challenge fees, and an unlimited scaling plan, it offers excellent long-term growth potential. The two-step evaluation is straightforward with fair targets, and the high forex leverage at 1:100 gives traders more room to work with. You can read our full evaluation on our \u003Ca href=\"/reviews/brightfunded\">BrightFunded review\u003C/a> page.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>While there’s no instant funding option and MT4 isn’t available, BrightFunded makes up for it with strong payouts, a growing community, and reliable trading conditions.\u003C/p>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"3-blueberry-funded--1100-financial-markets\">3. Blueberry Funded — 1,100+ Financial Markets\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>Blueberry Funded ranks as the 3rd best prop firm thanks to its range of challenges and accounts, low fees, and strong broker backing. You can choose between instant funding for immediate access to capital or structured evaluations through one and two step challenges. Across all account types and platforms, trading conditions stay transparent with raw spreads from 0.1 pips, profit splits up to 90%, and access to over 1,100 financial markets.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/blueberry-funded-logo.png\" alt=\"Blueberry Funded logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">Blueberry Funded\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">1,100+ Financial Markets\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">90%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Max DD\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">10%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Trustpilot\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">3.8 \u003Cspan class=\"text-amber-500\">★\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Ca href=\"/reviews/blueberry-funded\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-lg bg-teal-500 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-white hover:bg-teal-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n        Full Review →\n      \u003C/a>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose -mt-3 mb-6 rounded-xl border border-emerald-200 bg-emerald-50/80 px-5 py-3 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-3\">\n  \u003Ca href=\"https://blueberryfunded.com/?utm_source=affiliate&#x26;ref=1457\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-emerald-500 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-emerald-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n    Visit Blueberry Funded\n  \u003C/a>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2.5\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4 text-emerald-600 flex-shrink-0\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M7 7h.01M7 3h5c.512 0 1.024.195 1.414.586l7 7a2 2 0 010 2.828l-7 7a2 2 0 01-2.828 0l-7-7A1.994 1.994 0 013 12V7a4 4 0 014-4z\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm text-emerald-700 font-semibold\">20% Off — Code:\u003C/span>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"font-mono font-bold text-xs bg-white border border-dashed border-emerald-300 px-3 py-1.5 rounded text-emerald-700 tracking-wide select-all\">PROPFIRMS20\u003C/span>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Pros &#x26; Cons\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Pros\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Low challenge fees from $25\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Scaling up to $2 million\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>MT4, MT5, DXTrade, TradeLocker\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Limited educational resources\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Fewer payment options\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Higher spreads on some forex pairs\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"more-about-blueberry-funded\">More About Blueberry Funded\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Blueberry Funded is a prop trading firm that came in 3rd place in our rankings with a score of 93/100. This is because they’ve developed one of the most versatile setups among the top prop firms, giving you the choice between instant access and structured evaluation processes. Each challenge follows clear, rule-based conditions with defined drawdown limits and payout structures.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"prop-challenges-and-accounts-1\">Prop Challenges and Accounts\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Blueberry Funded offers everything from instant accounts to two-step challenges:\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Instant Lite &#x26; Instant Elite:\u003C/strong> No evaluation required. You trade funded capital immediately with fixed trailing drawdowns. Lite is tighter for short-term strategies, while Elite gives more room for longer trades.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Rapid Challenge:\u003C/strong> A single-phase evaluation designed for faster traders who want quick feedback and short timeframes.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>One Step Challenge:\u003C/strong> A straightforward, single-phase model suited to confident traders who prefer a clear target and static drawdown.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Two Step Challenge:\u003C/strong> A traditional two-phase evaluation for those who prefer structure and gradual progression.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Prime Challenge:\u003C/strong> A slightly stricter version of the Two Step challenge, built for consistency-focused traders.\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Cp>This great range of account options make Blueberry one of the few prop firms offering both instant funding and multiple evaluation processes, without overcomplicating the rules.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"markets-and-leverage-2\">Markets and Leverage\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Blueberry Funded gives access to over 1,100 instruments across six asset classes, with conditions and leverage varying slightly by challenge type.\u003C/p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003Ctable>\u003Cthead>\u003Ctr>\u003Cth>Asset Class\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Details\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Leverage\u003C/th>\u003C/tr>\u003C/thead>\u003Ctbody>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>Forex\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Available across all programs, spreads from 0.1 pips\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Up to 1:50 (Elite/Two Step/Prime) · 1:30 (Lite/One Step/Rapid)\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>Indices\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>14 global markets incl. US30, NAS100, GER30\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1:10\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>Commodities\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>17 products incl. gold, silver, oil, natural gas\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1:10\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>Crypto\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>52 pairs incl. BTC/USD, ETH/USD — 24/7 on MT5 &#x26; TradeLocker\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1:2\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>Stocks\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1,000+ US stock CFDs (Stock Challenge &#x26; Instant Elite)\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1:10\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>Synthetics\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>12 volatility-based indices (Synthetic Challenge only)\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1:30\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003C/tbody>\u003C/table>\n\u003Cp>The market coverage is broad enough for diversified trading across forex, commodities, and equities, while maintaining sensible leverage that supports steady, controlled performance.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"trading-platforms-2\">Trading Platforms\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Blueberry Funded offers four trading platforms:\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>MetaTrader 4 (MT4):\u003C/strong> Best for forex traders, with strong support for Expert Advisors (EAs) and advanced charting tools.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>MetaTrader 5 (MT5):\u003C/strong> Offers additional features like Depth of Market (DOM) and multi-threaded backtesting for more advanced traders.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>DXTrade:\u003C/strong> A browser-based platform, which, while flexible, lacks the advanced features of MT4 and MT5, making it less ideal for active traders.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>TradeLocker:\u003C/strong> A newer platform known for its clean interface and user-friendly layout. It’s accessible via web and mobile, and is especially useful for traders who want a modern, simplified trading experience without the heavier footprint of MT4/MT5.\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"trust-and-community-2\">Trust and Community\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Blueberry Funded’s partnership with Blueberry Markets, a regulated Australian broker (ASIC AFSL 535887), provides confidence in its pricing and operational integrity. The firm is also a founding member of The Prop Association, a group promoting transparency and trader protection across the industry.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Its growing Discord community now includes more than 30,000 members, offering daily updates, payout confirmations, and peer discussion for both new and funded traders.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Blueberry has also begun publishing verified payout proofs, showing consistent payment reliability as the program continues to expand.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"our-verdict-on-blueberry-funded\">Our Verdict on Blueberry Funded\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Blueberry Funded scored 93/100 overall which came down to accessible pricing, professional trading conditions, and a clear selection of challenges for every experience level. Whether you want instant access to capital or prefer to earn funding through structured evaluations, the options are well balanced with fair trading rules.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>With regulatory backing, strong platform coverage, and transparent costs, it’s by far one of the most complete prop trading firms currently available.\u003C/p>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"4-fxify--instant-funding-prop-firm\">4. FXIFY — Instant Funding Prop Firm\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>FXIFY ranked 4th overall, but it holds 1st place on our instant funding prop firm list. You can start with up to $50,000 in capital instantly, scale to $4 million, and keep up to 90% of your profits. Prefer to go through an evaluation? FXIFY also offers One Step, Two Step, and Three Step challenges.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Backed by FXPIG, FXIFY combines tight pricing, fast execution, and an active Discord community for added support.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/fxify-1-1-1-1.png\" alt=\"FXIFY logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">FXIFY\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">Instant Funding Prop Firm\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">90%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Max DD\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">10%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Trustpilot\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">4.2 \u003Cspan class=\"text-amber-500\">★\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Ca href=\"/reviews/fxify\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-lg bg-teal-500 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-white hover:bg-teal-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n        Full Review →\n      \u003C/a>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose -mt-3 mb-6 rounded-xl border border-emerald-200 bg-emerald-50/80 px-5 py-3 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-3\">\n  \u003Ca href=\"https://trader.fxify.com/purchasechallenge?affiliateId=5837\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-emerald-500 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-emerald-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n    Visit FXIFY\n  \u003C/a>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2.5\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4 text-emerald-600 flex-shrink-0\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M7 7h.01M7 3h5c.512 0 1.024.195 1.414.586l7 7a2 2 0 010 2.828l-7 7a2 2 0 01-2.828 0l-7-7A1.994 1.994 0 013 12V7a4 4 0 014-4z\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm text-emerald-700 font-semibold\">15% Off — Code:\u003C/span>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"font-mono font-bold text-xs bg-white border border-dashed border-emerald-300 px-3 py-1.5 rounded text-emerald-700 tracking-wide select-all\">PROPFIRMS15\u003C/span>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Pros &#x26; Cons\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Pros\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Instant funding with up to $50,000 capital\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>One, two, or three step evaluation processes\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Profit splits up to 90% with scaling up to $4M\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Limited transparency on actual trading costs\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Higher leverage upgrade has additional fee\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Payouts for larger accounts could be faster\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"more-about-fxify\">More About FXIFY\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>FXIFY scored 90/100 and is the 4th best prop firm we tested thanks to its instant funding accounts and flexible evaluation challenges. You can start with up to $50,000 in capital immediately, making it one of the best prop firms if you want to skip the entire evaluation process and trade straight away.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>For those who prefer an evaluation, FXIFY also offers Lightning, One Step, Two Step, and Three Step challenges, with scalable account sizes and profit splits up to 90%. You can also trade futures through their FXIFY Futures branch, which came in 8th place on our list after establishing a reputation as the best futures prop firm worldwide.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"prop-challenges-and-accounts-2\">Prop Challenges and Accounts\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>FXIFY offers four funding options, including a direct instant funding account and three evaluation challenges:\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Instant Funding Account:\u003C/strong> No challenge required — you can start trading immediately with up to $50,000 in capital. Comes with an 8% trailing drawdown and 90% profit split.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>One Step Challenge:\u003C/strong> A single-phase challenge with a 10% profit target and a 6% max drawdown, designed for traders who want a faster route to funding.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Two Step Challenge:\u003C/strong> A structured two-step evaluation, requiring 10% profit in Phase 1 and 5% in Phase 2, with a 10% trailing drawdown limit.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Three Step Challenge:\u003C/strong> The most gradual challenge, designed for lower-risk traders, requiring 5% profit in each phase, with a 5% daily loss cap.\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003Ctable>\u003Cthead>\u003Ctr>\u003Cth>Feature\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Instant Funding\u003C/th>\u003Cth>One Step\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Two Step\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Three Step\u003C/th>\u003C/tr>\u003C/thead>\u003Ctbody>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>Phases\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>None\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>2\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>3\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>Profit Target\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>—\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>10%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>10% / 5%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>5% per phase\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>Daily Loss Limit\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>3%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>3%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>3%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>5%\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>Max Drawdown\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>8% trailing\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>6% trailing\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>10% trailing\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>10% static\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>Starting Fee\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$69\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$59\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$59\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$39\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>Max Account\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$50K\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$400K\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$400K\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$400K\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003C/tbody>\u003C/table>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"markets-and-leverage-3\">Markets and Leverage\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>FXIFY provides access to 100+ trading instruments, including forex pairs, indices, commodities like gold and crude oil, major stocks (MT5 only), and cryptocurrencies (MT4 &#x26; MT5 only).\u003C/p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003Ctable>\u003Cthead>\u003Ctr>\u003Cth>Asset Class\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Leverage\u003C/th>\u003C/tr>\u003C/thead>\u003Ctbody>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>Forex &#x26; Gold\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>30:1 (upgradable to 50:1 for a fee)\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>Indices\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>10:1\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>Stocks\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>2:1\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>Crypto\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>2:1\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003C/tbody>\u003C/table>\n\u003Cp>Standard leverage is 30:1 for forex and gold, 10:1 for indices, and 2:1 for stocks and crypto, with an optional upgrade to 50:1 leverage for forex and gold.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"trust-and-community-3\">Trust and Community\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>FXIFY is backed by FXPIG, a trusted forex broker, ensuring competitive pricing and fast execution. The firm has built a strong trader community, with over 38,000 members on Discord and a \u003Cstrong>4.2/5 Trustpilot rating\u003C/strong>.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>While FXIFY generally receives positive reviews for its flexible account options and profit splits, some traders report delays in payouts for larger accounts and limited transparency on spreads.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"our-verdict-on-fxify\">Our Verdict on FXIFY\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>FXIFY is the best prop firm for instant funding, offering traders capital from day one without a challenge. With profit splits up to 90%, flexible evaluation options, and a scaling plan that can grow accounts to $4M, it took spot number four on our best prop trading firms list for 2026.\u003C/p>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"5-fundednext--good-tradingview-prop-firm\">5. FundedNext — Good TradingView Prop Firm\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>FundedNext came in 5th place, offering funded accounts with profit splits up to 95%, a flexible scaling plan, and fast withdrawals. You can choose between the Stellar and Stellar Lite models, depending on your trading style and budget. With account scaling up to $4 million and bi-weekly withdrawals, FundedNext is a top prop firm if you want fast access to funding and flexible trading options.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/fundednext.png\" alt=\"FundedNext logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">FundedNext\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">Good TradingView Prop Firm\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">95%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Max DD\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">10%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Trustpilot\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">4.6 \u003Cspan class=\"text-amber-500\">★\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Ca href=\"/reviews/fundednext\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-lg bg-teal-500 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-white hover:bg-teal-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n        Full Review →\n      \u003C/a>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose -mt-3 mb-6 rounded-xl border border-emerald-200 bg-emerald-50/80 px-5 py-3 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-3\">\n  \u003Ca href=\"https://fundednext.com/?fpr=noam82\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-emerald-500 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-emerald-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n    Visit FundedNext\n  \u003C/a>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2.5\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4 text-emerald-600 flex-shrink-0\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M7 7h.01M7 3h5c.512 0 1.024.195 1.414.586l7 7a2 2 0 010 2.828l-7 7a2 2 0 01-2.828 0l-7-7A1.994 1.994 0 013 12V7a4 4 0 014-4z\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm text-emerald-700 font-semibold\">120% Refund — Code:\u003C/span>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"font-mono font-bold text-xs bg-white border border-dashed border-emerald-300 px-3 py-1.5 rounded text-emerald-700 tracking-wide select-all\">PROPFIRMS\u003C/span>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Pros &#x26; Cons\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Pros\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Multiple account models (Stellar &#x26; Stellar Lite)\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Flexible scaling plan up to $4M\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>No time limits for challenges\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Higher fees for some accounts\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Limited market variety (83 instruments)\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Strict daily and overall loss limits\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"more-about-fundednext\">More About FundedNext\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>FundedNext has quickly become a recognised player in the prop trading space, earning a score of 92/100 and 5th place on our best prop firms list. Launched in 2022, it offers a high profit share, flexible trading challenges, and fast profit earning from the start of its evaluation phase.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Best Prop Firms readers can take advantage of our exclusive discount code, PROPFIRMS, to receive a 120% refund after completing the evaluation process.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"prop-challenges-and-accounts-3\">Prop Challenges and Accounts\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>FundedNext offers two core models: Stellar and Stellar Lite.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Stellar accounts\u003C/strong> include both one-step and two-step evaluations. You can earn 15% profit share during the challenge phase, with payouts just 5 business days after passing the one-step model, or monthly for the two-step.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Stellar Lite\u003C/strong> is a lower-cost, two-step model with slightly tighter risk limits. It doesn’t offer challenge-phase payouts, but unlocks 95% profit share once you’re funded.\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Cp>There are no time limits on any challenges, and you can boost flexibility with add-ons like no minimum trading days, extended drawdowns, and bi-weekly payouts.\u003C/p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003Ctable>\u003Cthead>\u003Ctr>\u003Cth>Model\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Phases\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Account Sizes\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Fees From\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Profit Target\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Max DD\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Profit Split\u003C/th>\u003C/tr>\u003C/thead>\u003Ctbody>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>Stellar 1-Step\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$6K – $200K\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$65\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>10%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>10%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Up to 95%\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>Stellar 2-Step\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>2\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$6K – $200K\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$59\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>8% / 5%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>10%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Up to 95%\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>Stellar Lite\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>2\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$5K – $100K\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$32\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>8% / 5%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>10%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Up to 95%\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003C/tbody>\u003C/table>\n\u003Cp>FundedNext publicly shares weekly payout data, with over $2.1 million paid out in the first week of April alone and an average payout time of just 8 hours and 34 minutes. This level of transparency, backed by real proof, sets FundedNext apart from less verified prop firms.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"markets-and-leverage-4\">Markets and Leverage\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>FundedNext gives you access to 83 markets: 50 forex pairs, 18 indices, 5 commodities, and 10 cryptocurrencies.\u003C/p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003Ctable>\u003Cthead>\u003Ctr>\u003Cth>Asset Class\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Instruments\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Leverage\u003C/th>\u003C/tr>\u003C/thead>\u003Ctbody>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>Forex\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>50 pairs\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Up to 1:100 (1:30 on Stellar 1-Step)\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>Indices\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>18 markets\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Up to 1:100\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>Commodities\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>5 products\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Up to 1:100\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>Crypto\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>10 pairs\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1:2\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003C/tbody>\u003C/table>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"trading-platforms-3\">Trading Platforms\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>You can trade using MT4, MT5, cTrader, or Match-Trader. MT4 and MT5 are free, but cTrader and Match-Trader have a $25 fee and are limited to smaller account sizes. MT5 also integrates with TradingView for advanced charting, though this feature is temporarily paused for updates.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>MT4 &#x26; MT5:\u003C/strong> Free, with full EA and algorithmic trading support.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>cTrader:\u003C/strong> $25 fee, limited to smaller accounts. Automated trading not available.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Match-Trader:\u003C/strong> $25 fee, limited to smaller accounts. Clean web-based interface.\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"trust-and-community-4\">Trust and Community\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>FundedNext has a \u003Cstrong>4.6/5 rating on Trustpilot\u003C/strong> and a large, active community with over 225,000 members on Discord. It also runs a busy Telegram channel and has 77K+ subscribers on YouTube with over 1,200 trading education videos.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Support is available 24/7 via live chat and email, and funded traders get direct access to in-house experts through Pro Support.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"our-verdict-on-fundednext\">Our Verdict on FundedNext\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>FundedNext offers a fast track to profitability, with an immediate 15% profit from day one and the potential to scale up to $4 million in capital. With profit splits up to 95%, a maximum funding cap of $4 million, and challenge models for every budget, it’s one of the most adaptable prop firms on the market.\u003C/p>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"most-popular-prop-firms-worldwide\">Most Popular Prop Firms Worldwide\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>Below is the full list of the best proprietary trading firms and the popularity of these prop firms based on monthly global Google searches.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>FundedNext and FTMO lead with 673,000 monthly searches each, dominating prop trader interest in 2026. FTMO’s position reflects its long-standing presence and reputation, while FundedNext’s rise is more recent, driven by flexible funding models and an expansion into futures trading.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>However, search volume doesn’t always align with firm quality. Funding Pips (450,000) and Topstep (368,000) rank high in visibility but didn’t crack our top 10 due to weaker payout terms and stricter evaluations, respectively. In contrast, newer but high-performing firms like DNA Funded and BrightFunded score in the 90s but remain under 10,000 searches, a sign that market awareness lags behind actual value.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-lg overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"bg-[#0d1b2a] px-5 py-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2.5\">\n      \u003Csvg class=\"h-5 w-5 text-teal-400 flex-shrink-0\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\n        \u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z\">\u003C/path>\n      \u003C/svg>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-black text-white uppercase tracking-wide flex-1\">Biggest Prop Firms Worldwide\u003C/p>\n      \u003Csvg class=\"h-5 w-5 text-teal-400 flex-shrink-0\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\n        \u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z\">\u003C/path>\n      \u003C/svg>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cp class=\"text-[11px] text-slate-400 mt-1\">Based on monthly global Google search volume\u003C/p>\n  \u003C/div>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center px-5 py-2 bg-teal-500 text-[10px] font-bold text-white uppercase tracking-widest\">\n    \u003Cspan class=\"w-8 flex-shrink-0\">#\u003C/span>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"flex-1\">Firm\u003C/span>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"text-right\">Searches/mo\u003C/span>\n  \u003C/div>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"divide-y divide-slate-100\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-3 px-5 py-2.5 hover:bg-teal-50/50 transition-colors\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-6 text-xs font-black text-slate-400\">1.\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/fundednext.png\" alt=\"FundedNext\" class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-md object-contain border border-slate-200 bg-white p-0.5 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-1 text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">FundedNext\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500\">673,000\u003C/span>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-3 px-5 py-2.5 hover:bg-teal-50/50 transition-colors\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-6 text-xs font-black text-slate-400\">2.\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/ftmo-logo-2-2-1-1-1.png\" alt=\"FTMO\" class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-md object-contain border border-slate-200 bg-white p-0.5 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-1 text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">FTMO\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500\">673,000\u003C/span>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-3 px-5 py-2.5 hover:bg-teal-50/50 transition-colors\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-6 text-xs font-black text-slate-400\">3.\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/funding-pips-1.png\" alt=\"Funding Pips\" class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-md object-contain border border-slate-200 bg-white p-0.5 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-1 text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Funding Pips\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500\">450,000\u003C/span>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-3 px-5 py-2.5 hover:bg-teal-50/50 transition-colors\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-6 text-xs font-black text-slate-400\">4.\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/topstep-logo-1-1-1-1-1.png\" alt=\"Topstep\" class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-md object-contain border border-slate-200 bg-white p-0.5 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-1 text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Topstep\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500\">368,000\u003C/span>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-3 px-5 py-2.5 hover:bg-teal-50/50 transition-colors\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-6 text-xs font-black text-slate-400\">5.\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/the5ers-logo-2-2-1-1-1.png\" alt=\"The 5%ers\" class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-md object-contain border border-slate-200 bg-white p-0.5 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-1 text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">The 5%ers\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500\">149,100\u003C/span>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-3 px-5 py-2.5 hover:bg-teal-50/50 transition-colors\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-6 text-xs font-black text-slate-400\">6.\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/apex-trader-funding-logo.png\" alt=\"Apex Trader Funding\" class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-md object-contain border border-slate-200 bg-white p-0.5 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-1 text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Apex Trader Funding\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500\">135,000\u003C/span>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-3 px-5 py-2.5 hover:bg-teal-50/50 transition-colors\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-6 text-xs font-black text-slate-400\">7.\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/instant-funding-logo-1.png\" alt=\"Instant Funding\" class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-md object-contain border border-slate-200 bg-white p-0.5 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-1 text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Instant Funding\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500\">90,500\u003C/span>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-3 px-5 py-2.5 hover:bg-teal-50/50 transition-colors\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-6 text-xs font-black text-slate-400\">8.\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-md bg-teal-500 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0\">\n        \u003Cspan class=\"text-[8px] font-black text-white\">EE\u003C/span>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-1 text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Equity Edge\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500\">90,500\u003C/span>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-3 px-5 py-2.5 hover:bg-teal-50/50 transition-colors\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-6 text-xs font-black text-slate-400\">9.\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/blueberry-funded-logo.png\" alt=\"Blueberry Funded\" class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-md object-contain border border-slate-200 bg-white p-0.5 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-1 text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Blueberry Funded\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500\">49,500\u003C/span>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-3 px-5 py-2.5 hover:bg-teal-50/50 transition-colors\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-6 text-xs font-black text-slate-400\">10.\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/alphacapital-1.png\" alt=\"Alpha Capital\" class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-md object-contain border border-slate-200 bg-white p-0.5 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-1 text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Alpha Capital\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500\">49,500\u003C/span>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"how-to-choose-the-best-prop-firms\">How to Choose The Best Prop Firms\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>To choose the best prop trading firm, you need to compare features that directly affect your chances of getting funded and earning payouts. Here are the key areas that matter:\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Challenges and Rules:\u003C/strong> Look for firms with realistic profit targets (under 10%), clear drawdown limits, and flexible evaluation formats.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Profit Splits and Scaling:\u003C/strong> The best firms let you keep at least 80% of profits and offer account scaling based on performance.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Fees and Spreads:\u003C/strong> Lower challenge fees and tight spreads make it easier to pass evaluations and stay profitable.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Trading Platforms:\u003C/strong> Choose a firm that supports platforms like MT4, MT5, cTrader, or TradingView, depending on your preference.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Market Access and Leverage:\u003C/strong> More asset classes and leverage options give you greater flexibility in how you trade.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Payouts:\u003C/strong> Fast and consistent withdrawals, low minimums, and clear buffer zone rules help you access profits quickly.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Support and Education:\u003C/strong> Look for responsive support and clear trading guidelines, especially if you’re new to prop trading.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Transparency and Trust:\u003C/strong> A good reputation, public reviews, and clear policies signal a firm you can rely on.\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"how-to-become-a-prop-trader\">How To Become A Prop Trader\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>To become a prop trader, you need to sign up with a proprietary trading firm, complete their evaluation process, and meet specific trading requirements. Most firms require traders to pass a challenge or evaluation phase before providing access to a funded account. Here’s a step-by-step guide on how to get started:\u003C/p>\n\u003Col>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Choose the right prop firm:\u003C/strong> Research prop trading firms based on factors such as evaluation fees, profit splits, trading platforms, and the types of financial instruments they offer (forex, equities, futures, etc.). Select the firm that aligns with your trading style and objectives. We have specific pages for:\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Ca href=\"/guides/uk\">UK Prop Traders\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Ca href=\"/guides/canada\">Canadian Prop Traders\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Ca href=\"/guides/india\">Indian Prop Traders\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Ca href=\"/guides/australia\">Australian Prop Traders\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Sign up and pay the evaluation fee:\u003C/strong> Register with the firm and pay the fee to start the evaluation process or challenge. Fees will vary depending on the account size and the specific challenge you choose.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Complete the evaluation or challenge:\u003C/strong> Follow the firm’s guidelines during the challenge. You’ll need to meet profit targets and avoid exceeding drawdown limits (maximum allowable losses). Challenges can vary in structure, with some requiring a single evaluation phase and others requiring two.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Pass the challenge to get funded:\u003C/strong> Once you successfully complete the evaluation, the firm will provide a funded account. This account allows you to trade using the firm’s capital.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Start trading and earn profits:\u003C/strong> Begin trading with the firm’s money, and share the profits based on the firm’s profit split (e.g., 80% for you, 20% for the firm). Be sure to follow their risk management rules to maintain your funded account.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Scale your account:\u003C/strong> Some firms offer scaling plans that allow you to increase your account size by consistently reaching profit targets. This can provide access to more capital over time, increasing your potential earnings.\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ol>\n\u003Cp>Following these steps can help you successfully become a prop trader, using the firm’s capital to trade and keep a portion of the profits you generate.\u003C/p>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"what-are-the-risks-of-prop-trading\">What Are The Risks Of Prop Trading?\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>Prop trading comes with several risks. One key risk is drawdown limits: prop firms impose strict daily or overall drawdown limits that, if breached, can result in disqualification. High-pressure evaluations also pose a challenge, where failing to meet profit targets can lead to the loss of entry fees without any payout. Additionally, some firms have restrictive rules, such as limiting trading styles or requiring strict risk management, which might not align with every trader’s strategy. Market volatility is another factor, as even the most skilled traders can face significant losses in unpredictable market conditions. Finally, some prop firms lack transparency, so researching their reputation and rules is crucial before signing up.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Pros &#x26; Cons of Prop Trading\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Pros\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Use firm capital, limiting personal risk\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Keep up to 90% of profits\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Only risk the initial fee\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Access larger capital through scaling\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Max trading skills with mentoring\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Strict rules on drawdowns and profit targets\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Pressure to perform within deadlines\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Lose fees if the challenge isn't passed\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Some strategies may be restricted\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Market volatility makes goals tougher\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cp>We developed a guide on our \u003Ca href=\"/risk-management\">risk management\u003C/a> page to explore this area further for those new to the industry.\u003C/p>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"faqs\">FAQs\u003C/h2>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"what-is-the-best-prop-firm\">What is the best prop firm?\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>DNA Funded is the best prop firm overall in 2026, with a top score of 97/100 in our testing. We evaluated over 28 prop firms firsthand using criteria like challenge rules, pricing, profit splits, platforms, and payout speed. In our 2026 prop firm testing, DNA Funded had the smoothest onboarding and account access, contributing to its high overall score.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>To reduce upfront fees, use DNA Funded promo code PROPFIRMS25 for 25% off.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"what-is-prop-trading\">What is prop trading?\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Proprietary trading (prop trading) allows traders to use virtual funds in financial markets like forex, shares, and commodities, after paying an initial evaluation fee. The aim is to meet specific profit targets to qualify for a funded account, where real money is provided by the prop firm. Profits are then shared between the trader and the firm, while any losses are covered by the prop company.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"how-many-prop-firms-are-forex-brokers\">How many prop firms are forex brokers?\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Many prop firms have ties to CFD brokers and use them as their providers for pricing and spreads. For example, DNA Funded is backed by Eightcap Challenges, a regulated CFD broker. However, when you’re doing the challenge, you’re in a simulated environment rather than live trading, so the prop firm itself isn’t acting as a broker. Only after you pass the challenge and get funded do you start trading in real markets, often through their broker partners.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>View our full list of \u003Ca href=\"/prop-firms\">broker backed prop firms\u003C/a>.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"why-use-a-prop-firm-rather-than-a-real-account\">Why use a prop firm rather than a real account?\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>The main advantage of using a prop firm over a real trading account is limiting personal financial risk. With a prop firm, you only risk the initial evaluation fee, while losses beyond that are covered by the firm. Once you qualify for a funded account, you receive a profit share without risking your own capital. Additionally, it’s a great way to refine your trading strategies before committing to a live forex or CFD account with your own funds.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"which-is-the-most-trusted-prop-firm\">Which is the most trusted prop firm?\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>The most trusted prop firms are DNA Funded and IC Funded, based on key factors such as reliability, user reviews, and trading conditions. DNA Funded is backed by Eightcap Challenges, ensuring low fees and an 80% profit split. IC Funded offers tight spreads, low entry costs, and strong backing from IC Markets. Each firm is known for transparency and trader support.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>It’s important to understand how these firms make money prior to opening an account.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"what-prop-firm-pays-the-fastest\">What prop firm pays the fastest?\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>The prop firms that offer the fastest payouts include DNA Funded, IC Funded, and Funded Trading Plus. DNA Funded allows traders to request profits as early as 14 days after their first trade, with flexible withdrawal options. IC Funded offers bi-weekly or on-demand withdrawals starting 14 days after the initial trade and has an outstanding crypto prop trading range. Funded Trading Plus also provides quick access to profits with instant funding and profit splits of up to 100%, making it another option for traders seeking fast payouts.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"which-prop-firm-is-better-than-ftmo\">Which prop firm is better than FTMO?\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>DNA Funded and IC Funded can be better options than FTMO, depending on what you’re looking for. DNA Funded has lower fees starting at $49, an 80% – 90% profit split, and flexible challenge options. IC Funded, on the other hand, offers super-low spreads from 0 pips, strong ties to IC Markets, and popular platforms like MT4, MT5, and cTrader. Both firms offer lower costs and better trading conditions than FTMO, especially when it comes to forex prop trading.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"what-are-the-top-prop-trading-firms-with-the-highest-profit-splits\">What are the top prop trading firms with the highest profit splits?\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Top prop trading firms with the highest profit splits include Topstep, which offers up to 100% profit split on the first $10,000 earned and 90% after that. Funded Trading Plus provides profit splits that can go up to 100%, making it a strong option for traders.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>While high profit splits are appealing, it’s crucial to also consider other factors such as challenge difficulty, fees, trading conditions, and customer support. Some firms with higher splits may have stricter rules or higher fees, so weigh the overall offering against your trading goals.\u003C/p>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"how-we-selected-the-best-prop-firms-for-2026\">How We Selected the Best Prop Firms for 2026\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>To find the best prop firms worldwide, we evaluated over 28 top prop trading firms, focusing on challenges, platform usability, payouts and targets, and cost structure. By personally testing each firm’s challenges, platforms, and trading conditions, we narrowed the list to the 10 best prop firms based on essential metrics.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Our comprehensive testing and analysis considered user experience, platform accessibility, and transparent fee structures, ensuring a balanced and realistic set of options for traders. Following our methodology allowed us to highlight firms offering the most achievable challenges and optimal profit-sharing terms, providing you with a clear, data-driven guide to selecting a prop trading firm that suits your needs.\u003C/p>",{"headings":4827,"localImagePaths":4963,"remoteImagePaths":4964,"frontmatter":4965,"imagePaths":4977},[4828,4831,4834,4837,4840,4843,4846,4849,4852,4855,4858,4861,4863,4865,4868,4870,4873,4876,4879,4881,4883,4885,4887,4890,4893,4896,4898,4900,4902,4905,4908,4911,4913,4915,4917,4919,4922,4925,4928,4931,4934,4937,4939,4942,4945,4948,4951,4954,4957,4960],{"depth":879,"slug":4829,"text":4830},"what-are-the-best-prop-firms-in-2026","What Are The Best Prop Firms In 2026?",{"depth":879,"slug":4832,"text":4833},"1-dna-funded--best-prop-firm-for-australian-traders","1. DNA Funded — Best Prop Firm For Australian Traders",{"depth":158,"slug":4835,"text":4836},"why-dna-funded-is-1-best-prop-firm","Why DNA Funded is #1 Best Prop Firm",{"depth":158,"slug":4838,"text":4839},"prop-challenges-and-accounts","Prop Challenges and Accounts",{"depth":158,"slug":4841,"text":4