4},"our-verdict-on-fxify","Our Verdict on FXIFY",{"depth":879,"slug":4906,"text":4907},"5-fundednext--good-tradingview-prop-firm","5. FundedNext — Good TradingView Prop Firm",{"depth":158,"slug":4909,"text":4910},"more-about-fundednext","More About FundedNext",{"depth":158,"slug":4912,"text":4839},"prop-challenges-and-accounts-3",{"depth":158,"slug":4914,"text":4842},"markets-and-leverage-4",{"depth":158,"slug":4916,"text":4845},"trading-platforms-3",{"depth":158,"slug":4918,"text":4848},"trust-and-community-4",{"depth":158,"slug":4920,"text":4921},"our-verdict-on-fundednext","Our Verdict on FundedNext",{"depth":879,"slug":4923,"text":4924},"most-popular-prop-firms-worldwide","Most Popular Prop Firms Worldwide",{"depth":879,"slug":4926,"text":4927},"how-to-choose-the-best-prop-firms","How to Choose The Best Prop Firms",{"depth":879,"slug":4929,"text":4930},"how-to-become-a-prop-trader","How To Become A Prop Trader",{"depth":879,"slug":4932,"text":4933},"what-are-the-risks-of-prop-trading","What Are The Risks Of Prop Trading?",{"depth":879,"slug":4935,"text":4936},"faqs","FAQs",{"depth":158,"slug":4938,"text":3445},"what-is-the-best-prop-firm",{"depth":158,"slug":4940,"text":4941},"what-is-prop-trading","What is prop trading?",{"depth":158,"slug":4943,"text":4944},"how-many-prop-firms-are-forex-brokers","How many prop firms are forex brokers?",{"depth":158,"slug":4946,"text":4947},"why-use-a-prop-firm-rather-than-a-real-account","Why use a prop firm rather than a real account?",{"depth":158,"slug":4949,"text":4950},"which-is-the-most-trusted-prop-firm","Which is the most trusted prop firm?",{"depth":158,"slug":4952,"text":4953},"what-prop-firm-pays-the-fastest","What prop firm pays the fastest?",{"depth":158,"slug":4955,"text":4956},"which-prop-firm-is-better-than-ftmo","Which prop firm is better than FTMO?",{"depth":158,"slug":4958,"text":4959},"what-are-the-top-prop-trading-firms-with-the-highest-profit-splits","What are the top prop trading firms with the highest profit splits?",{"depth":879,"slug":4961,"text":4962},"how-we-selected-the-best-prop-firms-for-2026","How We Selected the Best Prop Firms for 2026",[],[],{"title":4790,"excerpt":4791,"category":4792,"tags":4966,"author":4798,"authorImage":4799,"publishedAt":1273,"featured":110,"coverImage":4797,"readingTimeMinutes":104,"youtubeVideoId":4800,"featuredFirms":4967},[4794,4795,4796],[4968,4969,4970,4971,4972,4973,4974,4975,4976],{"slug":728,"descriptor":4803},{"slug":584,"descriptor":4805},{"slug":332,"descriptor":4807},{"slug":1599,"descriptor":4809},{"slug":1392,"descriptor":4811},{"slug":4813,"descriptor":4814},{"slug":1917,"descriptor":4816},{"slug":1550,"descriptor":4818},{"slug":1002,"descriptor":4820},[],"australia.md","canada",{"id":4979,"data":4981,"body":5007,"filePath":5008,"digest":5009,"rendered":5010,"legacyId":5166},{"title":4982,"excerpt":4983,"category":4792,"tags":4984,"coverImage":4986,"author":4798,"authorImage":4799,"publishedAt":1273,"featured":110,"readingTimeMinutes":104,"youtubeVideoId":4987,"featuredFirms":4988},"Best Prop Firms for Canadian Traders","Our list of the best prop firms in Canada offer a range of popular features like low fee challenges, high profit splits, scaling plans, instant funding, and more. To determine which prop firms are best for Canadian traders, we opened challenge accounts with each to test their trading conditions and platforms.",[4985,4795,4796],"Canada","/images/blog/Canada brokers.png","QHPnbIvv2qA",[4989,4991,4993,4995,4997,4999,5001,5003,5005],{"slug":584,"descriptor":4990},"Best Prop Firm in Canada Overall",{"slug":728,"descriptor":4992},"Broker Backed Prop Firm",{"slug":1392,"descriptor":4994},"Flexible Prop Challenges",{"slug":932,"descriptor":4996},"Broker Prop Challenge",{"slug":2563,"descriptor":4998},"Low Fee Prop Firm",{"slug":332,"descriptor":5000},"Scaling to $2 Million",{"slug":1002,"descriptor":5002},"Prop Firm for Share Trading",{"slug":1278,"descriptor":5004},"Instant Funding Accounts",{"slug":2621,"descriptor":5006},"Top Futures Prop Firm","## What Are The Best Prop Firms for Traders in Canada?\n\nThe best prop firms for Canadian traders offer affordable challenges, user-friendly platforms like MT4 or MT5, high profit splits, and reliable payout processes. Look for firms with flexible trading rules, low fees, and a solid reputation or forex broker connection.\n\nIn this guide, we rank the best prop firms available to Canadian traders in 2026, covering everything from challenge fees and profit splits to trading rules and withdrawal times.\n\n## What to Look for as a Canadian Trader\n\nBefore diving into our ranked list, here's what matters most when evaluating a prop firm from a Canadian perspective.\n\n### IIROC & CSA Regulation vs Offshore Operations\n\nMost prop firms operate offshore and are *not* regulated by the Canadian Securities Administrators (CSA) or the Canadian Investment Regulatory Organization (CIRO, formerly IIROC). This is legal — they are not offering financial products to retail clients, they are running evaluation challenges. However, regulation in other jurisdictions (such as ASIC in Australia or CySEC in Cyprus) does provide a meaningful layer of legitimacy and trader protection that you should look for.\n\n### Payout Track Record\n\nA firm's payout history is the most important trust signal. Look for firms with Trustpilot scores above 4.0, a large community of verified paid-out traders, and transparent terms around withdrawals. Firms that have been operating for 3+ years with consistent payouts are significantly lower risk than newer entrants.\n\n### CAD Account Support\n\nSome firms offer CAD-denominated accounts or CAD payout methods, which saves Canadian traders on currency conversion fees. Most firms pay in USD via crypto or bank wire, so factor in FX costs when comparing effective profit splits.\n\n### Platform Availability\n\nMT4, MT5, and TradeLocker are the most common platforms. cTrader has historically been popular with Canadian traders due to its clean execution model. Avoid firms that only support obscure or proprietary platforms with limited community track records.\n\n---\n\n## 1. BrightFunded — Best Prop Firm in Canada Overall\n\nCanadian traders can access a funded account with BrightFunded after completing a two-step evaluation process. Account sizes range from $5,000 to $200,000, and profit splits start at 80% but scale all the way up to 100%. Experienced traders can use cTrader or MT5, and beginners DXtrade, with forex spreads on both platforms going as low as 0 pips. With its unique scaling and rewards program, and all the tools you need regardless of experience level, BrightFunded is a great all-rounder prop firm.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/brightfunded-logo.png\" alt=\"BrightFunded logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\" />\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">BrightFunded\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">Best Prop Firm in Canada Overall\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">100%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Max DD\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">10%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Trustpilot\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">4.6 \u003Cspan class=\"text-amber-500\">★\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Ca href=\"/reviews/brightfunded\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-lg bg-teal-500 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-white hover:bg-teal-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n        Full Review →\n      \u003C/a>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose -mt-3 mb-6 rounded-xl border border-emerald-200 bg-emerald-50/80 px-5 py-3 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-3\">\n  \u003Ca href=\"https://brightfunded.com?affiliateId=rsBbtrzYQSyr3RcHYHQT5w\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-emerald-500 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-emerald-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14\" />\u003C/svg>\n    Visit BrightFunded\n  \u003C/a>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2.5\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4 text-emerald-600 flex-shrink-0\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M7 7h.01M7 3h5c.512 0 1.024.195 1.414.586l7 7a2 2 0 010 2.828l-7 7a2 2 0 01-2.828 0l-7-7A1.994 1.994 0 013 12V7a4 4 0 014-4z\" />\u003C/svg>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm text-emerald-700 font-semibold\">20% Off — Code:\u003C/span>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"font-mono font-bold text-xs bg-white border border-dashed border-emerald-300 px-3 py-1.5 rounded text-emerald-700 tracking-wide select-all\">PROPFIRMS20\u003C/span>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Pros & Cons\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Pros\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Profit shares up to 100%\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Unique Trade2Earn loyalty program\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Customisable challenge add-ons\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>36 crypto markets with 1:5 leverage\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Fast payouts via crypto and bank transfer\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Higher fees when using add-ons\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Strict trading rules on funded accounts\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Only crypto withdrawals or bank transfer\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Limited educational resources\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>No MT4 support\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n### Challenges and Fees\n\nBrightFunded offers a simple two-step evaluation process with clear profit targets and risk management requirements, keeping things nice and simple.\n\n**Step 1 (Evaluation Phase):** To pass the first step you need to reach an 8% profit target, while staying within a 5% daily drawdown limit plus a 10% maximum drawdown cap. You must trade for a minimum of five days before moving to the second step.\n\n**Step 2 (Verification Phase):** After passing the first step, you then need to trade for another five days at least, but your profit target is lower at 5%, with the daily and max drawdown staying the same as step one.\n\nOnce you pass the two evaluation stages, you will receive your funded demo account. Over time you can scale your profit share up to 100% by hitting certain milestones, and earn tokens when you trade via the Trade2Earn program.\n\n| Account Size | Challenge Fee | Phase 1 Target | Phase 2 Target | Max Daily Loss | Max Total Drawdown |\n|-------------|--------------|----------------|----------------|---------------|-------------------|\n| $5,000 | €55 | $400 | $250 | $250 | $500 |\n| $10,000 | €95 | $800 | $500 | $500 | $1,000 |\n| $25,000 | €195 | $2,000 | $1,250 | $1,250 | $2,500 |\n| $50,000 | €295 | $4,000 | $2,500 | $2,500 | $5,000 |\n| $100,000 | €495 | $8,000 | $5,000 | $5,000 | $10,000 |\n| $200,000 | €975 | $16,000 | $10,000 | $10,000 | $20,000 |\n\nBrightFunded offers several paid add-ons. These are optional, but allow you to personalise your challenge and funded account:\n\n- **Weekly Payouts:** Reduce your profit payout intervals to 7 days for a 25% fee.\n- **Higher Profit Splits:** Immediately increase your profit share to 90% for a 20% fee.\n- **No Minimum Trading Days:** Scrap the 5-day minimum trading day requirement for a 15% fee.\n- **Swap-Free Accounts:** Access swap-free trading for a 10% fee (made for Islamic prop traders).\n\n### Spreads and Trading Costs\n\nBrightFunded is not aligned with a broker — the prop firm aggregates market data from top-tier liquidity providers to simulate realistic trading conditions. During testing our team found forex spreads can be as low as 0 pips, and for popular currency pairs like EUR/USD, AUD/USD, or GBP/USD, average spreads are 0.1 pips, which is in line with or lower than most broker-backed prop firms.\n\nSimilar to CFD brokers, you pay a $3 commission per lot when trading forex, while crypto trading costs 0.024% of the trading volume. Commission for commodities is 0.0010% of trading volume, and indices are commission-free.\n\n### Funded Accounts and Payouts\n\nAfter successfully completing the evaluation, you can start trading with your funded account where you receive a profit share and can scale up.\n\n- **Profit Splits:** Start at 80%, scaling to 100% as you meet performance milestones.\n- **Scaling Plan:** Account balances increase by 30% every four months if you consistently trade (you must be profitable in at least 2 out of 4 months with at least 2 profit payouts).\n- **Payout Process:** Bi-weekly payouts are standard, but you can get weekly payouts with the add-on. Payouts are processed via crypto wallets (e.g., USDC ERC-20) or bank transfers, with no minimum withdrawal amount.\n\n### Trading Platforms and Markets\n\nMarket and platform access is solid with BrightFunded, and you can choose from MetaTrader 5 (MT5), cTrader, or DXtrade:\n\n**MT5** has just been introduced, giving you advanced charting, fast execution, and full support for automated trading with Expert Advisors.\n\n**cTrader** is designed for experienced manual and algorithmic traders. You get advanced features like Level II pricing, fast execution, and support for C#-based automated strategies. It's best if you prefer more control or plan to build your own EAs.\n\n**DXtrade** is a more flexible platform ideal for beginners, along with discretionary and hybrid traders. It includes built-in risk management tools, custom layouts, and multi-chart views, with a user-friendly interface that keeps things simple.\n\nChallenges and funded accounts are a simulated trading environment on all platforms, meaning you are trading via a demo account but with real market data.\n\n- **Forex:** 49 currency pairs, including majors like EUR/USD and exotics like USD/ZAR, with leverage up to 1:100.\n- **Commodities:** Includes gold, silver, crude oil, and natural gas with leverage up to 1:40.\n- **Indices:** Global indices like S&P 500, FTSE 100, and DAX 30 with leverage up to 1:20.\n- **Cryptocurrencies:** 36 cryptos including Bitcoin and Ethereum, max leverage 1:5 (most prop firms offer 1:2, so a good option for crypto traders).\n\n### Trust and Support\n\nBrightFunded has built a strong reputation in the prop trading industry, known for transparent policies and active community engagement.\n\n- **Trustpilot Score:** 4.6 out of 5 stars, with many positive reviews about its fast payouts and solid customer support.\n- **Community:** Over 16,000 members in its Discord server with active channels for strategy sharing, trader support, and educational resources.\n- **Support Availability:** 24/7 customer service via email, live chat, and WhatsApp. Our team found it helpful and responsive, with genuine responses to our questions around spreads etc.\n\n### Final Verdict\n\nOur team found BrightFunded to be the best prop firm in Canada because of its overall trading experience. From evaluation to funded trader status, the rules and requirements were clear, with opportunities along the way to scale up and earn real rewards for trading. While some prop firms make it hard at every step, BrightFunded offers a solid and genuine prop trading experience where you feel supported and given the tools to pass challenges.\n\n---\n\n## 2. DNA Funded — Broker Backed Prop Firm\n\nBacked by DNA Markets, an ASIC-regulated forex broker, DNA Funded gives you some of the most reliable trading conditions and lowest pricing. There are three challenge types including a rapid option, one-step, or two-step evaluation.\n\nDuring testing DNA Funded also ranked as the second best crypto prop firm, second best prop firm for stock trading, and fourth best for forex, thanks to its range of markets — showing it's a great option for anyone wanting to focus on multiple asset classes.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/dna-funded-logo.png\" alt=\"DNA Funded logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\" />\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">DNA Funded\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">Broker Backed Prop Firm\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">90%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Max DD\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">10%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Trustpilot\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">3.9 \u003Cspan class=\"text-amber-500\">★\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Ca href=\"/reviews/dna-funded\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-lg bg-teal-500 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-white hover:bg-teal-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n        Full Review →\n      \u003C/a>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose -mt-3 mb-6 rounded-xl border border-emerald-200 bg-emerald-50/80 px-5 py-3 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-3\">\n  \u003Ca href=\"https://partners.dnafunded.com/click?campaign_id=1&ref_id=30\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-emerald-500 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-emerald-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14\" />\u003C/svg>\n    Visit DNA Funded\n  \u003C/a>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2.5\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4 text-emerald-600 flex-shrink-0\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M7 7h.01M7 3h5c.512 0 1.024.195 1.414.586l7 7a2 2 0 010 2.828l-7 7a2 2 0 01-2.828 0l-7-7A1.994 1.994 0 013 12V7a4 4 0 014-4z\" />\u003C/svg>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm text-emerald-700 font-semibold\">25% Off — Code:\u003C/span>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"font-mono font-bold text-xs bg-white border border-dashed border-emerald-300 px-3 py-1.5 rounded text-emerald-700 tracking-wide select-all\">BESTPROPFIRMS\u003C/span>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Pros & Cons\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Pros\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Profit splits up to 90%\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Low fees starting at $49\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Access to over 800 financial markets\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Add-ons for higher profit splits and faster payouts\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>No cryptocurrency trading in Rapid Challenge\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Scaling plans not yet available\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Extra fees for features like faster payouts\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Lack of 24/7 customer support\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n### Challenges and Fees\n\nYou get a great range of challenges with DNA Funded — not too many to confuse you but enough to cover everything from a quick challenge to a two-step evaluation.\n\n- **Single Helix Challenge:** A one-step evaluation with unlimited trading days, making it ideal if you are swing trading or a position trader.\n- **Double Helix Challenge:** A two-step evaluation suited to disciplined traders who aren't in a rush, as there's again no max trading days.\n- **Rapid Challenge:** For the more experienced traders, well-suited to high-frequency traders and scalpers. You have a max of 10 days to complete the challenge and crypto trading is not available for this specific challenge.\n\nAll challenges have a minimum of three trading days, but each has different add-ons available. The one-step allows you to reduce the payout period to a week, the two-step lets you increase your profit split to 90%, while the Rapid challenge lets you do both.\n\n| Challenge | Early Payout (14 → 7 Days) | Profit Split (80% → 90%) | Add-on Fee Increase |\n|-----------|---------------------------|-------------------------|-------------------|\n| Single Helix (1-Step) | ✅ | ❌ | 20% |\n| Double Helix (2-Step) | ❌ | ✅ | 20% |\n| Rapid Challenge | ✅ | ✅ | 30% |\n\n### Spreads and Trading Costs\n\nThanks to being broker-backed by DNA Markets, the prop firm's spreads and commission fees are some of the most competitive in the industry.\n\n- **Spreads:** Starting from 0 pips for major forex pairs like EUR/USD.\n- **Commission Fees:** A low $5 per trade round-turn (i.e. $2.50 per side).\n\n### Profit Payouts\n\nOnce you pass the evaluation process, you can access your funded account. Unless you buy the add-on for weekly payouts, you will be able to withdraw profits every 14 days, with a minimum withdrawal of $200. Payment methods are standard with bank transfers and cryptocurrency.\n\nIt is important to point out that when we tested DNA Funded's challenges, we found there is a 40% daily profit cap applied across all challenges that could be easy to miss when signing up. This means you can only contribute up to 40% of your total payout target from profits made in a single day. As it's associated with a regulated broker, they have slightly stricter compliance requirements.\n\nRefunds of challenge fees are issued after the first profit payout, which means if you pass there's zero capital outlay.\n\n### Trading Platforms and Markets\n\nDNA Funded supports **TradeLocker** with a TradingView integration, so while a little restricted on platform choice, you get all the charting and analysis tools you need. One major restriction that will take DNA Funded off the list for some is that automated trading is not currently supported — this means no EAs.\n\nBut they make up for it with one of the best ranges of trading instruments available worldwide. You can develop strategies with over 800 trading instruments, including forex, indices, commodities, stocks, and cryptocurrencies.\n\nLeverage depends on challenge type:\n\n| Max Leverage | Forex | Commodities | Indices | Stocks | Crypto |\n|-------------|-------|-------------|---------|--------|--------|\n| Single Helix | 1:30 | 1:10 | 1:10 | 1:5 | 1:2 |\n| Double Helix | 1:50 | 1:10 | 1:10 | 1:5 | 1:2 |\n| Rapid Challenge | 1:30 | 1:10 | 1:10 | 1:5 | 1:2 |\n\n### Trust and Support\n\nDNA Funded gains a lot of credibility through partnering with DNA Markets, a well-regulated forex broker and the prop firm's liquidity provider.\n\nThey are limited in terms of educational resources at this stage, but are building their Discord server with channels for trader discussions and education. Customer support is currently limited to email, with plans to expand to live chat and other channels.\n\n### Final Verdict\n\nDNA Funded is one of the strongest all-round prop firms if you want access to more than just forex. Backed by DNA Markets, you get tight spreads, low commissions, and reliable trading conditions from a regulated broker. The three challenge types cover different trading styles, whether you want a fast evaluation, a single step, or a full two-step process.\n\n---\n\n## 3. FundedNext — Flexible Prop Challenges\n\nFundedNext lets you work towards a funded account via a one or two-step challenge, with account sizes from $5,000 to $200,000. Profit splits start at 80% and scale up to 95%, and you even receive a 15% profit split during the challenge phase, which is nearly unheard of. We tested the prop firm's Stellar Two Step challenge on MT5, and it took around two months to pass both phases and receive a funded account. It's one of the best all-rounder prop firms we've traded with, earning it 4th place on our shortlist for Canadian traders.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/fundednext.png\" alt=\"FundedNext logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\" />\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">FundedNext\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">Flexible Prop Challenges\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">95%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Max DD\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">10%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Trustpilot\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">4.6 \u003Cspan class=\"text-amber-500\">★\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Ca href=\"/reviews/fundednext\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-lg bg-teal-500 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-white hover:bg-teal-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n        Full Review →\n      \u003C/a>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose -mt-3 mb-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 px-5 py-3 flex items-center justify-center\">\n  \u003Ca href=\"https://fundednext.com/?fpr=noam82\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-emerald-500 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-emerald-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14\" />\u003C/svg>\n    Visit FundedNext\n  \u003C/a>\n\u003C/div>\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Pros & Cons\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Pros\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Profit splits up to 95%\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Flexible challenge models (1-step, 2-step, Lite)\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Competitive spreads from 0 pips\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Strict daily loss limits (3–5%)\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>No stock market access\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Minimum trading days required\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n### Challenges and Fees\n\nFundedNext has recently trimmed down its challenge options, which we believe is a good move. They've streamlined things into three challenge types, with a one-step or two-step evaluation.\n\n- **Stellar One Step:** A single-phase evaluation with a 10% profit target, 3% daily loss limit, and 6% overall drawdown. Includes a 15% profit share during the challenge and payouts just 5 days after passing. Fees range from $65 to $1,099.\n- **Stellar Two Step:** A two-phase challenge with 8% and 5% profit targets. Drawdown limits increase to 5% daily and 10% overall. Like the 1-Step, this model includes a 15% profit share during the challenge. Fees range from $59 to $999.\n- **Stellar Lite:** A lower-cost two-phase challenge with profit targets of 8% and 4%, and drawdowns set at 4% daily and 8% overall. No profit share during the challenge phase, but bi-weekly payouts after funding. Fees start at just $32.\n\nYou can also add optional upgrades:\n\n- No minimum trading days for a 20% fee\n- 10% overall drawdown for a 25% fee\n- Bi-weekly payouts for a 15% fee\n- Lifetime 95% payout for a 30% fee\n\n### Spreads and Trading Costs\n\nWhen we tested FundedNext, we found spreads for major forex pairs like EUR/USD could range anywhere from 0 pips to 1 pip. Commission fees depend on your account type — for Stellar One or Two Step challenges it's $5 per lot on forex and commodities, while for Stellar Lite accounts it's $7 per lot for both asset classes.\n\n### Funded Accounts and Payouts\n\nFundedNext offers one of the fastest payout schedules in the industry, with profit splits up to 95% for funded traders, and 15% while you are taking Stellar challenges.\n\n| Feature | Stellar 1-Step | Stellar 2-Step | Stellar Lite |\n|---------|----------------|----------------|--------------|\n| First Payout | 5 business days | 30 days | 21 days |\n| Subsequent Payouts | 5 business days | Bi-weekly | Bi-weekly |\n| Challenge Profit Share | 15% | 15% | N/A |\n| Funded Profit Split | Up to 95% | Up to 95% | Up to 95% |\n| Minimum Withdrawal | $20 | $20 | $20 |\n\n**Scaling Plan:** Grow your account by 40% every four months (up to $4 million) if you hit a 10% return and receive two payouts during that period.\n\n### Trading Platforms and Markets\n\nYou can choose from four popular trading platforms, so there should be something for everyone:\n\n- **MetaTrader 4 (MT4):** Ideal for forex trading and EAs.\n- **MetaTrader 5 (MT5):** Multi-asset trading with TradingView integration.\n- **cTrader:** Manual trading with Level II market depth (not available on 100K+ accounts).\n- **Match-Trader:** Web-based, mobile-friendly option with fast setup.\n\nWhen we tested FundedNext, we used MT5 and had a good experience. One thing we did notice was we had to constantly refresh the dashboard for updated stats, otherwise there was a significant lag which could get you in trouble.\n\nWe focused on forex trading USD/JPY during our challenge, but you can also trade:\n\n- **Forex:** 50 pairs, including majors, minors, and exotics.\n- **Indices:** 18 global indices.\n- **Commodities:** 5 key assets like gold and crude oil.\n- **Cryptocurrencies:** 10 coins, including BTC and ETH.\n- **Leverage:** Up to 100:1 for forex, 50:1 for indices, and 2:1 for crypto.\n\n### Trust and Support\n\nFundedNext has a strong Trustpilot rating and online community, including hundreds of thousands of Discord members.\n\n- **Trustpilot Score:** 4.6 out of 5 stars, with plenty of positive reviews around support and pricing.\n- **Customer Support:** 24/7 live chat and email assistance — we found our questions were always answered quickly.\n- **Educational Resources:** Trading guides, psychology sessions, and a YouTube channel with a decent range of training videos.\n\n### Final Verdict\n\nFundedNext is ideal if you want a payout during the challenge period, fast payments, and up to 95% profit splits as a funded trader. When testing this prop firm, it took about two months to complete the Stellar Two Step challenge, and we found pricing to be competitive and support to be helpful along the way.\n\n---\n\n## 4. Eightcap Challenges — Broker Prop Challenge\n\nEightcap Challenges is fully available to traders in Canada and operates differently from every other firm on this list. Instead of outsourcing liquidity or running a proprietary feed, it uses the same pricing it provides to its CFD brokerage clients. That results in extremely tight spreads, clean fills during active sessions, and stable chart behaviour — big positives for intraday traders.\n\nAccount sizes go from $10K to $200K for the One Step and Two Step challenges. The Day Trader challenge uses a fixed $10K balance and pays instantly based on the multiplier you choose.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/eightcap-logo-1.png\" alt=\"Eightcap Challenges logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\" />\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">Eightcap Challenges\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">Broker Prop Challenge\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">80%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Max DD\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">10%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Trustpilot\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">4.2 \u003Cspan class=\"text-amber-500\">★\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Ca href=\"/reviews/eightcap\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-lg bg-teal-500 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-white hover:bg-teal-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n        Full Review →\n      \u003C/a>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose -mt-3 mb-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 px-5 py-3 flex items-center justify-center\">\n  \u003Ca href=\"https://challenges.eightcap.com?campaign_id=1&ref_id=622\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-emerald-500 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-emerald-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14\" />\u003C/svg>\n    Visit Eightcap Challenges\n  \u003C/a>\n\u003C/div>\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Pros & Cons\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Pros\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Raw spreads with real broker pricing\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Full automation support on MT4/MT5\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Short-session Day Trader challenges\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>No traditional scaling plan\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Higher fees for large accounts\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>US stocks only in Day Trader challenge\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n### Challenges and Fees\n\nEightcap Challenges offers three challenge models, each suited to different trading styles:\n\n- **One Step Challenge:** Best for traders who want a simple, single-phase evaluation. Trade until you hit the target or breach the limits. Minimum trading days apply, but the structure is straightforward.\n- **Two Step Challenge:** A smoother progression with the target split into two phases. Drawdown limits are wider, so the evaluation feels more forgiving if you manage risk well.\n- **Day Trader Challenge:** A unique 1-to-8-hour timed session where you choose a stake and multiplier. Designed for traders who prefer fast results and short-term precision rather than multi-day planning. Fully manual on TradeLocker.\n\n| Feature | One Step | Two Step | Day Trader (1–8 Hour) |\n|---------|----------|----------|----------------------|\n| Account Size | $10K – $200K | $10K – $200K | Fixed $10K simulated |\n| Fee Range | $119 – $1,299 | $99 – $1,199 | $5 – $250 |\n| Profit Target | 10% | 10% / 8% | Varies by stake & multiplier |\n| Max Daily Loss | 4% | 5% | Fixed dollar drawdown |\n| Max Total Loss | 8% | 10% | Fixed dollar limit |\n| Min Trading Days | 5 | 3 per step | N/A |\n| Profit Split | 80% | 80% | Instant payout (2x, 5x or 10x) |\n\n### Spreads and Trading Costs\n\nBecause Eightcap Challenges uses its own live raw-spread feed, pricing is tighter than most prop firms operating in Canada.\n\nForex spreads can be 0.0 pips on major pairs, with a flat commission of $5 per round turn across forex, indices, and commodities. Crypto has no commission at all.\n\nUS stocks only appear in the Day Trader challenge and use a $4 round-turn fee.\n\nPricing stays consistent across MT4, MT5, and TradeLocker, and our testing found no spread widening or artificial execution quirks common with some prop firms.\n\n### Funded Accounts and Payouts\n\nFor the One Step and Two Step challenges, your first payout becomes available after 14 days, with a $100 minimum withdrawal. Crypto withdrawals can be made from $10.\n\nProfit splits start at 80%, and you can upgrade to 90% with a paid add-on. The Two Step challenge has no payout cap, while the One Step includes a capped first three payouts.\n\nDay Trader payouts work differently — you're paid instantly based on your chosen stake and multiplier, and no profit split is used.\n\n### Trading Platforms and Markets\n\nEightcap Challenges supports MT4, MT5, and TradeLocker, giving Canadian traders more platform choice than most firms on this list.\n\n- **MT4 and MT5:** Available for the One Step and Two Step challenges. Full Expert Advisor support, custom indicators, algo trading, and scripts are all allowed.\n- **TradeLocker:** Required for the Day Trader challenge. Fully manual with clean charting and fast order execution.\n\nMarkets include forex, indices, commodities, crypto, and ETFs on all challenges. US stocks are exclusive to the Day Trader model.\n\nLeverage is highest on the standard challenges, while the Day Trader challenge uses reduced leverage to keep the short-session format controlled.\n\n### Trust and Support\n\nEightcap Challenges is a long-standing global broker regulated by ASIC and the FCA, and its challenge program benefits from the same infrastructure and support team. During testing, live chat replies were quick and handled by real agents.\n\nUnlike many prop firms, the trading environment is transparent and predictable because it's built directly on a real broker's framework rather than outsourced feeds or private liquidity pools.\n\n### Final Verdict\n\nEightcap Challenges is one of the strongest prop options for Canadian forex traders who value consistent pricing, MT4/MT5 automation, and regulated-broker stability. The fees are higher and there's no traditional scaling plan, but the execution quality and platform environment are noticeably better than most independent firms.\n\nIt's best suited to traders who want a funded-account experience that behaves like a real brokerage account, not a proprietary simulation.\n\n---\n\n## 5. Think Capital -- Low Fee Prop Firm\n\nThink Capital is a broker-backed prop firm that offers some of the lowest challenge fees in the industry, starting from just $39 for a $5,000 Nexus account. Canadian traders get a choice of three evaluation types, account sizes up to $200,000, and profit splits up to 90%. With MT5 and ThinkTrader (which includes TradingView integration) both available, Think Capital gives you solid platform flexibility at a price point that undercuts most competitors.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/thinkcapital-icon.png\" alt=\"Think Capital logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\" />\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">Think Capital\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">Low Fee Prop Firm\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">90%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Max DD\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">6%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Trustpilot\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">4.3 \u003Cspan class=\"text-amber-500\">★\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Ca href=\"/reviews/think-capital\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-lg bg-teal-500 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-white hover:bg-teal-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n        Full Review →\n      \u003C/a>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose -mt-3 mb-6 rounded-xl border border-emerald-200 bg-emerald-50/80 px-5 py-3 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-3\">\n  \u003Ca href=\"https://www.thinkcapital.com/?sp_rid=677d98c8fcd21d60b8730003\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-emerald-500 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-emerald-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14\" />\u003C/svg>\n    Visit Think Capital\n  \u003C/a>\n\u003C/div>\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Pros & Cons\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Pros\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Broker-backed prop firm\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Fees starting from just $39\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Three challenge types to suit different styles\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>TradingView integration via ThinkTrader\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Scaling plan up to $1.5M\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Crypto is the only payout method\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Smaller trading community\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>EA support requires paid add-on\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>No MT4 support\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n### Challenges and Fees\n\nThink Capital offers three challenge types, each designed for different experience levels and trading styles.\n\n**Lightning (1-Step):** The fastest path to funding with a single 10% profit target, a 3% daily loss limit, and a 6% max drawdown. Leverage is capped at 1:30, making it suited to disciplined traders who prefer tighter risk management. No minimum trading days required.\n\n**Dual Step (2-Step):** A two-phase evaluation with an 8% profit target in Phase 1 and 5% in Phase 2. You get 1:100 leverage with a 5% daily loss limit and 10% max drawdown, which gives you more room to trade than the Lightning challenge. No minimum trading days required.\n\n**Nexus (3-Step):** The most affordable option starting at just $39 for a $5,000 account. It requires 18% total profit across three phases at 1:100 leverage. This challenge has the lowest fees but the highest total target.\n\n| Account Size | Nexus Fee | Lightning Fee | Dual Step Fee |\n|-------------|-----------|---------------|---------------|\n| $5,000 | $39 | $59 | $59 |\n| $10,000 | $79 | $99 | $99 |\n| $25,000 | $139 | $199 | $199 |\n| $50,000 | $199 | $299 | $299 |\n| $100,000 | $349 | $499 | $499 |\n| $200,000 | $649 | $949 | $949 |\n\nOptional paid add-ons are available to customise your challenge:\n\n- **90% Profit Split:** Increase your split from the default to 90% for a 25% fee.\n- **News Trading:** Unlock news trading on funded accounts for a 25% fee.\n- **Expert Advisors:** Enable EA trading on MT5 for a 25% fee.\n- **Weekly Payouts:** Reduce payout intervals from bi-weekly to weekly for a 25% fee.\n- **Reduced Targets:** Lower your profit targets by 10% for a 10% fee.\n\n### Spreads and Trading Costs\n\nThink Capital does not publish average spreads, but during testing ThinkTrader EUR/USD spreads started around 0.8 pips, widening to 2.5+ pips on minor pairs. MT5 offers tighter raw spreads with a $4 per lot per side commission ($8 round-trip) on forex and precious metals. ThinkTrader charges no commission on any asset class, using wider spreads instead.\n\nMT5 commissions are slightly above the $3 to $3.50 per side industry average, but the option to choose between raw spreads on MT5 or commission-free trading on ThinkTrader gives Canadian traders flexibility depending on their strategy.\n\n### Funded Accounts and Payouts\n\nOnce you pass your chosen challenge, you receive a funded account and can start earning from your trades.\n\n- **Profit Splits:** Up to 90% with the paid add-on, or the default rate without it.\n- **Scaling Plan:** Account balances increase by 20% every 3 months for traders who achieve 10% total profit, scaling up to a maximum of $1.5 million.\n- **Payout Schedule:** Bi-weekly by default (every 14 days from your first trade), with a weekly option available as an add-on.\n- **Processing Time:** Payouts are processed within 3 business days, with crypto withdrawals typically arriving within 24 to 48 hours.\n- **Payout Methods:** Cryptocurrency only at this time, though bank transfers are expected in the future.\n\n### Trading Platforms and Markets\n\nThink Capital supports two platforms for Canadian traders:\n\n**MT5** provides advanced charting, multi-asset capabilities, and full EA support (with the add-on). It offers raw spreads and is the better choice for algorithmic or experienced manual traders. Note that US-based traders cannot access MT5 due to regulatory restrictions, but this does not affect Canadian traders.\n\n**ThinkTrader** integrates TradingView charting tools directly into the platform, making it a strong option for traders who want professional-grade analysis tools in a user-friendly interface. It works on desktop, web, and mobile.\n\nMarkets available across both platforms include:\n\n- **Forex:** Major, minor, and exotic currency pairs with leverage up to 1:100 on Dual Step and Nexus challenges (1:30 on Lightning).\n- **Indices:** Global indices with leverage up to 1:15.\n- **Commodities:** Gold, silver, and oil with leverage up to 1:30.\n- **Cryptocurrencies:** Including Bitcoin and Ethereum with leverage up to 1:2.\n\n### Trust and Support\n\nThink Capital has a Trustpilot rating of 4.3 out of 5 from over 500 reviews, with the majority of users giving five stars. Positive reviews commonly mention transparent rules, fast payouts, and responsive customer support. The firm actively responds to critical feedback within 24 hours.\n\n- **Community:** Over 11,700 members on Discord with channels for trading ideas, psychology, and general support.\n- **Support Channels:** Live chat for instant help, plus email and a contact form for non-urgent queries.\n- **Educational Content:** Over 100 YouTube videos covering risk management, platform tutorials, and interviews with funded traders.\n\n### Final Verdict\n\nThink Capital stands out for Canadian traders looking for the most affordable entry point into prop trading. The Nexus challenge at $39 is one of the cheapest challenge fees available from any reputable firm, and the broker-backed infrastructure means your trading conditions are built on real market data rather than a proprietary simulation. The main drawback is that payouts are crypto-only for now, which may not suit every Canadian trader. If you want low fees, flexible challenge options, and solid platform choice, Think Capital is a strong pick.\n\n---\n\n## How We Picked the Best Prop Trading Firms In 2026\n\nOur methodology at Best Prop Firms is designed to identify the best prop trading firms for Canadian traders based on detailed criteria that reflect the needs of both new and experienced traders. By focusing on transparency, accessibility, and value, we ensure our rankings are useful for traders seeking funded account opportunities.\n\n### Evaluation Categories\n\nWe assess prop firms across multiple key areas, each weighted based on its impact on trading success:\n\n- **Challenges and Fees:** Evaluation of the types of challenges, profit targets, and drawdown limits. Firms offering low fees, flexible challenges, and achievable targets rank higher.\n- **Spreads and Trading Costs:** Transparent, competitive spreads and commission fees are prioritised. Firms with lower trading costs score better.\n- **Trading Platforms and Markets:** The availability of advanced trading platforms like MT5 and cTrader, along with access to diverse markets, is a crucial factor.\n- **Profit Payouts and Scaling Plans:** We look for firms offering frequent payouts, high profit splits, and scalable account growth opportunities.\n- **Trust and Support:** Ratings on Trustpilot, community engagement (e.g., Discord), and the availability of customer support influence this category.\n\n### Testing Process\n\nOur research team conducts hands-on testing of each firm's features, including:\n\n- **Platform Usability:** Real-world trading scenarios are simulated to evaluate platform performance and ease of use.\n- **Challenge Process:** Evaluation challenges are tested for fairness, accessibility, and alignment with traders' goals.\n- **Payout Reliability:** Firms are assessed for the speed and transparency of their payout processes.\n\n### Scoring System\n\nEach firm receives an overall score based on its performance in these categories. Firms with higher scores reflect consistent excellence across trading conditions, platform features, and trader support.\n\nBy combining rigorous testing and in-depth analysis, we provide a clear and comprehensive guide to help Canadian traders choose the best prop trading firms. Our commitment to transparency ensures our recommendations are unbiased and rooted in trader success.\n\n---\n\n## Pros and Cons of Prop Trading\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Pros\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Access to firm capital reduces personal risk\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>High profit shares, often up to 90%\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Options to scale accounts over time\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Promotes disciplined trading habits\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Strict drawdown and loss limits\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Requires consistent performance\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Time-limited evaluations can be stressful\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Restrictions on certain strategies\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n---\n\n## Most Popular Prop Firms In Canada\n\nFTMO and Topstep are the most popular prop trading firms in Canada, each attracting 12,100 monthly Google searches. FTMO's broad appeal comes from its long-standing presence and access to forex, indices, and stocks, while Topstep's consistent interest reflects its focus on futures trading and flexible evaluation structure.\n\nFundedNext ranks third with 4,400 searches, showing growing visibility thanks to its flexible challenges and high profit splits. Other firms like Funded Trading Plus (FTP), ThinkCapital, and Blueberry Funded follow with moderate but rising interest, signaling a shift toward firms offering instant funding, low fees, or scalable accounts.\n\nSearch volume is a useful indicator of trader attention — but doesn't always reflect evaluation difficulty or payout quality. Always compare visibility with actual trading conditions.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-lg overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"bg-[#0d1b2a] px-5 py-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2.5\">\n      \u003Csvg class=\"h-5 w-5 text-teal-400 flex-shrink-0\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\n        \u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z\" />\n      \u003C/svg>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-black text-white uppercase tracking-wide flex-1\">Most Searched Canadian Prop Firms\u003C/p>\n      \u003Csvg class=\"h-5 w-[26px] flex-shrink-0 rounded-[3px]\" viewBox=\"0 0 200 100\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n        \u003Crect width=\"50\" height=\"100\" fill=\"#FF0000\"/>\n        \u003Crect x=\"50\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" fill=\"#FFFFFF\"/>\n        \u003Crect x=\"150\" width=\"50\" height=\"100\" fill=\"#FF0000\"/>\n        \u003Cpath d=\"M100 20 L105 35 L120 35 L108 44 L112 58 L100 50 L88 58 L92 44 L80 35 L95 35 Z\" fill=\"#FF0000\"/>\n      \u003C/svg>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cp class=\"text-[11px] text-slate-400 mt-1\">Based on monthly Google search volume in Canada\u003C/p>\n  \u003C/div>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center px-5 py-2 bg-teal-500 text-[10px] font-bold text-white uppercase tracking-widest\">\n    \u003Cspan class=\"w-8 flex-shrink-0\">#\u003C/span>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"flex-1\">Firm\u003C/span>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"text-right\">Searches/mo\u003C/span>\n  \u003C/div>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"divide-y divide-slate-100\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-3 px-5 py-2.5 hover:bg-teal-50/50 transition-colors\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-6 text-xs font-black text-slate-400\">1.\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/ftmo-logo-2-2-1-1-1.png\" alt=\"FTMO\" class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-md object-contain border border-slate-200 bg-white p-0.5 flex-shrink-0\" />\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-1 text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">FTMO\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500\">12,100\u003C/span>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-3 px-5 py-2.5 hover:bg-teal-50/50 transition-colors\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-6 text-xs font-black text-slate-400\">2.\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/topstep-logo-1-1-1-1-1.png\" alt=\"Topstep\" class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-md object-contain border border-slate-200 bg-white p-0.5 flex-shrink-0\" />\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-1 text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Topstep\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500\">12,100\u003C/span>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-3 px-5 py-2.5 hover:bg-teal-50/50 transition-colors\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-6 text-xs font-black text-slate-400\">3.\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/fundednext.png\" alt=\"FundedNext\" class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-md object-contain border border-slate-200 bg-white p-0.5 flex-shrink-0\" />\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-1 text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">FundedNext\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500\">4,400\u003C/span>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-3 px-5 py-2.5 hover:bg-teal-50/50 transition-colors\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-6 text-xs font-black text-slate-400\">4.\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/funded-trading-plus.png\" alt=\"Funded Trading Plus\" class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-md object-contain border border-slate-200 bg-white p-0.5 flex-shrink-0\" />\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-1 text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Funded Trading Plus\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500\">720\u003C/span>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-3 px-5 py-2.5 hover:bg-teal-50/50 transition-colors\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-6 text-xs font-black text-slate-400\">5.\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/thinkcapital-icon.png\" alt=\"ThinkCapital\" class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-md object-contain border border-slate-200 bg-white p-0.5 flex-shrink-0\" />\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-1 text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">ThinkCapital\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500\">480\u003C/span>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-3 px-5 py-2.5 hover:bg-teal-50/50 transition-colors\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-6 text-xs font-black text-slate-400\">6.\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/blueberry-funded-logo.png\" alt=\"Blueberry Funded\" class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-md object-contain border border-slate-200 bg-white p-0.5 flex-shrink-0\" />\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-1 text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Blueberry Funded\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500\">480\u003C/span>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-3 px-5 py-2.5 hover:bg-teal-50/50 transition-colors\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-6 text-xs font-black text-slate-400\">7.\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/city-traders-imperium-logo.png\" alt=\"City Traders Imperium\" class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-md object-contain border border-slate-200 bg-white p-0.5 flex-shrink-0\" />\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-1 text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">City Traders Imperium\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500\">210\u003C/span>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-3 px-5 py-2.5 hover:bg-teal-50/50 transition-colors\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-6 text-xs font-black text-slate-400\">8.\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/brightfunded-logo.png\" alt=\"BrightFunded\" class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-md object-contain border border-slate-200 bg-white p-0.5 flex-shrink-0\" />\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-1 text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">BrightFunded\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500\">70\u003C/span>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-3 px-5 py-2.5 hover:bg-teal-50/50 transition-colors\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-6 text-xs font-black text-slate-400\">9.\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/dna-funded-logo.png\" alt=\"DNA Funded\" class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-md object-contain border border-slate-200 bg-white p-0.5 flex-shrink-0\" />\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-1 text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">DNA Funded\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500\">40\u003C/span>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n---\n\n## How To Start Trading\n\nGetting started with a prop trading firm is easier than it might seem. Follow these steps to choose the right firm, pass their evaluation, and begin trading with funded capital.\n\n1. **Choose the Right Prop Firm:** Research firms based on your trading goals, preferred financial markets (e.g., forex, commodities), evaluation fees, and trading platform options. Consider profit splits, challenge difficulty, and any scaling opportunities. Read all our [prop firm reviews](/reviews).\n2. **Sign Up and Pay the Evaluation Fee:** Register with the prop firm of your choice and pay the evaluation fee. This fee varies depending on the account size and challenge type you select.\n3. **Complete the Evaluation Challenge:** Follow the firm's trading rules to meet profit targets and stay within drawdown limits. Challenges may include single or multi-phase evaluations, depending on the firm.\n4. **Earn a Funded Account:** Once you pass the challenge, you'll gain access to a funded account with real capital provided by the firm.\n5. **Start Trading:** Begin trading using the firm's capital and share profits according to their profit split policy (e.g., 80%–90% for the trader). Stick to their trading rules to maintain your funded account.\n6. **Scale Your Account:** Some firms offer scaling plans, allowing you to grow your trading account over time by meeting specific profit milestones. This provides access to larger capital and potentially higher earnings.\n\nStarting with a prop firm allows you to trade without risking your own capital beyond the initial evaluation fee. By selecting a firm that aligns with your trading style and adhering to its rules, you can build your skills and grow as a funded trader.\n\n---\n\n## FAQs\n\n### What is the best prop firm in Canada?\n\nThe best prop firm in Canada is BrightFunded, offering customisable challenges, profit splits up to 100%, and an unlimited scaling plan. With account sizes ranging from $5,000 to $200,000, BrightFunded provides flexibility for traders of all experience levels. Its proprietary trading platform ensures seamless access to forex, crypto, indices, and commodities, while the Trade2Earn loyalty program rewards trading activity with valuable perks.\n\n### Are prop firms legal in Canada?\n\nYes, prop firms are legal in Canada as well as the USA, provided they operate within regulatory guidelines and do not require traders to deposit personal funds into trading accounts. Canadian traders participate in evaluation programs to access firm-funded accounts without violating securities laws. It's important to choose reputable prop firms that offer transparent terms, comply with financial regulations, and provide secure trading platforms.\n\n### Which prop firm is the cheapest?\n\nThe cheapest prop firm for fees is ThinkCapital, with evaluation fees starting at just $39, offering flexible challenges and profit splits up to 90%. For the lowest spreads, DNA Funded stands out, with spreads starting at 0.0 pips and low commission fees of $5 per round turn.\n\nBoth prop trading firms provide excellent value for traders, with ThinkCapital excelling in affordability and DNA Funded offering top-tier trading conditions, making them strong options depending on your priority.\n\n### Which is the most legit prop firm?\n\nThe most legit prop firm is DNA Funded, backed by the ASIC-regulated broker DNA Markets, ensuring tight spreads and reliable trading conditions. Its transparency, low fees starting at $49, and profit splits up to 90% provide traders with confidence.\n\nDNA Funded offers access to over 800 markets, including forex, indices, and commodities, along with solid platforms like TradeLocker. This firm's strong regulatory ties and clear trading rules make it a top choice for legitimacy and trust.\n\nTo find out more about who is the most trusted in the prop trading space, read about the [best prop trading firms](/prop-firms).\n\n### Which prop firm is the best for futures?\n\nThe best prop firm for futures trading is FXIFY Futures. It scored 88/100 in our review thanks to its one-step evaluation, no recurring fees, up to 100% profit splits, and access to real CME markets via the FFX platform. Fast payouts, low costs, and clear rules make it the top choice for Canadian futures traders.","src/content/blog/canada.md","f1bfaadbf77f7da1",{"html":5011,"metadata":5012},"\u003Ch2 id=\"what-are-the-best-prop-firms-for-traders-in-canada\">What Are The Best Prop Firms for Traders in Canada?\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>The best prop firms for Canadian traders offer affordable challenges, user-friendly platforms like MT4 or MT5, high profit splits, and reliable payout processes. Look for firms with flexible trading rules, low fees, and a solid reputation or forex broker connection.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>In this guide, we rank the best prop firms available to Canadian traders in 2026, covering everything from challenge fees and profit splits to trading rules and withdrawal times.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"what-to-look-for-as-a-canadian-trader\">What to Look for as a Canadian Trader\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>Before diving into our ranked list, here’s what matters most when evaluating a prop firm from a Canadian perspective.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"iiroc--csa-regulation-vs-offshore-operations\">IIROC &#x26; CSA Regulation vs Offshore Operations\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Most prop firms operate offshore and are \u003Cem>not\u003C/em> regulated by the Canadian Securities Administrators (CSA) or the Canadian Investment Regulatory Organization (CIRO, formerly IIROC). This is legal — they are not offering financial products to retail clients, they are running evaluation challenges. However, regulation in other jurisdictions (such as ASIC in Australia or CySEC in Cyprus) does provide a meaningful layer of legitimacy and trader protection that you should look for.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"payout-track-record\">Payout Track Record\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>A firm’s payout history is the most important trust signal. Look for firms with Trustpilot scores above 4.0, a large community of verified paid-out traders, and transparent terms around withdrawals. Firms that have been operating for 3+ years with consistent payouts are significantly lower risk than newer entrants.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"cad-account-support\">CAD Account Support\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Some firms offer CAD-denominated accounts or CAD payout methods, which saves Canadian traders on currency conversion fees. Most firms pay in USD via crypto or bank wire, so factor in FX costs when comparing effective profit splits.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"platform-availability\">Platform Availability\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>MT4, MT5, and TradeLocker are the most common platforms. cTrader has historically been popular with Canadian traders due to its clean execution model. Avoid firms that only support obscure or proprietary platforms with limited community track records.\u003C/p>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"1-brightfunded--best-prop-firm-in-canada-overall\">1. BrightFunded — Best Prop Firm in Canada Overall\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>Canadian traders can access a funded account with BrightFunded after completing a two-step evaluation process. Account sizes range from $5,000 to $200,000, and profit splits start at 80% but scale all the way up to 100%. Experienced traders can use cTrader or MT5, and beginners DXtrade, with forex spreads on both platforms going as low as 0 pips. With its unique scaling and rewards program, and all the tools you need regardless of experience level, BrightFunded is a great all-rounder prop firm.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/brightfunded-logo.png\" alt=\"BrightFunded logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">BrightFunded\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">Best Prop Firm in Canada Overall\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">100%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Max DD\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">10%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Trustpilot\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">4.6 \u003Cspan class=\"text-amber-500\">★\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Ca href=\"/reviews/brightfunded\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-lg bg-teal-500 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-white hover:bg-teal-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n        Full Review →\n      \u003C/a>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose -mt-3 mb-6 rounded-xl border border-emerald-200 bg-emerald-50/80 px-5 py-3 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-3\">\n  \u003Ca href=\"https://brightfunded.com?affiliateId=rsBbtrzYQSyr3RcHYHQT5w\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-emerald-500 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-emerald-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n    Visit BrightFunded\n  \u003C/a>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2.5\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4 text-emerald-600 flex-shrink-0\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M7 7h.01M7 3h5c.512 0 1.024.195 1.414.586l7 7a2 2 0 010 2.828l-7 7a2 2 0 01-2.828 0l-7-7A1.994 1.994 0 013 12V7a4 4 0 014-4z\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm text-emerald-700 font-semibold\">20% Off — Code:\u003C/span>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"font-mono font-bold text-xs bg-white border border-dashed border-emerald-300 px-3 py-1.5 rounded text-emerald-700 tracking-wide select-all\">PROPFIRMS20\u003C/span>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Pros &#x26; Cons\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Pros\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Profit shares up to 100%\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Unique Trade2Earn loyalty program\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Customisable challenge add-ons\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>36 crypto markets with 1:5 leverage\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Fast payouts via crypto and bank transfer\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Higher fees when using add-ons\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Strict trading rules on funded accounts\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Only crypto withdrawals or bank transfer\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Limited educational resources\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>No MT4 support\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"challenges-and-fees\">Challenges and Fees\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>BrightFunded offers a simple two-step evaluation process with clear profit targets and risk management requirements, keeping things nice and simple.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>Step 1 (Evaluation Phase):\u003C/strong> To pass the first step you need to reach an 8% profit target, while staying within a 5% daily drawdown limit plus a 10% maximum drawdown cap. You must trade for a minimum of five days before moving to the second step.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>Step 2 (Verification Phase):\u003C/strong> After passing the first step, you then need to trade for another five days at least, but your profit target is lower at 5%, with the daily and max drawdown staying the same as step one.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Once you pass the two evaluation stages, you will receive your funded demo account. Over time you can scale your profit share up to 100% by hitting certain milestones, and earn tokens when you trade via the Trade2Earn program.\u003C/p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003Ctable>\u003Cthead>\u003Ctr>\u003Cth>Account Size\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Challenge Fee\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Phase 1 Target\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Phase 2 Target\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Max Daily Loss\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Max Total Drawdown\u003C/th>\u003C/tr>\u003C/thead>\u003Ctbody>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>$5,000\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>€55\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$400\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$250\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$250\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$500\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>$10,000\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>€95\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$800\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$500\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$500\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$1,000\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>$25,000\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>€195\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$2,000\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$1,250\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$1,250\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$2,500\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>$50,000\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>€295\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$4,000\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$2,500\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$2,500\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$5,000\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>$100,000\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>€495\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$8,000\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$5,000\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$5,000\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$10,000\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>$200,000\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>€975\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$16,000\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$10,000\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$10,000\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$20,000\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003C/tbody>\u003C/table>\n\u003Cp>BrightFunded offers several paid add-ons. These are optional, but allow you to personalise your challenge and funded account:\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Weekly Payouts:\u003C/strong> Reduce your profit payout intervals to 7 days for a 25% fee.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Higher Profit Splits:\u003C/strong> Immediately increase your profit share to 90% for a 20% fee.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>No Minimum Trading Days:\u003C/strong> Scrap the 5-day minimum trading day requirement for a 15% fee.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Swap-Free Accounts:\u003C/strong> Access swap-free trading for a 10% fee (made for Islamic prop traders).\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"spreads-and-trading-costs\">Spreads and Trading Costs\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>BrightFunded is not aligned with a broker — the prop firm aggregates market data from top-tier liquidity providers to simulate realistic trading conditions. During testing our team found forex spreads can be as low as 0 pips, and for popular currency pairs like EUR/USD, AUD/USD, or GBP/USD, average spreads are 0.1 pips, which is in line with or lower than most broker-backed prop firms.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Similar to CFD brokers, you pay a $3 commission per lot when trading forex, while crypto trading costs 0.024% of the trading volume. Commission for commodities is 0.0010% of trading volume, and indices are commission-free.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"funded-accounts-and-payouts\">Funded Accounts and Payouts\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>After successfully completing the evaluation, you can start trading with your funded account where you receive a profit share and can scale up.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Profit Splits:\u003C/strong> Start at 80%, scaling to 100% as you meet performance milestones.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Scaling Plan:\u003C/strong> Account balances increase by 30% every four months if you consistently trade (you must be profitable in at least 2 out of 4 months with at least 2 profit payouts).\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Payout Process:\u003C/strong> Bi-weekly payouts are standard, but you can get weekly payouts with the add-on. Payouts are processed via crypto wallets (e.g., USDC ERC-20) or bank transfers, with no minimum withdrawal amount.\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"trading-platforms-and-markets\">Trading Platforms and Markets\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Market and platform access is solid with BrightFunded, and you can choose from MetaTrader 5 (MT5), cTrader, or DXtrade:\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>MT5\u003C/strong> has just been introduced, giving you advanced charting, fast execution, and full support for automated trading with Expert Advisors.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>cTrader\u003C/strong> is designed for experienced manual and algorithmic traders. You get advanced features like Level II pricing, fast execution, and support for C#-based automated strategies. It’s best if you prefer more control or plan to build your own EAs.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>DXtrade\u003C/strong> is a more flexible platform ideal for beginners, along with discretionary and hybrid traders. It includes built-in risk management tools, custom layouts, and multi-chart views, with a user-friendly interface that keeps things simple.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Challenges and funded accounts are a simulated trading environment on all platforms, meaning you are trading via a demo account but with real market data.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Forex:\u003C/strong> 49 currency pairs, including majors like EUR/USD and exotics like USD/ZAR, with leverage up to 1:100.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Commodities:\u003C/strong> Includes gold, silver, crude oil, and natural gas with leverage up to 1:40.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Indices:\u003C/strong> Global indices like S&#x26;P 500, FTSE 100, and DAX 30 with leverage up to 1:20.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Cryptocurrencies:\u003C/strong> 36 cryptos including Bitcoin and Ethereum, max leverage 1:5 (most prop firms offer 1:2, so a good option for crypto traders).\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"trust-and-support\">Trust and Support\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>BrightFunded has built a strong reputation in the prop trading industry, known for transparent policies and active community engagement.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Trustpilot Score:\u003C/strong> 4.6 out of 5 stars, with many positive reviews about its fast payouts and solid customer support.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Community:\u003C/strong> Over 16,000 members in its Discord server with active channels for strategy sharing, trader support, and educational resources.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Support Availability:\u003C/strong> 24/7 customer service via email, live chat, and WhatsApp. Our team found it helpful and responsive, with genuine responses to our questions around spreads etc.\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"final-verdict\">Final Verdict\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Our team found BrightFunded to be the best prop firm in Canada because of its overall trading experience. From evaluation to funded trader status, the rules and requirements were clear, with opportunities along the way to scale up and earn real rewards for trading. While some prop firms make it hard at every step, BrightFunded offers a solid and genuine prop trading experience where you feel supported and given the tools to pass challenges.\u003C/p>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"2-dna-funded--broker-backed-prop-firm\">2. DNA Funded — Broker Backed Prop Firm\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>Backed by DNA Markets, an ASIC-regulated forex broker, DNA Funded gives you some of the most reliable trading conditions and lowest pricing. There are three challenge types including a rapid option, one-step, or two-step evaluation.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>During testing DNA Funded also ranked as the second best crypto prop firm, second best prop firm for stock trading, and fourth best for forex, thanks to its range of markets — showing it’s a great option for anyone wanting to focus on multiple asset classes.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/dna-funded-logo.png\" alt=\"DNA Funded logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">DNA Funded\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">Broker Backed Prop Firm\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">90%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Max DD\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">10%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Trustpilot\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">3.9 \u003Cspan class=\"text-amber-500\">★\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Ca href=\"/reviews/dna-funded\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-lg bg-teal-500 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-white hover:bg-teal-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n        Full Review →\n      \u003C/a>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose -mt-3 mb-6 rounded-xl border border-emerald-200 bg-emerald-50/80 px-5 py-3 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-3\">\n  \u003Ca href=\"https://partners.dnafunded.com/click?campaign_id=1&#x26;ref_id=30\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-emerald-500 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-emerald-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n    Visit DNA Funded\n  \u003C/a>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2.5\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4 text-emerald-600 flex-shrink-0\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M7 7h.01M7 3h5c.512 0 1.024.195 1.414.586l7 7a2 2 0 010 2.828l-7 7a2 2 0 01-2.828 0l-7-7A1.994 1.994 0 013 12V7a4 4 0 014-4z\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm text-emerald-700 font-semibold\">25% Off — Code:\u003C/span>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"font-mono font-bold text-xs bg-white border border-dashed border-emerald-300 px-3 py-1.5 rounded text-emerald-700 tracking-wide select-all\">BESTPROPFIRMS\u003C/span>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Pros &#x26; Cons\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Pros\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Profit splits up to 90%\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Low fees starting at $49\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Access to over 800 financial markets\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Add-ons for higher profit splits and faster payouts\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>No cryptocurrency trading in Rapid Challenge\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Scaling plans not yet available\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Extra fees for features like faster payouts\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Lack of 24/7 customer support\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"challenges-and-fees-1\">Challenges and Fees\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>You get a great range of challenges with DNA Funded — not too many to confuse you but enough to cover everything from a quick challenge to a two-step evaluation.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Single Helix Challenge:\u003C/strong> A one-step evaluation with unlimited trading days, making it ideal if you are swing trading or a position trader.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Double Helix Challenge:\u003C/strong> A two-step evaluation suited to disciplined traders who aren’t in a rush, as there’s again no max trading days.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Rapid Challenge:\u003C/strong> For the more experienced traders, well-suited to high-frequency traders and scalpers. You have a max of 10 days to complete the challenge and crypto trading is not available for this specific challenge.\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Cp>All challenges have a minimum of three trading days, but each has different add-ons available. The one-step allows you to reduce the payout period to a week, the two-step lets you increase your profit split to 90%, while the Rapid challenge lets you do both.\u003C/p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003Ctable>\u003Cthead>\u003Ctr>\u003Cth>Challenge\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Early Payout (14 → 7 Days)\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Profit Split (80% → 90%)\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Add-on Fee Increase\u003C/th>\u003C/tr>\u003C/thead>\u003Ctbody>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Single Helix (1-Step)\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>✅\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>❌\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>20%\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Double Helix (2-Step)\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>❌\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>✅\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>20%\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Rapid Challenge\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>✅\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>✅\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>30%\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003C/tbody>\u003C/table>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"spreads-and-trading-costs-1\">Spreads and Trading Costs\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Thanks to being broker-backed by DNA Markets, the prop firm’s spreads and commission fees are some of the most competitive in the industry.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Spreads:\u003C/strong> Starting from 0 pips for major forex pairs like EUR/USD.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Commission Fees:\u003C/strong> A low $5 per trade round-turn (i.e. $2.50 per side).\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"profit-payouts\">Profit Payouts\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Once you pass the evaluation process, you can access your funded account. Unless you buy the add-on for weekly payouts, you will be able to withdraw profits every 14 days, with a minimum withdrawal of $200. Payment methods are standard with bank transfers and cryptocurrency.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>It is important to point out that when we tested DNA Funded’s challenges, we found there is a 40% daily profit cap applied across all challenges that could be easy to miss when signing up. This means you can only contribute up to 40% of your total payout target from profits made in a single day. As it’s associated with a regulated broker, they have slightly stricter compliance requirements.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Refunds of challenge fees are issued after the first profit payout, which means if you pass there’s zero capital outlay.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"trading-platforms-and-markets-1\">Trading Platforms and Markets\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>DNA Funded supports \u003Cstrong>TradeLocker\u003C/strong> with a TradingView integration, so while a little restricted on platform choice, you get all the charting and analysis tools you need. One major restriction that will take DNA Funded off the list for some is that automated trading is not currently supported — this means no EAs.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>But they make up for it with one of the best ranges of trading instruments available worldwide. You can develop strategies with over 800 trading instruments, including forex, indices, commodities, stocks, and cryptocurrencies.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Leverage depends on challenge type:\u003C/p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003Ctable>\u003Cthead>\u003Ctr>\u003Cth>Max Leverage\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Forex\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Commodities\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Indices\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Stocks\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Crypto\u003C/th>\u003C/tr>\u003C/thead>\u003Ctbody>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Single Helix\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1:30\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1:10\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1:10\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1:5\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1:2\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Double Helix\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1:50\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1:10\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1:10\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1:5\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1:2\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Rapid Challenge\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1:30\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1:10\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1:10\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1:5\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1:2\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003C/tbody>\u003C/table>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"trust-and-support-1\">Trust and Support\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>DNA Funded gains a lot of credibility through partnering with DNA Markets, a well-regulated forex broker and the prop firm’s liquidity provider.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>They are limited in terms of educational resources at this stage, but are building their Discord server with channels for trader discussions and education. Customer support is currently limited to email, with plans to expand to live chat and other channels.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"final-verdict-1\">Final Verdict\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>DNA Funded is one of the strongest all-round prop firms if you want access to more than just forex. Backed by DNA Markets, you get tight spreads, low commissions, and reliable trading conditions from a regulated broker. The three challenge types cover different trading styles, whether you want a fast evaluation, a single step, or a full two-step process.\u003C/p>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"3-fundednext--flexible-prop-challenges\">3. FundedNext — Flexible Prop Challenges\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>FundedNext lets you work towards a funded account via a one or two-step challenge, with account sizes from $5,000 to $200,000. Profit splits start at 80% and scale up to 95%, and you even receive a 15% profit split during the challenge phase, which is nearly unheard of. We tested the prop firm’s Stellar Two Step challenge on MT5, and it took around two months to pass both phases and receive a funded account. It’s one of the best all-rounder prop firms we’ve traded with, earning it 4th place on our shortlist for Canadian traders.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/fundednext.png\" alt=\"FundedNext logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">FundedNext\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">Flexible Prop Challenges\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">95%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Max DD\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">10%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Trustpilot\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">4.6 \u003Cspan class=\"text-amber-500\">★\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Ca href=\"/reviews/fundednext\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-lg bg-teal-500 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-white hover:bg-teal-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n        Full Review →\n      \u003C/a>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose -mt-3 mb-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 px-5 py-3 flex items-center justify-center\">\n  \u003Ca href=\"https://fundednext.com/?fpr=noam82\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-emerald-500 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-emerald-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n    Visit FundedNext\n  \u003C/a>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Pros &#x26; Cons\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Pros\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Profit splits up to 95%\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Flexible challenge models (1-step, 2-step, Lite)\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Competitive spreads from 0 pips\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Strict daily loss limits (3–5%)\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>No stock market access\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Minimum trading days required\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"challenges-and-fees-2\">Challenges and Fees\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>FundedNext has recently trimmed down its challenge options, which we believe is a good move. They’ve streamlined things into three challenge types, with a one-step or two-step evaluation.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Stellar One Step:\u003C/strong> A single-phase evaluation with a 10% profit target, 3% daily loss limit, and 6% overall drawdown. Includes a 15% profit share during the challenge and payouts just 5 days after passing. Fees range from $65 to $1,099.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Stellar Two Step:\u003C/strong> A two-phase challenge with 8% and 5% profit targets. Drawdown limits increase to 5% daily and 10% overall. Like the 1-Step, this model includes a 15% profit share during the challenge. Fees range from $59 to $999.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Stellar Lite:\u003C/strong> A lower-cost two-phase challenge with profit targets of 8% and 4%, and drawdowns set at 4% daily and 8% overall. No profit share during the challenge phase, but bi-weekly payouts after funding. Fees start at just $32.\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Cp>You can also add optional upgrades:\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>No minimum trading days for a 20% fee\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>10% overall drawdown for a 25% fee\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>Bi-weekly payouts for a 15% fee\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>Lifetime 95% payout for a 30% fee\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"spreads-and-trading-costs-2\">Spreads and Trading Costs\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>When we tested FundedNext, we found spreads for major forex pairs like EUR/USD could range anywhere from 0 pips to 1 pip. Commission fees depend on your account type — for Stellar One or Two Step challenges it’s $5 per lot on forex and commodities, while for Stellar Lite accounts it’s $7 per lot for both asset classes.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"funded-accounts-and-payouts-1\">Funded Accounts and Payouts\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>FundedNext offers one of the fastest payout schedules in the industry, with profit splits up to 95% for funded traders, and 15% while you are taking Stellar challenges.\u003C/p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003Ctable>\u003Cthead>\u003Ctr>\u003Cth>Feature\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Stellar 1-Step\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Stellar 2-Step\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Stellar Lite\u003C/th>\u003C/tr>\u003C/thead>\u003Ctbody>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>First Payout\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>5 business days\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>30 days\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>21 days\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Subsequent Payouts\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>5 business days\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Bi-weekly\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Bi-weekly\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Challenge Profit Share\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>15%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>15%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>N/A\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Funded Profit Split\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Up to 95%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Up to 95%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Up to 95%\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Minimum Withdrawal\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$20\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$20\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$20\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003C/tbody>\u003C/table>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>Scaling Plan:\u003C/strong> Grow your account by 40% every four months (up to $4 million) if you hit a 10% return and receive two payouts during that period.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"trading-platforms-and-markets-2\">Trading Platforms and Markets\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>You can choose from four popular trading platforms, so there should be something for everyone:\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>MetaTrader 4 (MT4):\u003C/strong> Ideal for forex trading and EAs.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>MetaTrader 5 (MT5):\u003C/strong> Multi-asset trading with TradingView integration.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>cTrader:\u003C/strong> Manual trading with Level II market depth (not available on 100K+ accounts).\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Match-Trader:\u003C/strong> Web-based, mobile-friendly option with fast setup.\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Cp>When we tested FundedNext, we used MT5 and had a good experience. One thing we did notice was we had to constantly refresh the dashboard for updated stats, otherwise there was a significant lag which could get you in trouble.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>We focused on forex trading USD/JPY during our challenge, but you can also trade:\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Forex:\u003C/strong> 50 pairs, including majors, minors, and exotics.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Indices:\u003C/strong> 18 global indices.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Commodities:\u003C/strong> 5 key assets like gold and crude oil.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Cryptocurrencies:\u003C/strong> 10 coins, including BTC and ETH.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Leverage:\u003C/strong> Up to 100:1 for forex, 50:1 for indices, and 2:1 for crypto.\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"trust-and-support-2\">Trust and Support\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>FundedNext has a strong Trustpilot rating and online community, including hundreds of thousands of Discord members.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Trustpilot Score:\u003C/strong> 4.6 out of 5 stars, with plenty of positive reviews around support and pricing.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Customer Support:\u003C/strong> 24/7 live chat and email assistance — we found our questions were always answered quickly.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Educational Resources:\u003C/strong> Trading guides, psychology sessions, and a YouTube channel with a decent range of training videos.\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"final-verdict-2\">Final Verdict\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>FundedNext is ideal if you want a payout during the challenge period, fast payments, and up to 95% profit splits as a funded trader. When testing this prop firm, it took about two months to complete the Stellar Two Step challenge, and we found pricing to be competitive and support to be helpful along the way.\u003C/p>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"4-eightcap-challenges--broker-prop-challenge\">4. Eightcap Challenges — Broker Prop Challenge\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>Eightcap Challenges is fully available to traders in Canada and operates differently from every other firm on this list. Instead of outsourcing liquidity or running a proprietary feed, it uses the same pricing it provides to its CFD brokerage clients. That results in extremely tight spreads, clean fills during active sessions, and stable chart behaviour — big positives for intraday traders.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Account sizes go from $10K to $200K for the One Step and Two Step challenges. The Day Trader challenge uses a fixed $10K balance and pays instantly based on the multiplier you choose.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/eightcap-logo-1.png\" alt=\"Eightcap Challenges logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">Eightcap Challenges\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">Broker Prop Challenge\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">80%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Max DD\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">10%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Trustpilot\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">4.2 \u003Cspan class=\"text-amber-500\">★\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Ca href=\"/reviews/eightcap\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-lg bg-teal-500 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-white hover:bg-teal-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n        Full Review →\n      \u003C/a>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose -mt-3 mb-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 px-5 py-3 flex items-center justify-center\">\n  \u003Ca href=\"https://challenges.eightcap.com?campaign_id=1&#x26;ref_id=622\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-emerald-500 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-emerald-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n    Visit Eightcap Challenges\n  \u003C/a>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Pros &#x26; Cons\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Pros\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Raw spreads with real broker pricing\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Full automation support on MT4/MT5\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Short-session Day Trader challenges\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>No traditional scaling plan\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Higher fees for large accounts\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>US stocks only in Day Trader challenge\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"challenges-and-fees-3\">Challenges and Fees\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Eightcap Challenges offers three challenge models, each suited to different trading styles:\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>One Step Challenge:\u003C/strong> Best for traders who want a simple, single-phase evaluation. Trade until you hit the target or breach the limits. Minimum trading days apply, but the structure is straightforward.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Two Step Challenge:\u003C/strong> A smoother progression with the target split into two phases. Drawdown limits are wider, so the evaluation feels more forgiving if you manage risk well.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Day Trader Challenge:\u003C/strong> A unique 1-to-8-hour timed session where you choose a stake and multiplier. Designed for traders who prefer fast results and short-term precision rather than multi-day planning. Fully manual on TradeLocker.\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003Ctable>\u003Cthead>\u003Ctr>\u003Cth>Feature\u003C/th>\u003Cth>One Step\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Two Step\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Day Trader (1–8 Hour)\u003C/th>\u003C/tr>\u003C/thead>\u003Ctbody>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Account Size\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$10K – $200K\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$10K – $200K\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Fixed $10K simulated\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Fee Range\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$119 – $1,299\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$99 – $1,199\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$5 – $250\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Profit Target\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>10%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>10% / 8%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Varies by stake &#x26; multiplier\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Max Daily Loss\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>4%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>5%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Fixed dollar drawdown\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Max Total Loss\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>8%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>10%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Fixed dollar limit\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Min Trading Days\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>5\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>3 per step\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>N/A\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Profit Split\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>80%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>80%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Instant payout (2x, 5x or 10x)\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003C/tbody>\u003C/table>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"spreads-and-trading-costs-3\">Spreads and Trading Costs\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Because Eightcap Challenges uses its own live raw-spread feed, pricing is tighter than most prop firms operating in Canada.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Forex spreads can be 0.0 pips on major pairs, with a flat commission of $5 per round turn across forex, indices, and commodities. Crypto has no commission at all.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>US stocks only appear in the Day Trader challenge and use a $4 round-turn fee.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Pricing stays consistent across MT4, MT5, and TradeLocker, and our testing found no spread widening or artificial execution quirks common with some prop firms.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"funded-accounts-and-payouts-2\">Funded Accounts and Payouts\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>For the One Step and Two Step challenges, your first payout becomes available after 14 days, with a $100 minimum withdrawal. Crypto withdrawals can be made from $10.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Profit splits start at 80%, and you can upgrade to 90% with a paid add-on. The Two Step challenge has no payout cap, while the One Step includes a capped first three payouts.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Day Trader payouts work differently — you’re paid instantly based on your chosen stake and multiplier, and no profit split is used.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"trading-platforms-and-markets-3\">Trading Platforms and Markets\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Eightcap Challenges supports MT4, MT5, and TradeLocker, giving Canadian traders more platform choice than most firms on this list.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>MT4 and MT5:\u003C/strong> Available for the One Step and Two Step challenges. Full Expert Advisor support, custom indicators, algo trading, and scripts are all allowed.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>TradeLocker:\u003C/strong> Required for the Day Trader challenge. Fully manual with clean charting and fast order execution.\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Cp>Markets include forex, indices, commodities, crypto, and ETFs on all challenges. US stocks are exclusive to the Day Trader model.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Leverage is highest on the standard challenges, while the Day Trader challenge uses reduced leverage to keep the short-session format controlled.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"trust-and-support-3\">Trust and Support\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Eightcap Challenges is a long-standing global broker regulated by ASIC and the FCA, and its challenge program benefits from the same infrastructure and support team. During testing, live chat replies were quick and handled by real agents.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Unlike many prop firms, the trading environment is transparent and predictable because it’s built directly on a real broker’s framework rather than outsourced feeds or private liquidity pools.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"final-verdict-3\">Final Verdict\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Eightcap Challenges is one of the strongest prop options for Canadian forex traders who value consistent pricing, MT4/MT5 automation, and regulated-broker stability. The fees are higher and there’s no traditional scaling plan, but the execution quality and platform environment are noticeably better than most independent firms.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>It’s best suited to traders who want a funded-account experience that behaves like a real brokerage account, not a proprietary simulation.\u003C/p>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"5-think-capital--low-fee-prop-firm\">5. Think Capital — Low Fee Prop Firm\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>Think Capital is a broker-backed prop firm that offers some of the lowest challenge fees in the industry, starting from just $39 for a $5,000 Nexus account. Canadian traders get a choice of three evaluation types, account sizes up to $200,000, and profit splits up to 90%. With MT5 and ThinkTrader (which includes TradingView integration) both available, Think Capital gives you solid platform flexibility at a price point that undercuts most competitors.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/thinkcapital-icon.png\" alt=\"Think Capital logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">Think Capital\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">Low Fee Prop Firm\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">90%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Max DD\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">6%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Trustpilot\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">4.3 \u003Cspan class=\"text-amber-500\">★\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Ca href=\"/reviews/think-capital\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-lg bg-teal-500 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-white hover:bg-teal-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n        Full Review →\n      \u003C/a>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose -mt-3 mb-6 rounded-xl border border-emerald-200 bg-emerald-50/80 px-5 py-3 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-3\">\n  \u003Ca href=\"https://www.thinkcapital.com/?sp_rid=677d98c8fcd21d60b8730003\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-emerald-500 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-emerald-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n    Visit Think Capital\n  \u003C/a>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Pros &#x26; Cons\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Pros\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Broker-backed prop firm\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Fees starting from just $39\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Three challenge types to suit different styles\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>TradingView integration via ThinkTrader\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Scaling plan up to $1.5M\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Crypto is the only payout method\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Smaller trading community\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>EA support requires paid add-on\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>No MT4 support\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"challenges-and-fees-4\">Challenges and Fees\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Think Capital offers three challenge types, each designed for different experience levels and trading styles.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>Lightning (1-Step):\u003C/strong> The fastest path to funding with a single 10% profit target, a 3% daily loss limit, and a 6% max drawdown. Leverage is capped at 1:30, making it suited to disciplined traders who prefer tighter risk management. No minimum trading days required.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>Dual Step (2-Step):\u003C/strong> A two-phase evaluation with an 8% profit target in Phase 1 and 5% in Phase 2. You get 1:100 leverage with a 5% daily loss limit and 10% max drawdown, which gives you more room to trade than the Lightning challenge. No minimum trading days required.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>Nexus (3-Step):\u003C/strong> The most affordable option starting at just $39 for a $5,000 account. It requires 18% total profit across three phases at 1:100 leverage. This challenge has the lowest fees but the highest total target.\u003C/p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003Ctable>\u003Cthead>\u003Ctr>\u003Cth>Account Size\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Nexus Fee\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Lightning Fee\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Dual Step Fee\u003C/th>\u003C/tr>\u003C/thead>\u003Ctbody>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>$5,000\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$39\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$59\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$59\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>$10,000\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$79\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$99\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$99\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>$25,000\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$139\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$199\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$199\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>$50,000\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$199\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$299\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$299\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>$100,000\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$349\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$499\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$499\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>$200,000\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$649\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$949\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$949\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003C/tbody>\u003C/table>\n\u003Cp>Optional paid add-ons are available to customise your challenge:\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>90% Profit Split:\u003C/strong> Increase your split from the default to 90% for a 25% fee.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>News Trading:\u003C/strong> Unlock news trading on funded accounts for a 25% fee.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Expert Advisors:\u003C/strong> Enable EA trading on MT5 for a 25% fee.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Weekly Payouts:\u003C/strong> Reduce payout intervals from bi-weekly to weekly for a 25% fee.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Reduced Targets:\u003C/strong> Lower your profit targets by 10% for a 10% fee.\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"spreads-and-trading-costs-4\">Spreads and Trading Costs\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Think Capital does not publish average spreads, but during testing ThinkTrader EUR/USD spreads started around 0.8 pips, widening to 2.5+ pips on minor pairs. MT5 offers tighter raw spreads with a $4 per lot per side commission ($8 round-trip) on forex and precious metals. ThinkTrader charges no commission on any asset class, using wider spreads instead.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>MT5 commissions are slightly above the $3 to $3.50 per side industry average, but the option to choose between raw spreads on MT5 or commission-free trading on ThinkTrader gives Canadian traders flexibility depending on their strategy.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"funded-accounts-and-payouts-3\">Funded Accounts and Payouts\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Once you pass your chosen challenge, you receive a funded account and can start earning from your trades.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Profit Splits:\u003C/strong> Up to 90% with the paid add-on, or the default rate without it.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Scaling Plan:\u003C/strong> Account balances increase by 20% every 3 months for traders who achieve 10% total profit, scaling up to a maximum of $1.5 million.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Payout Schedule:\u003C/strong> Bi-weekly by default (every 14 days from your first trade), with a weekly option available as an add-on.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Processing Time:\u003C/strong> Payouts are processed within 3 business days, with crypto withdrawals typically arriving within 24 to 48 hours.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Payout Methods:\u003C/strong> Cryptocurrency only at this time, though bank transfers are expected in the future.\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"trading-platforms-and-markets-4\">Trading Platforms and Markets\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Think Capital supports two platforms for Canadian traders:\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>MT5\u003C/strong> provides advanced charting, multi-asset capabilities, and full EA support (with the add-on). It offers raw spreads and is the better choice for algorithmic or experienced manual traders. Note that US-based traders cannot access MT5 due to regulatory restrictions, but this does not affect Canadian traders.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>ThinkTrader\u003C/strong> integrates TradingView charting tools directly into the platform, making it a strong option for traders who want professional-grade analysis tools in a user-friendly interface. It works on desktop, web, and mobile.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Markets available across both platforms include:\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Forex:\u003C/strong> Major, minor, and exotic currency pairs with leverage up to 1:100 on Dual Step and Nexus challenges (1:30 on Lightning).\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Indices:\u003C/strong> Global indices with leverage up to 1:15.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Commodities:\u003C/strong> Gold, silver, and oil with leverage up to 1:30.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Cryptocurrencies:\u003C/strong> Including Bitcoin and Ethereum with leverage up to 1:2.\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"trust-and-support-4\">Trust and Support\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Think Capital has a Trustpilot rating of 4.3 out of 5 from over 500 reviews, with the majority of users giving five stars. Positive reviews commonly mention transparent rules, fast payouts, and responsive customer support. The firm actively responds to critical feedback within 24 hours.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Community:\u003C/strong> Over 11,700 members on Discord with channels for trading ideas, psychology, and general support.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Support Channels:\u003C/strong> Live chat for instant help, plus email and a contact form for non-urgent queries.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Educational Content:\u003C/strong> Over 100 YouTube videos covering risk management, platform tutorials, and interviews with funded traders.\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"final-verdict-4\">Final Verdict\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Think Capital stands out for Canadian traders looking for the most affordable entry point into prop trading. The Nexus challenge at $39 is one of the cheapest challenge fees available from any reputable firm, and the broker-backed infrastructure means your trading conditions are built on real market data rather than a proprietary simulation. The main drawback is that payouts are crypto-only for now, which may not suit every Canadian trader. If you want low fees, flexible challenge options, and solid platform choice, Think Capital is a strong pick.\u003C/p>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"how-we-picked-the-best-prop-trading-firms-in-2026\">How We Picked the Best Prop Trading Firms In 2026\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>Our methodology at Best Prop Firms is designed to identify the best prop trading firms for Canadian traders based on detailed criteria that reflect the needs of both new and experienced traders. By focusing on transparency, accessibility, and value, we ensure our rankings are useful for traders seeking funded account opportunities.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"evaluation-categories\">Evaluation Categories\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>We assess prop firms across multiple key areas, each weighted based on its impact on trading success:\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Challenges and Fees:\u003C/strong> Evaluation of the types of challenges, profit targets, and drawdown limits. Firms offering low fees, flexible challenges, and achievable targets rank higher.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Spreads and Trading Costs:\u003C/strong> Transparent, competitive spreads and commission fees are prioritised. Firms with lower trading costs score better.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Trading Platforms and Markets:\u003C/strong> The availability of advanced trading platforms like MT5 and cTrader, along with access to diverse markets, is a crucial factor.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Profit Payouts and Scaling Plans:\u003C/strong> We look for firms offering frequent payouts, high profit splits, and scalable account growth opportunities.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Trust and Support:\u003C/strong> Ratings on Trustpilot, community engagement (e.g., Discord), and the availability of customer support influence this category.\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"testing-process\">Testing Process\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Our research team conducts hands-on testing of each firm’s features, including:\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Platform Usability:\u003C/strong> Real-world trading scenarios are simulated to evaluate platform performance and ease of use.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Challenge Process:\u003C/strong> Evaluation challenges are tested for fairness, accessibility, and alignment with traders’ goals.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Payout Reliability:\u003C/strong> Firms are assessed for the speed and transparency of their payout processes.\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"scoring-system\">Scoring System\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Each firm receives an overall score based on its performance in these categories. Firms with higher scores reflect consistent excellence across trading conditions, platform features, and trader support.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>By combining rigorous testing and in-depth analysis, we provide a clear and comprehensive guide to help Canadian traders choose the best prop trading firms. Our commitment to transparency ensures our recommendations are unbiased and rooted in trader success.\u003C/p>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"pros-and-cons-of-prop-trading\">Pros and Cons of Prop Trading\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Pros\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Access to firm capital reduces personal risk\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>High profit shares, often up to 90%\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Options to scale accounts over time\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Promotes disciplined trading habits\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Strict drawdown and loss limits\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Requires consistent performance\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Time-limited evaluations can be stressful\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Restrictions on certain strategies\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"most-popular-prop-firms-in-canada\">Most Popular Prop Firms In Canada\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>FTMO and Topstep are the most popular prop trading firms in Canada, each attracting 12,100 monthly Google searches. FTMO’s broad appeal comes from its long-standing presence and access to forex, indices, and stocks, while Topstep’s consistent interest reflects its focus on futures trading and flexible evaluation structure.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>FundedNext ranks third with 4,400 searches, showing growing visibility thanks to its flexible challenges and high profit splits. Other firms like Funded Trading Plus (FTP), ThinkCapital, and Blueberry Funded follow with moderate but rising interest, signaling a shift toward firms offering instant funding, low fees, or scalable accounts.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Search volume is a useful indicator of trader attention — but doesn’t always reflect evaluation difficulty or payout quality. Always compare visibility with actual trading conditions.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-lg overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"bg-[#0d1b2a] px-5 py-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2.5\">\n      \u003Csvg class=\"h-5 w-5 text-teal-400 flex-shrink-0\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\n        \u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z\">\u003C/path>\n      \u003C/svg>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-black text-white uppercase tracking-wide flex-1\">Most Searched Canadian Prop Firms\u003C/p>\n      \u003Csvg class=\"h-5 w-[26px] flex-shrink-0 rounded-[3px]\" viewBox=\"0 0 200 100\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n        \u003Crect width=\"50\" height=\"100\" fill=\"#FF0000\">\u003C/rect>\n        \u003Crect x=\"50\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" fill=\"#FFFFFF\">\u003C/rect>\n        \u003Crect x=\"150\" width=\"50\" height=\"100\" fill=\"#FF0000\">\u003C/rect>\n        \u003Cpath d=\"M100 20 L105 35 L120 35 L108 44 L112 58 L100 50 L88 58 L92 44 L80 35 L95 35 Z\" fill=\"#FF0000\">\u003C/path>\n      \u003C/svg>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cp class=\"text-[11px] text-slate-400 mt-1\">Based on monthly Google search volume in Canada\u003C/p>\n  \u003C/div>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center px-5 py-2 bg-teal-500 text-[10px] font-bold text-white uppercase tracking-widest\">\n    \u003Cspan class=\"w-8 flex-shrink-0\">#\u003C/span>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"flex-1\">Firm\u003C/span>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"text-right\">Searches/mo\u003C/span>\n  \u003C/div>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"divide-y divide-slate-100\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-3 px-5 py-2.5 hover:bg-teal-50/50 transition-colors\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-6 text-xs font-black text-slate-400\">1.\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/ftmo-logo-2-2-1-1-1.png\" alt=\"FTMO\" class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-md object-contain border border-slate-200 bg-white p-0.5 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-1 text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">FTMO\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500\">12,100\u003C/span>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-3 px-5 py-2.5 hover:bg-teal-50/50 transition-colors\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-6 text-xs font-black text-slate-400\">2.\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/topstep-logo-1-1-1-1-1.png\" alt=\"Topstep\" class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-md object-contain border border-slate-200 bg-white p-0.5 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-1 text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Topstep\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500\">12,100\u003C/span>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-3 px-5 py-2.5 hover:bg-teal-50/50 transition-colors\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-6 text-xs font-black text-slate-400\">3.\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/fundednext.png\" alt=\"FundedNext\" class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-md object-contain border border-slate-200 bg-white p-0.5 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-1 text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">FundedNext\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500\">4,400\u003C/span>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-3 px-5 py-2.5 hover:bg-teal-50/50 transition-colors\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-6 text-xs font-black text-slate-400\">4.\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/funded-trading-plus.png\" alt=\"Funded Trading Plus\" class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-md object-contain border border-slate-200 bg-white p-0.5 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-1 text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Funded Trading Plus\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500\">720\u003C/span>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-3 px-5 py-2.5 hover:bg-teal-50/50 transition-colors\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-6 text-xs font-black text-slate-400\">5.\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/thinkcapital-icon.png\" alt=\"ThinkCapital\" class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-md object-contain border border-slate-200 bg-white p-0.5 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-1 text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">ThinkCapital\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500\">480\u003C/span>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-3 px-5 py-2.5 hover:bg-teal-50/50 transition-colors\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-6 text-xs font-black text-slate-400\">6.\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/blueberry-funded-logo.png\" alt=\"Blueberry Funded\" class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-md object-contain border border-slate-200 bg-white p-0.5 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-1 text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Blueberry Funded\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500\">480\u003C/span>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-3 px-5 py-2.5 hover:bg-teal-50/50 transition-colors\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-6 text-xs font-black text-slate-400\">7.\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/city-traders-imperium-logo.png\" alt=\"City Traders Imperium\" class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-md object-contain border border-slate-200 bg-white p-0.5 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-1 text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">City Traders Imperium\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500\">210\u003C/span>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-3 px-5 py-2.5 hover:bg-teal-50/50 transition-colors\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-6 text-xs font-black text-slate-400\">8.\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/brightfunded-logo.png\" alt=\"BrightFunded\" class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-md object-contain border border-slate-200 bg-white p-0.5 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-1 text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">BrightFunded\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500\">70\u003C/span>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-3 px-5 py-2.5 hover:bg-teal-50/50 transition-colors\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-6 text-xs font-black text-slate-400\">9.\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/dna-funded-logo.png\" alt=\"DNA Funded\" class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-md object-contain border border-slate-200 bg-white p-0.5 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-1 text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">DNA Funded\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500\">40\u003C/span>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"how-to-start-trading\">How To Start Trading\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>Getting started with a prop trading firm is easier than it might seem. Follow these steps to choose the right firm, pass their evaluation, and begin trading with funded capital.\u003C/p>\n\u003Col>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Choose the Right Prop Firm:\u003C/strong> Research firms based on your trading goals, preferred financial markets (e.g., forex, commodities), evaluation fees, and trading platform options. Consider profit splits, challenge difficulty, and any scaling opportunities. Read all our \u003Ca href=\"/reviews\">prop firm reviews\u003C/a>.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Sign Up and Pay the Evaluation Fee:\u003C/strong> Register with the prop firm of your choice and pay the evaluation fee. This fee varies depending on the account size and challenge type you select.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Complete the Evaluation Challenge:\u003C/strong> Follow the firm’s trading rules to meet profit targets and stay within drawdown limits. Challenges may include single or multi-phase evaluations, depending on the firm.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Earn a Funded Account:\u003C/strong> Once you pass the challenge, you’ll gain access to a funded account with real capital provided by the firm.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Start Trading:\u003C/strong> Begin trading using the firm’s capital and share profits according to their profit split policy (e.g., 80%–90% for the trader). Stick to their trading rules to maintain your funded account.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Scale Your Account:\u003C/strong> Some firms offer scaling plans, allowing you to grow your trading account over time by meeting specific profit milestones. This provides access to larger capital and potentially higher earnings.\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ol>\n\u003Cp>Starting with a prop firm allows you to trade without risking your own capital beyond the initial evaluation fee. By selecting a firm that aligns with your trading style and adhering to its rules, you can build your skills and grow as a funded trader.\u003C/p>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"faqs\">FAQs\u003C/h2>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"what-is-the-best-prop-firm-in-canada\">What is the best prop firm in Canada?\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>The best prop firm in Canada is BrightFunded, offering customisable challenges, profit splits up to 100%, and an unlimited scaling plan. With account sizes ranging from $5,000 to $200,000, BrightFunded provides flexibility for traders of all experience levels. Its proprietary trading platform ensures seamless access to forex, crypto, indices, and commodities, while the Trade2Earn loyalty program rewards trading activity with valuable perks.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"are-prop-firms-legal-in-canada\">Are prop firms legal in Canada?\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Yes, prop firms are legal in Canada as well as the USA, provided they operate within regulatory guidelines and do not require traders to deposit personal funds into trading accounts. Canadian traders participate in evaluation programs to access firm-funded accounts without violating securities laws. It’s important to choose reputable prop firms that offer transparent terms, comply with financial regulations, and provide secure trading platforms.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"which-prop-firm-is-the-cheapest\">Which prop firm is the cheapest?\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>The cheapest prop firm for fees is ThinkCapital, with evaluation fees starting at just $39, offering flexible challenges and profit splits up to 90%. For the lowest spreads, DNA Funded stands out, with spreads starting at 0.0 pips and low commission fees of $5 per round turn.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Both prop trading firms provide excellent value for traders, with ThinkCapital excelling in affordability and DNA Funded offering top-tier trading conditions, making them strong options depending on your priority.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"which-is-the-most-legit-prop-firm\">Which is the most legit prop firm?\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>The most legit prop firm is DNA Funded, backed by the ASIC-regulated broker DNA Markets, ensuring tight spreads and reliable trading conditions. Its transparency, low fees starting at $49, and profit splits up to 90% provide traders with confidence.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>DNA Funded offers access to over 800 markets, including forex, indices, and commodities, along with solid platforms like TradeLocker. This firm’s strong regulatory ties and clear trading rules make it a top choice for legitimacy and trust.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>To find out more about who is the most trusted in the prop trading space, read about the \u003Ca href=\"/prop-firms\">best prop trading firms\u003C/a>.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"which-prop-firm-is-the-best-for-futures\">Which prop firm is the best for futures?\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>The best prop firm for futures trading is FXIFY Futures. It scored 88/100 in our review thanks to its one-step evaluation, no recurring fees, up to 100% profit splits, and access to real CME markets via the FFX platform. Fast payouts, low costs, and clear rules make it the top choice for Canadian futures traders.\u003C/p>",{"headings":5013,"localImagePaths":5151,"remoteImagePaths":5152,"frontmatter":5153,"imagePaths":5165},[5014,5017,5020,5023,5026,5029,5032,5035,5038,5041,5044,5047,5050,5053,5056,5058,5060,5063,5065,5067,5069,5072,5074,5076,5078,5080,5082,5084,5087,5089,5091,5093,5095,5097,5099,5102,5104,5106,5108,5110,5112,5114,5117,5120,5123,5126,5129,5132,5135,5136,5139,5142,5145,5148],{"depth":879,"slug":5015,"text":5016},"what-are-the-best-prop-firms-for-traders-in-canada","What Are The Best Prop Firms for Traders in Canada?",{"depth":879,"slug":5018,"text":5019},"what-to-look-for-as-a-canadian-trader","What to Look for as a Canadian Trader",{"depth":158,"slug":5021,"text":5022},"iiroc--csa-regulation-vs-offshore-operations","IIROC & CSA Regulation vs Offshore Operations",{"depth":158,"slug":