191},"Best Crypto Prop Firm with Instant Funding",{"slug":642,"descriptor":5193},"Good for Smaller $2.5K Challenges",{"slug":2380,"descriptor":5195},"Scaling up to $5 million",{"slug":244,"descriptor":5197},"Prop Firm for Crypto Futures Trading","## What Are The Best Prop Firms For Crypto Trading?\n\nTo determine the most suitable prop trading firm for those who primarily want to test the markets with cryptocurrency we factored in fees, features and the range of options each provider offers. Below is our shortlist where we aligned different brokers with different traders needs to find the most suitable provider for your needs.\n\nOur cryptocurrency prop firm list in 2026 is:\n\n1. **BrightFunded** — Best Crypto Prop Trading Firm Overall\n2. **DNA Funded** — Top Broker Backed Crypto Prop Firm\n3. **FundedNext** — Crypto Prop Firm with High Profit Split\n4. **Blueberry Funded** — Good Crypto Prop Firm for EAs\n5. **Funded Prime** — Meme Coin and Crypto Markets\n6. **FTMO** — Cryptocurrency Prop Firm with Scaling Plan\n7. **Funded Trading Plus** — Best Crypto Prop Firm with Instant Funding\n8. **City Traders Imperium** — Good for Smaller $2.5K Challenges\n9. **The Funded Trader** — Scaling up to $5 million\n10. **Apex Trader Funding** — Prop Firm for Crypto Futures Trading\n\n---\n\n## Crypto Prop Firm Comparison Table\n\nCryptocurrency specific trading conditions offered by the top 10 crypto prop firms, updated February 2026.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"overflow-x-auto\">\n    \u003Ctable class=\"w-full text-sm text-left border-collapse min-w-[1100px]\">\n      \u003Cthead>\n        \u003Ctr class=\"bg-slate-50 border-b border-slate-200\">\n          \u003Cth class=\"px-3 py-3 text-xs font-bold text-slate-600 uppercase tracking-wide sticky left-0 bg-slate-50 z-10 min-w-[160px]\">Feature\u003C/th>\n          \u003Cth class=\"px-3 py-3 text-xs font-semibold text-slate-7