00\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Customisable add-ons\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>No MT4 but MT5 available\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>No stock trading\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Crypto only withdrawals\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Not a broker backed prop firm\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Only simulated trading accounts\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n### Prop Firm Details\n\nBrightFunded is the best crypto prop firm thanks to its 35 digital assets, competitive pricing, and high leverage of 5:1 (when the industry standard is 2:1).\n\nYou can trade all the major cryptocurrency pairs like Bitcoin, Ethereum, Solana, and Rune, as well as lesser known coins, all the while benefiting from the perks of the prop firm's unique loyalty program, with a 100% profit split.\n\n### Evaluation Process\n\nTo get your BrightFunded trading account with unlimited scaling, you must work through a two step evaluation process.\n\n**Phase 1 Evaluation:** You need to achieve an 8% profit target with a 5% daily drawdown limit, a 10% total drawdown cap, and complete a minimum of 5 trading days.\n\n**Phase 2 Verification:** You need to reach a reduced 5% profit target while still adhering to the same drawdown limits as Phase 1. You need to trade for at least 5 days in this step too.\n\n**Funded Account:** After passing the evaluation, you get your funded demo account, retaining up to 100% of profits.\n\nOptional add-ons allow you to:\n\n- Increase your payout frequency to weekly or biweekly\n- Bump up your profit split to 90% from day one\n- Have no minimum trading days during your challenge\n- Make your challenge fee refundable, so you get it back at the funded stage\n- Use a swap free account to avoid overnight swaps, or align with Islamic beliefs\n\n### Payments and Payouts\n\nBrightFunded ensures seamless payments and flexible payouts:\n\n- **Profit Splits:** Start at 80% but you can scale up to 100% with consistent trading.\n- **Payout Frequency:** Monthly payout cycle, with addons available to reduce the timeframe.\n- **Payment Methods:** Fees and payouts can be handled through cryptocurrencies like Bitcoin and Ethereum or traditional bank transfers.\n\n### Trading Platforms\n\nBrightFunded offers three popular prop trading platforms with cTrader, MT5, and DXtrade available.\n\n**MT5** will be ideal if you already run bots or Expert Advisors, and want advanced charting and multi asset support without leaving your comfort zone.\n\n**cTrader** is the high performance pick for crypto scalpers and algo traders. You get lightning fast execution, Depth of Market, and automation with cBots built in C#.\n\n**DXtrade** is the easiest entry point for manual or hybrid traders, with a clean, customisable interface and built-in risk tools that make handling volatile crypto pairs more manageable.\n\nYou can use all crypto trading platforms on desktop, browser, and mobile, giving you 24/7 access to trade major and emerging cryptocurrencies.\n\n### Support and Trust\n\nYou can reach BrightFunded through their 24/7 customer support, available via email, live chat, and WhatsApp.\n\n- **Trustpilot Score:** 4.7/5 stars, with most praising the rapid payout process and transparent policies.\n- **Community Engagement:** An active Discord server with thousands of members, giving you a collaborative environment to share insights and strategies.\n\n### Final Verdict\n\nBrightFunded is the best crypto prop firm scoring 95/100 overall, thanks to its unmatched range of 35+ digital assets, high 5:1 leverage, and tight spreads that beat most competitors. Add in flexible payouts, unlimited scaling, and the Trade2Earn rewards program, and it's clear why they earned the top spot.\n\n---\n\n## 2. DNA Funded — Top Broker Backed Crypto Prop Firm\n\nDNA Funded is a broker-backed prop firm offering low-cost crypto trading, high payout flexibility, and access to over 120 crypto pairs during evaluation. You can trade major coins like BTC and ETH in both the Single Helix and Double Helix challenges, with spreads starting from 0 pips and fees as low as $49.\n\nYou can also deposit and withdraw using crypto, and select optional add-ons to reduce payout cycles or boost your profit share to 90%.\n\nUse promo code PROPFIRMS25 to get 25% off your challenge fee, making it even cheaper to trade digital assets.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/dna-funded-logo.png\" alt=\"DNA Funded logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\" />\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">DNA Funded\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">Top Broker Backed Crypto Prop Firm\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">90%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Max DD\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">10%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Trustpilot\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">4.9 \u003Cspan class=\"text-amber-500\">★\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Ca href=\"/reviews/dna-funded\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-lg bg-teal-500 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-white hover:bg-teal-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n        Full Review →\n      \u003C/a>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose -mt-3 mb-6 rounded-xl border border-emerald-200 bg-emerald-50/80 px-5 py-3 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-3\">\n  \u003Ca href=\"https://partners.dnafunded.com/click?campaign_id=1&ref_id=30\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-emerald-500 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-emerald-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14\" />\u003C/svg>\n    Visit DNA Funded\n  \u003C/a>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2.5\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4 text-emerald-600 flex-shrink-0\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M7 7h.01M7 3h5c.512 0 1.024.195 1.414.586l7 7a2 2 0 010 2.828l-7 7a2 2 0 01-2.828 0l-7-7A1.994 1.994 0 013 12V7a4 4 0 014-4z\" />\u003C/svg>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm text-emerald-700 font-semibold\">25% Off — Code:\u003C/span>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"font-mono font-bold text-xs bg-white border border-dashed border-emerald-300 px-3 py-1.5 rounded text-emerald-700 tracking-wide select-all\">PROPFIRMS25\u003C/span>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Pros & Cons\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Pros\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0