 items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>No EAs or automated trading\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n### Prop Firm Details\n\nCrypto trading is available in the Single Helix and Double Helix challenges. You can't trade crypto in the Rapid Challenge, which is focused on faster evaluation and traditional assets.\n\nDNA Funded offers access to 120+ crypto pairs with a 2:1 leverage cap, which applies to both evaluation and funded accounts. This provides controlled exposure given crypto's volatility and aligns with their broker-backed compliance model.\n\n### Evaluation Process\n\nDNA Funded offers three types of challenges:\n\n**Single Helix (1-step):** A simple evaluation requiring a 10% profit target with no time limit. This option is ideal for traders focusing on consistency rather than speed.\n\n**Double Helix (2-step):** A more structured process with a 10% profit target in Phase 1 and 5% in Phase 2. Like the Single Helix, this challenge has no time restrictions.\n\n**Rapid Challenge (1-step):** Designed for experienced traders, the Rapid Challenge requires hitting a 5% profit target within 10 calendar days. However, crypto trading is not allowed in this challenge.\n\nDNA Funded also offers optional add-ons to customize your experience. You can upgrade to a 90% profit split or reduce the payout period to 7 days, making it easier to access your earnings quickly.\n\n| Attribute | Single Helix | Double Helix | Rapid Challenge | Instant Funding |\n|-----------|-------------|-------------|----------------|----------------|\n| Evaluation Process | 1 Step | 2 Step | 1 Step | None (Instant Access) |\n| One-Off Fee | $59 - $1,209 | $49 – $1,079 | $99 – $549 | $199 – $979 |\n| Account Sizes | $5,000 - $200,000 | $5,000 – $200,000 | $10,000 – $100,000 | $5,000 – $50,000 |\n| Fee for Add-Ons | 20% | 20% | 30% | NA |\n| Profit Share | 80% | 80% | 80% | 80% |\n| Profit Target | 10% | 10%, then 5% | 5% | NA |\n| Max Daily Drawdown | 5% | 6%, then 5% | 4% | 4% (Trailing) |\n| Max Total Drawdown | 10% | 10% | 5% | 4% (Trailing) |\n| Max Active Trading Days | Unlimited | Unlimited | 10 Calendar Days | NA |\n| Crypto Trading Allowed | Yes | Yes | No | Yes |\n\n### Payments and Payouts\n\nProfit payouts follow a standard 14-day cycle, with the option to reduce this to weekly payouts using the add-on. The profit split starts at 80% for successful traders, which can also be increased to 90% for a fee.\n\nRecently, DNA Funded has introduced a 40% daily profit cap. This rule limits the maximum amount you can contribute toward your payout target in a single day to 40%. Any profits above that threshold won't count until the next trading day. This policy supports consistent trading behaviour and aligns with their risk management framework.\n\nYou can pay for challenges and receive withdrawals in crypto, with a 1% transaction fee for digital currency transfers.\n\n### Trading Platforms\n\nDNA Funded provides access to one trading platform, TradeLocker integrated with TradingView. Currently, there are no EAs available, creating a barrier for automated trading.\n\nThe prop trading platform supports crypto trading, and is known for its advanced charting and ease of use. Its seamless integration with TradingView gives you access to custom indicators, on-chart trading, and risk management tools, making it ideal for manual crypto traders.\n\n### Support and Trust\n\nAs a new firm, DNA Funded currently offers email support but is expected to expand its customer service options. It is backed by DNA Markets, a regulated forex broker with a strong track record for low spreads and reliable execution.\n\nWhile DNA Funded is still building its community, its active Discord server provides a space for prop traders to connect and share strategies.\n\n### Final Verdict\n\nDNA Funded is the best crypto prop firm for manual traders who want a balance of tight spreads, low fees, and solid platform tools. With payouts available in crypto, 2:1 leverage on over 120 pairs, and broker-grade execution via DNA Markets, DNA Funded stands out for serious crypto traders. Just note that crypto is not tradable in the Pro Challenge, and the 40% daily cap rule encourages consistent strategy execution.\n\n---\n\n## 3. FundedNext — Crypto Prop Firm with High Profit Split\n\nFundedNext is a great option if you want zero-commission crypto trading, profit splits up to 95%, and access to multiple trading platforms like MT4, MT5, and cTrader. Payouts are processed every two weeks, keeping withdrawals consistent.\n\nUse promo code PROPFIRMS to get 120% of your challenge fee refunded — that's your entire fee back plus an extra 20% as a bonus.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/fundednext.png\" alt=\"FundedNext logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\" />\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">FundedNext\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">Crypto Prop Firm with High Profit Split\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">95%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cd