ode:\u003C/span>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"font-mono font-bold text-xs bg-white border border-dashed border-emerald-300 px-3 py-1.5 rounded text-emerald-700 tracking-wide select-all\">PROPFIRMS\u003C/span>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Pros & Cons\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Pros\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Commission-free crypto trading\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Allows Expert Advisors (EAs)\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Up to 95% profit split\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Strict daily loss limits\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Only 10 crypto markets\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>cTrader/Match-Trader cost $25\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n### Prop Firm Details\n\nFundedNext provides access to 10 crypto markets including BTC/USD, ETH/USD, and XRP/USD. All crypto trades are commission-free with a fixed 2:1 leverage cap.\n\nTraders can use EAs on MT4 and MT5, but automation is not supported on cTrader. This makes FundedNext a strong choice for crypto scalpers and algo traders using MetaTrader.\n\n### Evaluation Process\n\nFundedNext offers three crypto-compatible challenges:\n\n**Stellar One Step:** 10% profit target, 3% daily / 6% overall loss. 15% profit share during the challenge, 95% when funded.\n\n**Stellar Two Step:** Two-phase model with 8% and 5% targets. Includes 15% profit share during the challenge and 95% when funded.\n\n**Stellar Lite:** Two-step option with lower entry fees and tighter rules. No profit share during the challenge, but 95% once funded.\n\nAll models are time-unlimited and allow for challenge add-ons like no minimum trading days or extended loss limits.\n\n| Feature | Stellar (1-Step) | Stellar (2-Step) | Stellar Lite |\n|---------|-----------------|-----------------|-------------|\n| Challenge Phases | 1 Phase | 2 Phases | 2 Phases |\n| Account Sizes | 6K - 200K | 6K - 200K | 5K - 100K |\n| Audition Fees | $65 - $1,099 | $59 - $999 | $32 - $399 |\n| Leverage | 30:1 | 100:1 | 100:1 |\n| Commission | $5 | $5 | $7 |\n| Profit Target | 10% | 8%, 5% | 8%, 4% |\n| Maximum Daily Loss | 3% | 5% | 4% |\n| Maximum Overall Loss | 6% | 10% | 8% |\n| Time Limit | No Time Limit | No Time Limit | No Time Limit |\n| Challenge Phase Profit Share | 15% | 15% | N/A |\n| Funded Profit Split | 95% | 95% | 95% |\n| Minimum Trading Days | 2 | 5 | 5 |\n\n### Payments and Payouts\n\nWithdrawals are available every 14 days for most models, and every 21 days for Stellar Lite. You can withdraw via crypto, Deel, or bank transfer.\n\n- **Minimum Payout:** $20\n- **Crypto Payouts:** Only option if under $50\n- **Evaluation Fee:** Fully refunded after your first funded withdrawal, with an added 20% bonus using the PROPFIRMS code\n\n### Trading Platforms\n\nYou can trade crypto on FundedNext using:\n\n- **MT4 & MT5:** EA support, free access\n- **cTrader:** Manual trading only, $25 platform fee, not available for accounts above $100K\n- **Match-Trader:** Web-based with mobile access, $25 fee, also unavailable above $100K\n\nTradingView is available via MT5 for advanced charting.\n\n### Support and Trust\n\nWith a Trustpilot rating of 4.6/5 stars and an active community across Telegram and Discord, FundedNext maintains a strong reputation.\n\nThe prop firm's strong educational resources, including webinars and a detailed dashboard, ensure traders have the support needed to succeed.\n\n### Final Verdict\n\nFundedNext is a top choice for crypto traders seeking high profit splits, commission-free trading, and strong platform variety. With three challenge types, bi-weekly payouts, and a large active community, it strikes a great balance for both manual and algorithmic crypto trading.\n\n---\n\n## 4. Blueberry Funded — Good Crypto Prop Firm for EAs\n\nBlueberry Funded is a strong option if you want EA-friendly crypto trading with 24/7 access and low fees starting from $32.50. With four challenge types and support for 52 crypto markets, you can choose between structured or rapid evaluations to match your trading pace.\n\nUse promo code PROPFIRMS20 to get 20% off your challenge, so you can get started with lower upfront costs.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/blueberry-funded-logo.png\" alt=\"Blueberry Funded logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\" />\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">Blueberry Funded\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">Good Crypto Prop Firm for EAs\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">90%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Max DD\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">10%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Trustpilot\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">3.8 \u003Cspan class=\"text-amber-500\">★\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Ca href=\"/reviews/blueberry-funded\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-lg bg-teal-500 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-white hover:bg-teal-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n        Full Review →\n      \u003C/a>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose -mt-3 mb-6 rounded-xl border border-emerald-200 bg-emerald-50/80 px-5 py-3 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-3\">\n  \u003Ca href=\"https://blueberryfunded.com/?utm_source=affiliate&ref=1457\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-emerald-500 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-emerald-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14\" />\u003C/svg>\n    Visit Blueberry Funded\n  \u003C/a>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2.5\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4 text-emerald-600 flex-shrink-0\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M7 7h.01M7 3h5c.512 0 1.024.195 1.414.586l7 7a2 2 0 010 2.828l-7 7a2 2 0 01-2.828 0l-7-7A1.994 1.994 0 013 12V7a4 4 0 014-4z\" />\u003C/svg>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm text-emerald-700 font-semibold\">20% Off — Code:\u003C/span>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"font-mono font-bold text-xs bg-white border border-dashed border-emerald-300 px-3 py-1.5 rounded text-emerald-700 tracking-wide select-all\">PROPFIRMS20\u003C/span>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Pros & Cons\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Pros\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>52 cryptocurrency markets\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Commission free crypto trading\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Scaling up to $2 million\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Strict drawdown rules\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Limited payment options\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Minimal educational resources\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n### Prop Firm Details\n\nBlueberry Funded scored 93/100 during testing, and ranked in 4th place on our list of the best crypto prop firms. You can trade 52 crypto pairs, one of the best selections available, including BTC/USD, ETH/USD, SOL/USD, and XRP/USD. Leverage is capped at 1:2 for all challenge types. Crypto is commission-free, and spreads are competitive — EUR/USD averages 0.2 pips and BTC/USD remains tightly priced.\n\nYou can use Expert Advisors (EAs) on MT4 and MT5, which is ideal for crypto algo traders. TradeLocker is also available for browser-based access, with stocks and crypto supported natively.\n\nTheir scaling model increases capital by 25% every 3 months, with a maximum simulated allocation of $2 million.\n\n### Evaluation Process\n\nBlueberry Funded offers four challenge types suited to different strategies:\n\n**One Step Challenge:** 10% profit target, 6% drawdown, no time limit.\n\n**Two Step Challenge:** 10% and 5% targets across two phases, with 10% drawdown and 1:50 leverage.\n\n**Rapid Challenge:** 5% target within 7 days, 3% daily and 4% total trailing drawdown.\n\n**Stock Challenge:** 10% and 6% targets with stricter drawdown and trading hour limits (crypto not included here).\n\nAll challenges provide 80% profit splits initially, upgradeable to 90%.\n\n### Payments and Payouts\n\nYou can pay for challenges via credit card or cryptocurrency, with fees ranging from $32.50 to $1,100 depending on account size and model.\n\nProfit payouts are processed every 14 days via RiseWorks, with a minimum withdrawal of $100. Payouts are available in USDC or USDT, and crypto accounts are treated the same as forex in terms of rules and withdrawal eligibility.\n\n### Trading Platforms\n\nBlueberry Funded supports four platforms:\n\n- **MetaTrader 4 (MT4):** EA support, advanced charting, great for scalping bots.\n- **MetaTrader 5 (MT5):** Access to stocks + crypto, DOM, more indicators.\n- **DXTrade:** Basic, browser-based, fewer tools.\n- **TradeLocker:** Clean UI, mobile support, stocks and crypto enabled.\n\nFor crypto traders, MT5 and TradeLocker offer the best blend of automation, usability, and market access.\n\n### Support and Trust\n\nSupport is available 24/5 via live chat and email, with a helpful Discord community of over 27,000 members. Blueberry Funded is backed by Blueberry Markets, an ASIC-regulated broker, and became a founding member of The Prop Association in 2025.\n\nThe firm currently holds a TrustPilot rating of 4.1/5, and offers consistent payouts and transparent rules, though some traders cite strict news trading restrictions as a downside.\n\n### Final Verdict\n\nBlueberry Funded is one of the top crypto prop firms for EA users, offering commission-free access to 50+ pairs and 24/7 trading. With four challenge types, low fees, platform variety, and strong scaling potential, it's a well-rounded choice for both manual and automated crypto traders.\n\n---\n\n## 5. Funded Prime — Meme Coins and Crypto Markets\n\nIf you want crypto plus something a bit different, Funded Prime is worth a look. You get standard crypto pairs in the regular one and two step challenges, and a separate Meme Coin Challenge where tokens like PEPE, WIF, and TRUMP run at 10:1 leverage with no exchange or wallet setup. Pricing tracks Eightcap Challenges' live feed (a top forex broker). EAs are allowed on all challenges and payouts are fast, so you can test both systematic and discretionary ideas without juggling prop firms.\n\nYou can drop your upfront fees by 25% by using the promo code PROPFIRMS25.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/fundedprime-logo.png\" alt=\"Funded Prime logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\" />\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">Funded Prime\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">Meme Coins and Crypto Markets\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">90%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Max DD\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">10%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Trustpilot\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">— \u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cspan class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-lg bg-slate-300 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500 cursor-not-allowed whitespace-nowrap\">\n        Full Review →\n      \u003C/span>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose -mt-3 mb-6 rounded-xl border border-emerald-200 bg-emerald-50/80 px-5 py-3 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-3\">\n  \u003Ca href=\"http://fundedprime.com/?linkId=lp_213737&sourceId=bestpropfirms&tenantId=fundedprime\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-emerald-500 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-emerald-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14\" />\u003C/svg>\n    Visit Funded Prime\n  \u003C/a>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2.5\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4 text-emerald-600 flex-shrink-0\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M7 7h.01M7 3h5c.512 0 1.024.195 1.414.586l7 7a2 2 0 010 2.828l-7 7a2 2 0 01-2.828 0l-7-7A1.994 1.994 0 013 12V7a4 4 0 014-4z\" />\u003C/svg>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm text-emerald-700 font-semibold\">25% Off — Code:\u003C/span>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"font-mono font-bold text-xs bg-white border border-dashed border-emerald-300 px-3 py-1.5 rounded text-emerald-700 tracking-wide select-all\">PROPFIRMS25\u003C/span>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Pros & Cons\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Pros\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Meme Coin Challenge 10:1 leverage\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Broker backed pricing via Eightcap Challenges\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>EAs allowed on both platforms\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Standard crypto capped at 1:1\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>No MT4 or MT5\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>No live chat support\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n### Prop Firm Details\n\nFunded Prime scored 80/100 thanks to keeping things simple with account sizes between $5K and $200K and fees from $35 to $1,235. The base profit split is 80%, and you can bump this up to 90% with the Profit Booster add-on. There's also an option to speed up your first payout with the Early Payout add-on.\n\n### Evaluation Process\n\nYou can choose from four evaluation models depending on what you want to trade.\n\n**One Step:** Single evaluation with 5% daily and 10% overall loss limits.\n\n**Two Step:** Same limits as One Step, but split across two phases. Funded accounts on this model qualify for weekly payouts.\n\n**Stock Challenge:** A one step model restricted to equities, with 1:5 leverage.\n\n**Meme Coin Challenge:** Built for higher-volatility trading, with 10:1 leverage on tokens like PEPE and TRUMP, no daily loss cap, and a 5% trailing drawdown. It's the only model where weekend trading is allowed.\n\nA few extra rules matter for crypto traders. Standard crypto pairs like BTC and ETH are capped at 1:1 leverage, which feels restrictive compared to other firms. If you want more flexibility, the Meme Coin Challenge is where you'll find it, since leverage jumps to 10:1.\n\nNews trading is only open on Two Step accounts, while elsewhere you'll need to respect a 10 minute buffer around announcements.\n\n### Payments and Payouts\n\nWithdrawals are straightforward once you've cleared KYC. The minimum withdrawal is $100, and approved requests are usually processed in one to two days. The first payout comes after 14 days on One Step, Stock, and Meme Coin accounts, but it's cut to 7 days on the Two Step.\n\nDaily profit caps are in place — 30% of a payout cycle's total, or 40% for meme coin accounts — so you're pushed toward consistency instead of banking everything on a single spike.\n\n### Trading Platforms\n\nYou'll be trading on either DXTrade or TradeLocker, both of which allow Expert Advisors and automation.\n\n- **DXTrade:** Available on One Step and Two Step challenges. It's stable, lightweight, and fits well if you run algorithmic setups.\n- **TradeLocker:** Available across all challenges, including crypto and meme coins. It integrates directly with TradingView, making it easier to handle technical analysis and execute trades from your charts.\n\n### Support and Trust\n\nSupport is still basic, offered through a ticket system and a searchable FAQ. There's no live chat yet, but responses are generally quick. Funded Prime launched in 2023 and uses pricing from Eightcap Challenges, so even though trading is simulated, spreads and execution track closely with live conditions.\n\nIts Discord and X communities are active and growing, and payouts during our testing came through quickly.\n\n### Final Verdict\n\nFor crypto, Funded Prime's edge is the Meme Coin Challenge and EA-friendly platforms. Standard crypto leverage is conservative at 1:1, but the 10:1 meme model and quick payouts make it a good fit if you want a focused crypto lane and a sandbox for higher-volatility tokens — without leaving a broker-backed environment.\n\n---\n\n## How To Compare Crypto Prop Trading Firms\n\nAt Best Prop Firms, we use a data driven approach to shortlist proprietary trading firms, focusing on the factors that matter most to traders. Our methodology covers a wide range of criteria to ensure accurate and unbiased recommendations:\n\n- **Challenge Structures:** We assess the flexibility and fairness of evaluation processes, including profit targets, drawdown limits, and the variety of funding options available.\n- **Trading Costs:** Spreads, commissions, and other fees are compared to identify firms offering competitive trading conditions.\n- **Market Access and Platforms:** Firms are rated based on the financial instruments they offer, forex, crypto, indices, and more, and the quality of platforms like MT4, MT5, or TradingView.\n- **Profit Payouts and Payments:** We prioritise firms with frequent and flexible payout schedules, higher profit splits, and reasonable withdrawal policies.\n- **Reputation, Trust, and Support:** Trust scores, customer reviews, and the availability of reliable support are key factors in our evaluations.\n\nThis standardized process of reviewing prop firms ensures traders find firms that suit their trading strategies, experience, and goals.\n\n---\n\n## Risk Management for Prop Traders\n\nRisk management is essential for successful proprietary trading, especially in volatile markets like cryptocurrencies. Key tools for risk management include stop-loss orders to limit potential losses and take-profit orders to lock in gains when targets are reached. These tools help remove emotion from trading decisions and ensure a disciplined approach to exits.\n\nPosition sizing is equally important. A common strategy is risking no more than 1–2% of your account balance on a single trade. This keeps losses manageable and supports long-term profitability. For cryptocurrencies, where volatility is higher, keeping position sizes smaller and using lower leverage is a good way to mitigate risk. Leverage amplifies both potential profits and losses, so you should use it carefully. Many prop firms cap leverage for crypto trading at 1:2, providing moderate exposure while limiting risk.\n\nThe risk-to-reward ratio is another fundamental aspect of risk management. Targeting a ratio of at least 1:2, where the potential profit is double the risk, allows traders to remain profitable even with lower win rates. Coupling this with diversified trades across different instruments further spreads risk. Lastly, adherence to a well-defined trading plan is crucial. This plan should outline entry and exit points, risk limits, and strategies for different market conditions. Avoiding emotional reactions, such as revenge trading, and sticking to your plan will improve consistency and results.\n\n---\n\n## FAQs\n\n### What's the best crypto prop firm?\n\nThe best cryptocurrency proprietary trading firm is BrightFunded, offering 5:1 leverage and over 40 crypto pairs to trade during the evaluation process, as well as with a live funded account. The prop firm is also ranked second in the prop firm list for 2026 thanks to its well rounded offering with profit splits up to 100% and a unique loyalty program.\n\nWhile DNA Funded is the best prop firm in terms of execution and flexibility, firms like DNA Funded and Blueberry Funded also provide solid options for experienced crypto traders.\n\n### What is a crypto proprietary trading firm?\n\nA crypto proprietary trading firm funds traders to trade cryptocurrencies using the firm's capital, allowing traders to keep a share of the profits. These prop firms offer evaluation challenges to assess your trading skills before being granted funded trader status, or instant funding programs for more experienced traders. You can trade a range of markets during challenges such as Bitcoin and Ethereum traded as CFDs, spot assets, or futures.\n\n### Which prop firms allow crypto trading?\n\nMany prop firms allow crypto trading, including BrightFunded, DNA Funded, Blueberry Funded, FundedNext, FTMO, Funded Trading Plus, City Traders Imperium and others. These prop trading firms offer access to major cryptocurrencies like Bitcoin (BTC) and Ethereum (ETH), as well as a few providing access to more unique digital coins. Many prop firms also offer commission-free trading for crypto markets, and leverage up to 1:2.\n\n### Can you trade crypto on FTMO?\n\nYes, you can trade cryptocurrencies on FTMO, but the selection is limited to 10 pairs, such as BTC/USD and ETH/USD. The firm offers capped leverage at 1:1 for standard accounts and 1:3.3 for Swing accounts, making it less flexible compared to competitors. While FTMO's structured evaluation process and scaling plan to $2 million are appealing, other firms, like DNA Funded or Blueberry Funded, provide a broader range of crypto trading options and more competitive features.\n\n### What are the top-rated crypto prop trading firms for experienced traders?\n\nExperienced traders should opt for prop firms like DNA Funded, Blueberry Funded, and FundedNext for crypto trading. DNA Funded is considered the best prop firm overall with a competitive 90% profit splits and crypto-focused challenges, while Blueberry Funded and FundedNext both offer high profit splits and automated trading features.\n\nMore experienced CFD traders may also be interested in the best instant funding prop firms, which allow you to skip the evaluation process altogether and fast track to funded trader status.\n\n### What are the best crypto prop trading firms for beginner traders?\n\nCrypto prop trading isn't ideal for beginners due to the complexity, high-risk, and volatility of cryptocurrency markets. If you are new to online trading, you should approach it cautiously and develop your trading experience first through demo accounts. For those determined to start, BrightFunded offers account sizes starting at $10,000 with a straightforward 2-step challenge and manageable profit targets.\n\n### Which prop firm is the most trusted?\n\nDNA Funded is the most trusted prop firm, earning a top score of 97/100 in our evaluations. Partnered with DNA Markets, an ASIC-regulated broker, it provides institutional-grade trading conditions, spreads starting at 0 pips, and transparent policies. Its flexible challenges, customizable payouts up to 90%, and reliable trading platforms like TradeLocker enhance trustworthiness.\n\nAs the best broker backed prop firm, DNA Funded ensures secure and transparent trading, setting it apart in the prop trading industry.\n\n### What is the best prop firm to trade futures?\n\nThe best futures prop firm is Topstep, which scored 89/100 in our analysis. Topstep provides a flexible three-step evaluation process, allowing traders to progress at their own pace without time limits. With a 100% profit split on the first $10,000 and 90% thereafter, Topstep offers competitive payouts. Its platform options, including NinjaTrader and commission-free TopstepX, cater to diverse trading styles, making it ideal for futures traders at all levels.\n\n---\n\n## About PropFirms\n\nPropFirms is dedicated to helping traders find the best proprietary trading firms to suit their needs. Our team of researchers evaluates prop firms based on critical factors such as account options, trading platforms, profit splits, and evaluation processes.\n\nBy providing transparent, data-driven comparisons, we aim to simplify the decision-making process for traders of all experience levels. Whether you're exploring instant funding options or multi-step challenges, our detailed prop firm reviews ensure you have the insights to make informed choices.","src/content/blog/crypto.md","c23cad5f01af4ddc",{"html":5202,"metadata":5203},"\u003Ch2 id=\"what-are-the-best-prop-firms-for-crypto-trading\">What Are The Best Prop Firms For Crypto Trading?\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>To determine the most suitable prop trading firm for those who primarily want to test the markets with cryptocurrency we factored in fees, features and the range of options each provider offers. Below is our shortlist where we aligned different brokers with different traders needs to find the most suitable provider for your needs.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Our cryptocurrency prop firm list in 2026 is:\u003C/p>\n\u003Col>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>BrightFunded\u003C/strong> — Best Crypto Prop Trading Firm Overall\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>DNA Funded\u003C/strong> — Top Broker Backed Crypto Prop Firm\u003C/li>\n