.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Customisable add-ons\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>No MT4 but MT5 available\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>No stock trading\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Crypto only withdrawals\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Not a broker backed prop firm\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Only simulated trading accounts\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"prop-firm-details\">Prop Firm Details\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>BrightFunded is the best crypto prop firm thanks to its 35 digital assets, competitive pricing, and high leverage of 5:1 (when the industry standard is 2:1).\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>You can trade all the major cryptocurrency pairs like Bitcoin, Ethereum, Solana, and Rune, as well as lesser known coins, all the while benefiting from the perks of the prop firm’s unique loyalty program, with a 100% profit split.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"evaluation-process\">Evaluation Process\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>To get your BrightFunded trading account with unlimited scaling, you must work through a two step evaluation process.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>Phase 1 Evaluation:\u003C/strong> You need to achieve an 8% profit target with a 5% daily drawdown limit, a 10% total drawdown cap, and complete a minimum of 5 trading days.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>Phase 2 Verification:\u003C/strong> You need to reach a reduced 5% profit target while still adhering to the same drawdown limits as Phase 1. You need to trade for at least 5 days in this step too.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>Funded Account:\u003C/strong> After passing the evaluation, you get your funded demo account, retaining up to 100% of profits.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Optional add-ons allow you to:\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>Increase your payout frequency to weekly or biweekly\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>Bump up your profit split to 90% from day one\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>Have no minimum trading days during your challenge\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>Make your challenge fee refundable, so you get it back at the funded stage\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>Use a swap free account to avoid overnight swaps, or align with Islamic beliefs\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"payments-and-payouts\">Payments and Payouts\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>BrightFunded ensures seamless payments and flexible payouts:\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Profit Splits:\u003C/strong> Start at 80% but you can scale up to 100% with consistent trading.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Payout Frequency:\u003C/strong> Monthly payout cycle, with addons available to reduce the timeframe.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Payment Methods:\u003C/strong> Fees and payouts can be handled through cryptocurrencies like Bitcoin and Ethereum or traditional bank transfers.\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"trading-platforms\">Trading Platforms\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>BrightFunded offers three popular prop trading platforms with cTrader, MT5, and DXtrade available.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>MT5\u003C/strong> will be ideal if you already run bots or Expert Advisors, and want advanced charting and multi asset support without leaving your comfort zone.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>cTrader\u003C/strong> is the high performance pick for crypto scalpers and algo traders. You get lightning fast execution, Depth of Market, and automation with cBots built in C#.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>DXtrade\u003C/strong> is the easiest entry point for manual or hybrid traders, with a clean, customisable interface and built-in risk tools that make handling volatile crypto pairs more manageable.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>You can use all crypto trading platforms on desktop, browser, and mobile, giving you 24/7 access to trade major and emerging cryptocurrencies.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"support-and-trust\">Support and Trust\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>You can reach BrightFunded through their 24/7 customer support, available via email, live chat, and WhatsApp.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Trustpilot Score:\u003C/strong> 4.7/5 stars, with most praising the rapid payout process and transparent policies.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Community Engagement:\u003C/strong> An active Discord server with thousands of members, giving you a collaborative environment to share insights and strategies.\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"final-verdict\">Final Verdict\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>BrightFunded is the best crypto prop firm scoring 95/100 overall, thanks to its unmatched range of 35+ digital assets, high 5:1 leverage, and tight spreads that beat most competitors. Add in flexible payouts, unlimited scaling, and the Trade2Earn rewards program, and it’s clear why they earned the top spot.\u003C/p>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"2-dna-funded--top-broker-backed-crypto-prop-firm\">2. DNA Funded — Top Broker Backed Crypto Prop Firm\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>DNA Funded is a broker-backed prop firm offering low-cost crypto trading, high payout flexibility, and access to over 120 crypto pairs during evaluation. You can trade major coins like BTC and ETH in both the Single Helix and Double Helix challenges, with spreads starting from 0 pips and fees as low as $49.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>You can also deposit and withdraw using crypto, and select optional add-ons to reduce payout cycles or boost your profit share to 90%.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Use promo code PROPFIRMS25 to get 25% off your challenge fee, making it even cheaper to trade digital assets.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/dna-funded-logo.png\" alt=\"DNA Funded logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">DNA Funded\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">Top Broker Backed Crypto Prop Firm\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-