icing\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>MT4 and MT5 automation allowed\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Tight and consistent forex spreads\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>1, 2, 4 and 8-hour Day Trader challenge\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Strong regulation (ASIC/FCA)\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Higher fees on larger accounts\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>No traditional scaling plan\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>First payout in 14 days on standard challenges\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>US traders not accepted\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>No challenge fee refund after passing\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n### Prop Firm Details\n\nEightcap Challenges scored 89/100 in our testing, mainly because it offers something structurally different to every other firm on this list. You trade on the broker itself, not a prop-firm-styled server. That means raw pricing, predictable spreads, stable fills, and a lot less uncertainty about feed quality.\n\nThe challenge rules are clean and achievable, especially for forex traders who prefer raw pricing and normal brokerage behaviour. The higher fees and lack of a scaling plan restrict it slightly, but Eightcap Challenges still feels like one of the most stable places to run a prop evaluation.\n\n### Challenges and Accounts\n\nEightcap Challenges offers three evaluation types:\n\n**One Step Challenge:** A straightforward one step evaluation. Drawdown is static, automation is allowed, and execution matches Eightcap Challenges' normal raw accounts.\n\n**Two Step Challenge:** A two step evaluation with a larger first target and a smaller second target.\n\n**Day Trader Challenge:** A unique timed evaluation where you trade a fixed $10K balance for 1, 2, 4 or 8 hours. No automation, and sessions are fully manual. Payouts are instant based on stake × multiplier.\n\n| Feature | One-Phase | Two-Phase | Fast Day Trader (1–8 Hour) |\n|---------|----------|----------|-----------------------------|\n| Account Size Range | $10,000 – $200,000 | $10,000 – $200,000 | Fixed $10,000 simulated balance |\n| Fee Range | $119 – $1,299 | $99 – $1,199 | $5 – $250 |\n| Evaluation Process | One Step | Two Step | 1, 2, 4 or 8-hour |\n| Profit Target | 10% | 10% / 8% | Varies by stake & multiplier |\n| Max Daily Loss | 4% | 5% | Fixed dollar drawdown |\n| Max Total Loss | 8% | 10% | Fixed dollar limit based on chosen stake |\n| Minimum Trading Days | 5 | 3 per step | N/A |\n| Profit Split | 80% | 80% | Instant payout based on 2x, 5x or 10x multiplier |\n\n### Profit Splits and Payouts\n\nEightcap Challenges starts funded traders at an 80% profit split, with a paid add-on available to raise it to 90%.\n\nStandard funded accounts follow a 14-day first payout window, then regular payout cycles afterwards. Crypto can be used for smaller withdrawals, and larger payouts can go through bank transfer after KYC and verification checks.\n\nThe Day Trader challenge pays out immediately after a successful session, since there is no ongoing funded account, just one session, one result.\n\nWhile this payout structure is stable, the delayed first payout and no-fee-refund policy are the main reasons Eightcap Challenges didn't score higher in payouts.\n\n### Markets and Leverage\n\nYou can trade a broad range of markets including forex pairs, indices, commodities, cryptocurrencies, ETFs, and US stock CFDs (Day Trader only).\n\nLeverage is highest on the One Step and Two Step challenges, which makes sense for multi-day forex trading. These accounts behave like typical Eightcap Challenges raw-spread brokerage setups, so if you run multi-asset portfolios or EAs, this is the natural fit.\n\n| Asset Class | One Step | Two Step | Day Trader | Notes |\n|------------|---------|---------|-----------|-------|\n| Forex | 1:100 | 1:100 | 1:30 | Majors, minors and exotics supported |\n| Indices | 1:30 | 1:30 | 1:10 | Includes US30, NAS100, SPX500, UK100, GER40 |\n| Commodities | 1:20 | 1:20 | 1:10 | Metals and energies |\n| Crypto | 1:3 | 1:3 | 1:2 | Wide crypto list across all models |\n| US Stocks | N/A | N/A | 1:5 | Day Trader only |\n| ETFs | 1:5 | 1:5 | 1:5 | ASX and US ETFs available |\n\nThe Day Trader model deliberately reduces leverage across all markets. This keeps the short-session format controlled so performance comes from execution rather than oversized position sizes.\n\n### Trading Platforms and Rules\n\nEightcap Challenges supports MT4, MT5 and TradeLocker, with platform behaviour identical to their real brokerage accounts.\n\n**MT4 / MT5:** Available on the One Step and Two Step challenges, including full EA support, custom indicators, scripts, and rule-based automation. Charting and execution feel like a real raw account.\n\n**TradeLocker:** Used exclusively for the Day Trader challenge. Completely manual, lightweight, and built for quick execution inside timed sessions. You can optionally choose it on standard challenges, but most forex traders prefer MT4/MT5 for automation.\n\n### Trust and Community\n\nEightcap Challenges is a regulated forex broker, licensed by ASIC in Australia, CySEC in Europe, and the FCA in the UK. It's been operating since 2009, and holds a 4.2/5 Trustpilot rating across thousands of reviews for its brokerage operations.\n\nBecause the prop challenges run on that same infrastructure, the conditions feel more transparent and consistent than typical prop firm environments.\n\nSupport is responsive through live chat and email, and traders can rely on the same operational backbone that Eightcap Challenges uses for its retail clients.\n\nYou also get access to the broker's educational materials and research ecosystem, including weekly insights and structured education through Eightcap Challenges Labs. These aren't prop-specific resources, but they translate well because they cover the same markets used in the challenges.\n\n### Our Final Verdict on Eightcap Challenges\n\nEightcap Challenges scores 89/100 and takes second place on our forex prop firm shortlist because it's ideal for forex traders who prefer a funded account experience that feels like trading with a real broker. The fees are higher and there's no scaling plan, but the raw pricing, stable execution and full MT4/MT5 automation make it a stronger environment than most independent prop firms.\n\n---\n\n## 3. BrightFunded — Loyalty Program for Prop Traders\n\nBrightFunded is the third best forex prop firm with an overall score of 95/100, and includes an industry leading loyalty program that makes it easy for you to scale up and keep more of your profits. With account sizes from $5K to $200K and profit splits up to 100%, it's one of the best forex prop firms for traders looking to grow their capital.\n\nThe Trade2Earn loyalty program can reduce your trading costs overtime by allowing you to earn tokens that unlock free evaluations, higher profit splits, and lower drawdowns. Add that to an unlimited scaling plan, and you've got a prop firm that rewards consistency and growth.\n\nUse promo code PROPFIRMS20 for 20% off challenge fees.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/brightfunded-logo.png\" alt=\"BrightFunded logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\" />\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">BrightFunded\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">Loyalty Program for Prop Traders\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">100%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Max DD\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">10%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Trustpilot\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">4.4 \u003Cspan class=\"text-amber-500\">★\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Ca href=\"/reviews/brightfunded\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-lg bg-teal-500 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-white hover:bg-teal-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n        Full Review →\n      \u003C/a>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose -mt-3 mb-6 rounded-xl border border-emerald-200 bg-emerald-50/80 px-5 py-3 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-3\">\n  \u003Ca href=\"https://brightfunded.com?affiliateId=rsBbtrzYQSyr3RcHYHQT5w\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-emerald-500 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-emerald-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14\" />\u003C/svg>\n    Visit BrightFunded\n  \u003C/a>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2.5\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4 text-emerald-600 flex-shrink-0\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M7 7h.01M7 3h5c.512 0 1.024.195 1.414.586l7 7a2 2 0 010 2.828l-7 7a2 2 0 01-2.828 0l-7-7A1.994 1.994 0 013 12V7a4 4 0 014-4z\" />\u003C/svg>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm text-emerald-700 font-semibold\">20% Off — Code:\u003C/span>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"font-mono font-bold text-xs bg-white border border-dashed border-emerald-300 px-3 py-1.5 rounded text-emerald-700 tracking-wide select-all\">PROPFIRMS20\u003C/span>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Pros & Cons\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Pros\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Profit splits up to 100%\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Unlimited scaling plan\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Challenge add-ons\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>No MT4 (MT5 now available)\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>No share trading options\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Withdrawals only USD and crypto\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n### Prop Firm Details\n\nBrightFunded rewards consistency with an unlimited scaling plan, allowing you to increase your account size by 30% every four months if you meet performance targets.\n\nOnce you hit the third scale-up, you can keep 100% of profits, making it one of the most rewarding growth models in the prop trading industry.\n\n| Challenge Type | Account Sizes | Fees (€) | Profit Targets | Max Daily Loss | Overall Drawdown |\n|---------------|--------------|----------|---------------|---------------|-----------------|\n| Two Step Challenge | $5K - $200K | €55 - €1,824 | 8% (Phase 1) / 5% (Phase 2) | 5% | 10% |\n\nBrightFunded also provides customisable challenge add-ons such as faster payout cycles, higher profit splits, and no minimum trading days to cater to different trading styles.\n\n### Profit Splits and Payouts\n\nBrightFunded's profit-sharing model allows traders to keep 80% to 100% of their earnings, depending on scaling milestones and loyalty program participation. You can also request payouts weekly or bi-weekly based on selected add-ons.\n\n| Payout Frequency | Default Split | Upgrade Options |\n|-----------------|--------------|----------------|\n| Standard | 80% | N/A |\n| Loyalty Tier | 90% | +20% fee |\n| Maximum Tier | 100% | Available via Trade2Earn |\n\nWithdrawals are processed via bank transfer or cryptocurrency, with no minimum withdrawal amount.\n\n### Trade2Earn Loyalty Program\n\nThe Trade2Earn program is a unique feature of the prop firm where you can earn BrightFunded Tokens for every trade, which can be redeemed for:\n\n- Free evaluations (skip paying for challenges!)\n- Higher profit splits (up to 100%)\n- Lower drawdown limits for more trading flexibility\n- Discounts on challenge fees up to 50%\n\nThis program makes BrightFunded even more rewarding for prop traders who stay active and consistent.\n\n### Markets and Leverage\n\nBrightFunded provides you access to 49 forex pairs, commodities, indices, and 35 cryptocurrencies. Leverage is flexible, with forex at 1:100, commodities at 1:40, and crypto at 1:5.\n\n| Market Type | Instruments | Leverage |\n|------------|-------------|---------|\n| Forex | 49 currency pairs | Up to 1:100 |\n| Commodities | Gold, Silver, WTI, UK Oil | Up to 1:40 |\n| Indices | ASX 200, DAX 30, FTSE 100 | Up to 1:20 |\n| Crypto | BTC, ETH, SOL, THORChain | Up to 1:5 |\n\n### Trading Platforms\n\nOne of BrightFunded's biggest upgrades in 2026 was adding MetaTrader 5 (MT5) to its lineup, giving traders a choice of three platforms: MT5, cTrader, and DXtrade. Each works across desktop, web, and mobile, and all run on BrightFunded's simulated environment with real market data.\n\n**MT5** is the go to for traders who want reliability and automation. It supports Expert Advisors, custom indicators, and advanced charting, and will be ideal if you're already running strategies on MT4 or MT5 and want to plug straight into prop trading.\n\n**cTrader** is the performance driven option for more advanced traders, known for its clean interface, fast execution, and Depth of Market tools. It's especially popular with scalpers, algo traders, and anyone who wants full control over order flow and automation in C#.\n\n**DXtrade** rounds out the lineup as a flexible choice for discretionary traders. It has built-in risk controls and a layout you can adjust to your own workflow, but we found it less polished than MT5 or cTrader.\n\n### Trust and Community\n\nBrightFunded holds a 4.7/5 TrustPilot rating, with traders praising its fast payouts and transparent rules.\n\nThe prop firm has an active Discord community with over 16,000 members, offering trade ideas, market insights, and direct support from the BrightFunded team.\n\n### Our Final Verdict on BrightFunded\n\nBrightFunded's scaling plan, loyalty program, and flexible trading model make it a strong choice for traders focused on long term growth and high profit splits. If you're looking for a prop firm that rewards consistency and active trading, BrightFunded is one of the best options out there.\n\n---\n\n## 4. DNA Funded — Low Commission Fees\n\nDNA Funded is the fourth best forex prop firm with a score of 97/100 plus low commission fees, a wide range of tradable forex pairs, and fast payouts. With challenges starting at $49, it's one of the more affordable ways to get funded. The optional add-ons let you increase profit splits or shorten withdrawal times, giving you extra flexibility.\n\nUse promo code PROPFIRMS25 to get 25% off your challenge fee, so you can start trading for less.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/dna-funded-logo.png\" alt=\"DNA Funded logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\" />\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">DNA Funded\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">Low Commission Fees\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">90%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Max DD\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">10%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp