 1.414.586l7 7a2 2 0 010 2.828l-7 7a2 2 0 01-2.828 0l-7-7A1.994 1.994 0 013 12V7a4 4 0 014-4z\" />\u003C/svg>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm text-emerald-700 font-semibold\">20% Off — Code:\u003C/span>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"font-mono font-bold text-xs bg-white border border-dashed border-emerald-300 px-3 py-1.5 rounded text-emerald-700 tracking-wide select-all\">PROPFIRMS20\u003C/span>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Pros & Cons\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Pros\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Rapid Challenge with a 7-day evaluation\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Access to 1,100+ financial instruments\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Strong forex trading community support\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Limited educational resources\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>14-day payout cycle, which may not suit all\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Limited payment options for challenge fees\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n### Prop Firm Details\n\nBlueberry Funded is one of the best forex prop firms for traders who want to scale capital as they grow.\n\nThe prop firm's structured scaling plan increases your funded account by 25% every 3 months, up to a $2 million cap, if you hit 10% profit and complete four payouts. The rules are clearly defined, and your trading conditions stay the same as you scale.\n\n### Challenges and Accounts\n\nBlueberry Funded offers four evaluation models, and three out of four are built for forex and CFD prop trading. You can choose a challenge based on your trading speed, style, and risk preference.\n\n**One Step Challenge:** No time limit, 10% profit target, and static 6% max drawdown.\n\n**Two Step Challenge:** Two phases with 10% and 5% targets, and higher leverage (1:50) for forex trading.\n\n**Rapid Challenge:** 7-day evaluation, 5% profit target, trailing drawdown, and no minimum trading days.\n\n**Stock Challenge:** Two-phase evaluation with over 1,000 US stocks. Only available for equity traders.\n\n### Profit Splits and Payouts\n\nBlueberry Funded starts all traders at an 80% profit split, with the option to upgrade to 90% as you scale. Payouts are available every 14 days, with a low $100 minimum and no open trades required. Profits are withdrawn through RiseWorks, with options including crypto (USDT, USDC) and bank transfer. The initial challenge fee is fully refunded after your first successful withdrawal.\n\n### Markets and Leverage\n\nBlueberry Funded gives you access to a wide range of forex and CFD markets, with consistent leverage rules and low-cost trading across all challenge types.\n\nHere's what you can trade:\n\n- **Forex:** 45 pairs, including majors and exotics. Leverage up to 1:50 (2 Step), or 1:30 (1 Step, Rapid).\n- **Indices:** 14 global indices like US30 and GER30, capped at 1:10 leverage.\n- **Commodities:** 17 instruments including gold and oil, with 1:10 leverage.\n- **Crypto:** 52 pairs including BTC, ETH, ADA. 1:2 leverage, available on 1 Step and Rapid only.\n- **Stocks:** 1,000+ US stocks, exclusive to the Stock Challenge.\n\n### Trading Platforms\n\nBlueberry Funded supports four trading platforms, MT4, MT5, DXTrade, and TradeLocker, allowing you to select one that best fits your style.\n\n**MetaTrader 4 (MT4):** Known for reliability and customisable EAs, making it a popular choice for forex traders.\n\n**MetaTrader 5 (MT5):** Offers more order types and indicators than MT4, with enhanced charting for advanced traders.\n\n**DXTrade:** A browser-based option with a flexible layout, though it may experience performance issues during high trading volumes.\n\n**TradeLocker:** A clean, mobile-friendly web platform built for fast execution. Offers real-time monitoring, drag-and-drop orders, and easy charting without needing to install software.\n\n### Trust and Community\n\nBlueberry Funded is backed by Blueberry Markets, a regulated forex broker licensed by ASIC. In 2025, it became a founding member of The Prop Association (TPA), which promotes transparency and trader protection.\n\nWith over 27,000 Discord members, active support channels, and verified payouts, Blueberry has a growing reputation for reliability and fairness in the prop space.\n\n### Support and Education\n\nYou get access to 24/5 support via live chat and email, with responses typically under one business day. Educational content is limited, but an active Discord community fills the gap with peer guidance, trading tips, and support from staff. While their YouTube content is minimal, the platform experience and helpdesk coverage are strong.\n\n### Our Final Verdict on Blueberry Funded\n\nBlueberry Funded is a smart pick if you're a forex trader looking to scale over time without changing your trading style. The combination of clear rules, low fees, and a defined path to $2 million in simulated capital makes it one of the most scalable prop firms in the market.\n\n---\n\n## How We Shortlisted The Best Forex Prop Firms\n\nWhen selecting the best forex prop trading firm, we consider several factors that will directly impact your experience as a prop trader, as well as earnings potential and success in the program:\n\n- **Prop Challenges:** When we review prop firms, we look at the flexibility, clarity, and cost of the firm's evaluation challenges. Prop firms that offer varied options such as one-step or two-step challenges, achievable profit targets, and flexible drawdown limits are often more accessible to a broader range of traders. Low one-time fees and clear policies are also good signs.\n- **Spreads and Commission Fees:** Low spreads and commission fees are crucial, and prop firms with transparent pricing and low trading costs are ranked better.\n- **Financial Markets and Leverage:** Prop firms offering a good range of forex CFDs and higher leverage from 50:1 to 100:1 score better during our assessments. A firm with broader market access lets traders diversify and better manage their risk.\n- **Trading Platform Options:** Prop firms supporting major trading platforms like MT4, MT5, and cTrader, as well as advanced charting, order types, and mobile compatibility are especially valuable for traders aiming to trade forex on the go.\n- **Profit Payout Structure:** The best prop firms offer fast payouts, high-profit splits (typically above 80%), and low minimum withdrawal amounts.\n- **Customer Support and Education:** A strong support network with 24/7 availability, live chat, and comprehensive educational resources can significantly enhance the trading experience, as well as strong educational resources like webinars and trading tutorials.\n- **Trust and Community:** Positive Trustpilot scores and reviews, transparency in policies, and an active trading community (e.g., on platforms like Discord) build trust and foster a collaborative environment, which can be valuable for trader engagement and shared learning.\n- **Account Opening:** A straightforward sign-up process and efficient onboarding lets traders access demo or live accounts quickly, enabling you to focus on your trading goals with minimal delay.\n\nOverall, forex prop trading firms offer an accessible way for traders to gain capital, trade forex and CFDs, and work within a structured, supportive environment.\n\nOur list of the 10 best forex prop trading firms provides various account balance options, from smaller starter accounts to large scale funding for experienced traders, catering to those seeking to develop and profit from their trading skills. Prop firms that offer forex trading, but scored low during testing (ie E8 Markets and AquaFunded), didn't make the cut.\n\n---\n\n## How We Selected the Best Forex Prop Firms for 2026\n\nWe selected the best forex prop trading firms by following our methodology that involves giving each firm a score out of 10 across eight core criteria. We look first at challenge structure, evaluating how accessible and varied each firm's programs are, including funding steps, drawdown limits, and profit targets. We rank each prop firms account options to assess competitiveness and value for money.\n\nNext, we assess trading costs, covering forex spreads and commission fees to ensure competitive pricing. Market range and leverage is another essential factor, highlighting prop firms that support diverse trading strategies with options across forex, commodities, indices, and cryptocurrencies.\n\nTrading platform quality is central, with preference given to firms that offer multiple tools, like MT4, MT5, or cTrader, supporting different trading styles. Profit payout structures are also a priority, focusing on payout frequency, profit splits, and withdrawal minimums to determine how well firms accommodate steady earnings.\n\nCustomer support and education are important for a smooth trading experience, with higher ratings for firms that offer accessible help and practical learning resources. We also look closely at trust and community, noting positive TrustPilot scores, strong Discord servers, and transparent policies as indicators of reliability.\n\nFinally, a streamlined sign-up process that allows quick access to evaluation programs and easy payment methods also plays a role.\n\n---\n\n## What are forex prop trading firms?\n\nForex prop trading firms give forex traders the opportunity to trade with substantial capital provided by the firm rather than relying on their own funds. These firms evaluate traders through structured challenges or assessments to gauge their skill level, consistency, and risk management.\n\nTraders who meet these requirements earn access to funded live accounts, allowing them to trade forex with a higher account balance than they might otherwise afford. Profits generated on these accounts are shared between the trader and the firm, making it possible for traders to earn from forex trading without risking more than the initial challenge fee.\n\n---\n\n## How do forex prop firms work?\n\nForex prop trading firms offer traders a pathway to access greater capital for forex markets, beginning with an evaluation phase. In this phase, you partake in a challenge where you are aiming to meet specific performance targets and risk management requirements, such as a 10% profit target with daily and overall drawdown limits of 5% and 10%. Success in this evaluation phase demonstrates your skills and risk management ability, qualifying you for a funded account backed by the prop firm's capital.\n\nOnce you reach the funded trader stage, you receive a profit share, typically between 80-90%, while the firm retains a smaller share. To encourage ongoing success, prop trading firms often conduct regular assessments and may offer scaling plans, allowing you to grow your capital as you demonstrate consistent, profitable trading performance.\n\nThis model provides a structured, low-risk way for forex traders to access significant capital without risking personal funds, aside from any initial evaluation fees. You can read the full forex prop trading guide for more information about the types of forex prop firms, the best trading strategies, and so on.\n\n---\n\n## FAQs\n\n### Which prop firm is best for forex?\n\nFundedNext is considered the best prop trading firm for forex due to its competitive spreads, high profit splits, and diverse account options. It offers leverage up to 1:100 and a choice between two-phase and instant funding models, making it accessible for different trading styles. FundedNext's challenge structure provides a balanced mix of realistic evaluation targets and trader-friendly conditions.\n\n### What are proprietary trading firms?\n\nProprietary trading firms, aka prop firms, provide traders with access to capital, allowing them to trade financial markets without risking personal funds. Forex prop firms evaluate CFD traders through challenge programs, assessing skills in managing risk and meeting profit targets. Successful traders gain funded accounts, sharing a percentage of their profits with the firm.\n\n### Which prop firm has the best trading conditions?\n\nIC Funded and DNA Funded are two of the cheapest prop firms with the best trading conditions for forex traders. IC Funded's partnership with IC Markets allows it to offer spreads from 0 pips and leverage up to 50:1, making it a strong choice for those prioritising low trading costs.\n\nDNA Funded also offers low fees, up to 90% profit split, and flexible account types. Both firms suit a variety of trading styles and budgets.\n\n### Which prop firm has the highest leverage?\n\nFundedNext offers leverage up to 100:1 on forex pairs, giving traders strong high-exposure potential. For commodities and indices, a leverage cap of 50:1 is common among top prop firms. As with CFD trading, make sure you employ solid risk management strategies when participating in prop challenges.\n\n### Which prop firm is better than FTMO?\n\nIC Funded, DNA Funded, and Blueberry Funded are some of the best prop firms and much better than FTMO. IC Funded provides ultra-low spreads through its partnership with IC Markets, while DNA Funded is known for its low fees and high profit splits of up to 90%, with various flexible challenges.\n\nLastly, Blueberry Funded Rapid Challenge is one of the fastest evaluation processes in the industry, enabling traders to achieve funding within 7 days.\n\n### How do prop challenges work?\n\nProp trading firms use challenges to evaluate traders before granting access to funded accounts. These challenges typically require you to meet profit targets while adhering to risk management rules, such as drawdown limits and maximum loss thresholds. Most firms offer one-step or two-step evaluations, with structured guidelines on trading performance. To learn more about the process, visit our guide on how challenges work.","src/content/blog/forex.md","aa5e1899a8fb455c",{"html":5469,"metadata":5470},"\u003Ch2 id=\"what-are-the-best-forex-funded-accounts\">What Are The Best Forex Funded Accounts?\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>Prop trading firms provide forex traders with access to capital, enabling them to trade larger amounts without using their own money. We’ve reviewed the best forex prop trading firms, focusing on those with low fees, a good range of forex pairs, and solid profit-sharing models to help traders make the most of their opportunities.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Our list of the best prop firms for forex trading is the following.\u003C/p>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"the-10-best-forex-prop-firms-we-tested-in-2026\">The 10 Best Forex Prop Firms We Tested in 2026\u003C/h2>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"1-fundednext--best-forex-prop-firm-overall\">1. FundedNext — Best Forex Prop Firm Overall\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>FundedNext is the best forex prop firm with an overall score of 92/100 thanks to its solid scaling plan, flexible challenge types, and profit splits up to 95%. Whether you want quick funding or a structured evaluation, there’s an option for you.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Use promo code PROPFIRMS to get a 120% refund after passing the challenge — your entire fee back, plus a 20% bonus when you make your first withdrawal.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/fundednext.png\" alt=\"FundedNext logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">FundedNext\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">Best Forex Prop Firm Overall\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">95%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Max DD\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">10%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Trustpilot\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">4.5 \u003Cspan class=\"text-amber-500\">★\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Ca href=\"/reviews/fundednext\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-lg bg-teal-500 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-white hover:bg-teal-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n        Full Review →\n      \u003C/a>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose -mt-3 mb-6 rounded-xl border border-emerald-200 bg-emerald-50/80 px-5 py-3 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-3\">\n  \u003Ca href=\"https://fundednext.com/?fpr=noam82\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-emerald-500 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-emerald-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n    Visit FundedNext\n  \u003C/a>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2.5\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4 text-emerald-600 flex-shrink-0\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M7 7h.01M7 3h5c.512 0 1.024.195 1.414.586l7 7a2 2 0 010 2.828l-7 7a2 2 0 01-2.828 0l-7-7A1.994 1.994 0 013 12V7a4 4 0 014-4z\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm text-emerald-700 font-semibold\">120% Refund — Code:\u003C/span>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"font-mono font-bold text-xs bg-white border border-dashed border-emerald-300 px-3 py-1.5 rounded text-emerald-700 tracking-wide select-all\">PROPFIRMS\u003C/span>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Pros &#x26; Cons\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Pros\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Profit splits up to 95%\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Flexible scaling plan up to $4 million\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>MT4, MT5, cTrader, and Match-Trader\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Platform fee on cTrader and Match-Trader\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Limited access to stock markets\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Requires disciplined trading\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"prop-firm-details\">Prop Firm Details\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>FundedNext’s structured scale-up model and bi-weekly payouts make it the best forex prop firm for traders focused on consistency and long-term growth. The max funding limit is $4 million, with scaling every 4 months for traders who hit 10% growth, 2 payouts, and stay profitable.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"challenges-and-accounts\">Challenges and Accounts\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>FundedNext runs three challenge types across two core models:\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>Stellar One Step:\u003C/strong> One-phase challenge, 10% profit target, low 3% daily / 6% overall loss, 15% payout during challenge, 95% funded.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>Stellar Two Step:\u003C/strong> 8% + 5% targets, 5% daily / 10% total drawdown, 15% payout during challenge, 95% funded.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>Stellar Lite:\u003C/strong> Two-step, lower-cost model, 8% + 4% targets, 4% daily / 8% overall drawdown, no payout during challenge, 95% funded.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>All challenges are time unlimited, and optional add-ons include no minimum trading days, 10% drawdown, and lifetime 95% profit splits.\u003C/p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003Ctable>\u003Cthead>\u003Ctr>\u003Cth>Feature\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Stellar (1-Step)\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Stellar (2-Step)\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Stellar Lite\u003C/th>\u003C/tr>\u003C/thead>\u003Ctbody>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Challenge Phases\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1 Phase\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>2 Phases\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>2 Phases\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Account Sizes\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>6K - 200K\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>6K - 200K\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>5K - 100K\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Audition Fees\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$65 - $1,099\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$59 - $999\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$32 - $399\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Leverage\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>30:1\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>100:1\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>100:1\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Commission\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$5\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$5\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$7\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Profit Target\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>10%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>8%, 5%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>8%, 4%\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Maximum Daily Loss\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>3%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>5%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>4%\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Maximum Overall Loss\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>6%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>10%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>8%\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Time Limit\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>No Time Limit\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>No Time Limit\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>No Time Limit\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Challenge Phase Profit Share\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>15%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>15%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>N/A\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Funded Profit Split\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>95%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>95%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>95%\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Minimum Trading Days\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>2\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>5\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>5\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>First Reward\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>5 Business Days\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Monthly\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>21 Days\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Subsequent Rewards\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>5 Business Days\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Bi-Weekly\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Bi-Weekly\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003C/tbody>\u003C/table>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"profit-splits-and-payouts\">Profit Splits and Payouts\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Profit splits go up to 95%, with 15% paid during the challenge on Stellar models. Payout schedules vary by model:\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Stellar One Step:\u003C/strong> First reward in 5 business days, then bi-weekly\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Stellar Two Step:\u003C/strong> Monthly, then bi-weekly\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Stellar Lite:\u003C/strong> First reward in 21 days, then bi-weekly\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Minimum Withdrawal:\u003C/strong> $20 (crypto-only if under $50)\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Evaluation Fee:\u003C/strong> 100% refunded with a 20% bonus on your first profit withdrawal\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"markets-and-leverage\">Markets and Leverage\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>With access to 83 financial instruments across forex, indices, commodities, and cryptocurrencies, FundedNext caters to traders looking for diversity in their trading options. Leverage varies by account type and asset class, providing tailored exposure to manage risk.\u003C/p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003Ctable>\u003Cthead>\u003Ctr>\u003Cth>Asset Class\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Instruments\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Leverage (Varies by Model)\u003C/th>\u003C/tr>\u003C/thead>\u003Ctbody>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Forex\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>50 pairs\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Up to 100:1\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Indices\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>18 indices\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>5:1 - 50:1\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Commodities\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>5 commodities\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>10:1 - 50:1\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Cryptocurrencies\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>10 cryptos\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Fixed at 2:1\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003C/tbody>\u003C/table>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"trading-platforms\">Trading Platforms\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>FundedNext offers access to:\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>MT4 &#x26; MT5:\u003C/strong> Free access; EAs allowed\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>cTrader:\u003C/strong> $25 fee, not available on 100K+ accounts\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Match-Trader:\u003C/strong> $25 fee, not available on 100K+ accounts\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Cp>TradingView is available through MT5 integration.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"trust-and-community\">Trust and Community\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>FundedNext has a strong presence on social media, with active communities on Discord, Telegram, and Facebook. The prop firm’s excellent TrustPilot rating of 4.6 out of 5 reflects positive customer feedback, supported by high engagement across its online platforms.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Discord:\u003C/strong> Hundreds of thousands of members\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Telegram:\u003C/strong> 46,000+ subscribers\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Facebook and Twitter:\u003C/strong> High follower engagement with frequent updates\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Cp>The firm’s community channels provide traders with valuable insights, support, and real-time announcements.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"support-and-education\">Support and Education\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>FundedNext provides 24/7 support via live chat and email, complemented by a comprehensive range of educational resources, including trading guides, market updates, and a YouTube channel featuring over 1,200 videos.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>These resources cover essential topics like trading psychology, strategy development, and market trends, while the YouTube content offers tutorials, webinars, and valuable insights into prop trading.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"our-final-verdict-on-fundednext\">Our Final Verdict on FundedNext\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>FundedNext is the best forex prop firm in 2026 for traders who want multiple challenge options, fast withdrawals, and a realistic path to scaling. The high profit splits, wide platform support, and low entry cost on Stellar Lite make it accessible for all skill levels.\u003C/p>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"2-eightcap-challenges--day-trading-forex-challenge\">2. Eightcap Challenges — Day Trading Forex Challenge\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>Eightcap Challenges is the only forex prop option on this list where the challenges run directly on a regulated broker’s infrastructure instead of a traditional prop setup. That means you trade using Eightcap Challenges’ own raw pricing, execution feed, and trading servers, a big difference compared to prop firms that use private feeds, synthetic spreads or restricted routing.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>You can choose between a simple one-step evaluation, a more structured two-step, or Eightcap Challenges’ unique timed Day Trader challenge, which condenses the entire evaluation into a 1–8 hour session. If you value stability, raw pricing and clean infrastructure over marketing gimmicks, Eightcap Challenges is one of the most reliable forex prop options available.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/eightcap-logo-1.png\" alt=\"Eightcap Challenges logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">Eightcap Challenges\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">Day Trading Forex Challenge\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">90%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Max DD\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">10%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Trustpilot\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">4.0 \u003Cspan class=\"text-amber-500\">★\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Ca href=\"/reviews/eightcap\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-lg bg-teal-500 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-white hover:bg-teal-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n        Full Review →\n      \u003C/a>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose -mt-3 mb-6 rounded-xl border border-emerald-200 bg-emerald-50/80 px-5 py-3 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-3\">\n  \u003Ca href=\"https://challenges.eightcap.com?campaign_id=1&#x26;ref_id=622\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-emerald-500 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-emerald-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n    Visit Eightcap Challenges\n  \u003C/a>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2.5\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4 text-emerald-600 flex-shrink-0\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M7 7h.01M7 3h5c.512 0 1.024.195 1.414.586l7 7a2 2 0 010 2.828l-7 7a2 2 0 01-2.828 0l-7-7A1.994 1.994 0 013 12V7a4 4 0 014-4z\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm text-emerald-700 font-semibold\">20% Off — Code:\u003C/span>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"font-mono font-bold text-xs bg-white border border-dashed border-emerald-300 px-3 py-1.5 rounded text-emerald-700 tracking-wide select-all\">PROPFIRMS20\u003C/span>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Pros &#x26; Cons\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Pros\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Broker-backed raw spreads and real pricing\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>MT4 and MT5 automation allowed\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Tight and consistent forex spreads\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>1, 2, 4 and 8-hour Day Trader challenge\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Strong regulation (ASIC/FCA)\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Higher fees on larger accounts\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>No traditional scaling plan\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>First payout in 14 days on standard challenges\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>US traders not accepted\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>No challenge fee refund after passing\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"prop-firm-details-1\">Prop Firm Details\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Eightcap Challenges scored 89/100 in our testing, mainly because it offers something structurally different to every other firm on this list. You trade on the broker itself, not a prop-firm-styled server. That means raw pricing, predictable spreads, stable fills, and a lot less uncertainty about feed quality.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>The challenge rules are clean and achievable, especially for forex traders who prefer raw pricing and normal brokerage behaviour. The higher fees and lack of a scaling plan restrict it slightly, but Eightcap Challenges still feels like one of the most stable places to run a prop evaluation.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"challenges-and-accounts-1\">Challenges and Accounts\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Eightcap Challenges offers three evaluation types:\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>One Step Challenge:\u003C/strong> A straightforward one step evaluation. Drawdown is static, automation is allowed, and execution matches Eightcap Challenges’ normal raw accounts.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>Two Step Challenge:\u003C/strong> A two step evaluation with a larger first target and a smaller second target.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>Day Trader Challenge:\u003C/strong> A unique timed evaluation where you trade a fixed $10K balance for 1, 2, 4 or 8 hours. No automation, and sessions are fully manual. Payouts are instant based on stake × multiplier.\u003C/p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003Ctable>\u003Cthead>\u003Ctr>\u003Cth>Feature\u003C/th>\u003Cth>One-Phase\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Two-Phase\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Fast Day Trader (1–8 Hour)\u003C/th>\u003C/tr>\u003C/thead>\u003Ctbody>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Account Size Range\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$10,000 – $200,000\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$10,000 – $200,000\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Fixed $10,000 simulated balance\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Fee Range\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$119 – $1,299\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$99 – $1,199\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$5 – $250\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Evaluation Process\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>One Step\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Two Step\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1, 2, 4 or 8-hour\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Profit Target\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>10%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>10% / 8%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Varies by stake &#x26; multiplier\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Max Daily Loss\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>4%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>5%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Fixed dollar drawdown\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Max Total Loss\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>8%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>10%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Fixed dollar limit based on chosen stake\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Minimum Trading Days\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>5\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>3 per step\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>N/A\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Profit Split\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>80%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>80%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Instant payout based on 2x, 5x or 10x multiplier\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003C/tbody>\u003C/table>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"profit-splits-and-payouts-1\">Profit Splits and Payouts\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Eightcap Challenges starts funded traders at an 80% profit split, with a paid add-on available to raise it to 90%.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Standard funded accounts follow a 14-day first payout window, then regular payout cycles afterwards. Crypto can be used for smaller withdrawals, and larger payouts can go through bank transfer after KYC and verification checks.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>The Day Trader challenge pays out immediately after a successful session, since there is no ongoing funded account, just one session, one result.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>While this payout structure is stable, the delayed first payout and no-fee-refund policy are the main reasons Eightcap Challenges didn’t score higher in payouts.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"markets-and-leverage-1\">Markets and Leverage\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>You can trade a broad range of markets including forex pairs, indices, commodities, cryptocurrencies, ETFs, and US stock CFDs (Day Trader only).\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Leverage is highest on the One Step and Two Step challenges, which makes sense for multi-day forex trading. These accounts behave like typical Eightcap Challenges raw-spread brokerage setups, so if you run multi-asset portfolios or EAs, this is the natural fit.\u003C/p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003Ctable>\u003Cthead>\u003Ctr>\u003Cth>Asset Class\u003C/th>\u003Cth>One Step\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Two Step\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Day Trader\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Notes\u003C/th>\u003C/tr>\u003C/thead>\u003Ctbody>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Forex\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1:100\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1:100\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1:30\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Majors, minors and exotics supported\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Indices\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1:30\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1:30\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1:10\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Includes US30, NAS100, SPX500, UK100, GER40\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Commodities\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1:20\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1:20\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1:10\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Metals and energies\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Crypto\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1:3\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1:3\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1:2\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Wide crypto list across all models\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>US Stocks\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>N/A\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>N/A\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1:5\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Day Trader only\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>ETFs\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1:5\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1:5\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1:5\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>ASX and US ETFs available\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003C/tbody>\u003C/table>\n\u003Cp>The Day Trader model deliberately reduces leverage across all markets. This keeps the short-session format controlled so performance comes from execution rather than oversized position sizes.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"trading-platforms-and-rules\">Trading Platforms and Rules\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Eightcap Challenges supports MT4, MT5 and TradeLocker, with platform behaviour identical to their real brokerage accounts.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>MT4 / MT5:\u003C/strong> Available on the One Step and Two Step challenges, including full EA support, custom indicators, scripts, and rule-based automation. Charting and execution feel like a real raw account.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>TradeLocker:\u003C/strong> Used exclusively for the Day Trader challenge. Completely manual, lightweight, and built for quick execution inside timed sessions. You can optionally choose it on standard challenges, but most forex traders prefer MT4/MT5 for automation.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"trust-and-community-1\">Trust and Community\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Eightcap Challenges is a regulated forex broker, licensed by ASIC in Australia, CySEC in Europe, and the FCA in the UK. It’s been operating since 2009, and holds a 4.2/5 Trustpilot rating across thousands of reviews for its brokerage operations.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Because the prop challenges run on that same infrastructure, the conditions feel more transparent and consistent than typical prop firm environments.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Support is responsive through live chat and email, and traders can rely on the same operational backbone that Eightcap Challenges uses for its retail clients.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>You also get access to the broker’s educational materials and research ecosystem, including weekly insights and structured education through Eightcap Challenges Labs. These aren’t prop-specific resources, but they translate well because they cover the same markets used in the challenges.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"our-final-verdict-on-eightcap-challenges\">Our Final Verdict on Eightcap Challenges\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Eightcap Challenges scores 89/100 and takes second place on our forex prop firm shortlist because it’s ideal for forex traders who prefer a funded account experience that feels like trading with a real broker. The fees are higher and there’s no scaling plan, but the raw pricing, stable execution and full MT4/MT5 automation make it a stronger environment than most independent prop firms.\u003C/p>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"3-brightfunded--loyalty-program-for-prop-traders\">3. BrightFunded — Loyalty Program for Prop Traders\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>BrightFunded is the third best forex prop firm with an overall score of 95/100, and includes an industry leading loyalty program that makes it easy for you to scale up and keep more of your profits. With account sizes from $5K to $200K and profit splits up to 100%, it’s one of the best forex prop firms for traders looking to grow their capital.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>The Trade2Earn loyalty program can reduce your trading costs overtime by allowing you to earn tokens that unlock free evaluations, higher profit splits, and lower drawdowns. Add that to an unlimited scaling plan, and you’ve got a prop firm that rewards consistency and growth.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Use promo code PROPFIRMS20 for 20% off challenge fees.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/brightfunded-logo.png\" alt=\"BrightFunded logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">BrightFunded\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">Loyalty Program for Prop Traders\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">100%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Max DD\u003C/p>\n   