-white border border-dashed border-emerald-300 px-3 py-1.5 rounded text-emerald-700 tracking-wide select-all\">PROPFIRMS20\u003C/span>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Pros &#x26; Cons\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Pros\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Profit splits up to 100%\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Unlimited scaling plan\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Challenge add-ons\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>No MT4 (MT5 now available)\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>No share trading options\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Withdrawals only USD and crypto\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"prop-firm-details-2\">Prop Firm Details\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>BrightFunded rewards consistency with an unlimited scaling plan, allowing you to increase your account size by 30% every four months if you meet performance targets.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Once you hit the third scale-up, you can keep 100% of profits, making it one of the most rewarding growth models in the prop trading industry.\u003C/p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003Ctable>\u003Cthead>\u003Ctr>\u003Cth>Challenge Type\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Account Sizes\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Fees (€)\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Profit Targets\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Max Daily Loss\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Overall Drawdown\u003C/th>\u003C/tr>\u003C/thead>\u003Ctbody>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Two Step Challenge\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$5K - $200K\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>€55 - €1,824\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>8% (Phase 1) / 5% (Phase 2)\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>5%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>10%\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003C/tbody>\u003C/table>\n\u003Cp>BrightFunded also provides customisable challenge add-ons such as faster payout cycles, higher profit splits, and no minimum trading days to cater to different trading styles.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"profit-splits-and-payouts-2\">Profit Splits and Payouts\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>BrightFunded’s profit-sharing model allows traders to keep 80% to 100% of their earnings, depending on scaling milestones and loyalty program participation. You can also request payouts weekly or bi-weekly based on selected add-ons.\u003C/p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003Ctable>\u003Cthead>\u003Ctr>\u003Cth>Payout Frequency\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Default Split\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Upgrade Options\u003C/th>\u003C/tr>\u003C/thead>\u003Ctbody>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Standard\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>80%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>N/A\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Loyalty Tier\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>90%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>+20% fee\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Maximum Tier\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>100%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Available via Trade2Earn\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003C/tbody>\u003C/table>\n\u003Cp>Withdrawals are processed via bank transfer or cryptocurrency, with no minimum withdrawal amount.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"trade2earn-loyalty-program\">Trade2Earn Loyalty Program\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>The Trade2Earn program is a unique feature of the prop firm where you can earn BrightFunded Tokens for every trade, which can be redeemed for:\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>Free evaluations (skip paying for challenges!)\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>Higher profit splits (up to 100%)\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>Lower drawdown limits for more trading flexibility\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>Discounts on challenge fees up to 50%\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Cp>This program makes BrightFunded even more rewarding for prop traders who stay active and consistent.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"markets-and-leverage-2\">Markets and Leverage\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>BrightFunded provides you access to 49 forex pairs, commodities, indices, and 35 cryptocurrencies. Leverage is flexible, with forex at 1:100, commodities at 1:40, and crypto at 1:5.\u003C/p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003Ctable>\u003Cthead>\u003Ctr>\u003Cth>Market Type\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Instruments\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Leverage\u003C/th>\u003C/tr>\u003C/thead>\u003Ctbody>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Forex\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>49 currency pairs\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Up to 1:100\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Commodities\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Gold, Silver, WTI, UK Oil\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Up to 1:40\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Indices\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>ASX 200, DAX 30, FTSE 100\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Up to 1:20\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Crypto\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>BTC, ETH, SOL, THORChain\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Up to 1:5\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003C/tbody>\u003C/table>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"trading-platforms-1\">Trading Platforms\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>One of BrightFunded’s biggest upgrades in 2026 was adding MetaTrader 5 (MT5) to its lineup, giving traders a choice of three platforms: MT5, cTrader, and DXtrade. Each works across desktop, web, and mobile, and all run on BrightFunded’s simulated environment with real market data.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>MT5\u003C/strong> is the go to for traders who want reliability and automation. It supports Expert Advisors, custom indicators, and advanced charting, and will be ideal if you’re already running strategies on MT4 or MT5 and want to plug straight into prop trading.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>cTrader\u003C/strong> is the performance driven option for more advanced traders, known for its clean interface, fast execution, and Depth of Market tools. It’s especially popular with scalpers, algo traders, and anyone who wants full control over order flow and automation in C#.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>DXtrade\u003C/strong> rounds out the lineup as a flexible choice for discretionary traders. It has built-in risk controls and a layout you can adjust to your own workflow, but we found it less polished than MT5 or cTrader.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"trust-and-community-2\">Trust and Community\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>BrightFunded holds a 4.7/5 TrustPilot rating, with traders praising its fast payouts and transparent rules.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>The prop firm has an active Discord community with over 16,000 members, offering trade ideas, market insights, and direct support from the BrightFunded team.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"our-final-verdict-on-brightfunded\">Our Final Verdict on BrightFunded\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>BrightFunded’s scaling plan, loyalty program, and flexible trading model make it a strong choice for traders focused on long term growth and high profit splits. If you’re looking for a prop firm that rewards consistency and active trading, BrightFunded is one of the best options out there.\u003C/p>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"4-dna-funded--low-commission-fees\">4. DNA Funded — Low Commission Fees\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>DNA Funded is the fourth best forex prop firm with a score of 97/100 plus low commission fees, a wide range of tradable forex pairs, and fast payouts. With challenges starting at $49, it’s one of the more affordable ways to get funded. The optional add-ons let you increase profit splits or shorten withdrawal times, giving you extra flexibility.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Use promo code PROPFIRMS25 to get 25% off your challenge fee, so you can start trading for less.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/dna-funded-logo.png\" alt=\"DNA Funded logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">DNA Funded\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">Low Commission Fees\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">90%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Max DD\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">10%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Trustpilot\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">4.9 \u003Cspan class=\"text-amber-500\">★\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Ca href=\"/reviews/dna-funded\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-lg bg-teal-500 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-white hover:bg-teal-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n        Full Review →\n      \u003C/a>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose -mt-3 mb-6 rounded-xl border border-emerald-200 bg-emerald-50/80 px-5 py-3 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-3\">\n  \u003Ca href=\"https://partners.dnafunded.com/click?campaign_id=1&#x26;ref_id=30\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-emerald-500 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-emerald-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n    Visit DNA Funded\n  \u003C/a>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2.5\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4 text-emerald-600 flex-shrink-0\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M7 7h.01M7 3h5c.512 0 1.024.195 1.414.586l7 7a2 2 0 010 2.828l-7 7a2 2 0 01-2.828 0l-7-7A1.994 1.994 0 013 12V7a4 4 0 014-4z\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm text-emerald-700 font-semibold\">25% Off — Code:\u003C/span>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"font-mono font-bold text-xs bg-white border border-dashed border-emerald-300 px-3 py-1.5 rounded text-emerald-700 tracking-wide select-all\">PROPFIRMS25\u003C/span>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Pros &#x26; Cons\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Pros\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Up to 90% profit split\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>TradingView integration\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Over 800 financial markets\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>No crypto trading on Pro challenge\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Higher drawdown requirements for Double Helix\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Limited customer support initially\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"prop-firm-details-3\">Prop Firm Details\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Ranked as the third best forex prop firm overall, DNA Funded stands out for its low fees, range of account types, wide market access, and strong partnership with DNA Markets.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>With a solid overall score of 97/100, DNA Funded offers three challenge types with account sizes up to $200,000 and maximum leverage of 50:1 on forex pairs.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"challenges-and-accounts-2\">Challenges and Accounts\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>DNA Funded is designed to be competitive, with some of the lowest fees in the prop trading industry, starting from just $49.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>The prop firm offers three challenge types to suit different trading styles and goals:\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>Single Helix (1 Step):\u003C/strong> Simple challenge with a 10% profit target and unlimited trading days. Add-ons are available for an early payout, reducing the standard 14-day payout period to just 7 days.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>Double Helix (2 Step):\u003C/strong> Two-step evaluation with a 10% profit target in Phase 1 and a reduced 5% target in Phase 2. Add-ons allow traders to increase the profit split from 80% to 90%, providing higher potential earnings.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>Rapid Challenge (1 Step):\u003C/strong> Fast-paced challenge requiring a 5% profit target within 10 days, suited for high-frequency traders. Add-ons here include both a faster payout option and an increased profit split to 90%.\u003C/p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003Ctable>\u003Cthead>\u003Ctr>\u003Cth>Attribute\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Single Helix\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Double Helix\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Rapid Challenge\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Instant Funding\u003C/th>\u003C/tr>\u003C/thead>\u003Ctbody>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Evaluation Process\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1 Step\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>2 Step\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1 Step\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>None (Instant Access)\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>One-Off Fee\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$59 - $1,209\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$49 – $1,079\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$99 – $549\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$199 – $979\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Account Sizes\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$5,000 - $200,000\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$5,000 – $200,000\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$10,000 – $100,000\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$5,000 – $50,000\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Fee for Add-Ons\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>20%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>20%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>30%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>NA\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Add-On Options\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Early Payout\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Higher Profit Split\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Early Payout + Higher Profit Split\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Early Payout + Higher Profit Split\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Profit Share\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>80%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>80%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>80%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>80%\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Profit Target\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>10%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>10%, then 5%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>5%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>NA\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Max Daily Drawdown\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>5%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>6%, then 5%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>4%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>4% (Trailing)\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Max Total Drawdown\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>10%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>10%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>5%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>4% (Trailing)\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Max Active Trading Days\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Unlimited\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Unlimited\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>10 Calendar Days\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>NA\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Crypto Trading Allowed\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Yes\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Yes\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>No\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Yes\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003C/tbody>\u003C/table>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"profit-splits-and-payouts-3\">Profit Splits and Payouts\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>DNA Funded offers a profit split starting at 80%, with an option to increase it to 90% through an add-on. Flexible payout options are available to funded traders, with a standard 14-day payout cycle, and an add-on to enable weekly (7-day) payouts.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Evaluation Fee Refund:\u003C/strong> Traders receive their initial challenge fee back after their first profit withdrawal.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Minimum Withdrawal Thresholds:\u003C/strong> A $20 minimum is required for bank transfers, while crypto payouts require $150.\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Cp>Additionally, DNA Funded recently started enforcing a 40% daily profit cap. This rule limits you to earning a maximum of 40% of your total payout target from any one trading day. If you exceed this cap, any additional profits made that day will not count toward your payout eligibility until the following day. This policy aligns with DNA Funded’s broker-backed model and supports more stable and sustainable trading behaviours.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"markets-and-leverage-3\">Markets and Leverage\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>DNA Funded gives traders access to over 800 financial instruments, with a strong focus on forex:\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Forex Pairs:\u003C/strong> 66 currency pairs, including major, minor, and exotic pairs, allowing for diverse forex trading opportunities.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Commodities:\u003C/strong> Gold, Silver, Brent, and Crude Oil, with leverage options supporting flexible trading.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Indices:\u003C/strong> 25 major global indices, providing exposure to global stock market performance.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Stocks:\u003C/strong> Select stocks from global markets, giving traders added options in equity trading.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Cryptocurrencies:\u003C/strong> Limited crypto options like BTC/USD and ETH/USD, available for the Single Helix and Double Helix challenges only.\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Cp>Leverage varies by market to help manage risk.\u003C/p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003Ctable>\u003Cthead>\u003Ctr>\u003Cth>Market\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Leverage\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Example Instruments\u003C/th>\u003C/tr>\u003C/thead>\u003Ctbody>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Forex\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Up to 50:1\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>EUR/USD, GBP/USD, USD/JPY\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Commodities\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Up to 10:1\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Gold, Silver, Brent Oil, Crude Oil\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Indices\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Up to 10:1\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>AUS200, US500, UK100, DE40\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Stocks\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Up to 5:1\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Selected stocks from global exchanges\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Cryptocurrencies\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Up to 1:2\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>BTC/USD, ETH/USD (Single Helix &#x26; Double Helix only)\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003C/tbody>\u003C/table>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"trading-platforms-2\">Trading Platforms\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>DNA Funded provides access to one trading platform, TradeLocker integrated with TradingView. The platform is highly customisable, offering advanced charting and risk management tools, ideal for manual traders.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"trust-and-community-3\">Trust and Community\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>As a new prop trading firm, DNA Funded partners with the reputable DNA Markets, an ASIC regulated broker known for reliable spreads and execution speeds. DNA Markets holds a TrustPilot rating of 3.9/5, which boosts DNA Funded’s credibility.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>DNA Funded has initiated a private Discord server to build a secure trading community, where traders can interact, share insights, and receive support.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"support-and-education-1\">Support and Education\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>DNA Funded currently offers customer support via email. Educational resources are expected to grow and may include webinars, tutorials, and a comprehensive FAQ section in the future.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Customer Support:\u003C/strong> Limited to email initially\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Educational Resources:\u003C/strong> Light educational resources currently available, with plans to expand to a full learning portal.\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"our-final-verdict-on-dna-funded\">Our Final Verdict on DNA Funded\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>DNA Funded is a strong choice for traders seeking flexible challenges with low fees. Ranking as the second-best prop firm for forex traders with a score of 97/100, it provides competitive spreads, accessible payout options, and reliable trading through DNA Markets.\u003C/p>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"5-blueberry-funded--scaling-to-2-million\">5. Blueberry Funded — Scaling to $2 million\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>Blueberry Funded is the 5th best forex prop firm in 2026, earning a score of 93/100 for its clear scaling plan, low fees, and solid forex trading conditions.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>The scaling model increases your funded account by 25% every 3 months, up to $2 million, if you achieve 10% profit and make four withdrawals. You can trade 45 forex pairs with raw spreads from 0.1 pips and up to 1:50 leverage.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Use promo code PROPFIRMS20 to get 20% off your challenge fee.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/blueberry-funded-logo.png\" alt=\"Blueberry Funded logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">Blueberry Funded\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">Scaling to $2 million\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">90%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Max DD\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">10%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Trustpilot\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">3.8 \u003Cspan class=\"text-amber-500\">★\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Ca href=\"/reviews/blueberry-funded\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-lg bg-teal-500 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-white hover:bg-teal-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n        Full Review →\n      \u003C/a>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose -mt-3 mb-6 rounded-xl border border-emerald-200 bg-emerald-50/80 px-5 py-3 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-3\">\n  \u003Ca href=\"https://blueberryfunded.com/?utm_source=affiliate&#x26;ref=1457\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-emerald-500 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-emerald-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n    Visit Blueberry Funded\n  \u003C/a>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2.5\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4 text-emerald-600 flex-shrink-0\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M7 7h.01M7 3h5c.512 0 1.024.195 1.414.586l7 7a2 2 0 010 2.828l-7 7a2 2 0 01-2.828 0l-7-7A1.994 1.994 0 013 12V7a4 4 0 014-4z\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm text-emerald-700 font-semibold\">20% Off — Code:\u003C/span>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"font-mono font-bold text-xs bg-white border border-dashed border-emerald-300 px-3 py-1.5 rounded text-emerald-700 tracking-wide select-all\">PROPFIRMS20\u003C/span>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Pros &#x26; Cons\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Pros\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Rapid Challenge with a 7-day evaluation\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Access to 1,100+ financial instruments\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Strong forex trading community support\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Limited educational resources\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>14-day payout cycle, which may not suit all\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Limited payment options for challenge fees\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"prop-firm-details-4\">Prop Firm Details\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Blueberry Funded is one of the best forex prop firms for traders who want to scale capital as they grow.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>The prop firm’s structured scaling plan increases your funded account by 25% every 3 months, up to a $2 million cap, if you hit 10% profit and complete four payouts. The rules are clearly defined, and your trading conditions stay the same as you scale.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"challenges-and-accounts-3\">Challenges and Accounts\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Blueberry Funded offers four evaluation models, and three out of four are built for forex and CFD prop trading. You can choose a challenge based on your trading speed, style, and risk preference.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>One Step Challenge:\u003C/strong> No time limit, 10% profit target, and static 6% max drawdown.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>Two Step Challenge:\u003C/strong> Two phases with 10% and 5% targets, and higher leverage (1:50) for forex trading.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>Rapid Challenge:\u003C/strong> 7-day evaluation, 5% profit target, trailing drawdown, and no minimum trading days.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>Stock Challenge:\u003C/strong> Two-phase evaluation with over 1,000 US stocks. Only available for equity traders.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"profit-splits-and-payouts-4\">Profit Splits and Payouts\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Blueberry Funded starts all traders at an 80% profit split, with the option to upgrade to 90% as you scale. Payouts are available every 14 days, with a low $100 minimum and no open trades required. Profits are withdrawn through RiseWorks, with options including crypto (USDT, USDC) and bank transfer. The initial challenge fee is fully refunded after your first successful withdrawal.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"markets-and-leverage-4\">Markets and Leverage\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Blueberry Funded gives you access to a wide range of forex and CFD markets, with consistent leverage rules and low-cost trading across all challenge types.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Here’s what you can trade:\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Forex:\u003C/strong> 45 pairs, including majors and exotics. Leverage up to 1:50 (2 Step), or 1:30 (1 Step, Rapid).\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Indices:\u003C/strong> 14 global indices like US30 and GER30, capped at 1:10 leverage.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Commodities:\u003C/strong> 17 instruments including gold and oil, with 1:10 leverage.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Crypto:\u003C/strong> 52 pairs including BTC, ETH, ADA. 1:2 leverage, available on 1 Step and Rapid only.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Stocks:\u003C/strong> 1,000+ US stocks, exclusive to the Stock Challenge.\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"trading-platforms-3\">Trading Platforms\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Blueberry Funded supports four trading platforms, MT4, MT5, DXTrade, and TradeLocker, allowing you to select one that best fits your style.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>MetaTrader 4 (MT4):\u003C/strong> Known for reliability and customisable EAs, making it a popular choice for forex traders.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>MetaTrader 5 (MT5):\u003C/strong> Offers more order types and indicators than MT4, with enhanced charting for advanced traders.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>DXTrade:\u003C/strong> A browser-based option with a flexible layout, though it may experience performance issues during high trading volumes.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>TradeLocker:\u003C/strong> A clean, mobile-friendly web platform built for fast execution. Offers real-time monitoring, drag-and-drop orders, and easy charting without needing to install software.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"trust-and-community-4\">Trust and Community\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Blueberry Funded is backed by Blueberry Markets, a regulated forex broker licensed by ASIC. In 2025, it became a founding member of The Prop Association (TPA), which promotes transparency and trader protection.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>With over 27,000 Discord members, active support channels, and verified payouts, Blueberry has a growing reputation for reliability and fairness in the prop space.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"support-and-education-2\">Support and Education\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>You get access to 24/5 support via live chat and email, with responses typically under one business day. Educational content is limited, but an active Discord community fills the gap with peer guidance, trading tips, and support from staff. While their YouTube content is minimal, the platform experience and helpdesk coverage are strong.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"our-final-verdict-on-blueberry-funded\">Our Final Verdict on Blueberry Funded\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Blueberry Funded is a smart pick if you’re a forex trader looking to scale over time without changing your trading style. The combination of clear rules, low fees, and a defined path to $2 million in simulated capital makes it one of the most scalable prop firms in the market.\u003C/p>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"how-we-shortlisted-the-best-forex-prop-firms\">How We Shortlisted The Best Forex Prop Firms\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>When selecting the best forex prop trading firm, we consider several factors that will directly impact your experience as a prop trader, as well as earnings potential and success in the program:\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Prop Challenges:\u003C/strong> When we review prop firms, we look at the flexibility, clarity, and cost of the firm’s evaluation challenges. Prop firms that offer varied options such as one-step or two-step challenges, achievable profit targets, and flexible drawdown limits are often more accessible to a broader range of traders. Low one-time fees and clear policies are also good signs.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Spreads and Commission Fees:\u003C/strong> Low spreads and commission fees are crucial, and prop firms with transparent pricing and low trading costs are ranked better.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Financial Markets and Leverage:\u003C/strong> Prop firms offering a good range of forex CFDs and higher leverage from 50:1 to 100:1 score better during our assessments. A firm with broader market access lets traders diversify and better manage their risk.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Trading Platform Options:\u003C/strong> Prop firms supporting major trading platforms like MT4, MT5, and cTrader, as well as advanced charting, order types, and mobile compatibility are especially valuable for traders aiming to trade forex on the go.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Profit Payout Structure:\u003C/strong> The best prop firms offer fast payouts, high-profit splits (typically above 80%), and low minimum withdrawal amounts.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Customer Support and Education:\u003C/strong> A strong support network with 24/7 availability, live chat, and comprehensive educational resources can significantly enhance the trading experience, as well as strong educational resources like webinars and trading tutorials.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Trust and Community:\u003C/strong> Positive Trustpilot scores and reviews, transparency in policies, and an active trading community (e.g., on platforms like Discord) build trust and foster a collaborative environment, which can be valuable for trader engagement and shared learning.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Account Opening:\u003C/strong> A straightforward sign-up process and efficient onboarding lets traders access demo or live accounts quickly, enabling you to focus on your trading goals with minimal delay.\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Cp>Overall, forex prop trading firms offer an accessible way for traders to gain capital, trade forex and CFDs, and work within a structured, supportive environment.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Our list of the 10 best forex prop trading firms provides various account balance options, from smaller starter accounts to large scale funding for experienced traders, catering to those seeking to develop and profit from their trading skills. Prop firms that offer forex trading, but scored low during testing (ie E8 Markets and AquaFunded), didn’t make the cut.\u003C/p>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"how-we-selected-the-best-forex-prop-firms-for-2026\">How We Selected the Best Forex Prop Firms for 2026\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>We selected the best forex prop trading firms by following our methodology that involves giving each firm a score out of 10 across eight core criteria. We look first at challenge structure, evaluating how accessible and varied each firm’s programs are, including funding steps, drawdown limits, and profit targets. We rank each prop firms account options to assess competitiveness and value for money.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Next, we assess trading costs, covering forex spreads and commission fees to ensure competitive pricing. Market range and leverage is another essential factor, highlighting prop firms that support diverse trading strategies with options across forex, commodities, indices, and cryptocurrencies.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Trading platform quality is central, with preference given to firms that offer multiple tools, like MT4, MT5, or cTrader, supporting different trading styles. Profit payout structures are also a priority, focusing on payout frequency, profit splits, and withdrawal minimums to determine how well firms accommodate steady earnings.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Customer support and education are important for a smooth trading experience, with higher ratings for firms that offer accessible help and practical learning resources. We also look closely at trust and community, noting positive TrustPilot scores, strong Discord servers, and transparent policies as indicators of reliability.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Finally, a streamlined sign-up process that allows quick access to evaluation programs and easy payment methods also plays a role.\u003C/p>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"what-are-forex-prop-trading-firms\">What are forex prop trading firms?\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>Forex prop trading firms give forex traders the opportunity to trade with substantial capital provided by the firm rather than relying on their own funds. These firms evaluate traders through structured challenges or assessments to gauge their skill level, consistency, and risk management.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Traders who meet these requirements earn access to funded live accounts, allowing them to trade forex with a higher account balance than they might otherwise afford. Profits generated on these accounts are shared between the trader and the firm, making it possible for traders to earn from forex trading without risking more than the initial challenge fee.\u003C/p>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"how-do-forex-prop-firms-work\">How do forex prop firms work?\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>Forex prop trading firms offer traders a pathway to access greater capital for forex markets, beginning with an evaluation phase. In this phase, you partake in a challenge where you are aiming to meet specific performance targets and risk management requirements, such as a 10% profit target with daily and overall drawdown limits of 5% and 10%. Success in this evaluation phase demonstrates your skills and risk management ability, qualifying you for a funded account backed by the prop firm’s capital.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Once you reach the funded trader stage, you receive a profit share, typically between 80-90%, while the firm retains a smaller share. To encourage ongoing success, prop trading firms often conduct regular assessments and may offer scaling plans, allowing you to grow your capital as you demonstrate consistent, profitable trading performance.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>This model provides a structured, low-risk way for forex traders to access significant capital without risking personal funds, aside from any initial evaluation fees. You can read the full forex prop trading guide for more information about the types of forex prop firms, the best trading strategies, and so on.\u003C/p>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"faqs\">FAQs\u003C/h2>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"which-prop-firm-is-best-for-forex\">Which prop firm is best for forex?\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>FundedNext is considered the best prop trading firm for forex due to its competitive spreads, high profit splits, and diverse account options. It offers leverage up to 1:100 and a choice between two-phase and instant funding models, making it accessible for different trading styles. FundedNext’s challenge structure provides a balanced mix of realistic evaluation targets and trader-friendly conditions.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"what-are-proprietary-trading-firms\">What are proprietary trading firms?\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Proprietary trading firms, aka prop firms, provide traders with access to capital, allowing them to trade financial markets without risking personal funds. Forex prop firms evaluate CFD traders through challenge programs, assessing skills in managing risk and meeting profit targets. Successful traders gain funded accounts, sharing a percentage of their profits with the firm.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"which-prop-firm-has-the-best-trading-conditions\">Which prop firm has the best trading conditions?\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>IC Funded and DNA Funded are two of the cheapest prop firms with the best trading conditions for forex traders. IC Funded’s partnership with IC Markets allows it to offer spreads from 0 pips and leverage up to 50:1, making it a strong choice for those prioritising low trading costs.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>DNA Funded also offers low fees, up to 90% profit split, and flexible account types. Both firms suit a variety of trading styles and budgets.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"which-prop-firm-has-the-highest-leverage\">Which prop firm has the highest leverage?\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>FundedNext offers leverage up to 100:1 on forex pairs, giving traders strong high-exposure potential. For commodities and indices, a leverage cap of 50:1 is common among top prop firms. As with CFD trading, make sure you employ solid risk management strategies when participating in prop challenges.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"which-prop-firm-is-better-than-ftmo\">Which prop firm is better than FTMO?\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>IC Funded, DNA Funded, and Blueberry Funded are some of the best prop firms and much better than FTMO. IC Funded provides ultra-low spreads through its partnership with IC Markets, while DNA Funded is known for its low fees and high profit splits of up to 90%, with various flexible challenges.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Lastly, Blueberry Funded Rapid Challenge is one of the fastest evaluation processes in the industry, enabling traders to achieve funding within 7 days.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"how-do-prop-challenges-work\">How do prop challenges work?\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Prop trading firms use challenges to evaluate traders before granting access to funded accounts. These challenges typically require you to meet profit targets while adhering to risk management rules, such as drawdown limits and maximum loss thresholds. Most firms offer one-step or two-step evaluations, with structured guidelines on trading performance. To learn more about the process, visit our guide on how challenges work.\u003C/p>",{"headings":5471,"localImagePaths":5588,"remoteImagePaths":5589,"frontmatter":5590,"imagePaths":5601},[5472,5475,5478,5481,5482,5485,5488,5489,5490,5491,5494,5497,5500,5501,5503,5505,5506,5509,5510,5513,5516,5517,5519,5522,5523,5524,5525,5528,5531,5532,5534,5536,5537,5538,5539,5541,5544,5547,5548,5550,5552,5553,5554,5555,5557,5560,5563,5566,5569,5572,5573,5576,5578,5581,5584,5585],{"depth":879,"slug":5473,"text":5474},"what-are-the-best-forex-funded-accounts","What Are The Best Forex Funded Accounts?",{"depth":879,"slug":5476,"text":5477},"the-10-best-forex-prop-firms-we-tested-in-2026","The 10 Best Forex Prop Firms We Tested in 2026",{"depth":879,"slug":5479,"text":5480},"1-fundednext--best-forex-prop-firm-overall","1. FundedNext — Best Forex Prop Firm Overall",{"depth":158,"slug":5218,"text":5219},{"depth":158,"slug":5483,"text":5484},"challenges-and-accounts","Challenges and Accounts",{"depth":158,"slug":5486,"text":5487},"profit-splits-and-payouts","Profit Splits and Payouts",{"depth":158,"slug":4841,"text":4842},{"depth":158,"slug":4844,"text":4845},{"depth":158,"slug":4847,"text":4848},{"depth":158,"slug":5492,"text":5493},"support-and-education","Support and Education",{"depth":158,"slug":5495,"text":5496},"our-final-verdict-on-fundednext","Our Final Verdict on FundedNext",{"depth":879,"slug":5498,"text":5499},"2-eightcap-challenges--day-trading-forex-challenge","2. Eightcap Challenges — Day Trading Forex Challenge",{"depth":158,"slug":5235,"text":5219},{"depth":158,"slug":5502,"text":5484},"challenges-and-accounts-1",{"depth":158,"slug":5504,"text":5487},"profit-splits-and-payouts-1",{"depth":158,"slug":4862,"text":4842},{"depth":158,"slug":5507,"text":5508},"trading-platforms-and-rules","Trading Platforms and Rules",{"depth":158,"slug":4869,"text":4848},{"depth":158,"slug":5511,"text":5512},"our-final-verdict-on-eightcap-challenges","Our Final Verdict on Eightcap Challenges",{"depth":879,"slug":5514,"text":5515},"3-brightfunded--loyalty-program-for-prop-traders","3. BrightFunded — Loyalty Program for Prop Traders",{"depth":158,"slug":5248,"text":5219},{"depth":158,"slug":5518,"text":5487},"profit-splits-and-payouts-2",{"depth":158,"slug":5520,"text":5521},"trade2earn-loyalty-program","Trade2Earn Loyalty Program",{"depth":158,"slug":4882,"text":4842},{"depth":158,"slug":4864,"text":4845},{"depth":158,"slug":4886,"text":4848},{"depth":158,"slug":5526,"text":5527},"our-final-verdict-on-brightfunded","Our Final Verdict on BrightFunded",{"depth":879,"slug":5529,"text":5530},"4-dna-funded--low-commission-fees","4. DNA Funded — Low Commission Fees",{"depth":158,"slug":5261,"text":5219},{"depth":158,"slug":5533,"text":5484},"challenges-and-accounts-2",{"depth":158,"slug":5535,"text":5487},"profit-splits-and-payouts-3",{"depth":158,"slug":4899,"text":4842},{"depth":158,"slug":4884,"text":4845},{"depth":158,"slug":4901,"text":4848},{"depth":158,"slug":5540,"text":5493},"support-and-education-1",{"depth":158,"slug":5542,"text":5543},"our-final-verdict-on-dna-funded","Our Final Verdict on DNA Funded",{"depth":879,"slug":5545,"text":5546},"5-blueberry-funded--scaling-to-2-million","5. Blueberry Funded — Scaling to $2 million",{"depth":158,"slug":5274,"text":5219},{"depth":158,"slug":5549,"text":5484},"challenges-and-accounts-3",{"depth":158,"slug":5551,"text":5487},"profit-splits-and-payouts-4",{"depth":158,"slug":4914,"text":4842},{"depth":158,"slug":4916,"text":4845},{"depth":158,"slug":4918,"text":4848},{"depth":158,"slug":5556,"text":5493},"support-and-education-2",{"depth":158,"slug":5558,"text":5559},"our-final-verdict-on-blueberry-funded","Our Final Verdict on Blueberry Funded",{"depth":879,"slug":5561,"text":5562},"how-we-shortlisted-the-best-forex-prop-firms","How We Shortlisted The Best Forex Prop Firms",{"depth":879,"slug":5564,"text":5565},"how-we-selected-the-best-forex-prop-firms-for-2026","How We Selected the Best Forex Prop Firms for 2026",{"depth":879,"slug":5567,"text":5568},"what-are-forex-prop-trading-firms","What are forex prop trading firms?",{"depth":879,"slug":5570,"text":5571},"how-do-forex-prop-firms-work","How do forex prop firms work?",{"depth":879,"slug":4935,"text":4936},{"depth":158,"slug":5574,"text":5575},"which-prop-firm-is-best-for-forex","Which prop firm is best for forex?",{"depth":158,"slug":5577,"text":3495},"what-are-proprietary-trading-firms",{"depth":158,"slug":5579,"text":5580},"which-prop-firm-has-the-best-trading-conditions","Which prop firm has the best trading conditions?",{"depth":158,"slug":5582,"text":5583},"which-prop-firm-has-the-highest-leverage","Which prop firm has the highest leverage?",{"depth":158,"slug":4955,"text":4956},{"depth":158,"slug":5586,"text":5587},"how-do-prop-challenges-work","How do prop challenges work?",[],[],{"title":5444,"excerpt":5445,"category":5171,"tags":5591,"author":4798,"authorImage":4799,"publishedAt":1273,"featured":110,"readingTimeMinutes":1764,"youtubeVideoId":4800,"featuredFirms":5592},[4795,5173,4796,5447],[5593,5594,5595,5596,5597,5598,5599,5600],{"slug":1392,"descriptor":5450},{"slug":932,"descriptor":5452},{"slug":584,"descriptor":5454},{"slug":728,"descriptor":5456},{"slug":332,"descriptor":5458},{"slug":1599,"descriptor":5460},{"slug":1002,"descriptor":5462},{"slug":1278,"descriptor":5464},[],"forex.md","funded-trading-accounts",{"id":5603,"data":5605,"body":5632,"filePath":5633,"digest":5634,"rendered":5635,"legacyId":5780},{"title":5606,"excerpt":5607,"category":5171,"tags":5608,"coverImage":5612,"author":4798,"authorImage":4799,"publishedAt":240,"featured":110,"readingTimeMinutes":405,"youtubeVideoId":4800,"featuredFirms":5613},"Best Funded Trading Accounts (Verified Testing 2026)","We've reviewed the top funded trading accounts to compare profit splits, scaling opportunities, and challenge rules. This guide highlights the best proprietary trading firms and funded accounts for traders seeking capital growth, loyalty rewards, and fair evaluation processes.",[4796,5173,5609,5610,5611],"prop trading","funded trading","scaling","/images/blog/funded.png",[5614,5616,5618,5620,5622,5624,5626,5628,5630],{"slug":1392,"descriptor":5615},"Best Funded Account Overall",{"slug":584,"descriptor":5617},"Best Trader Loyalty Program",{"slug":1599,"descriptor":5619},"Scaling Plan to $4 Million",{"slug":332,"descriptor":5621},"Broker Backed Funded Accounts",{"slug":642,"descriptor":5623},"Prop Firm Paying Trader Salaries",{"slug":1002,"descriptor":5625},"Best Funded Account for Stocks",{"slug":4813,"descriptor":5627},"High Leverage Funded Accounts",{"slug":1917,"descriptor":5629},"Funded Accounts with Low Spreads",{"slug":2507,"descriptor":5631},"Up to 100% Profit Split","## Which Prop Firms Have the Best Funded Accounts?\n\nThe best funded accounts provide high profit splits of 80% or more, scalable account options for consistent traders, and loyalty programs that reward activity with perks like higher payouts or reduced fees. Fast and reliable payouts, combined with flexible trading rules, make these the best funded trading accounts for long-term growth.\n\nWe reviewed the best funded accounts offered by top prop firms:\n\n1. **FundedNext** — Best Funded Account Overall\n2. **BrightFunded** — Best Trader Loyalty Program\n3. **FXIFY** — Scaling Plan to $4 Million\n4. **Blueberry Funded** — Broker Backed Funded Accounts\n5. **City Traders Imperium** — Prop Firm Paying Trader Salaries\n6. **FTMO** — Best Funded Account for Stocks\n7. **ThinkCapital** — High Leverage Funded Accounts\n8. **IC Funded** — Funded Accounts with Low Spreads\n9. **The 5%ers** — Up to 100% Profit Split\n\n---\n\n## The 9 Best Funded Trading Accounts We Tested in 2026\n\n---\n\n## 1. FundedNext — Best Funded Account Overall\n\nFundedNext takes the top spot with flexible models, low-cost challenge options, and the ability to earn up to 95% profit split. Traders can choose from multiple evaluation styles — including the fast-track Stellar One Step, standard two-phase Evaluation, and budget-friendly Stellar Lite — with funded accounts from $5,000 to $200,000. With the ability to scale accounts to $4 million, it's designed for long-term growth.\n\nUse code PROPFIRMS for a 120% refund — 100% of your challenge fee back plus 20% extra as a bonus once funded.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/fundednext.png\" alt=\"FundedNext logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\" />\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">FundedNext\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">Best Funded Account Overall\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">95%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Max DD\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">10%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Trustpilot\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">4.5 \u003Cspan class=\"text-amber-500\">★\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Ca href=\"/reviews/fundednext\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-lg bg-teal-500 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-white hover:bg-teal-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n        Full Review →\n      \u003C/a>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose -mt-3 mb-6 rounded-xl border border-emerald-200 bg-emerald-50/80 px-5 py-3 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-3\">\n  \u003Ca href=\"https://fundednext.com/?fpr=noam82\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-emerald-500 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-emerald-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14\" />\u003C/svg>\n    Visit FundedNext\n  \u003C/a>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2.5\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4 text-emerald-600 flex-shrink-0\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M7 7h.01M7 3h5c.512 0 1.024.195 1.414.586l7 7a2 2 0 010 2.828l-7 7a2 2 0 01-2.828 0l-7-7A1.994 1.994 0 013 12V7a4 4 0 014-4z\" />\u003C/svg>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm text-emerald-700 font-semibold\">120% Refund — Code:\u003C/span>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"font-mono font-bold text-xs bg-white border border-dashed border-emerald-300 px-3 py-1.5 rounded text-emerald-700 tracking-wide select-all\">PROPFIRMS\u003C/span>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Pros & Cons\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Pros\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Profit splits up to 95% with clear scaling criteria\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>MT4, MT5, cTrader, and Match-Trader\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Scaling plan and 120% refund on challenge fees\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Strict loss limits\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>No access to stocks\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Scaling caps\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n### Prop Firm Details\n\nFundedNext runs exclusively on three models: Stellar One Step, Stellar Two Step, and Stellar Lite. All options offer 95% profit splits once funded, with flexible rules and no time limits. Funded accounts start at $5,000 and scale up to $200,000, with maximum capital allocation capped at $4 million through their scale-up program.\n\n| Feature | Details |\n|---------|---------|\n| Profit Split | Up to 95% |\n| Account Sizes | $5,000 – $200,000 |\n| Scaling Plan | Up to $4 million |\n| Platforms | MT4, MT5, cTrader, Match-Trader |\n| Payout Schedule | Bi-weekly (5 days for 1-Step) |\n| Challenge Fee (from) | $32 |\n\n### Funded Trading Accounts\n\nWith FundedNext, you don't have to wait to start earning — traders on the Stellar One Step and Two Step models get a 15% profit share during the challenge phase. Once funded, payouts can start as early as five business days for Stellar One Step accounts, while Stellar Lite accounts unlock bi-weekly withdrawals.\n\nDrawdown limits vary by model, ranging from 3% to 5% daily and 6% to 10% overall, giving you some breathing room while keeping risk in check. Leverage is capped at 30:1 for the One Step, but jumps to 100:1 for Stellar Two Step and Lite, which is ideal if you prefer more flexibility.\n\nExpert Advisors (EAs) are also permitted on MT4 and MT5 — great if you rely on automation or advanced strategies.\n\n### Scaling Plan\n\nFundedNext scales your account by 40% every four months if you:\n\n- Grow the account by 10%\n- Complete two successful withdrawals\n- Finish the final cycle in profit\n\nThis continues up to a max of $4 million. So a $100K account could scale to $140K in 4 months, $196K in 8 months, and so on.\n\n### How to Become a FundedNext Trader?\n\nFundedNext offers three challenge models, each designed to suit a different type of trader.\n\n**Stellar One Step** is ideal if you want to skip the long evaluation and get funded fast. It's a single-phase challenge with moderate risk limits and a 15% profit share from the moment you start.\n\n**Stellar Two Step** is better suited for consistent traders who prefer a more structured path. The two-phase format gives you more flexibility on risk and strategy, while still offering a profit share during the challenge.\n\n**Stellar Lite** is the most affordable option, designed for traders starting out or testing the waters. It has tighter drawdowns, no payouts during the challenge, and smaller account sizes — but it's a solid choice if you want lower upfront fees and still access a 95% split once funded.\n\nYou can customise your evaluation by adding the following (fees are percentage-based and applied to the base challenge fee):\n\n- **Lifetime 95% Payout (+30%):** Lock in the full 95% profit split from day one, even before scaling.\n- **Double Up (+40%):** Automatically double your funded account size upon successful challenge completion.\n- **No Minimum Trading Days (+20%):** Remove the minimum trading day requirement.\n- **10% Overall Loss Limit (+25%):** Increases the drawdown buffer for Stellar Lite accounts only.\n- **Bi-Weekly Payouts (+15%):** Unlock faster payout schedules.\n- **Swap-Free Account (+10%):** Removes overnight swap fees across all account types and sizes. Ideal for traders following religious or swing-trading strategies.\n\n### Final Verdict\n\nFundedNext ranks as the best funded account overall for traders wanting fast access to capital, strong earning potential, and flexible rules. With options for low-cost entry, fast withdrawals, and challenge-phase payouts, it's suited for serious traders focused on consistent growth.\n\n---\n\n## 2. BrightFunded — Best Trader Loyalty Program\n\nBrightFunded earnt the second spot on our shortlist for its challenge customisation, unlimited scaling plan, and unique Trade2Earn loyalty program which rewards you with practical perks like free evaluations and higher profit splits. With profit shares up to 100%, fast payouts, and 24/7 support, BrightFunded is a top prop firm if you are looking to grow your account over the long term and be rewarded for your trading activity along the way.\n\nUse promo code PROPFIRMS20 for a 20% discount!\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/brightfunded-logo.png\" alt=\"BrightFunded logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\" />\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">BrightFunded\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">Best Trader Loyalty Program\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class