2V7a4 4 0 014-4z\" />\u003C/svg>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm text-emerald-700 font-semibold\">20% Off — Code:\u003C/span>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"font-mono font-bold text-xs bg-white border border-dashed border-emerald-300 px-3 py-1.5 rounded text-emerald-700 tracking-wide select-all\">PROPFIRMS20\u003C/span>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Pros & Cons\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Pros\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Unlimited scaling potential\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Profit splits up to 100%\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Trade2Earn loyalty program rewards traders\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Higher fees for optional add-ons\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>MetaTrader 5 but not MT4\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Payouts only in USD or crypto\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n### Prop Firm Details\n\nBrightFunded takes the number two spot on our list because it combines competitive challenges with real long-term value. With accounts from $5K to $200K, profit splits that can reach 100%, and one of the only unlimited scaling plans in the industry, BrightFunded is a great fit if you want more than just a short-term challenge. Add in the unique Trade2Earn loyalty program, and you've got a prop firm that rewards activity, not just winning results.\n\n| Feature | Details |\n|---------|---------|\n| Profit Split | Up to 100% |\n| Account Sizes | €5,000 – €200,000 |\n| Scaling Plan | Unlimited |\n| Platforms | MT5, cTrader, DXTrade |\n| Payout Schedule | Bi-weekly |\n| Challenge Fee (from) | €55 |\n\n### Funded Accounts\n\nBrightFunded runs a simple two-step evaluation before you unlock your funded account. The model is clear and fair, with a 5% daily loss limit and 10% total drawdown applied across all account sizes. You start on an 80% profit split, which can be increased to 90% through add-ons or scaled up to 100% as you grow your account.\n\nCustomisation is another big draw here. Optional add-ons let you shorten payout cycles to weekly or bi-weekly, remove the 5-day minimum trading rule, or even refund your challenge fee after funding.\n\nBrightFunded gives you access to forex, commodities, indices, and a great range of cryptocurrency markets on three platforms: MetaTrader 5, cTrader, and DXtrade.\n\n### Trade2Earn Loyalty Program\n\nBrightFunded's Trade2Earn program is a unique perk that rewards every trade you place, whether profitable or not. Tokens are added automatically to your dashboard and can be redeemed for:\n\n- Free evaluations or discounts of up to 50% on future challenges\n- Profit split boosts all the way to 100%\n- Lower profit targets or extended drawdown limits during challenges\n- Practical perks that reduce trading costs and increase flexibility\n\nSo far, BrightFunded has distributed more than 175,000 tokens and paid out an extra $200,000 through their loyalty program. It's a genuine long-term incentive that makes them unique from other prop firms.\n\n### Scaling Plan\n\nOne of BrightFunded's biggest selling points is its unlimited scaling plan. Every 4 months, you can increase your balance by 30% of the original size as long as you:\n\n- Achieve at least 10% profit over the period\n- Are profitable in 2 out of 4 months\n- Complete two profit payouts\n- Finish the cycle with a positive balance\n\nThere's no cap on how many times you can scale, and once you hit the third milestone you keep 100% of profits. This makes BrightFunded one of the most future-proof prop firms for traders who want real account growth.\n\n### How to Become a BrightFunded Trader?\n\nBrightFunded keeps things clear and simple with a traditional two-step evaluation process:\n\n**Step One:** Hit an 8% profit target while staying within the 5% daily loss limit and 10% overall drawdown. You'll also need to trade for at least 5 days.\n\n**Step Two:** The target drops to 5%, with the same risk rules and a minimum of another 5 trading days.\n\n**Funded Account:** Pass both steps and you'll unlock your funded account, starting with an 80% profit split and the chance to scale all the way to 100% through add-ons or long-term performance.\n\nThe process is flexible too. With add-ons, you can speed up payouts, skip the minimum trading days, or even start with a higher profit split. That means you can shape the evaluation to match your exact needs instead of being stuck with a one-size-fits-all challenge.\n\n### Final Verdict\n\nBrightFunded earns an overall score of 95/100 and its place near the top of our list thanks to its unlimited scaling, loyalty rewards, and flexible account setup. It's rare to find a prop firm that offers both low entry costs and long-term growth, but BrightFunded manages both. With three strong platforms including MT5, 100% profit splits, and genuine perks, it's a great option for forex and crypto traders.\n\n---\n\n## 3. FXIFY — Scaling Plan to $4 Million\n\nFXIFY makes the cut thanks to its flexible account options, generous profit splits of up to 90%, and a clear scaling plan that allows traders to double their account size every three months with consistent performance. Traders can choose from instant funding or evaluation challenges tailored to different experience levels, while platform options like MT4, MT5, and DXTrade provide access to diverse markets, including forex, commodities, and indices.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/image