pace-nowrap\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14\" />\u003C/svg>\n    Visit FXIFY\n  \u003C/a>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2.5\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4 text-emerald-600 flex-shrink-0\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M7 7h.01M7 3h5c.512 0 1.024.195 1.414.586l7 7a2 2 0 010 2.828l-7 7a2 2 0 01-2.828 0l-7-7A1.994 1.994 0 013 12V7a4 4 0 014-4z\" />\u003C/svg>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm text-emerald-700 font-semibold\">15% Off — Code:\u003C/span>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"font-mono font-bold text-xs bg-white border border-dashed border-emerald-300 px-3 py-1.5 rounded text-emerald-700 tracking-wide select-all\">PROPFIRMS15\u003C/span>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Pros & Cons\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Pros\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Profit splits up to 90%\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>EAs and news trading allowed\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Scaling doubles accounts every 3 months\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Minimal educational resources\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>No average spread data\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Slower payouts on high-tier accounts\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n### Prop Firm Details\n\nFXIFY combines flexibility and growth potential, offering traders the opportunity to scale their accounts and maximise profits with structured trading rules. Their funded accounts provide adaptable options like instant funding or multi-phase challenges, paired with advanced platforms and a supportive community.\n\nWhile FXIFY's transparency around trading costs could improve, their focus on scaling and profit-sharing options makes them an attractive choice for traders who prioritise capital growth.\n\n| Feature | Details |\n|---------|---------|\n| Profit Split | Up to 90% |\n| Account Sizes | $5,000 – $400,000 |\n| Scaling Plan | Up to $4 million |\n| Platforms | MT4, MT5, DXTrade |\n| Payout Schedule | Bi-weekly |\n| Challenge Fee (from) | $39 |\n\n### Funded Trading Accounts\n\nFXIFY funded accounts provide a starting profit split of 80%, which can be upgraded to 90% with an add-on during account setup. Payouts are flexible, with traders able to request withdrawals immediately after their first profitable trade. Bi-weekly payouts are also available for an additional fee.\n\nOnce you reach funded trader status with FXIFY, you need to follow these trading rules to keep your trading account:\n\n- **Daily Loss Limits:** Differ between challenge types, ensuring traders maintain discipline.\n- **Maximum Drawdown:** Between 6–10% depending on the account type.\n- **Permitted Trading Strategies:** Automated strategies (EAs), news trading, and copy trading between personal FXIFY accounts are allowed, while arbitrage and high-frequency trading are restricted.\n\nTo tailor your funded account, you can choose various add-ons when you initially sign up:\n\n- **Increased Leverage:** Up to 50:1 for forex and gold with a 25% fee.\n- **Higher Profit Splits:** Upgrade to a 90% profit split for a 20% fee increase.\n- **Bi-Weekly Payouts:** Add this feature for a 5% fee.\n\nThese features make FXIFY's funded accounts highly customisable and suitable for traders with a range of strategies, from short-term scalping to long-term trend trading.\n\n### Scaling Plan\n\nFXIFY's scaling plan rewards consistent performance with substantial growth opportunities. Traders who achieve a 10% profit within the first three months, with two of those months in profit, receive a 25% account increase. After this, accounts can double every three months if the same targets are met.\n\nExample of Scaling Progression:\n\n| Timeline | Account Size |\n|----------|-------------|\n| Initial | $400,000 |\n| Month 3 | $500,000 |\n| Month 6 | $1,000,000 |\n| Month 9 | $2,000,000 |\n| Month 12 | $4,000,000 |\n\nThis straightforward system not only motivates traders to maintain discipline but also provides a clear path to handling larger capital allocations over time. The plan's focus on gradual scaling ensures traders have the opportunity to grow sustainably.\n\n### How to Become a FXIFY Funded Trader?\n\nFXIFY offers four distinct paths to secure a funded account, ensuring flexibility for different trading styles:\n\n- **One Phase Challenge:** Reach the profit target in a single stage with no time limits while staying within the drawdown cap.\n- **Two Phase Challenge:** Complete two stages by meeting profit targets in each phase while following risk parameters.\n- **Three Phase Challenge:** Progress through three structured steps with smaller targets, ideal for traders who prefer a gradual approach.\n- **Instant Funding:** Skip the evaluation entirely and start trading live capital immediately with profit-sharing from day one.\n- **Lightning Challenge:** A fast-tracked evaluation with a short timeframe and strict consistency rules.\n\nEach pathway enforces strict drawdown rules to encourage risk management, but traders have the flexibility to choose the evaluation style and timeline that suits their goals.\n\n### Final Verdict\n\nFXIFY is a solid choice for traders focused on growth, offering a clear scaling plan that doubles account size every three months with consistent performance. The 80% profit split, upgradeable to 90%, provides strong earning potential, while flexible account customisations like increased leverage and bi-weekly payouts cater to diverse trading needs.\n\n---\n\n## 4. Blueberry Funded — Broker Backed Funded Accounts\n\nBlueberry Funded ranks 4th in our 2026 list of the best funded accounts, with a strong score of 93/100, making it one of the highest-rated firms we tested this year. It offers low-cost challenges starting at just $32.50, access to five asset classes including stocks and crypto, and four evaluation types, including a dedicated stock trading challenge. The firm is backed by ASIC-regulated broker Blueberry Markets, adding transparency and trust for funded traders.\n\nUse our Blueberry Funded promo code PROPFIRMS20 for a 20% discount on all challenges.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/blueberry-funded-logo.png\" alt=\"Blueberry Funded logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\" />\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">Blueberry Funded\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">Broker Backed Funded Accounts\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">90%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Max DD\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">10%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Trustpilot\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">3.8 \u003Cspan class=\"text-amber-500\">★\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Ca href=\"/reviews/blueberry-funded\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-lg bg-teal-500 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-white hover:bg-teal-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n        Full Review →\n      \u003C/a>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose -mt-3 mb-6 rounded-xl border border-emerald-200 bg-emerald-50/80 px-5 py-3 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-3\">\n  \u003Ca href=\"https://blueberryfunded.com/?utm_source=affiliate&ref=1457\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-emerald-500 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-emerald-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14\" />\u003C/svg>\n    Visit Blueberry Funded\n  \u003C/a>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2.5\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4 text-emerald-600 flex-shrink-0\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M7 7h.01M7 3h5c.512 0 1.024.195 1.414.586l7 7a2 2 0 010 2.828l-7 7a2 2 0 01-2.828 0l-7-7A1.994 1.994 0 013 12V7a4 4 0 014-4z\" />\u003C/svg>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm text-emerald-700 font-semibold\">20% Off — Code:\u003C/span>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"font-mono font-bold text-xs bg-white border border-dashed border-emerald-300 px-3 py-1.5 rounded text-emerald-700 tracking-wide select-all\">PROPFIRMS20\u003C/span>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Pros & Cons\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Pros\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Profit splits up to 90%\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Fees from $32.50\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Over 1,100 trading instruments\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Restrictions around news trading\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Limited payment methods\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>No true instant funding\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n### Prop Firm Details\n\nBlueberry Funded offers four flexible evaluations: 1 Step, 2 Step, 7-Day Rapid, and a dedicated Stock Challenge. These cater to traders seeking everything from rapid funding to structured evaluations. Account sizes range from $5,000 to $200,000, with scaling up to $2 million.\n\nSpreads start from 0.1 pips, and commissions are fixed at $7 round-turn for forex and $2 per lot for stocks. The firm supports MT4, MT5, DXTrade, and TradeLocker across various challenge types.\n\n| Feature | Details |\n|---------|---------|\n| Profit Split | Up to 90% |\n| Account Sizes | $5,000 – $200,000 |\n| Scaling Plan | Up to $2 million |\n| Platforms | MT4, MT5, DXTrade, TradeLocker |\n| Payout Schedule | Every 14 days |\n| Challenge Fee (from) | $32.50 |\n\n### Funded Trading Account\n\nAll Blueberry Funded accounts follow clear rules, including:\n\n- **Profit Splits:** 80% standard, 90% with performance\n- **Drawdown Limits:** Up to 10% total and 5% daily\n- **Trading Rules:** EAs allowed, no mandatory stop-loss, weekend trading permitted\n- **Profit Payouts:** Every 14 days via RiseWorks (USDC/USDT)\n\nStock Challenge accounts include additional rules like a consistency rule for withdrawals and restricted trading around market open/close. These help enforce risk control for equity traders.\n\n### Scaling Plan\n\nBlueberry Funded's scaling plan increases account size by 25% every 3 months if you meet:\n\n- A 10% net profit target\n- At least four successful payouts within the same period\n\nThe maximum capital allocation is $2 million, and trading rules stay the same as your account grows — no stricter limits or new evaluations.\n\n### How To Become A Blueberry Funded Trader?\n\nYou can choose from four evaluations:\n\n- **One Step:** 10% profit target, 6% drawdown, no time limit\n- **Two Step:** 10% in Phase 1, 5% in Phase 2, 10% drawdown, higher leverage (1:50)\n- **Rapid Challenge:** 7 days to reach 5% profit, 4% trailing drawdown\n- **Stock Challenge:** Two-phase evaluation for US stocks, strict drawdowns, and payout rules\n\nAll challenges are priced competitively and come with simple risk parameters and platform flexibility.\n\n### Final Verdict\n\nBlueberry Funded ranks as the 4th best funded account in 2026 with a score of 93/100. Its low entry fees, strong challenge variety, and access to over 1,100 assets — including US stocks and crypto — make it one of the most flexible prop firms available.\n\nWhile news trading restrictions and limited payment options are drawbacks, the clear scaling plan, broker-backed credibility, and high TrustPilot rating support its position as one of the most trader-friendly options on the market.\n\n---\n\n## 5. City Traders Imperium — Prop Firm Paying Trader Salaries\n\nCity Traders Imperium (CTI) offers competitive profit splits reaching up to 100%, diverse funding options like 1-Step, 2-Step, and Instant Funding programs, and trader salaries as a unique perk. With affordable fees, clear scaling opportunities up to $2 million, and an engaged trading community, CTI caters to both beginner and experienced traders seeking long-term growth.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/city-traders-imperium-logo.png\" alt=\"City Traders Imperium logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\" />\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">City Traders Imperium\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">Prop Firm Paying Trader Salaries\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">100%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Max DD\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">10%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Score\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">72/100\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Ca href=\"/reviews/city-traders-imperium\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-lg bg-teal-500 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-white hover:bg-teal-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n        Full Review →\n      \u003C/a>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Pros & Cons\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Pros\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Profit splits up to 100%\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Scaling up to $2 million\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Golden Trader program rewards performance\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>High drawdown limits for specific accounts\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Requires a stop-loss on every trade\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Higher entry fees compared to other prop firms\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n### Prop Firm Details\n\nFounded in 2018 and based in Dubai, CTI has established itself as a leading prop trading firm with a strong focus on scalability and trader development. CTI provides access to forex, indices, commodities, and cryptocurrencies through MetaTrader 5 and Match Trader platforms, offering flexibility and comprehensive trading tools for traders at all levels.\n\n| Feature | Details |\n|---------|---------|\n| Profit Split | Up to 100% |\n| Account Sizes | From $2,500 |\n| Scaling Plan | Up to $2 million |\n| Platforms | MT5, Match Trader |\n| Payout Schedule | Monthly |\n| Unique Feature | Monthly trader salary |\n\n### CTI Funded Accounts\n\nCity Traders Imperium (CTI) provides funded accounts that combine attractive profit splits, scaling opportunities, and rewards through the Golden Trader Loyalty Program. These accounts are designed for traders seeking both flexibility and long-term growth.\n\n**Profit Splits:** Accounts start with an 80% profit split and can increase to 100% as traders achieve performance milestones.\n\n**Golden Trader Loyalty Program:** Rewards consistent performance with additional benefits:\n\n- **Bronze Level:** Weekly payouts, a 90% profit split, coaching, and discounts.\n- **Silver Level:** On-demand payouts, a 100% profit split, and personalized merchandise.\n- **Gold Level:** Institutional-grade trading conditions, custom funding terms, and a potential one-year salary.\n\nCTI's funded accounts include rules to promote disciplined and consistent trading:\n\n- **Daily Drawdown Limits:** Ranges from 6–10% depending on the account type, encouraging disciplined trading.\n- **News Trading Permitted:** Traders can hold positions during high-impact news events and over weekends.\n- **Stop-Loss Requirement:** All trades must include a stop-loss, automatically enforced for risk management.\n\n### Scaling Plan\n\nCTI's scaling plan rewards consistent performance by doubling account sizes up to $2 million while increasing profit splits to 100%.\n\nProgression Example:\n\n- **Start with $50,000:** A 10% profit milestone doubles the account to $100,000.\n- **Maintain Consistency:** Accounts continue doubling as traders meet additional milestones.\n- **Profit Split Growth:** Each milestone increases the profit split by 10%, capping at 100%.\n\nCTI also offers the Golden Trader Loyalty Program, which adds further rewards, such as VIP coaching, merchandise, and even a potential guaranteed salary at the Gold level.\n\n### How to Become a CTI Trader?\n\nCTI provides flexibility with evaluation challenges tailored to various trading styles:\n\n- **1-Step Challenge:** Complete a single phase with a 10% profit target and 6% drawdown cap.\n- **2-Step Challenge:** Phase 1 requires a 10% profit target, while Phase 2 lowers the target to 5%.\n- **Instant Funding:** Skip evaluations and access capital immediately, with up to 100% profit splits.\n\nBoth challenges have no time limits, allowing traders to progress at their own pace while focusing on consistency and discipline.\n\n### Final Verdict\n\nCTI combines high profit potential with unique benefits like trader salaries, flexible evaluations, and a supportive community. While the firm's 1:10 leverage for commodities and indices may limit position sizes, its broad market access, affordable fees, and clear scaling opportunities make it an excellent choice for traders aiming for long-term growth.\n\n---\n\n## 6. FTMO — Best Funded Account for Stocks\n\nFTMO scores 83/100 and is the most established prop firm in the industry, operating since 2015. With a Trustpilot rating of 4.8 and a proven track record of paying out traders, FTMO is the go-to for conservative traders who want a reliable funded account. Their stock market access makes them the best option for equity traders.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/ftmo-logo-2-2-1-1-1.png\" alt=\"FTMO logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\" />\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">FTMO\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">Best Funded Account for Stocks\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">90%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Max DD\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">10%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Trustpil