lex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Profit splits max at 80%\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Trustpilot rating of 2.7 is below average\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>No cTrader support\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n### Funded Account Details\n\nIC Funded offers 1-step, 2-step, and three-phase challenges with account sizes from $5,000 to $200,000. Fees start at just $29.75 for a $5,000 1-step account. The IC Markets backing ensures institutional-grade execution with raw spreads from 0 pips.\n\n| Feature | Details |\n|---------|---------|\n| Profit Split | Up to 80% |\n| Account Sizes | $5,000 – $200,000 |\n| Platforms | MT4, MT5 |\n| Payout Schedule | Bi-weekly |\n| Commission | $3.50 per lot |\n| Challenge Fee (from) | $29.75 |\n\n---\n\n## 9. The 5%ers — Up to 100% Profit Split\n\nThe 5%ers score 78/100 and have been operating since 2016, making them one of the most established prop firms. With profit splits up to 100%, scaling to $4 million, and a monthly salary for top performers, The 5%ers offer a comprehensive funded trading experience with a Trustpilot rating of 4.9.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/the5ers-logo-2-2-1-1-1.png\" alt=\"The 5%ers logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\" />\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">The 5%ers\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">Up to 100% Profit Split\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">100%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Max DD\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">10%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Trustpilot\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">4.9 \u003Cspan class=\"text-amber-500\">★\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Ca href=\"/reviews/the5ers\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-lg bg-teal-500 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-white hover:bg-teal-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n        Full Review →\n      \u003C/a>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Pros & Cons\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Pros\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Profit splits up to 100%\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Scaling plan up to $4 million\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Highest Trustpilot rating (4.9) and monthly salary\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Limited to MT5 and MatchTrader platforms\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Overall score of 78 below top competitors\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Strict consistency rules on some challenges\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n### Funded Account Details\n\nThe 5%ers offer 1-step and 2-step evaluations with account sizes from $5,000. The High Stakes 2-step starts at $39. Scaling goes up to $4 million, and funded traders can receive a monthly salary. The Trustpilot rating of 4.9 is the highest in the industry.\n\n| Feature | Details |\n|---------|---------|\n| Profit Split | Up to 100% |\n| Account Sizes | From $5,000 |\n| Scaling Plan | Up to $4 million |\n| Platforms | MT5, MatchTrader |\n| Payout Schedule | Monthly |\n| Challenge Fee (from) | $39 |\n\n---\n\n## How We Choose the Best Funded Accounts\n\nWe evaluated funded accounts based on the trader experience after passing evaluation challenges. Our methodology prioritises factors like profit splits, trading rules, scaling opportunities, and ease of access to live capital. The goal was to identify firms offering fair and transparent funding models that support traders' long-term success. Here's what we focused on:\n\n### 1. Profit Splits\n\nProfit splits are a key metric for determining the earning potential of funded accounts. Firms with splits starting at 75% or higher, and opportunities to scale up to 90%-100%, scored higher.\n\n### 2. Evaluation Challenges\n\nWe reviewed the structure and accessibility of evaluation challenges, including:\n\n- **Profit Targets:** Reasonable targets, typically 8%-10% for Phase 1 and 4%-5% for Phase 2.\n- **Drawdown Limits:** Flexible limits, such as 5% daily and 10% overall, that balance risk with opportunity.\n- **Evaluation Process:** One-step, two-step, or instant funding options to cater to different trader preferences.\n\n### 3. Scaling Plans\n\nFirms with clear, achievable scaling plans ranked higher. We prioritised those offering incremental account growth, such as 25%-40% increases every few months, and those allowing accounts to scale up to $2 million or more.\n\n### 4. Payout Policies\n\nFrequent, fast payouts were essential. We assessed minimum withdrawal amounts, payout frequency (weekly or bi-weekly), and profit split terms to ensure traders could access their earnings quickly and efficiently.\n\n### 5. Trading Rules and Platforms\n\nTransparent trading rules and platform flexibility were crucial. Firms allowing strategies like news trading, EAs, and weekend trading scored higher. Platforms like MT4, MT5, and cTrader were rated for usability, advanced tools, and multi-device compatibility.\n\n### 6. Costs and Fees\n\nWe reviewed challenge fees, commissions, and spreads to assess cost-efficiency. Firms offering low entry fees, spreads below 1 pip for popular forex pairs, and transparent pricing ranked higher.\n\nThis methodology focuses on funded accounts that provide fair evaluations, strong earning potential, and scalability. By combining technical and trader-focused assessments, we aim to highlight firms that not only help traders get funded but also support long-term growth and profitability.\n\nOur prop firm reviews provide a clear and actionable framework for selecting the best funded accounts, ensuring traders can make informed decisions.\n\n---\n\n## FAQs\n\n### What is the best funded trading?\n\nThe best funded trading accounts offer high profit splits, scaling opportunities, and fair rules. FundedNext provides up to 95% profit splits with a 110% fee refund on successful challenge completion, making it a strong choice for traders seeking high payouts and reduced upfront costs. The top prop firms support long-term trader growth with scaling plans and frequent payouts.\n\n### How to get a funded trading account?\n\nYou can get a funded trading account by passing a prop firm's evaluation challenge, which requires meeting profit targets while staying within drawdown limits. Some firms also offer instant funding, allowing traders to skip the evaluation process and start trading with a live account immediately — though these often come with lower profit splits or higher fees.\n\n### Which funded account is best for beginners?\n\nThe best funded account for beginner prop traders is BrightFunded or Blueberry Funded due to their beginner-friendly tools and features. BrightFunded's proprietary platform offers intuitive trading tools, customisable evaluations, and the Trade2Earn programme, which simplifies challenges for new traders. Blueberry Funded supports beginners with low challenge fees, spreads from 0 pips, and user-friendly platforms like MT4 and MT5, known for their simplicity and flexibility.\n\n### How much does a 100K funded account cost?\n\nThe cost of a 100K funded account depends on the prop firm. The cheapest prop firms include BrightFunded which charges €495 for its evaluation challenge, offering flexible scaling and high profit splits. FXIFY prices range from $399 to $499, depending on the selected challenge type, while FundedNext charges $549 to $569, influenced by optional add-ons like faster payouts.\n\n### Is trading with a funded account worth it?\n\nTrading with a funded account can be worth it for disciplined traders who want access to capital without risking personal funds. By joining a prop firm, traders can leverage firm-provided funds, access advanced trading platforms, and earn high profit splits, often between 75% and 90%. Successful traders also benefit from scaling plans and growth opportunities.","src/content/blog/funded-trading-accounts.md","1f467c8b9802b639",{"html":5636,"metadata":5637},"\u003Ch2 id=\"which-prop-firms-have-the-best-funded-accounts\">Which Prop Firms Have the Best Funded Accounts?\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>The best funded accounts provide high profit splits of 80% or more, scalable account options for consistent traders, and loyalty programs that reward activity with perks like higher payouts or reduced fees. Fast and reliable payouts, combined with flexible trading rules, make these the best funded trading accounts for long-term growth.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>We reviewed the best funded accounts offered by top prop firms:\u003C/p>\n\u003Col>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>FundedNext\u003C/strong> — Best Funded Account Overall\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>BrightFunded\u003C/strong> — Best Trader Loyalty Program\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>FXIFY\u003C/strong> — Scaling Plan to $4 Million\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Blueberry Funded\u003C/strong> — Broker Backed Funded Accounts\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>City Traders Imperium\u003C/strong> — Prop Firm Paying Trader Salaries\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>FTMO\u003C/strong> — Best Funded Account for Stocks\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>ThinkCapital\u003C/strong> — High Leverage Funded Accounts\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>IC Funded\u003C/strong> — Funded Accounts with Low Spreads\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>The 5%ers\u003C/strong> — Up to 100% Profit Split\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ol>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"the-9-best-funded-trading-accounts-we-tested-in-2026\">The 9 Best Funded Trading Accounts We Tested in 2026\u003C/h2>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"1-fundednext--best-funded-account-overall\">1. FundedNext — Best Funded Account Overall\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>FundedNext takes the top spot with flexible models, low-cost challenge options, and the ability to earn up to 95% profit split. Traders can choose from multiple evaluation styles — including the fast-track Stellar One Step, standard two-phase Evaluation, and budget-friendly Stellar Lite — with funded accounts from $5,000 to $200,000. With the ability to scale accounts to $4 million, it’s designed for long-term growth.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Use code PROPFIRMS for a 120% refund — 100% of your challenge fee back plus 20% extra as a bonus once funded.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/fundednext.png\" alt=\"FundedNext logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">FundedNext\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">Best Funded Account Overall\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">95%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Max DD\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">10%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Trustpilot\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">4.5 \u003Cspan class=\"text-amber-500\">★\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Ca href=\"/reviews/fundednext\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-lg bg-teal-500 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-white hover:bg-teal-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n        Full Review →\n      \u003C/a>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose -mt-3 mb-6 rounded-xl border border-emerald-200 bg-emerald-50/80 px-5 py-3 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-3\">\n  \u003Ca href=\"https://fundednext.com/?fpr=noam82\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-emerald-500 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-emerald-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n    Visit FundedNext\n  \u003C/a>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2.5\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4 text-emerald-600 flex-shrink-0\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M7 7h.01M7 3h5c.512 0 1.024.195 1.414.586l7 7a2 2 0 010 2.828l-7 7a2 2 0 01-2.828 0l-7-7A1.994 1.994 0 013 12V7a4 4 0 014-4z\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm text-emerald-700 font-semibold\">120% Refund — Code:\u003C/span>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"font-mono font-bold text-xs bg-white border border-dashed border-emerald-300 px-3 py-1.5 rounded text-emerald-700 tracking-wide select-all\">PROPFIRMS\u003C/span>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Pros &#x26; Cons\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Pros\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Profit splits up to 95% with clear scaling criteria\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>MT4, MT5, cTrader, and Match-Trader\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Scaling plan and 120% refund on challenge fees\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Strict loss limits\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>No access to stocks\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Scaling caps\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"prop-firm-details\">Prop Firm Details\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>FundedNext runs exclusively on three models: Stellar One Step, Stellar Two Step, and Stellar Lite. All options offer 95% profit splits once funded, with flexible rules and no time limits. Funded accounts start at $5,000 and scale up to $200,000, with maximum capital allocation capped at $4 million through their scale-up program.\u003C/p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003Ctable>\u003Cthead>\u003Ctr>\u003Cth>Feature\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Details\u003C/th>\u003C/tr>\u003C/thead>\u003Ctbody>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Profit Split\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Up to 95%\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Account Sizes\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$5,000 – $200,000\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Scaling Plan\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Up to $4 million\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Platforms\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>MT4, MT5, cTrader, Match-Trader\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Payout Schedule\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Bi-weekly (5 days for 1-Step)\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Challenge Fee (from)\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$32\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003C/tbody>\u003C/table>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"funded-trading-accounts\">Funded Trading Accounts\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>With FundedNext, you don’t have to wait to start earning — traders on the Stellar One Step and Two Step models get a 15% profit share during the challenge phase. Once funded, payouts can start as early as five business days for Stellar One Step accounts, while Stellar Lite accounts unlock bi-weekly withdrawals.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Drawdown limits vary by model, ranging from 3% to 5% daily and 6% to 10% overall, giving you some breathing room while keeping risk in check. Leverage is capped at 30:1 for the One Step, but jumps to 100:1 for Stellar Two Step and Lite, which is ideal if you prefer more flexibility.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Expert Advisors (EAs) are also permitted on MT4 and MT5 — great if you rely on automation or advanced strategies.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"scaling-plan\">Scaling Plan\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>FundedNext scales your account by 40% every four months if you:\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>Grow the account by 10%\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>Complete two successful withdrawals\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>Finish the final cycle in profit\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Cp>This continues up to a max of $4 million. So a $100K account could scale to $140K in 4 months, $196K in 8 months, and so on.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"how-to-become-a-fundednext-trader\">How to Become a FundedNext Trader?\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>FundedNext offers three challenge models, each designed to suit a different type of trader.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>Stellar One Step\u003C/strong> is ideal if you want to skip the long evaluation and get funded fast. It’s a single-phase challenge with moderate risk limits and a 15% profit share from the moment you start.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>Stellar Two Step\u003C/strong> is better suited for consistent traders who prefer a more structured path. The two-phase format gives you more flexibility on risk and strategy, while still offering a profit share during the challenge.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>Stellar Lite\u003C/strong> is the most affordable option, designed for traders starting out or testing the waters. It has tighter drawdowns, no payouts during the challenge, and smaller account sizes — but it’s a solid choice if you want lower upfront fees and still access a 95% split once funded.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>You can customise your evaluation by adding the following (fees are percentage-based and applied to the base challenge fee):\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Lifetime 95% Payout (+30%):\u003C/strong> Lock in the full 95% profit split from day one, even before scaling.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Double Up (+40%):\u003C/strong> Automatically double your funded account size upon successful challenge completion.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>No Minimum Trading Days (+20%):\u003C/strong> Remove the minimum trading day requirement.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>10% Overall Loss Limit (+25%):\u003C/strong> Increases the drawdown buffer for Stellar Lite accounts only.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Bi-Weekly Payouts (+15%):\u003C/strong> Unlock faster payout schedules.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Swap-Free Account (+10%):\u003C/strong> Removes overnight swap fees across all account types and sizes. Ideal for traders following religious or swing-trading strategies.\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"final-verdict\">Final Verdict\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>FundedNext ranks as the best funded account overall for traders wanting fast access to capital, strong earning potential, and flexible rules. With options for low-cost entry, fast withdrawals, and challenge-phase payouts, it’s suited for serious traders focused on consistent growth.\u003C/p>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"2-brightfunded--best-trader-loyalty-program\">2. BrightFunded — Best Trader Loyalty Program\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>BrightFunded earnt the second spot on our shortlist for its challenge customisation, unlimited scaling plan, and unique Trade2Earn loyalty program which rewards you with practical perks like free evaluations and higher profit splits. With profit shares up to 100%, fast payouts, and 24/7 support, BrightFunded is a top prop firm if you are looking to grow your account over the long term and be rewarded for your trading activity along the way.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Use promo code PROPFIRMS20 for a 20% discount!\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/brightfunded-logo.png\" alt=\"BrightFunded logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">BrightFunded\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">Best Trader Loyalty Program\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">100%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Max DD\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">10%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Trustpilot\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">4.4 \u003Cspan class=\"text-amber-500\">★\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Ca href=\"/reviews/brightfunded\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-lg bg-teal-500 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-white hover:bg-teal-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n        Full Review →\n      \u003C/a>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose -mt-3 mb-6 rounded-xl border border-emerald-200 bg-emerald-50/80 px-5 py-3 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-3\">\n  \u003Ca href=\"https://brightfunded.com?affiliateId=rsBbtrzYQSyr3RcHYHQT5w\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-emerald-500 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-emerald-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n    Visit BrightFunded\n  \u003C/a>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2.5\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4 text-emerald-600 flex-shrink-0\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M7 7h.01M7 3h5c.512 0 1.024.195 1.414.586l7 7a2 2 0 010 2.828l-7 7a2 2 0 01-2.828 0l-7-7A1.994 1.994 0 013 12V7a4 4 0 014-4z\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm text-emerald-700 font-semibold\">20% Off — Code:\u003C/span>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"font-mono font-bold text-xs bg-white border border-dashed border-emerald-300 px-3 py-1.5 rounded text-emerald-700 tracking-wide select-all\">PROPFIRMS20\u003C/span>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Pros &#x26; Cons\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Pros\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Unlimited scaling potential\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Profit splits up to 100%\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Trade2Earn loyalty program rewards traders\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Higher fees for optional add-ons\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>MetaTrader 5 but not MT4\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Payouts only in USD or crypto\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"prop-firm-details-1\">Prop Firm Details\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>BrightFunded takes the number two spot on our list because it combines competitive challenges with real long-term value. With accounts from $5K to $200K, profit splits that can reach 100%, and one of the only unlimited scaling plans in the industry, BrightFunded is a great fit if you want more than just a short-term challenge. Add in the unique Trade2Earn loyalty program, and you’ve got a prop firm that rewards activity, not just winning results.\u003C/p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003Ctable>\u003Cthead>\u003Ctr>\u003Cth>Feature\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Details\u003C/th>\u003C/tr>\u003C/thead>\u003Ctbody>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Profit Split\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Up to 100%\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Account Sizes\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>€5,000 – €200,000\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Scaling Plan\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Unlimited\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Platforms\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>MT5, cTrader, DXTrade\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Payout Schedule\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Bi-weekly\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Challenge Fee (from)\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>€55\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003C/tbody>\u003C/table>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"funded-accounts\">Funded Accounts\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>BrightFunded runs a simple two-step evaluation before you unlock your funded account. The model is clear and fair, with a 5% daily loss limit and 10% total drawdown applied across all account sizes. You start on an 80% profit split, which can be increased to 90% through add-ons or scaled up to 100% as you grow your account.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Customisation is another big draw here. Optional add-ons let you shorten payout cycles to weekly or bi-weekly, remove the 5-day minimum trading rule, or even refund your challenge fee after funding.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>BrightFunded gives you access to forex, commodities, indices, and a great range of cryptocurrency markets on three platforms: MetaTrader 5, cTrader, and DXtrade.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"trade2earn-loyalty-program\">Trade2Earn Loyalty Program\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>BrightFunded’s Trade2Earn program is a unique perk that rewards every trade you place, whether profitable or not. Tokens are added automatically to your dashboard and can be redeemed for:\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>Free evaluations or discounts of up to 50% on future challenges\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>Profit split boosts all the way to 100%\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>Lower profit targets or extended drawdown limits during challenges\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>Practical perks that reduce trading costs and increase flexibility\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Cp>So far, BrightFunded has distributed more than 175,000 tokens and paid out an extra $200,000 through their loyalty program. It’s a genuine long-term incentive that makes them unique from other prop firms.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"scaling-plan-1\">Scaling Plan\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>One of BrightFunded’s biggest selling points is its unlimited scaling plan. Every 4 months, you can increase your balance by 30% of the original size as long as you:\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>Achieve at least 10% profit over the period\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>Are profitable in 2 out of 4 months\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>Complete two profit payouts\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>Finish the cycle with a positive balance\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Cp>There’s no cap on how many times you can scale, and once you hit the third milestone you keep 100% of profits. This makes BrightFunded one of the most future-proof prop firms for traders who want real account growth.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"how-to-become-a-brightfunded-trader\">How to Become a BrightFunded Trader?\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>BrightFunded keeps things clear and simple with a traditional two-step evaluation process:\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>Step One:\u003C/strong> Hit an 8% profit target while staying within the 5% daily loss limit and 10% overall drawdown. You’ll also need to trade for at least 5 days.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>Step Two:\u003C/strong> The target drops to 5%, with the same risk rules and a minimum of another 5 trading days.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>Funded Account:\u003C/strong> Pass both steps and you’ll unlock your funded account, starting with an 80% profit split and the chance to scale all the way to 100% through add-ons or long-term performance.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>The process is flexible too. With add-ons, you can speed up payouts, skip the minimum trading days, or even start with a higher profit split. That means you can shape the evaluation to match your exact needs instead of being stuck with a one-size-fits-all challenge.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"final-verdict-1\">Final Verdict\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>BrightFunded earns an overall score of 95/100 and its place near the top of our list thanks to its unlimited scaling, loyalty rewards, and flexible account setup. It’s rare to find a prop firm that offers both low entry costs and long-term growth, but BrightFunded manages both. With three strong platforms including MT5, 100% profit splits, and genuine perks, it’s a great option for forex and crypto traders.\u003C/p>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"3-fxify--scaling-plan-to-4-million\">3. FXIFY — Scaling Plan to $4 Million\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>FXIFY makes the cut thanks to its flexible account options, generous profit splits of up to 90%, and a clear scaling plan that allows traders to double their account size every three months with consistent performance. Traders can choose from instant funding or evaluation challenges tailored to different experience levels, while platform options like MT4, MT5, and DXTrade provide access to diverse markets, including forex, commodities, and indices.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/fxify-1-1-1-1.png\" alt=\"FXIFY logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">FXIFY\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">Scaling Plan to $4 Million\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">90%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Max DD\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">10%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Trustpilot\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">4.4 \u003Cspan class=\"text-amber-500\">★\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Ca href=\"/reviews/fxify\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-lg bg-teal-500 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-white hover:bg-teal-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n        Full Review →\n      \u003C/a>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose -mt-3 mb-6 rounded-xl border border-emerald-200 bg-emerald-50/80 px-5 py-3 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-3\">\n  \u003Ca href=\"https://trader.fxify.com/purchasechallenge?affiliateId=5837\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-emerald-500 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-emerald-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n    Visit FXIFY\n  \u003C/a>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2.5\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4 text-emerald-600 flex-shrink-0\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M7 7h.01M7 3h5c.512 0 1.024.195 1.414.586l7 7a2 2 0 010 2.828l-7 7a2 2 0 01-2.828 0l-7-7A1.994 1.994 0 013 12V7a4 4 0 014-4z\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm text-emerald-700 font-semibold\">15% Off — Code:\u003C/span>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"font-mono font-bold text-xs bg-white border border-dashed border-emerald-300 px-3 py-1.5 rounded text-emerald-700 tracking-wide select-all\">PROPFIRMS15\u003C/span>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Pros &#x26; Cons\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Pros\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Profit splits up to 90%\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>EAs and news trading allowed\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Scaling doubles accounts every 3 months\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Minimal educational resources\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>No average spread data\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Slower payouts on high-tier accounts\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"prop-firm-details-2\">Prop Firm Details\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>FXIFY combines flexibility and growth potential, offering traders the opportunity to scale their accounts and maximise profits with structured trading rules. Their funded accounts provide adaptable options like instant funding or multi-phase challenges, paired with advanced platforms and a supportive community.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>While FXIFY’s transparency around trading costs could improve, their focus on scaling and profit-sharing options makes them an attractive choice for traders who prioritise capital growth.\u003C/p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003Ctable>\u003Cthead>\u003Ctr>\u003Cth>Feature\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Details\u003C/th>\u003C/tr>\u003C/thead>\u003Ctbody>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Profit Split\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Up to 90%\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Account Sizes\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$5,000 – $400,000\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Scaling Plan\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Up to $4 million\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Platforms\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>MT4, MT5, DXTrade\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Payout Schedule\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Bi-weekly\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Challenge Fee (from)\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$39\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003C/tbody>\u003C/table>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"funded-trading-accounts-1\">Funded Trading Accounts\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>FXIFY funded accounts provide a starting profit split of 80%, which can be upgraded to 90% with an add-on during account setup. Payouts are flexible, with traders able to request withdrawals immediately after their first profitable trade. Bi-weekly payouts are also available for an additional fee.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Once you reach funded trader status with FXIFY, you need to follow these trading rules to keep your trading account:\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Daily Loss Limits:\u003C/strong> Differ between challenge types, ensuring traders maintain discipline.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Maximum Drawdown:\u003C/strong> Between 6–10% depending on the account type.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Permitted Trading Strategies:\u003C/strong> Automated strategies (EAs), news trading, and copy trading between personal FXIFY accounts are allowed, while arbitrage and high-frequency trading are restricted.\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Cp>To tailor your funded account, you can choose various add-ons when you initially sign up:\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Increased Leverage:\u003C/strong> Up to 50:1 for forex and gold with a 25% fee.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Higher Profit Splits:\u003C/strong> Upgrade to a 90% profit split for a 20% fee increase.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Bi-Weekly Payouts:\u003C/strong> Add this feature for a 5% fee.\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Cp>These features make FXIFY’s funded accounts highly customisable and suitable for traders with a range of strategies, from short-term scalping to long-term trend trading.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"scaling-plan-2\">Scaling Plan\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>FXIFY’s scaling plan rewards consistent performance with substantial growth opportunities. Traders who achieve a 10% profit within the first three months, with two of those months in profit, receive a 25% account increase. After this, accounts can double every three months if the same targets are met.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Example of Scaling Progression:\u003C/p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003Ctable>\u003Cthead>\u003Ctr>\u003Cth>Timeline\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Account Size\u003C/th>\u003C/tr>\u003C/thead>\u003Ctbody>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Initial\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$400,000\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Month 3\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$500,000\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Month 6\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$1,000,000\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Month 9\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$2,000,000\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Month 12\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$4,000,000\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003C/tbody>\u003C/table>\n\u003Cp>This straightforward system not only motivates traders to maintain discipline but also provides a clear path to handling larger capital allocations over time. The plan’s focus on gradual scaling ensures traders have the opportunity to grow sustainably.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"how-to-become-a-fxify-funded-trader\">How to Become a FXIFY Funded Trader?\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>FXIFY offers four distinct paths to secure a funded account, ensuring flexibility for different trading styles:\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>One Phase Challenge:\u003C/strong> Reach the profit target in a single stage with no time limits while staying within the drawdown cap.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Two Phase Challenge:\u003C/strong> Complete two stages by meeting profit targets in each phase while following risk parameters.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Three Phase Challenge:\u003C/strong> Progress through three structured steps with smaller targets, ideal for traders who prefer a gradual approach.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Instant Funding:\u003C/strong> Skip the evaluation entirely and start trading live capital immediately with profit-sharing from day one.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Lightning Challenge:\u003C/strong> A fast-tracked evaluation with a short timeframe and strict consistency rules.\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Cp>Each pathway enforces strict drawdown rules to encourage risk management, but traders have the flexibility to choose the evaluation style and timeline that suits their goals.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"final-verdict-2\">Final Verdict\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>FXIFY is a solid choice for traders focused on growth, offering a clear scaling plan that doubles account size every three months with consistent performance. The 80% profit split, upgradeable to 90%, provides strong earning potential, while flexible account customisations like increased leverage and bi-weekly payouts cater to diverse trading needs.\u003C/p>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"4-blueberry-funded--broker-backed-funded-accounts\">4. Blueberry Funded — Broker Backed Funded Accounts\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>Blueberry Funded ranks 4th in our 2026 list of the best funded accounts, with a strong score of 93/100, making it one of the highest-rated firms we tested this year. It offers low-cost challenges starting at just $32.50, access to five asset classes including stocks and crypto, and four evaluation types, including a dedicated stock trading challenge. The firm is backed by ASIC-regulated broker Blueberry Markets, adding transparency and trust for funded traders.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Use our Blueberry Funded promo code PROPFIRMS20 for a 20% discount on all challenges.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/blueberry-funded-logo.png\" alt=\"Blueberry Funded logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">Blueberry Funded\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">Broker Backed Funded Accounts\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">90%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Max DD\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">10%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Trustpilot\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">3.8 \u003Cspan class=\"text-amber-500\">★\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Ca href=\"/reviews/blueberry-funded\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-lg bg-teal-500 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-white hover:bg-teal-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n        Full Review →\n      \u003C/a>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose -mt-3 mb-6 rounded-xl border border-emerald-200 bg-emerald-50/80 px-5 py-3 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-3\">\n  \u003Ca href=\"https://blueberryfunded.com/?utm_source=affiliate&#x26;ref=1457\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-emerald-500 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-emerald-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n    Visit Blueberry Funded\n  \u003C/a>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2.5\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4 text-emerald-600 flex-shrink-0\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M7 7h.01M7 3h5c.512 0 1.024.195 1.414.586l7 7a