struments\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Restrictions around news trading\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Limited payment methods\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>No true instant funding\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"prop-firm-details-3\">Prop Firm Details\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Blueberry Funded offers four flexible evaluations: 1 Step, 2 Step, 7-Day Rapid, and a dedicated Stock Challenge. These cater to traders seeking everything from rapid funding to structured evaluations. Account sizes range from $5,000 to $200,000, with scaling up to $2 million.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Spreads start from 0.1 pips, and commissions are fixed at $7 round-turn for forex and $2 per lot for stocks. The firm supports MT4, MT5, DXTrade, and TradeLocker across various challenge types.\u003C/p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003Ctable>\u003Cthead>\u003Ctr>\u003Cth>Feature\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Details\u003C/th>\u003C/tr>\u003C/thead>\u003Ctbody>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Profit Split\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Up to 90%\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Account Sizes\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$5,000 – $200,000\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Scaling Plan\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Up to $2 million\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Platforms\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>MT4, MT5, DXTrade, TradeLocker\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Payout Schedule\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Every 14 days\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Challenge Fee (from)\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$32.50\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003C/tbody>\u003C/table>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"funded-trading-account\">Funded Trading Account\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>All Blueberry Funded accounts follow clear rules, including:\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Profit Splits:\u003C/strong> 80% standard, 90% with performance\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Drawdown Limits:\u003C/strong> Up to 10% total and 5% daily\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Trading Rules:\u003C/strong> EAs allowed, no mandatory stop-loss, weekend trading permitted\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Profit Payouts:\u003C/strong> Every 14 days via RiseWorks (USDC/USDT)\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Cp>Stock Challenge accounts include additional rules like a consistency rule for withdrawals and restricted trading around market open/close. These help enforce risk control for equity traders.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"scaling-plan-3\">Scaling Plan\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Blueberry Funded’s scaling plan increases account size by 25% every 3 months if you meet:\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>A 10% net profit target\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>At least four successful payouts within the same period\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Cp>The maximum capital allocation is $2 million, and trading rules stay the same as your account grows — no stricter limits or new evaluations.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"how-to-become-a-blueberry-funded-trader\">How To Become A Blueberry Funded Trader?\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>You can choose from four evaluations:\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>One Step:\u003C/strong> 10% profit target, 6% drawdown, no time limit\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Two Step:\u003C/strong> 10% in Phase 1, 5% in Phase 2, 10% drawdown, higher leverage (1:50)\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Rapid Challenge:\u003C/strong> 7 days to reach 5% profit, 4% trailing drawdown\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Stock Challenge:\u003C/strong> Two-phase evaluation for US stocks, strict drawdowns, and payout rules\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Cp>All challenges are priced competitively and come with simple risk parameters and platform flexibility.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"final-verdict-3\">Final Verdict\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Blueberry Funded ranks as the 4th best funded account in 2026 with a score of 93/100. Its low entry fees, strong challenge variety, and access to over 1,100 assets — including US stocks and crypto — make it one of the most flexible prop firms available.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>While news trading restrictions and limited payment options are drawbacks, the clear scaling plan, broker-backed credibility, and high TrustPilot rating support its position as one of the most trader-friendly options on the market.\u003C/p>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"5-city-traders-imperium--prop-firm-paying-trader-salaries\">5. City Traders Imperium — Prop Firm Paying Trader Salaries\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>City Traders Imperium (CTI) offers competitive profit splits reaching up to 100%, diverse funding options like 1-Step, 2-Step, and Instant Funding programs, and trader salaries as a unique perk. With affordable fees, clear scaling opportunities up to $2 million, and an engaged trading community, CTI caters to both beginner and experienced traders seeking long-term growth.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/city-traders-imperium-logo.png\" alt=\"City Traders Imperium logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">City Traders Imperium\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">Prop Firm Paying Trader Salaries\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">100%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Max DD\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">10%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Score\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">72/100\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Ca href=\"/reviews/city-traders-imperium\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-lg bg-teal-500 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-white hover:bg-teal-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n        Full Review →\n      \u003C/a>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Pros &#x26; Cons\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Pros\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Profit splits up to 100%\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Scaling up to $2 million\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Golden Trader program rewards performance\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>High drawdown limits for specific accounts\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Requires a stop-loss on every trade\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Higher entry fees compared to other prop firms\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"prop-firm-details-4\">Prop Firm Details\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Founded in 2018 and based in Dubai, CTI has established itself as a leading prop trading firm with a strong focus on scalability and trader development. CTI provides access to forex, indices, commodities, and cryptocurrencies through MetaTrader 5 and Match Trader platforms, offering flexibility and comprehensive trading tools for traders at all levels.\u003C/p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003Ctable>\u003Cthead>\u003Ctr>\u003Cth>Feature\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Details\u003C/th>\u003C/tr>\u003C/thead>\u003Ctbody>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Profit Split\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Up to 100%\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Account Sizes\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>From $2,500\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Scaling Plan\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Up to $2 million\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Platforms\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>MT5, Match Trader\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Payout Schedule\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Monthly\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Unique Feature\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Monthly trader salary\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003C/tbody>\u003C/table>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"cti-funded-accounts\">CTI Funded Accounts\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>City Traders Imperium (CTI) provides funded accounts that combine attractive profit splits, scaling opportunities, and rewards through the Golden Trader Loyalty Program. These accounts are designed for traders seeking both flexibility and long-term growth.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>Profit Splits:\u003C/strong> Accounts start with an 80% profit split and can increase to 100% as traders achieve performance milestones.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>Golden Trader Loyalty Program:\u003C/strong> Rewards consistent performance with additional benefits:\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Bronze Level:\u003C/strong> Weekly payouts, a 90% profit split, coaching, and discounts.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Silver Level:\u003C/strong> On-demand payouts, a 100% profit split, and personalized merchandise.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Gold Level:\u003C/strong> Institutional-grade trading conditions, custom funding terms, and a potential one-year salary.\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Cp>CTI’s funded accounts include rules to promote disciplined and consistent trading:\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Daily Drawdown Limits:\u003C/strong> Ranges from 6–10% depending on the account type, encouraging disciplined trading.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>News Trading Permitted:\u003C/strong> Traders can hold positions during high-impact news events and over weekends.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Stop-Loss Requirement:\u003C/strong> All trades must include a stop-loss, automatically enforced for risk management.\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"scaling-plan-4\">Scaling Plan\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>CTI’s scaling plan rewards consistent performance by doubling account sizes up to $2 million while increasing profit splits to 100%.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Progression Example:\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Start with $50,000:\u003C/strong> A 10% profit milestone doubles the account to $100,000.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Maintain Consistency:\u003C/strong> Accounts continue doubling as traders meet additional milestones.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Profit Split Growth:\u003C/strong> Each milestone increases the profit split by 10%, capping at 100%.\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Cp>CTI also offers the Golden Trader Loyalty Program, which adds further rewards, such as VIP coaching, merchandise, and even a potential guaranteed salary at the Gold level.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"how-to-become-a-cti-trader\">How to Become a CTI Trader?\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>CTI provides flexibility with evaluation challenges tailored to various trading styles:\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>1-Step Challenge:\u003C/strong> Complete a single phase with a 10% profit target and 6% drawdown cap.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>2-Step Challenge:\u003C/strong> Phase 1 requires a 10% profit target, while Phase 2 lowers the target to 5%.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Instant Funding:\u003C/strong> Skip evaluations and access capital immediately, with up to 100% profit splits.\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Cp>Both challenges have no time limits, allowing traders to progress at their own pace while focusing on consistency and discipline.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"final-verdict-4\">Final Verdict\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>CTI combines high profit potential with unique benefits like trader salaries, flexible evaluations, and a supportive community. While the firm’s 1:10 leverage for commodities and indices may limit position sizes, its broad market access, affordable fees, and clear scaling opportunities make it an excellent choice for traders aiming for long-term growth.\u003C/p>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"6-ftmo--best-funded-account-for-stocks\">6. FTMO — Best Funded Account for Stocks\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>FTMO scores 83/100 and is the most established prop firm in the industry, operating since 2015. With a Trustpilot rating of 4.8 and a proven track record of paying out traders, FTMO is the go-to for conservative traders who want a reliable funded account. Their stock market access makes them the best option for equity traders.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/ftmo-logo-2-2-1-1-1.png\" alt=\"FTMO logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">FTMO\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">Best Funded Account for Stocks\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">90%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Max DD\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">10%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Trustpilot\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">4.8 \u003Cspan class=\"text-amber-500\">★\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Ca href=\"/reviews/ftmo\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-lg bg-teal-500 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-white hover:bg-teal-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n        Full Review →\n      \u003C/a>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Pros &#x26; Cons\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Pros\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Highest Trustpilot rating (4.8) in the industry\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Operating since 2015 with proven payouts\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Access to stocks, forex, indices, and commodities\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Higher challenge fees than competitors\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Only 2-step challenge available\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Profit splits capped at 90%\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"funded-account-details\">Funded Account Details\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>FTMO runs a 2-step evaluation with 10% and 5% profit targets, 5% daily and 10% overall drawdown. Account sizes range from €10,000 to €200,000, with fees starting at €155. Scaling goes up to $2 million. FTMO supports 18+ languages and operates with a dedicated performance coach for funded traders.\u003C/p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003Ctable>\u003Cthead>\u003Ctr>\u003Cth>Feature\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Details\u003C/th>\u003C/tr>\u003C/thead>\u003Ctbody>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Profit Split\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Up to 90%\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Account Sizes\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>€10,000 – €200,000\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Scaling Plan\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Up to $2 million\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Platforms\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>MT4, MT5, cTrader, DXTrade\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Payout Schedule\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Monthly\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Challenge Fee (from)\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>€155\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003C/tbody>\u003C/table>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"7-thinkcapital--high-leverage-funded-accounts\">7. ThinkCapital — High Leverage Funded Accounts\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>ThinkCapital offers high leverage funded accounts that appeal to aggressive traders looking for maximum exposure. With competitive leverage ratios and a streamlined evaluation process, ThinkCapital caters to traders who want to maximise their trading potential.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/thinkcapital-icon.png\" alt=\"ThinkCapital logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">ThinkCapital\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">High Leverage Funded Accounts\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Focus\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">Leverage\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Type\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">Multi\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Ca href=\"https://www.thinkcapital.com/?sp_rid=677d98c8fcd21d60b8730003\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-lg bg-teal-500 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-white hover:bg-teal-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n        Visit Site →\n      \u003C/a>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Pros &#x26; Cons\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Pros\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>High leverage options for funded accounts\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Streamlined evaluation process\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Competitive pricing\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Higher leverage increases risk of breaching drawdown\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Limited community and review data available\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"8-ic-funded--funded-accounts-with-low-spreads\">8. IC Funded — Funded Accounts with Low Spreads\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>IC Funded scores 79/100 and is backed by IC Markets, one of the world’s largest forex brokers. With spreads from 0 pips, commissions of $3.50 per lot, and challenge fees starting at just $29.75, IC Funded offers some of the lowest trading costs in the funded account space.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/ic-funded-logo.png\" alt=\"IC Funded logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">IC Funded\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">Funded Accounts with Low Spreads\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">80%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdi