 Schedule\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Bi-weekly\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Commission\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$3.50 per lot\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Challenge Fee (from)\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$29.75\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003C/tbody>\u003C/table>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"9-the-5ers--up-to-100-profit-split\">9. The 5%ers — Up to 100% Profit Split\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>The 5%ers score 78/100 and have been operating since 2016, making them one of the most established prop firms. With profit splits up to 100%, scaling to $4 million, and a monthly salary for top performers, The 5%ers offer a comprehensive funded trading experience with a Trustpilot rating of 4.9.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/the5ers-logo-2-2-1-1-1.png\" alt=\"The 5%ers logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">The 5%ers\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">Up to 100% Profit Split\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">100%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Max DD\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">10%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Trustpilot\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">4.9 \u003Cspan class=\"text-amber-500\">★\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Ca href=\"/reviews/the5ers\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-lg bg-teal-500 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-white hover:bg-teal-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n        Full Review →\n      \u003C/a>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Pros &#x26; Cons\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Pros\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Profit splits up to 100%\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Scaling plan up to $4 million\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Highest Trustpilot rating (4.9) and monthly salary\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Limited to MT5 and MatchTrader platforms\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Overall score of 78 below top competitors\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Strict consistency rules on some challenges\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"funded-account-details-2\">Funded Account Details\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>The 5%ers offer 1-step and 2-step evaluations with account sizes from $5,000. The High Stakes 2-step starts at $39. Scaling goes up to $4 million, and funded traders can receive a monthly salary. The Trustpilot rating of 4.9 is the highest in the industry.\u003C/p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003Ctable>\u003Cthead>\u003Ctr>\u003Cth>Feature\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Details\u003C/th>\u003C/tr>\u003C/thead>\u003Ctbody>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Profit Split\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Up to 100%\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Account Sizes\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>From $5,000\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Scaling Plan\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Up to $4 million\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Platforms\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>MT5, MatchTrader\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Payout Schedule\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Monthly\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Challenge Fee (from)\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$39\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003C/tbody>\u003C/table>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"how-we-choose-the-best-funded-accounts\">How We Choose the Best Funded Accounts\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>We evaluated funded accounts based on the trader experience after passing evaluation challenges. Our methodology prioritises factors like profit splits, trading rules, scaling opportunities, and ease of access to live capital. The goal was to identify firms offering fair and transparent funding models that support traders’ long-term success. Here’s what we focused on:\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"1-profit-splits\">1. Profit Splits\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Profit splits are a key metric for determining the earning potential of funded accounts. Firms with splits starting at 75% or higher, and opportunities to scale up to 90%-100%, scored higher.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"2-evaluation-challenges\">2. Evaluation Challenges\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>We reviewed the structure and accessibility of evaluation challenges, including:\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Profit Targets:\u003C/strong> Reasonable targets, typically 8%-10% for Phase 1 and 4%-5% for Phase 2.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Drawdown Limits:\u003C/strong> Flexible limits, such as 5% daily and 10% overall, that balance risk with opportunity.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Evaluation Process:\u003C/strong> One-step, two-step, or instant funding options to cater to different trader preferences.\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"3-scaling-plans\">3. Scaling Plans\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Firms with clear, achievable scaling plans ranked higher. We prioritised those offering incremental account growth, such as 25%-40% increases every few months, and those allowing accounts to scale up to $2 million or more.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"4-payout-policies\">4. Payout Policies\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Frequent, fast payouts were essential. We assessed minimum withdrawal amounts, payout frequency (weekly or bi-weekly), and profit split terms to ensure traders could access their earnings quickly and efficiently.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"5-trading-rules-and-platforms\">5. Trading Rules and Platforms\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Transparent trading rules and platform flexibility were crucial. Firms allowing strategies like news trading, EAs, and weekend trading scored higher. Platforms like MT4, MT5, and cTrader were rated for usability, advanced tools, and multi-device compatibility.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"6-costs-and-fees\">6. Costs and Fees\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>We reviewed challenge fees, commissions, and spreads to assess cost-efficiency. Firms offering low entry fees, spreads below 1 pip for popular forex pairs, and transparent pricing ranked higher.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>This methodology focuses on funded accounts that provide fair evaluations, strong earning potential, and scalability. By combining technical and trader-focused assessments, we aim to highlight firms that not only help traders get funded but also support long-term growth and profitability.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Our prop firm reviews provide a clear and actionable framework for selecting the best funded accounts, ensuring traders can make informed decisions.\u003C/p>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"faqs\">FAQs\u003C/h2>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"what-is-the-best-funded-trading\">What is the best funded trading?\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>The best funded trading accounts offer high profit splits, scaling opportunities, and fair rules. FundedNext provides up to 95% profit splits with a 110% fee refund on successful challenge completion, making it a strong choice for traders seeking high payouts and reduced upfront costs. The top prop firms support long-term trader growth with scaling plans and frequent payouts.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"how-to-get-a-funded-trading-account\">How to get a funded trading account?\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>You can get a funded trading account by passing a prop firm’s evaluation challenge, which requires meeting profit targets while staying within drawdown limits. Some firms also offer instant funding, allowing traders to skip the evaluation process and start trading with a live account immediately — though these often come with lower profit splits or higher fees.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"which-funded-account-is-best-for-beginners\">Which funded account is best for beginners?\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>The best funded account for beginner prop traders is BrightFunded or Blueberry Funded due to their beginner-friendly tools and features. BrightFunded’s proprietary platform offers intuitive trading tools, customisable evaluations, and the Trade2Earn programme, which simplifies challenges for new traders. Blueberry Funded supports beginners with low challenge fees, spreads from 0 pips, and user-friendly platforms like MT4 and MT5, known for their simplicity and flexibility.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"how-much-does-a-100k-funded-account-cost\">How much does a 100K funded account cost?\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>The cost of a 100K funded account depends on the prop firm. The cheapest prop firms include BrightFunded which charges €495 for its evaluation challenge, offering flexible scaling and high profit splits. FXIFY prices range from $399 to $499, depending on the selected challenge type, while FundedNext charges $549 to $569, influenced by optional add-ons like faster payouts.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"is-trading-with-a-funded-account-worth-it\">Is trading with a funded account worth it?\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Trading with a funded account can be worth it for disciplined traders who want access to capital without risking personal funds. By joining a prop firm, traders can leverage firm-provided funds, access advanced trading platforms, and earn high profit splits, often between 75% and 90%. Successful traders also benefit from scaling plans and growth opportunities.\u003C/p>",{"headings":5638,"localImagePaths":5765,"remoteImagePaths":5766,"frontmatter":5767,"imagePaths":5779},[5639,5642,5645,5648,5649,5651,5653,5656,5657,5660,5661,5664,5665,5667,5670,5671,5674,5675,5677,5679,5682,5683,5686,5687,5690,5692,5695,5696,5699,5700,5703,5705,5708,5709,5712,5715,5718,5721,5723,5726,5728,5731,5734,5737,5740,5743,5746,5749,5750,5753,5756,5759,5762],{"depth":879,"slug":5640,"text":5641},"which-prop-firms-have-the-best-funded-accounts","Which Prop Firms Have the Best Funded Accounts?",{"depth":879,"slug":5643,"text":5644},"the-9-best-funded-trading-accounts-we-tested-in-2026","The 9 Best Funded Trading Accounts We Tested in 2026",{"depth":879,"slug":5646,"text":5647},"1-fundednext--best-funded-account-overall","1. FundedNext — Best Funded Account Overall",{"depth":158,"slug":5218,"text":5219},{"depth":158,"slug":5603,"text":5650},"Funded Trading Accounts",{"depth":158,"slug":5652,"text":238},"scaling-plan",{"depth":158,"slug":5654,"text":5655},"how-to-become-a-fundednext-trader","How to Become a FundedNext Trader?",{"depth":158,"slug":5051,"text":5052},{"depth":879,"slug":5658,"text":5659},"2-brightfunded--best-trader-loyalty-program","2. BrightFunded — Best Trader Loyalty Program",{"depth":158,"slug":5235,"text":5219},{"depth":158,"slug":5662,"text":5663},"funded-accounts","Funded Accounts",{"depth":158,"slug":5520,"text":5521},{"depth":158,"slug":5666,"text":238},"scaling-plan-1",{"depth":158,"slug":5668,"text":5669},"how-to-become-a-brightfunded-trader","How to Become a BrightFunded Trader?",{"depth":158,"slug":5068,"text":5052},{"depth":879,"slug":5672,"text":5673},"3-fxify--scaling-plan-to-4-million","3. FXIFY — Scaling Plan to $4 Million",{"depth":158,"slug":5248,"text":5219},{"depth":158,"slug":5676,"text":5650},"funded-trading-accounts-1",{"depth":158,"slug":5678,"text":238},"scaling-plan-2",{"depth":158,"slug":5680,"text":5681},"how-to-become-a-fxify-funded-trader","How to Become a FXIFY Funded Trader?",{"depth":158,"slug":5083,"text":5052},{"depth":879,"slug":5684,"text":5685},"4-blueberry-funded--broker-backed-funded-accounts","4. Blueberry Funded — Broker Backed Funded Accounts",{"depth":158,"slug":5261,"text":5219},{"depth":158,"slug":5688,"text":5689},"funded-trading-account","Funded Trading Account",{"depth":158,"slug":5691,"text":238},"scaling-plan-3",{"depth":158,"slug":5693,"text":5694},"how-to-become-a-blueberry-funded-trader","How To Become A Blueberry Funded Trader?",{"depth":158,"slug":5098,"text":5052},{"depth":879,"slug":5697,"text":5698},"5-city-traders-imperium--prop-firm-paying-trader-salaries","5. City Traders Imperium — Prop Firm Paying Trader Salaries",{"depth":158,"slug":5274,"text":5219},{"depth":158,"slug":5701,"text":5702},"cti-funded-accounts","CTI Funded Accounts",{"depth":158,"slug":5704,"text":238},"scaling-plan-4",{"depth":158,"slug":5706,"text":5707},"how-to-become-a-cti-trader","How to Become a CTI Trader?",{"depth":158,"slug":5113,"text":5052},{"depth":879,"slug":5710,"text":5711},"6-ftmo--best-funded-account-for-stocks","6. FTMO — Best Funded Account for Stocks",{"depth":158,"slug":5713,"text":5714},"funded-account-details","Funded Account Details",{"depth":879,"slug":5716,"text":5717},"7-thinkcapital--high-leverage-funded-accounts","7. ThinkCapital — High Leverage Funded Accounts",{"depth":879,"slug":5719,"text":5720},"8-ic-funded--funded-accounts-with-low-spreads","8. IC Funded — Funded Accounts with Low Spreads",{"depth":158,"slug":5722,"text":5714},"funded-account-details-1",{"depth":879,"slug":5724,"text":5725},"9-the-5ers--up-to-100-profit-split","9. The 5%ers — Up to 100% Profit Split",{"depth":158,"slug":5727,"text":5714},"funded-account-details-2",{"depth":879,"slug":5729,"text":5730},"how-we-choose-the-best-funded-accounts","How We Choose the Best Funded Accounts",{"depth":158,"slug":5732,"text":5733},"1-profit-splits","1. Profit Splits",{"depth":158,"slug":5735,"text":5736},"2-evaluation-challenges","2. Evaluation Challenges",{"depth":158,"slug":5738,"text":5739},"3-scaling-plans","3. Scaling Plans",{"depth":158,"slug":5741,"text":5742},"4-payout-policies","4. Payout Policies",{"depth":158,"slug":5744,"text":5745},"5-trading-rules-and-platforms","5. Trading Rules and Platforms",{"depth":158,"slug":5747,"text":5748},"6-costs-and-fees","6. Costs and Fees",{"depth":879,"slug":4935,"text":4936},{"depth":158,"slug":5751,"text":5752},"what-is-the-best-funded-trading","What is the best funded trading?",{"depth":158,"slug":5754,"text":5755},"how-to-get-a-funded-trading-account","How to get a funded trading account?",{"depth":158,"slug":5757,"text":5758},"which-funded-account-is-best-for-beginners","Which funded account is best for beginners?",{"depth":158,"slug":5760,"text":5761},"how-much-does-a-100k-funded-account-cost","How much does a 100K funded account cost?",{"depth":158,"slug":5763,"text":5764},"is-trading-with-a-funded-account-worth-it","Is trading with a funded account worth it?",[],[],{"title":5606,"excerpt":5607,"category":5171,"tags":5768,"author":4798,"authorImage":4799,"publishedAt":240,"featured":110,"coverImage":5612,"readingTimeMinutes":405,"youtubeVideoId":4800,"featuredFirms":5769},[4796,5173,5609,5610,5611],[5770,5771,5772,5773,5774,5775,5776,5777,5778],{"slug":1392,"descriptor":5615},{"slug":584,"descriptor":5617},{"slug":1599,"descriptor":5619},{"slug":332,"descriptor":5621},{"slug":642,"descriptor":5623},{"slug":1002,"descriptor":5625},{"slug":4813,"descriptor":5627},{"slug":1917,"descriptor":5629},{"slug":2507,"descriptor":5631},[],"funded-trading-accounts.md",{"id":2465,"data":5782,"body":5809,"filePath":5810,"digest":5811,"rendered":5812,"legacyId":5949},{"title":5783,"excerpt":5784,"category":5171,"tags":5785,"coverImage":5788,"author":4798,"authorImage":4799,"publishedAt":1273,"featured":110,"readingTimeMinutes":1764,"youtubeVideoId":5344,"featuredFirms":5789},"Best Futures Prop Firms (Verified Testing 2026)","We tested 16 futures prop firms firsthand in 2026 and ranked them based on funding options, profit splits, evaluation rules, and trading platform access. This shortlist of the 10 best futures prop firms looks at how each one scored and what you can expect in terms of trading conditions, fees, and payout models.",[2465,5173,4796,5786,5787],"CME","futures trading","/images/blog/futures.png",[5790,5791,5793,5795,5797,5799,5801,5803,5805,5807],{"slug":1550,"descriptor":4818},{"slug":1341,"descriptor":5792},"24 Hour Profit Payouts",{"slug":2621,"descriptor":5794},"Popular Futures Trading Firm",{"slug":2442,"descriptor":5796},"Futures and CFDs",{"slug":1682,"descriptor":5798},"Instant Funding Futures Account",{"slug":2251,"descriptor":5800},"High Profit Split",{"slug":2819,"descriptor":5802},"250K Funded Accounts",{"slug":1055,"descriptor":5804},"Free NinjaTrader Platform",{"slug":244,"descriptor":5806},"Good Range of Futures Markets",{"slug":870,"descriptor":5808},"Good Educational Materials","## What Are The Best Prop Firms For Futures Trading?\n\nWe tested 16 futures prop firms firsthand in 2026 and ranked them based on funding options, profit splits, evaluation rules, and trading platform access. This shortlist of the 10 best futures prop firms looks at how each one scored and what you can expect in terms of trading conditions, fees, and payout models.\n\nOur best futures prop firms list in 2026 is:\n\n1. **FXIFY Futures** — Best Futures Prop Firm\n2. **FundedNext Futures** — 24 Hour Profit Payouts\n3. **Topstep** — Popular Futures Trading Firm\n4. **The Trading Pit** — Futures and CFDs\n5. **Goat Funded Futures** — Instant Funding Futures Account\n6. **MyFundedFutures** — High Profit Split\n7. **TradeDay** — 250K Funded Accounts\n8. **Elite Trader Funding** — Free NinjaTrader Platform\n9. **Apex Trader Funding** — Good Range of Futures Markets\n10. **Earn2Trade** — Good Educational Materials\n\nIf you are interested in futures prop trading, you should choose a prop firm based on their fees, challenge requirements, and trading platform offered. We found a few different types of futures traders exist and aligned them to the best prop firm based on their needs.\n\n---\n\n## The 5 Best Futures Prop Firms We Tested in 2026\n\n---\n\n## 1. FXIFY Futures — Best Futures Prop Firm\n\nFXIFY Futures is the best futures prop firm we reviewed with an overall score of 88/100. You go through a one step evaluation process to receive a funded account with up to 100% profit split. You also get access to real-time CME data with TradingView charts.\n\nYou can also save 15% on all futures challenge fees by using the promo code PROPFIRMS15 at checkout.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/fxify-futures.png\" alt=\"FXIFY Futures logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\" />\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">FXIFY Futures\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">Best Futures Prop Firm\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">100%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Max DD\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">5%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Trustpilot\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">3.9 \u003Cspan class=\"text-amber-500\">★\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Ca href=\"/reviews/fxify-futures\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-lg bg-teal-500 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-white hover:bg-teal-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n        Full Review →\n      \u003C/a>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose -mt-3 mb-6 rounded-xl border border-emerald-200 bg-emerald-50/80 px-5 py-3 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-3\">\n  \u003Ca href=\"https://app.fxifyfutures.com?ref=VNPb7mgMLt63\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-emerald-500 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-emerald-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14\" />\u003C/svg>\n    Visit FXIFY Futures\n  \u003C/a>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2.5\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4 text-emerald-600 flex-shrink-0\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M7 7h.01M7 3h5c.512 0 1.024.195 1.414.586l7 7a2 2 0 010 2.828l-7 7a2 2 0 01-2.828 0l-7-7A1.994 1.994 0 013 12V7a4 4 0 014-4z\" />\u003C/svg>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm text-emerald-700 font-semibold\">15% Off — Code:\u003C/span>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"font-mono font-bold text-xs bg-white border border-dashed border-emerald-300 px-3 py-1.5 rounded text-emerald-700 tracking-wide select-all\">PROPFIRMS15\u003C/span>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Pros & Cons\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Pros\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Profit splits up to 100%\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>No time limits on evaluation\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>TradingView charts\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Payouts follow a tiered system\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>No NinjaTrader or Rithmic integration\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Buffer zone required before withdrawals\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n### Prop Firm Details\n\nFXIFY Futures is the top-rated futures prop firm if you are looking for a funded account with high profit splits and no time limits. With a one-step evaluation and scalable profit-sharing up to 100%, you get an accessible pathway to a professional style trading environment.\n\nYou can choose from two challenge types being Starter and Expert. In terms of trading platforms, the FFX Platform doesn't have any third-party integrations but does give you TradingView charts and real-time CME data.\n\nFXIFY Futures straight up pricing structure means you don't need to worry about hidden fees, with your monthly challenge payments covering all trading costs. Profit payouts are tiered, starting at 80% and going all the way up to 100%.\n\n**Key Features**\n\n- **Evaluation Process:** One-step challenge with no time limits, allowing you to hit profit targets at your own pace.\n- **Platform Options:** The FFX Platform with TradingView charts and real-time CME data.\n- **Futures Market Access:** Includes forex, equities, commodities, and bonds.\n- **Profit Split:** Tiered payout system, starting at 80% and scaling to 100% based on withdrawal milestones.\n\n### Trading Costs and Fees\n\nFXIFY Futures' pricing structure is clear and straightforward, with monthly fees for the evaluation phase and no recurring costs after funding. Unlike other futures prop firms, FXIFY does not charge platform fees, data fees, or per-trade commissions, making it a cost-effective choice for funded trading.\n\nChallenge Fees depend on the account size and plan:\n\n- **Starter Plan:** $89/month for a $50K account, scaling up to $225/month for $150K.\n- **Expert Plan:** $149/month for a $50K account, increasing to $349/month for $150K.\n\nOnce funded, Starter accounts require a one-time activation fee of $125, while Expert accounts have no activation fee, allowing immediate access to withdrawals.\n\nProfit payouts follow a tiered structure, starting at 60% on the first withdrawal, increasing to 100% after the fifth payout. Before withdrawing, traders must maintain a buffer zone, ensuring account stability. For example, a $50,000 funded account requires at least $500 in profits above the buffer before requesting a payout.\n\nUnlike many futures prop firms that require monthly exchange data fees, FXIFY provides real-time CME data for free. All trading commissions are covered in the evaluation fee, meaning no additional per-trade costs.\n\nTraders can upgrade their profit split by 10% at checkout, increasing the Starter payout from 80% to 90% and Expert from 90% to 100%. Expert traders can also remove daily drawdown limits, providing more flexibility in risk management.\n\nWith no hidden fees, no platform costs, and a structured withdrawal model, FXIFY Futures ensures traders keep more of their profits while maintaining a disciplined trading approach.\n\n### Support and Community\n\nFXIFY Futures provides customer support via live chat, email, and Discord, allowing traders to access real-time assistance. While educational resources are limited, the firm offers platform guides and payout proof channels in its community.\n\n- **Live Chat & Email Support:** Available during trading hours.\n- **Discord Community:** Traders can engage with peers, discuss strategies, and verify payouts.\n- **Help Center:** Provides detailed guides on rules, funding, and withdrawal policies.\n\nFXIFY Futures has a growing trader base, but its Trustpilot rating is still developing. While traders report smooth withdrawals and platform stability, some note delays in customer service response times.\n\n### Final Verdict on FXIFY Futures\n\nFXIFY Futures is the best futures prop firm with high profit splits, no time limits, and no hidden fees. The one-step evaluation offers scalable payouts up to 100%, and while the FFX Platform lacks third-party integrations, it provides TradingView charts and real-time CME data.\n\n---\n\n## 2. FundedNext Futures — 24 Hour Profit Payouts\n\nFundedNext Futures is the best prop firm for fast payouts and simple evaluations. You keep 100% of your profits after passing a one step challenge with no time limit, real CME pricing, and no activation or monthly fees. One of the biggest perks is FundedNext offers a $1,000 payout guarantee if they miss their 24-hour withdrawal promise, which isn't a common promise in the prop trading industry.\n\nYou can also save 5% on your challenge fee by using the promo code PF at checkout.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/fn-futures.png\" alt=\"FundedNext Futures logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\" />\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">