"h-4 w-4 text-emerald-600 flex-shrink-0\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M7 7h.01M7 3h5c.512 0 1.024.195 1.414.586l7 7a2 2 0 010 2.828l-7 7a2 2 0 01-2.828 0l-7-7A1.994 1.994 0 013 12V7a4 4 0 014-4z\" />\u003C/svg>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm text-emerald-700 font-semibold\">25% Off — Code:\u003C/span>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"font-mono font-bold text-xs bg-white border border-dashed border-emerald-300 px-3 py-1.5 rounded text-emerald-700 tracking-wide select-all\">PROPFIRMS25\u003C/span>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Pros & Cons\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Pros\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Access to over 800 instruments\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Profit splits up to 90%\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Broker-backed by DNA Markets\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Newly launched, fewer reviews\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>No scaling plan currently\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Basic educational resources\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n### Evaluation Process\n\nDNA Funded's evaluation process includes three challenge types, each tailored to different trading strategies and skill levels:\n\n| Feature | Single Helix | Double Helix | Rapid Challenge |\n|---------|-------------|-------------|----------------|\n| **Phases** | 1 | 2 | 1 |\n| **Profit Target** | 10% | 10% / 5% | 5% |\n| **Daily Loss Limit** | 5% | 5% | 5% |\n| **Max Drawdown** | 10% | 10% | 10% |\n| **Time Limit** | None | None | 10 days |\n| **Profit Split** | 80% (up to 90%) | 80% (up to 90%) | 80% (up to 90%) |\n| **Starting Fee** | $49 | $49 | $49 |\n\nEach challenge offers 80% profit splits, upgradeable to 90% through add-ons, and traders have the option to customise accounts for faster payouts.\n\n### Fees and Profit Payouts\n\nDNA Funded's fees range from $49 to $1,451, depending on the account size and challenge type. Add-ons for a higher profit split or faster payouts incur additional costs, with fees increasing by 20%–30%. All fees are one-time and refundable after the first successful withdrawal.\n\nYou start with an 80% profit split, upgradeable to 90%. Payouts follow a 14-day cycle by default, with an optional add-on reducing the cycle to 7 days for quicker access to profits.\n\nA 40% daily profit cap also applies across all challenges. This means no more than 40% of your payout target can be generated in a single trading day. The cap supports consistent performance and reflects DNA Funded's broker-backed compliance model.\n\nFlexible payout methods, including cryptocurrency and bank transfers, accommodate traders in India and beyond.\n\n### Markets and Leverage\n\nDNA Funded gives traders access to over 800 financial instruments:\n\n| Asset Class | Instruments | Leverage |\n|------------|------------|---------|\n| Forex | Majors, minors, exotics | Up to 1:50 |\n| Indices | S&P 500, Nifty, and more | Up to 1:10 |\n| Commodities | Gold, silver, crude oil | Up to 1:10 |\n| Stocks | Diverse equity options | Up to 1:5 |\n| Crypto | Available on Single & Double Helix | Up to 1:2 |\n\n### Trading Platforms\n\nDNA Funded supports one trading platform — **TradeLocker** integrated with TradingView. This user-friendly platform offers advanced charting tools, seamless on-chart trading, and reliable performance across devices. It's ideal for manual traders focused on technical analysis. Since DNA Funded discontinued its support of DXTrade, automated trading with Expert Advisors is no longer available.\n\n### Trust and Support\n\nAlthough newly launched, DNA Funded benefits from its partnership with DNA Markets, a well-regarded ASIC-regulated liquidity provider, lending credibility to the firm. DNA Funded holds a **3.5/5 on Trustpilot** and is building a trader community through Discord, with channels for strategy discussions and support. Customer support is currently limited to email but expected to expand.\n\n### Final Verdict\n\nDNA Funded's combination of low fees, flexible challenges, and strong backing from DNA Markets makes it a top choice for traders in India. Its customisable options, high profit splits, and access to 800+ markets ensure appeal for both beginners and experienced traders. As the firm continues to grow, its value as a reliable prop trading option is set to increase.\n\n---\n\n## 4. BrightFunded — Best Prop Trader Rewards Program\n\nBrightFunded is a top prop trading firm, known for its flexible challenges, trader-focused add-ons, and a unique reward system. With account sizes ranging from $5K to $200K, its two-step evaluation process, unlimited scaling plan, and unique Trade2Earn Rewards Program make it a great option for Indian traders.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/brightfunded-logo.png\" alt=\"BrightFunded logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\" />\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">BrightFunded\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">Best Prop Trader Rewards Program\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n    