" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M7 7h.01M7 3h5c.512 0 1.024.195 1.414.586l7 7a2 2 0 010 2.828l-7 7a2 2 0 01-2.828 0l-7-7A1.994 1.994 0 013 12V7a4 4 0 014-4z\" />\u003C/svg>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm text-emerald-700 font-semibold\">20% Off — Code:\u003C/span>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"font-mono font-bold text-xs bg-white border border-dashed border-emerald-300 px-3 py-1.5 rounded text-emerald-700 tracking-wide select-all\">PROPFIRMS20\u003C/span>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Pros & Cons\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Pros\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Profit splits up to 100%\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Traditional two-step evaluation\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>No minimum trading days with add-on\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Add-ons increase costs\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>No MetaTrader 4, but MT5 added\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>No stock markets\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n### Evaluation Process\n\nBrightFunded's challenges involve a multi-stage evaluation process, with clear rules and the opportunity to customise your trading experience:\n\n| Feature | Phase 1 | Phase 2 | Funded Account |\n|---------|---------|---------|---------------|\n| **Profit Target** | 8% | 5% | — |\n| **Daily Loss Limit** | 5% | 5% | 5% |\n| **Max Drawdown** | 10% | 10% | 10% |\n| **Min Trading Days** | 5 (waivable) | 5 (waivable) | — |\n| **Time Limit** | None | None | — |\n| **Profit Split** | — | — | Up to 100% |\n\nBrightFunded allows traders to personalise their challenges with add-ons like higher profit splits, faster payouts, and waived minimum trading day requirements.\n\n| Account Size | Challenge Fee |\n|-------------|-------------|\n| $5,000 | €55 |\n| $10,000 | €95 |\n| $25,000 | €195 |\n| $50,000 | €295 |\n| $100,000 | €495 |\n| $200,000 | €975 |\n\n### Fees and Profit Payouts\n\nChallenge fees range from €55 to €975 depending on the account size you choose. These fees are a one-time cost with no hidden charges and can be refunded after reaching funded status.\n\nProfit splits start at 80% and can increase to 100% through the scaling plan or add-ons. BrightFunded's Trade2Earn Rewards Program also allows traders to earn tokens for every trade, which can be redeemed for profit split boosts, free evaluations, or discounts on future challenges.\n\nPayouts are flexible and paid out monthly by default, with add-ons available for weekly or bi-weekly cycles. Payments are processed via bank transfer or cryptocurrency, with no minimum withdrawal limits, making it easy for traders to access their earnings efficiently.\n\n### Markets and Leverage\n\nBrightFunded provides access to a diverse range of trading instruments:\n\n| Asset Class | Instruments | Leverage |\n|------------|------------|---------|\n| Forex | 49 pairs (majors, minors, exotics) | Up to 1:100 |\n| Commodities | Energy, precious metals | Up to 1:50 |\n| Indices | S&P 500, DAX, and more | Up to 1:20 |\n| Crypto | 36 digital assets (BTC, ETH, etc.) | Up to 1:10 |\n\n### Trading Platforms\n\nBrightFunded now supports three platforms — **MetaTrader 5 (MT5)**, **cTrader**, and **DXTrade**. All are available on desktop, mobile, and web.\n\n- **MT5** is the industry standard and the best choice if you want advanced charting, fast execution, and automated trading with Expert Advisors.\n- **cTrader** is designed for precision and speed, with features like Level II depth of market, customizable charts, and support for C# algo trading.\n- **DXTrade** is the most beginner-friendly, with a simple layout, built-in risk tools, and multi-asset support, making it an option for discretionary traders.\n\n### Trust and Support\n\nBrightFunded holds a **4.7/5 on Trustpilot**, with praise for fast payouts and clear policies. The firm has a Discord server with 16,000+ members that fosters collaboration and strategy discussion. Customer support is available 24/7 via email, live chat, and WhatsApp, alongside comprehensive FAQs and platform guides for all traders.\n\n### Final Verdict\n\nBrightFunded's flexibility, unlimited scaling, and trader rewards make it an ideal choice for both beginners and experienced traders in India. Its two-step challenges and customisable options provide growth opportunities, while fast payouts and community engagement ensure a supportive trading environment.\n\n---\n\n## 5. Blueberry Funded — Good Stock and Crypto Prop Firm\n\nBlueberry Funded is the fifth best prop firm in India, standing out for its low fees, stock and crypto access, and four evaluation models that suit beginners and advanced traders alike. The firm is backed by a regulated broker and offers scaling up to $2 million, helping Indian traders grow their funded accounts long-term.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/blueberry-funded-logo.png\" alt=\"Blueberry Funded logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\" />\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">Blueberry Funded\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">Good Stock and Crypto Prop Firm\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">90%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Max DD\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">10%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Trustpilot\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">4.1 \u003Cspan class=\"text-amber-500\">★\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Ca href=\"/reviews/blueberry-funded\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-lg bg-teal-500 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-white hover:bg-teal-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n        Full Review →\n      \u003C/a>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose -mt-3 mb-6 rounded-xl border border-emerald-200 bg-emerald-50/80 px-5 py-3 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-3\">\n  \u003Ca href=\"https://blueberryfunded.com/?utm_source=affiliate&ref=1457\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-emerald-500 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-emerald-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14\" />\u003C/svg>\n    Visit Blueberry Funded\n  \u003C/a>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2.5\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4 text-emerald-600 flex-shrink-0\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M7 7h.01M7 3h5c.512 0 1.024.195 1.414.586l7 7a2 2 0 010 2.828l-7 7a2 2 0 01-2.828 0l-7-7A1.994 1.994 0 013 12V7a4 4 0 014-4z\" />\u003C/svg>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm text-emerald-700 font-semibold\">20% Off — Code:\u003C/span>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"font-mono font-bold text-xs bg-white border border-dashed border-emerald-300 px-3 py-1.5 rounded text-emerald-700 tracking-wide select-all\">PROPFIRMS20\u003C/span>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Pros & Cons\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Pros\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Low fees with refundable challenges\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Access to over 1,100 financial markets\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Profit splits up to 90%\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Higher fees for premium challenges\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Cryptos have restricted leverage\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Minimal educational materials\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n### Evaluation Process\n\nBlueberry Funded offers four challenge types, each designed for a different style of trader:\n\n| Feature | 1 Step | 2 Step | Rapid | Stock Challenge |\n|---------|--------|--------|-------|----------------|\n| **Phases** | 1 | 2 | 1 | 2 |\n| **Profit Target** | 10% | 10% / 5% | 5% | 10% / 6% |\n| **Daily Loss Limit** | 4% | 5% | 5% | 5% |\n| **Max Drawdown** | 6% static | 10% | 6% trailing | 10% |\n| **Time Limit** | None | None | 7 days | None |\n| **Consistency Rule** | No | No | No | Yes |\n| **Starting Fee** | $40 | $35 | $50 | $32.50 |\n\nAll challenge fees are refunded after your first payout. With this range, Blueberry is a strong choice whether you're a day trader, crypto scalper, or stock swing trader.\n\n### Fees and Profit Payouts\n\nFees at Blueberry Funded start from $32.50 for the Stock Challenge, $35 for the 2 Step, and $40 for the 1 Step. Even the Rapid Challenge — which offers the fastest route to a funded account — starts from just $50.\n\nProfit splits begin at 80%, with upgrades to 90% available for traders who withdraw consistently. Payouts are available every 14 days, with a minimum profit of $100 required. Payments are processed through RiseWorks, using crypto options like USDT and USDC. Challenge fees can be paid using crypto or credit card, though e-wallets like Neteller and Skrill aren't currently supported.\n\n### Markets and Leverage\n\nBlueberry Funded offers one of the broadest market selections of any prop firm, including both crypto and stocks:\n\n| Asset Class | Instruments | Leverage |\n|------------|------------|---------|\n| Forex | 45 pairs | Up to 1:50 (2 Step) / 1:30 (others) |\n| Stocks | 1,000+ US stocks (Stock Challenge only) | 1:10 |\n| Crypto | 52 coins, tradable 24/7 | 1:2 |\n| Indices | 14 global indices | 1:10 |\n| Commodities | 17 assets (gold, silver, oil) | 1:10 |\n\nYou can trade crypto and commodities commission-free, and the AUD/USD and EUR/USD spreads are among the tightest in the industry.\n\n### Trading Platforms\n\nBlueberry Funded supports four platforms, giving Indian traders the freedom to choose based on preference:\n\n- **MetaTrader 4 (MT4):** Simple UI, great for forex and EAs.\n- **MetaTrader 5 (MT5):** Required for stock trading, includes more indicators.\n- **DXTrade:** Browser-based with a flexible layout.\n- **TradeLocker:** Fast and mobile-friendly, also supports stock trading.\n\nAll challenge types are available on MT4, MT5, DXTrade, and TradeLocker — except the Stock Challenge, which is only available on MT5 and TradeLocker.\n\n### Trust and Support\n\nBlueberry Funded is backed by Blueberry Markets, an ASIC-regulated broker, and is a founding member of The Prop Association, which promotes transparency in the industry. It has a **Trustpilot rating of 4.1/5** and an established Discord community. Customer support is available 24/5 via live chat and email, though educational content is limited.\n\n### Final Verdict\n\nBlueberry Funded is the best prop firm in India for stock and crypto traders. You get access to 1,000+ shares, 52 cryptocurrencies, and four different challenge types starting from just $32.50. Its 14-day payout cycle, strong platform range, and backing by a regulated broker all make it a safe and practical choice.\n\nIt's also one of the most affordable prop firms, and the only one in this list offering a dedicated Stock Challenge with strict but fair rules for equity trading.\n\n---\n\n## How We Rank the Best Prop Firms\n\nWe tested dozens of prop firms to identify the best options for Indian traders, focusing on factors that directly impact their trading experience and potential earnings. Our research involved rigorous evaluation of key metrics, ensuring that our recommendations align with the needs of both beginner and advanced traders.\n\nOur methodology involves assessing each prop trading firm across multiple categories:\n\n- **Challenge Accounts:** We examined the variety of challenges offered, ensuring that prop firms cater to different trading styles and risk levels. Firms with flexible and transparent evaluation processes scored higher.\n- **Trading Costs:** Spread and commission fees were analysed to find firms with competitive, transparent pricing structures, particularly for high-frequency traders.\n- **Markets and Leverage:** We evaluated firms based on their market diversity, ensuring access to forex, indices, commodities, and cryptocurrencies, paired with balanced leverage levels suited to traders in India.\n- **Payments and Profit Payouts:** Firms were rated on profit split percentages, payout frequency, and minimum withdrawal requirements to identify those offering the best value for traders.\n- **Trading Platforms:** We tested platforms like MT4, MT5, and cTrader for their usability, features, and accessibility across devices, ensuring compatibility with Indian traders' preferences.\n- **Customer Support and Education:** We rated firms on the availability of support channels and quality of educational resources, prioritising those that provide timely assistance and practical training for traders.\n- **Trust and Community:** Trustpilot scores, community engagement, and transparency in policies were key factors in determining a firm's credibility and supportiveness.\n\nBy integrating these insights into a weighted scoring system, we ensured that our rankings reflect the real-world needs of Indian traders. This systematic approach provides a balanced view of each firm's strengths and limitations, helping you make informed decisions when selecting a prop trading partner.\n\n---\n\n## Most Popular Prop Firms In India\n\nFundedNext is the most popular prop trading firm in India, with 90,500 monthly Google searches — far exceeding any other provider. Its wide platform access, flexible challenge formats, and high payout potential make it a top choice for Indian traders looking to grow with prop capital.\n\nThe Funded Trader ranks second with 18,100 monthly searches, driven by its large online community and accessible challenge structure. FTMO remains third with 12,100 searches, reflecting strong global reputation despite not offering instant funding or localised features for Indian users.\n\nOther firms like FXIFY (4,400) and Blueberry Funded (3,600) show growing interest, likely due to low-cost funding options, platform flexibility, and crypto or stock access — features increasingly important to India's retail trading base.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-lg overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"bg-[#0d1b2a] px-5 py-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2.5\">\n      \u003Csvg class=\"h-5 w-5 text-teal-400 flex-shrink-0\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\n        \u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z\" />\n      \u003C/svg>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-black text-white uppercase tracking-wide flex-1\">Most Searched Indian Prop Firms\u003C/p>\n      \u003Csvg class=\"h-5 w-[26px] flex-shrink-0 rounded-[3px]\" viewBox=\"0 0 60 30\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n        \u003Crect width=\"60\" height=\"10\" fill=\"#FF9933\"/>\n        \u003Crect y=\"10\" width=\"60\" height=\"10\" fill=\"#FFFFFF\"/>\n        \u003Crect y=\"20\" width=\"60\" height=\"10\" fill=\"#138808\"/>\n        \u003Ccircle cx=\"30\" cy=\"15\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#000080\" stroke-width=\"0.6\"/>\n        \u003Ccircle cx=\"30\" cy=\"15\" r=\"0.6\" fill=\"#000080\"/>\n      \u003C/svg>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cp class=\"text-[11px] text-slate-400 mt-1\">Based on monthly Google search volume in India\u003C/p>\n  \u003C/div>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center px-5 py-2 bg-teal-500 text-[10px] font-bold text-white uppercase tracking-widest\">\n    \u003Cspan class=\"w-8 flex-shrink-0\">#\u003C/span>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"flex-1\">Firm\u003C/span>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"text-right\">Searches/mo\u003C/span>\n  \u003C/div>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"divide-y divide-slate-100\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-3 px-5 py-2.5 hover:bg-teal-50/50 transition-colors\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-6 text-xs font-black text-slate-400\">1.\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/fundednext.png\" alt=\"FundedNext\" class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-md object-contain border border-slate-200 bg-white p-0.5 flex-shrink-0\" />\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-1 text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">FundedNext\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500\">90,500\u003C/span>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-3 px-5 py-2.5 hover:bg-teal-50/50 transition-colors\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-6 text-xs font-black text-slate-400\">2.\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/the-funded-trader-1-1-1-1.png\" alt=\"The Funded Trader\" class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-md object-contain border border-slate-200 bg-white p-0.5 flex-shrink-0\" />\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-1 text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">The Funded Trader\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500\">18,100\u003C/span>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-3 px-5 py-2.5 hover:bg-teal-50/50 transition-colors\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-6 text-xs font-black text-slate-400\">3.\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/ftmo-logo-2-2-1-1-1.png\" alt=\"FTMO\" class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-md object-contain border border-slate-200 bg-white p-0.5 flex-shrink-0\" />\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-1 text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">FTMO\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500\">12,100\u003C/span>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-3 px-5 py-2.5 hover:bg-teal-50/50 transition-colors\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-6 text-xs font-black text-slate-400\">4.\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/fxify-1-1-1-1.png\" alt=\"FXIFY\" class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-md object-contain border border-slate-200 bg-white p-0.5 flex-shrink-0\" />\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-1 text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">FXIFY\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500\">4,400\u003C/span>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-3 px-5 py-2.5 hover:bg-teal-50/50 transition-colors\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-6 text-xs font-black text-slate-400\">5.\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/blueberry-funded-logo.png\" alt=\"Blueberry Funded\" class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-md object-contain border border-slate-200 bg-white p-0.5 flex-shrink-0\" />\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-1 text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Blueberry Funded\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500\">3,600\u003C/span>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-3 px-5 py-2.5 hover:bg-teal-50/50 transition-colors\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-6 text-xs font-black text-slate-400\">6.\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/ic-funded-logo.png\" alt=\"IC Funded\" class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-md object-contain border border-slate-200 bg-white p-0.5 flex-shrink-0\" />\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-1 text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">IC Funded\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500\">720\u003C/span>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-3 px-5 py-2.5 hover:bg-teal-50/50 transition-colors\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-6 text-xs font-black text-slate-400\">7.\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/thinkcapital-icon.png\" alt=\"ThinkCapital\" class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-md object-contain border border-slate-200 bg-white p-0.5 flex-shrink-0\" />\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-1 text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">ThinkCapital\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500\">390\u003C/span>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-3 px-5 py-2.5 hover:bg-teal-50/50 transition-colors\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-6 text-xs font-black text-slate-400\">8.\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/brightfunded-logo.png\" alt=\"BrightFunded\" class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-md object-contain border border-slate-200 bg-white p-0.5 flex-shrink-0\" />\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-1 text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">BrightFunded\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500\">320\u003C/span>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-3 px-5 py-2.5 hover:bg-teal-50/50 transition-colors\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-6 text-xs font-black text-slate-400\">9.\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/dna-funded-logo.png\" alt=\"DNA Funded\" class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-md object-contain border border-slate-200 bg-white p-0.5 flex-shrink-0\" />\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-1 text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">DNA Funded\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500\">150\u003C/span>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n---\n\n## How To Choose The Right Indian Prop Trading Firm\n\nWe have provided our list (in order) of the top proprietary trading firms for Indian traders but the final choice could come down to a few factors.\n\n### 1. Reputation and Track Record\n\nThe most important factor for traders in India is trust, leading to firms being researched based on their standing in the trading community. The history of the company is often also researched including how long they have been offering prop trading (or CFD trading), how reliable their payouts are and their overall stability. Forums and review sites (such as Trustpilot) are often the primary sources to get this information.\n\n### 2. Regulatory Compliance\n\nProp firms don't require regulation including being setup under the Securities and Exchange Board of India (SEBI). That said, broker-backed firms that also offer forex trading or share trading require regulation by default and must adhere to industry standards.\n\n### 3. Capital and Funding Process\n\nUnderstand the prop trading firm's funding process and the capital requirements. This includes the evaluation phases at each stage and the funding required at each stage to match your capital expectations.\n\n### 4. Fees\n\nUnderstanding all the prop trading fees of a firm is a must. There can be hidden fees that require additional funding or fees that impact the chances of passing a stage such as spreads, commissions or even trading platform fees.\n\n### 5. Profit Payout Policies\n\nIf you pass the evaluation stages it's important to understand what profit-share is available and when the firm will payout. How much capital they will make available is also important as it will dictate the potential profit a trader may make.\n\n### 6. Trading Platforms\n\nMost individuals that have traded before have a preference when it comes to the trading software they use such as MetaTrader 4 (MT4), MetaTrader 5 (MT5), cTrader or TradingView. These traders should shortlist the prop firms that offer the trading software that they are familiar with.\n\n### 7. Risk Management\n\nAll prop firms have inbuilt risk management tools (e.g. margin requirements) which exist to protect traders when their account balances run low or limit leverage. This can impact trading styles and lead to the early exits of evaluation stages so understanding the firm's in-built systems is a must.\n\n### 8. Community and Customer Support\n\nProp traders require more support than general forex traders. This is because many individuals are new to trading, have questions about evaluation stages, and require additional onboarding. For this reason, traders should look at the types and quality of the customer service available and if a wider community can support them, such as Discord, to help them during the onboarding and evaluation period.\n\n---\n\n## FAQs\n\n### What is the best prop firm in India?\n\nFundedNext is the best prop firm in India, offering flexible challenges, high profit splits up to 95%, and fast bi-weekly payouts. You can choose between one-step or two-step models, trade on MT4, MT5, or cTrader, and access forex, indices, commodities, and crypto. With low fees starting from $32 and a strong Indian user base, it's the top prop firm for traders seeking capital and consistent funding options.\n\n### Is prop fund trading legal in India?\n\nYes, prop fund trading is legal in India. Traders can access capital through top prop trading firms like FXIFY or DNA Funded, among others. These prop firms offer a variety of challenges, flexible profit splits, and advanced trading platforms like MT4 and MT5. With options tailored to different styles and experience levels, Indian traders can benefit from scalable funding opportunities and competitive profit-sharing arrangements through these proprietary trading firms.\n\n### Are there any prop trading firms in India?\n\nYes, Indian traders can choose from a number of top prop firms, including FXIFY, popular for its flexible challenges and profit splits up to 90%, and DNA Funded, who we consider to be the best broker-backed prop firm with low fees and access to over 800 markets. BrightFunded is another strong option, with its Trade2Earn Rewards Program allowing traders to earn tokens for upgrades or free challenges.\n\n### Is Forex prop trading a good idea in India?\n\nYes, forex prop trading can be a good idea in India, as it provides traders with access to significant capital without risking their own funds. It's ideal for disciplined traders who can meet profit targets and manage drawdowns effectively. By trading on advanced platforms like MT4 and MT5, you can access global forex markets with competitive spreads. For a detailed guide, visit our list of the [top forex prop firms](/prop-firms).\n\n### What is the most trusted prop firm?\n\nThe most trusted prop firms are broker-backed firms, as they operate in partnership with regulated brokers, ensuring secure trading conditions and transparent policies. These firms offer access to reliable trading platforms and low-cost trading environments. DNA Funded is a prime example, known for its partnership with a regulated broker. To learn more about the most trusted firms, read about the [best prop trading firms](/prop-firms).\n\n### What is a prop trading firm?\n\nProp trading firms provide traders with capital to trade financial markets, earning a share of profits in return. Traders undergo evaluations or access instant funding to trade larger amounts without risking personal money. These prop firms generate revenue through fees, profit splits, and additional services, making them a popular choice for skilled traders looking to scale.","src/content/blog/india.md","6b2a7c902cf0bdc7",{"html":6076,"metadata":6077},"\u003Ch2 id=\"which-prop-firm-is-the-best-in-india\">Which Prop Firm Is The Best In India?\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>The best prop firm for Indian traders depends on the individual’s requirements so we have shortlisted the top prop trading firms based on the challenge pricing tiers, profit splits and access to major trading platforms. Based on the shortlisted firms you can find the prop trading firm best suited for your needs. You can also find a list of the top 10 futures prop firms in India if you are focusing on futures markets rather than CFD trading.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"what-to-look-for-as-an-indian-trader\">What to Look for as an Indian Trader\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>Before diving into our ranked list, here’s what matters most when evaluating a prop firm from an Indian perspective.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"sebi-regulation-vs-offshore-operations\">SEBI Regulation vs Offshore Operations\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Most prop firms operate offshore and are \u003Cem>not\u003C/em> regulated by the Securities and Exchange Board of India (SEBI). This is common across the industry — prop firms are not offering financial products to retail clients, they are running evaluation challenges and funded account programmes. However, regulation in other jurisdictions (such as ASIC in Australia or CySEC in Cyprus) does provide a meaningful layer of legitimacy and trader protection that you should look for.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"payout-track-record\">Payout Track Record\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>A firm’s payout history is the most important trust signal. Look for firms with Trustpilot scores above 4.0, a large community of verified paid-out traders, and transparent terms around withdrawals. Firms that have been operating for 3+ years with consistent payouts are significantly lower risk than newer entrants.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"inr-payment-options\">INR Payment Options\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Most prop firms charge in USD, which means Indian traders should factor in currency conversion costs. Some firms support crypto payouts which can offer more flexibility. Look for firms with multiple withdrawal options including bank transfer and crypto to minimise conversion fees.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"platform-availability\">Platform Availability\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>MT4, MT5, and cTrader are the most common platforms and all work well for Indian traders. Some newer firms offer TradeLocker or proprietary platforms. Make sure the platform supports your preferred trading style, whether that’s manual trading, EAs, or algo strategies.\u003C/p>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"1-fundednext--best-prop-firm-in-india\">1. FundedNext — Best Prop Firm in India\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>FundedNext is the best prop trading firm for Indian traders, offering three tailored challenge models — Stellar One Step, Stellar Two Step, and Stellar Lite — with account sizes from $5,000 to $200,000. Traders can earn up to 95% profit share and benefit from payouts as early as five days after passing.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/fundednext.png\" alt=\"FundedNext logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">FundedNext\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">Best Prop Firm in India\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">95%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Max DD\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">10%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Trustpilot\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">4.6 \u003Cspan class=\"text-amber-500\">★\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Ca href=\"/reviews/fundednext\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-lg bg-teal-500 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-white hover:bg-teal-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n        Full Review →\n      \u003C/a>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose -mt-3 mb-6 flex justify-center\">\n  \u003Ca href=\"https://fundednext.com/?fpr=noam82\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-emerald-500 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-emerald-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n    Visit FundedNext\n  \u003C/a>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Pros &#x26; Cons\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Pros\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Profit splits up to 95%\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Scaling plan to $4 million\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Free retakes and extensions\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>No instant funding\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>cTrader and Match-Trader cost $25\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>News trading limits apply once funded\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"evaluation-process\">Evaluation Process\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>FundedNext offers three challenge types:\u003C/p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003Ctable>\u003Cthead>\u003Ctr>\u003Cth>Feature\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Stellar One Step\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Stellar Two Step\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Stellar Lite\u003C/th>\u003C/tr>\u003C/thead>\u003Ctbody>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>Phases\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>2\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>2\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>Profit Target\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>10%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>8% / 5%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>8% / 4%\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>Daily Loss Limit\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>3%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>5%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>4%\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>Max Drawdown\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>6%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>10%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>8%\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>Profit Share (Challenge)\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>15%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>15%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>None\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>Profit Share (Funded)\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Up to 95%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Up to 95%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Up to 95%\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>First Payout\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>5 days\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Bi-weekly\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Bi-weekly\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>Time Limit\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>None\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>None\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>None\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>Starting Fee\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$65\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$59\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$32\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003C/tbody>\u003C/table>\n\u003Cp>All models have no time limits and optional add-ons, including no minimum trading days and extended drawdowns.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"fees-and-profit-payouts\">Fees and Profit Payouts\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Fees range from $32 to $1,099 depending on model and account size. Profit splits are capped at 95%, with 15% profit share paid during the challenge on Stellar accounts. Withdrawals start from $20 (crypto-only under $50) and are processed bi-weekly using Deel, crypto, or bank transfer.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"markets-and-leverage\">Markets and Leverage\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>FundedNext gives access to 83 markets across four asset classes:\u003C/p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003Ctable>\u003Cthead>\u003Ctr>\u003Cth>Asset Class\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Leverage\u003C/th>\u003C/tr>\u003C/thead>\u003Ctbody>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Forex\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Up to 100:1\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Indices\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Up to 50:1\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Commodities\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Up to 50:1\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Crypto\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>2:1\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003C/tbody>\u003C/table>\n\u003Cp>This setup supports flexible trading strategies while maintaining risk control.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"trading-platforms\">Trading Platforms\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>FundedNext supports four major platforms:\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>MT4 &#x26; MT5:\u003C/strong> Free and compatible with EAs (MT5 also has TradingView integration).\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>cTrader:\u003C/strong> Manual-friendly but costs $25; not available for 100K+ accounts.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Match-Trader:\u003C/strong> Browser-based, also $25 fee, not available for 100K+ accounts.\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"trust-and-support\">Trust and Support\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>FundedNext holds a \u003Cstrong>4.6/5 on Trustpilot\u003C/strong>, reflecting strong satisfaction from traders globally. The firm has an active Discord community with hundreds of thousands of members, plus Telegram and social media engagement. Customer support is available 24/7 via live chat and email, with enhanced Pro Support for funded traders. Educational resources include extensive FAQs, guides, and 1,200+ videos on YouTube.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"final-verdict\">Final Verdict\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>FundedNext leads for Indian traders thanks to its competitive pricing, up to 95% payouts, flexible models, and quick withdrawals. Its strong community and optional add-ons make it a standout choice, even if strict news trading rules and platform fees apply on some accounts.\u003C/p>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"2-fxify--best-instant-funding-prop-firm\">2. FXIFY — Best Instant Funding Prop Firm\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>FXIFY is a strong prop trading firm for Indian traders, offering a variety of challenges, customisable accounts, and reliable platforms like MT4, MT5, and DXTrade. With profit splits of up to 90% and a strong trading community of over 38,000 members, it’s a solid option for both beginners and experienced traders.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/fxify-1-1-1-1.png\" alt=\"FXIFY logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">FXIFY\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">Best Instant Funding Prop Firm\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">90%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Max DD\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">10%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Trustpilot\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">4.1 \u003Cspan class=\"text-amber-500\">★\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Ca href=\"/reviews/fxify\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-lg bg-teal-500 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-white hover:bg-teal-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n        Full Review →\n      \u003C/a>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose -mt-3 mb-6 rounded-xl border border-emerald-200 bg-emerald-50/80 px-5 py-3 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-3\">\n  \u003Ca href=\"https://trader.fxify.com/purchasechallenge?affiliateId=5837\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-emerald-500 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-emerald-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4