ule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Instant funding available\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>MT4, MT5, and TradingView\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Add-ons increase fees\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Limited educational resources\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Leverage capped at 30:1 by default\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"evaluation-process-1\">Evaluation Process\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>FXIFY offers four challenge types plus instant funding, each tailored to different trading styles and experience levels:\u003C/p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003Ctable>\u003Cthead>\u003Ctr>\u003Cth>Feature\u003C/th>\u003Cth>One Phase\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Two Phase\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Three Phase\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Lightning\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Instant Funding\u003C/th>\u003C/tr>\u003C/thead>\u003Ctbody>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>Phases\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>2\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>3\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1 (7 days)\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>None\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>Profit Target\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>10%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>10% / 5%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>5% per phase\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>5%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>—\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>Daily Loss Limit\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>3%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>3%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>3%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>3%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>3%\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>Max Drawdown\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>6% trailing\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>10% trailing\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>10% static\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>6% trailing\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>8% trailing\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>Time Limit\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>None\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>None\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>None\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>7 days\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>—\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>Starting Fee\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$59\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$59\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$39\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$59\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$69\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>Max Account\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$400K\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$400K\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$400K\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$100K\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$50K\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003C/tbody>\u003C/table>\n\u003Cp>Each challenge has no maximum trading day limit (except Lightning), allowing traders to proceed at their own pace.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"fees-and-profit-payouts-1\">Fees and Profit Payouts\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Challenge fees range from $39 to $2,950, depending on the account size and challenge type. Add-ons such as increased leverage or a higher profit split incur additional costs. All fees are fully refundable after the first successful withdrawal.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Profit splits start at 80% and can be upgraded to 90% with an add-on. Traders can request their first payout immediately after achieving profitability, with monthly payouts by default. A bi-weekly payout option is available for an extra fee, offering flexibility for traders who prioritise frequent withdrawals.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"markets-and-leverage-1\">Markets and Leverage\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>FXIFY offers access to a variety of asset classes, though its leverage is conservative to encourage responsible trading. Traders can use up to 30:1 leverage on forex and gold, with an option to increase to 50:1 for a fee.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Forex:\u003C/strong> 42 currency pairs, including majors, minors, and exotics\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Indices:\u003C/strong> 13 global indices, including S&#x26;P 500 and Nifty\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Commodities:\u003C/strong> Gold, silver, and crude oil\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Stocks:\u003C/strong> 30 equities, available exclusively on MT5\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Cryptocurrencies:\u003C/strong> Bitcoin, Ethereum, and Ripple on MT4/MT5\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"trading-platforms-1\">Trading Platforms\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>FXIFY supports three major platforms, offering a range of tools and features to suit different trading strategies:\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>MT4:\u003C/strong> Ideal for automated trading with EAs and a user-friendly interface.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>MT5:\u003C/strong> Offers multi-asset capabilities, depth of market data, and advanced order types for experienced traders.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>DXTrade + TradingView:\u003C/strong> Combines DXTrade’s customisation with TradingView’s powerful charting tools, suitable for traders focused on detailed technical analysis.\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"trust-and-support-1\">Trust and Support\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>FXIFY holds a \u003Cstrong>4.1/5 on Trustpilot\u003C/strong>, with reviews highlighting quick payouts and flexible trading rules. The firm has a Discord server with 38,000+ members and active social media channels connecting traders. Customer support is available via live chat and email, though response times may vary during high traffic periods. Educational resources are limited, with a basic FAQ section and minimal video tutorials.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"final-verdict-1\">Final Verdict\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>FXIFY’s flexible challenges, customisable accounts, and active community make it a strong choice for Indian traders. With profit splits up to 90% and reliable platforms like MT4, MT5, and DXTrade, FXIFY provides the tools, flexibility, and support needed for traders to grow and succeed.\u003C/p>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"3-dna-funded--top-broker-backed-prop-firm\">3. DNA Funded — Top Broker Backed Prop Firm\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>DNA Funded is a top prop firm with low fees, reliable trading conditions, and funding options for all traders. Backed by DNA Markets, it offers tight spreads and fast execution. With three challenge types — Single Helix, Double Helix, and Rapid Challenge — it provides flexibility and profit splits of up to 90%.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/dna-funded-logo.png\" alt=\"DNA Funded logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">DNA Funded\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">Top Broker Backed Prop Firm\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">90%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Max DD\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">10%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Trustpilot\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">3.5 \u003Cspan class=\"text-amber-500\">★\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Ca href=\"/reviews/dna-funded\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-lg bg-teal-500 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-white hover:bg-teal-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n        Full Review →\n      \u003C/a>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose -mt-3 mb-6 rounded-xl border border-emerald-200 bg-emerald-50/80 px-5 py-3 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-3\">\n  \u003Ca href=\"https://partners.dnafunded.com/click?campaign_id=1&#x26;ref_id=30\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-emerald-500 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-emerald-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n    Visit DNA Funded\n  \u003C/a>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2.5\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4 text-emerald-600 flex-shrink-0\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M7 7h.01M7 3h5c.512 0 1.024.195 1.414.586l7 7a2 2 0 010 2.828l-7 7a2 2 0 01-2.828 0l-7-7A1.994 1.994 0 013 12V7a4 4 0 014-4z\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm text-emerald-700 font-semibold\">25% Off — Code:\u003C/span>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"font-mono font-bold text-xs bg-white border border-dashed border-emerald-300 px-3 py-1.5 rounded text-emerald-700 tracking-wide select-all\">PROPFIRMS25\u003C/span>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Pros &#x26; Cons\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Pros\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Access to over 800 instruments\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Profit splits up to 90%\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Broker-backed by DNA Markets\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Newly launched, fewer reviews\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>No scaling plan currently\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Basic educational resources\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"evaluation-process-2\">Evaluation Process\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>DNA Funded’s evaluation process includes three challenge types, each tailored to different trading strategies and skill levels:\u003C/p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003Ctable>\u003Cthead>\u003Ctr>\u003Cth>Feature\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Single Helix\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Double Helix\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Rapid Challenge\u003C/th>\u003C/tr>\u003C/thead>\u003Ctbody>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>Phases\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>2\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>Profit Target\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>10%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>10% / 5%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>5%\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>Daily Loss Limit\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>5%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>5%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>5%\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>Max Drawdown\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>10%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>10%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>10%\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>Time Limit\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>None\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>None\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>10 days\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>Profit Split\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>80% (up to 90%)\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>80% (up to 90%)\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>80% (up to 90%)\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>Starting Fee\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$49\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$49\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$49\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003C/tbody>\u003C/table>\n\u003Cp>Each challenge offers 80% profit splits, upgradeable to 90% through add-ons, and traders have the option to customise accounts for faster payouts.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"fees-and-profit-payouts-2\">Fees and Profit Payouts\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>DNA Funded’s fees range from $49 to $1,451, depending on the account size and challenge type. Add-ons for a higher profit split or faster payouts incur additional costs, with fees increasing by 20%–30%. All fees are one-time and refundable after the first successful withdrawal.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>You start with an 80% profit split, upgradeable to 90%. Payouts follow a 14-day cycle by default, with an optional add-on reducing the cycle to 7 days for quicker access to profits.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>A 40% daily profit cap also applies across all challenges. This means no more than 40% of your payout target can be generated in a single trading day. The cap supports consistent performance and reflects DNA Funded’s broker-backed compliance model.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Flexible payout methods, including cryptocurrency and bank transfers, accommodate traders in India and beyond.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"markets-and-leverage-2\">Markets and Leverage\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>DNA Funded gives traders access to over 800 financial instruments:\u003C/p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003Ctable>\u003Cthead>\u003Ctr>\u003Cth>Asset Class\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Instruments\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Leverage\u003C/th>\u003C/tr>\u003C/thead>\u003Ctbody>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Forex\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Majors, minors, exotics\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Up to 1:50\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Indices\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>S&#x26;P 500, Nifty, and more\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Up to 1:10\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Commodities\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Gold, silver, crude oil\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Up to 1:10\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Stocks\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Diverse equity options\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Up to 1:5\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Crypto\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Available on Single &#x26; Double Helix\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Up to 1:2\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003C/tbody>\u003C/table>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"trading-platforms-2\">Trading Platforms\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>DNA Funded supports one trading platform — \u003Cstrong>TradeLocker\u003C/strong> integrated with TradingView. This user-friendly platform offers advanced charting tools, seamless on-chart trading, and reliable performance across devices. It’s ideal for manual traders focused on technical analysis. Since DNA Funded discontinued its support of DXTrade, automated trading with Expert Advisors is no longer available.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"trust-and-support-2\">Trust and Support\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Although newly launched, DNA Funded benefits from its partnership with DNA Markets, a well-regarded ASIC-regulated liquidity provider, lending credibility to the firm. DNA Funded holds a \u003Cstrong>3.5/5 on Trustpilot\u003C/strong> and is building a trader community through Discord, with channels for strategy discussions and support. Customer support is currently limited to email but expected to expand.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"final-verdict-2\">Final Verdict\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>DNA Funded’s combination of low fees, flexible challenges, and strong backing from DNA Markets makes it a top choice for traders in India. Its customisable options, high profit splits, and access to 800+ markets ensure appeal for both beginners and experienced traders. As the firm continues to grow, its value as a reliable prop trading option is set to increase.\u003C/p>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"4-brightfunded--best-prop-trader-rewards-program\">4. BrightFunded — Best Prop Trader Rewards Program\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>BrightFunded is a top prop trading firm, known for its flexible challenges, trader-focused add-ons, and a unique reward system. With account sizes ranging from $5K to $200K, its two-step evaluation process, unlimited scaling plan, and unique Trade2Earn Rewards Program make it a great option for Indian traders.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/brightfunded-logo.png\" alt=\"BrightFunded logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">BrightFunded\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">Best Prop Trader Rewards Program\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">100%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Max DD\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">10%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Trustpilot\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">4.7 \u003Cspan class=\"text-amber-500\">★\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Ca href=\"/reviews/brightfunded\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-lg bg-teal-500 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-white hover:bg-teal-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n        Full Review →\n      \u003C/a>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose -mt-3 mb-6 rounded-xl border border-emerald-200 bg-emerald-50/80 px-5 py-3 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-3\">\n  \u003Ca href=\"https://brightfunded.com?affiliateId=rsBbtrzYQSyr3RcHYHQT5w\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-emerald-500 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-emerald-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002