l two-step evaluation\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>No minimum trading days with add-on\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Add-ons increase costs\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>No MetaTrader 4, but MT5 added\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>No stock markets\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"evaluation-process-3\">Evaluation Process\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>BrightFunded’s challenges involve a multi-stage evaluation process, with clear rules and the opportunity to customise your trading experience:\u003C/p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003Ctable>\u003Cthead>\u003Ctr>\u003Cth>Feature\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Phase 1\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Phase 2\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Funded Account\u003C/th>\u003C/tr>\u003C/thead>\u003Ctbody>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>Profit Target\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>8%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>5%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>—\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>Daily Loss Limit\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>5%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>5%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>5%\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>Max Drawdown\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>10%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>10%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>10%\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>Min Trading Days\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>5 (waivable)\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>5 (waivable)\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>—\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>Time Limit\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>None\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>None\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>—\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>Profit Split\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>—\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>—\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Up to 100%\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003C/tbody>\u003C/table>\n\u003Cp>BrightFunded allows traders to personalise their challenges with add-ons like higher profit splits, faster payouts, and waived minimum trading day requirements.\u003C/p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003Ctable>\u003Cthead>\u003Ctr>\u003Cth>Account Size\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Challenge Fee\u003C/th>\u003C/tr>\u003C/thead>\u003Ctbody>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>$5,000\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>€55\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>$10,000\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>€95\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>$25,000\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>€195\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>$50,000\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>€295\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>$100,000\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>€495\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>$200,000\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>€975\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003C/tbody>\u003C/table>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"fees-and-profit-payouts-3\">Fees and Profit Payouts\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Challenge fees range from €55 to €975 depending on the account size you choose. These fees are a one-time cost with no hidden charges and can be refunded after reaching funded status.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Profit splits start at 80% and can increase to 100% through the scaling plan or add-ons. BrightFunded’s Trade2Earn Rewards Program also allows traders to earn tokens for every trade, which can be redeemed for profit split boosts, free evaluations, or discounts on future challenges.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Payouts are flexible and paid out monthly by default, with add-ons available for weekly or bi-weekly cycles. Payments are processed via bank transfer or cryptocurrency, with no minimum withdrawal limits, making it easy for traders to access their earnings efficiently.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"markets-and-leverage-3\">Markets and Leverage\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>BrightFunded provides access to a diverse range of trading instruments:\u003C/p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003Ctable>\u003Cthead>\u003Ctr>\u003Cth>Asset Class\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Instruments\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Leverage\u003C/th>\u003C/tr>\u003C/thead>\u003Ctbody>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Forex\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>49 pairs (majors, minors, exotics)\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Up to 1:100\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Commodities\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Energy, precious metals\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Up to 1:50\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Indices\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>S&#x26;P 500, DAX, and more\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Up to 1:20\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Crypto\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>36 digital assets (BTC, ETH, etc.)\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Up to 1:10\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003C/tbody>\u003C/table>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"trading-platforms-3\">Trading Platforms\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>BrightFunded now supports three platforms — \u003Cstrong>MetaTrader 5 (MT5)\u003C/strong>, \u003Cstrong>cTrader\u003C/strong>, and \u003Cstrong>DXTrade\u003C/strong>. All are available on desktop, mobile, and web.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>MT5\u003C/strong> is the industry standard and the best choice if you want advanced charting, fast execution, and automated trading with Expert Advisors.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>cTrader\u003C/strong> is designed for precision and speed, with features like Level II depth of market, customizable charts, and support for C# algo trading.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>DXTrade\u003C/strong> is the most beginner-friendly, with a simple layout, built-in risk tools, and multi-asset support, making it an option for discretionary traders.\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"trust-and-support-3\">Trust and Support\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>BrightFunded holds a \u003Cstrong>4.7/5 on Trustpilot\u003C/strong>, with praise for fast payouts and clear policies. The firm has a Discord server with 16,000+ members that fosters collaboration and strategy discussion. Customer support is available 24/7 via email, live chat, and WhatsApp, alongside comprehensive FAQs and platform guides for all traders.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"final-verdict-3\">Final Verdict\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>BrightFunded’s flexibility, unlimited scaling, and trader rewards make it an ideal choice for both beginners and experienced traders in India. Its two-step challenges and customisable options provide growth opportunities, while fast payouts and community engagement ensure a supportive trading environment.\u003C/p>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"5-blueberry-funded--good-stock-and-crypto-prop-firm\">5. Blueberry Funded — Good Stock and Crypto Prop Firm\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>Blueberry Funded is the fifth best prop firm in India, standing out for its low fees, stock and crypto access, and four evaluation models that suit beginners and advanced traders alike. The firm is backed by a regulated broker and offers scaling up to $2 million, helping Indian traders grow their funded accounts long-term.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/blueberry-funded-logo.png\" alt=\"Blueberry Funded logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">Blueberry Funded\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">Good Stock and Crypto Prop Firm\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">90%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Max DD\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">10%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Trustpilot\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">4.1 \u003Cspan class=\"text-amber-500\">★\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Ca href=\"/reviews/blueberry-funded\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-lg bg-teal-500 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-white hover:bg-teal-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n        Full Review →\n      \u003C/a>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose -mt-3 mb-6 rounded-xl border border-emerald-200 bg-emerald-50/80 px-5 py-3 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-3\">\n  \u003Ca href=\"https://blueberryfunded.com/?utm_source=affiliate&#x26;ref=1457\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-emerald-500 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-emerald-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n    Visit Blueberry Funded\n  \u003C/a>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2.5\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4 text-emerald-600 flex-shrink-0\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M7 7h.01M7 3h5c.512 0 1.024.195 1.414.586l7 7a2 2 0 010 2.828l-7 7a2 2 0 01-2.828 0l-7-7A1.994 1.994 0 013 12V7a4 4 0 014-4z\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm text-emerald-700 font-semibold\">20% Off — Code:\u003C/span>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"font-mono font-bold text-xs bg-white border border-dashed border-emerald-300 px-3 py-1.5 rounded text-emerald-700 tracking-wide select-all\">PROPFIRMS20\u003C/span>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Pros &#x26; Cons\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Pros\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Low fees with refundable challenges\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Access to over 1,100 financial markets\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Profit splits up to 90%\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Higher fees for premium challenges\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Cryptos have restricted leverage\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Minimal educational materials\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"evaluation-process-4\">Evaluation Process\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Blueberry Funded offers four challenge types, each designed for a different style of trader:\u003C/p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003Ctable>\u003Cthead>\u003Ctr>\u003Cth>Feature\u003C/th>\u003Cth>1 Step\u003C/th>\u003Cth>2 Step\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Rapid\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Stock Challenge\u003C/th>\u003C/tr>\u003C/thead>\u003Ctbody>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>Phases\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>2\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>2\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>Profit Target\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>10%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>10% / 5%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>5%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>10% / 6%\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>Daily Loss Limit\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>4%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>5%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>5%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>5%\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>Max Drawdown\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>6% static\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>10%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>6% trailing\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>10%\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>Time Limit\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>None\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>None\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>7 days\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>None\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>Consistency Rule\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>No\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>No\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>No\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Yes\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>\u003Cstrong>Starting Fee\u003C/strong>\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$40\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$35\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$50\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$32.50\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003C/tbody>\u003C/table>\n\u003Cp>All challenge fees are refunded after your first payout. With this range, Blueberry is a strong choice whether you’re a day trader, crypto scalper, or stock swing trader.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"fees-and-profit-payouts-4\">Fees and Profit Payouts\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Fees at Blueberry Funded start from $32.50 for the Stock Challenge, $35 for the 2 Step, and $40 for the 1 Step. Even the Rapid Challenge — which offers the fastest route to a funded account — starts from just $50.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Profit splits begin at 80%, with upgrades to 90% available for traders who withdraw consistently. Payouts are available every 14 days, with a minimum profit of $100 required. Payments are processed through RiseWorks, using crypto options like USDT and USDC. Challenge fees can be paid using crypto or credit card, though e-wallets like Neteller and Skrill aren’t currently supported.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"markets-and-leverage-4\">Markets and Leverage\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Blueberry Funded offers one of the broadest market selections of any prop firm, including both crypto and stocks:\u003C/p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003Ctable>\u003Cthead>\u003Ctr>\u003Cth>Asset Class\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Instruments\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Leverage\u003C/th>\u003C/tr>\u003C/thead>\u003Ctbody>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Forex\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>45 pairs\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Up to 1:50 (2 Step) / 1:30 (others)\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Stocks\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1,000+ US stocks (Stock Challenge only)\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1:10\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Crypto\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>52 coins, tradable 24/7\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1:2\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Indices\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>14 global indices\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1:10\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Commodities\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>17 assets (gold, silver, oil)\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1:10\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003C/tbody>\u003C/table>\n\u003Cp>You can trade crypto and commodities commission-free, and the AUD/USD and EUR/USD spreads are among the tightest in the industry.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"trading-platforms-4\">Trading Platforms\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Blueberry Funded supports four platforms, giving Indian traders the freedom to choose based on preference:\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>MetaTrader 4 (MT4):\u003C/strong> Simple UI, great for forex and EAs.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>MetaTrader 5 (MT5):\u003C/strong> Required for stock trading, includes more indicators.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>DXTrade:\u003C/strong> Browser-based with a flexible layout.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>TradeLocker:\u003C/strong> Fast and mobile-friendly, also supports stock trading.\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Cp>All challenge types are available on MT4, MT5, DXTrade, and TradeLocker — except the Stock Challenge, which is only available on MT5 and TradeLocker.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"trust-and-support-4\">Trust and Support\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Blueberry Funded is backed by Blueberry Markets, an ASIC-regulated broker, and is a founding member of The Prop Association, which promotes transparency in the industry. It has a \u003Cstrong>Trustpilot rating of 4.1/5\u003C/strong> and an established Discord community. Customer support is available 24/5 via live chat and email, though educational content is limited.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"final-verdict-4\">Final Verdict\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Blueberry Funded is the best prop firm in India for stock and crypto traders. You get access to 1,000+ shares, 52 cryptocurrencies, and four different challenge types starting from just $32.50. Its 14-day payout cycle, strong platform range, and backing by a regulated broker all make it a safe and practical choice.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>It’s also one of the most affordable prop firms, and the only one in this list offering a dedicated Stock Challenge with strict but fair rules for equity trading.\u003C/p>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"how-we-rank-the-best-prop-firms\">How We Rank the Best Prop Firms\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>We tested dozens of prop firms to identify the best options for Indian traders, focusing on factors that directly impact their trading experience and potential earnings. Our research involved rigorous evaluation of key metrics, ensuring that our recommendations align with the needs of both beginner and advanced traders.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Our methodology involves assessing each prop trading firm across multiple categories:\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Challenge Accounts:\u003C/strong> We examined the variety of challenges offered, ensuring that prop firms cater to different trading styles and risk levels. Firms with flexible and transparent evaluation processes scored higher.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Trading Costs:\u003C/strong> Spread and commission fees were analysed to find firms with competitive, transparent pricing structures, particularly for high-frequency traders.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Markets and Leverage:\u003C/strong> We evaluated firms based on their market diversity, ensuring access to forex, indices, commodities, and cryptocurrencies, paired with balanced leverage levels suited to traders in India.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Payments and Profit Payouts:\u003C/strong> Firms were rated on profit split percentages, payout frequency, and minimum withdrawal requirements to identify those offering the best value for traders.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Trading Platforms:\u003C/strong> We tested platforms like MT4, MT5, and cTrader for their usability, features, and accessibility across devices, ensuring compatibility with Indian traders’ preferences.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Customer Support and Education:\u003C/strong> We rated firms on the availability of support channels and quality of educational resources, prioritising those that provide timely assistance and practical training for traders.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Trust and Community:\u003C/strong> Trustpilot scores, community engagement, and transparency in policies were key factors in determining a firm’s credibility and supportiveness.\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Cp>By integrating these insights into a weighted scoring system, we ensured that our rankings reflect the real-world needs of Indian traders. This systematic approach provides a balanced view of each firm’s strengths and limitations, helping you make informed decisions when selecting a prop trading partner.\u003C/p>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"most-popular-prop-firms-in-india\">Most Popular Prop Firms In India\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>FundedNext is the most popular prop trading firm in India, with 90,500 monthly Google searches — far exceeding any other provider. Its wide platform access, flexible challenge formats, and high payout potential make it a top choice for Indian traders looking to grow with prop capital.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>The Funded Trader ranks second with 18,100 monthly searches, driven by its large online community and accessible challenge structure. FTMO remains third with 12,100 searches, reflecting strong global reputation despite not offering instant funding or localised features for Indian users.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Other firms like FXIFY (4,400) and Blueberry Funded (3,600) show growing interest, likely due to low-cost funding options, platform flexibility, and crypto or stock access — features increasingly important to India’s retail trading base.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-lg overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"bg-[#0d1b2a] px-5 py-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2.5\">\n      \u003Csvg class=\"h-5 w-5 text-teal-400 flex-shrink-0\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\n        \u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z\">\u003C/path>\n      \u003C/svg>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-black text-white uppercase tracking-wide flex-1\">Most Searched Indian Prop Firms\u003C/p>\n      \u003Csvg class=\"h-5 w-[26px] flex-shrink-0 rounded-[3px]\" viewBox=\"0 0 60 30\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n        \u003Crect width=\"60\" height=\"10\" fill=\"#FF9933\">\u003C/rect>\n        \u003Crect y=\"10\" width=\"60\" height=\"10\" fill=\"#FFFFFF\">\u003C/rect>\n        \u003Crect y=\"20\" width=\"60\" height=\"10\" fill=\"#138808\">\u003C/rect>\n        \u003Ccircle cx=\"30\" cy=\"15\" r=\"3.5\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#000080\" stroke-width=\"0.6\">\u003C/circle>\n        \u003Ccircle cx=\"30\" cy=\"15\" r=\"0.6\" fill=\"#000080\">\u003C/circle>\n      \u003C/svg>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cp class=\"text-[11px] text-slate-400 mt-1\">Based on monthly Google search volume in India\u003C/p>\n  \u003C/div>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center px-5 py-2 bg-teal-500 text-[10px] font-bold text-white uppercase tracking-widest\">\n    \u003Cspan class=\"w-8 flex-shrink-0\">#\u003C/span>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"flex-1\">Firm\u003C/span>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"text-right\">Searches/mo\u003C/span>\n  \u003C/div>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"divide-y divide-slate-100\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-3 px-5 py-2.5 hover:bg-teal-50/50 transition-colors\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-6 text-xs font-black text-slate-400\">1.\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/fundednext.png\" alt=\"FundedNext\" class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-md object-contain border border-slate-200 bg-white p-0.5 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-1 text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">FundedNext\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500\">90,500\u003C/span>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-3 px-5 py-2.5 hover:bg-teal-50/50 transition-colors\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-6 text-xs font-black text-slate-400\">2.\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/the-funded-trader-1-1-1-1.png\" alt=\"The Funded Trader\" class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-md object-contain border border-slate-200 bg-white p-0.5 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-1 text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">The Funded Trader\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500\">18,100\u003C/span>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-3 px-5 py-2.5 hover:bg-teal-50/50 transition-colors\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-6 text-xs font-black text-slate-400\">3.\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/ftmo-logo-2-2-1-1-1.png\" alt=\"FTMO\" class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-md object-contain border border-slate-200 bg-white p-0.5 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-1 text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">FTMO\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500\">12,100\u003C/span>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-3 px-5 py-2.5 hover:bg-teal-50/50 transition-colors\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-6 text-xs font-black text-slate-400\">4.\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/fxify-1-1-1-1.png\" alt=\"FXIFY\" class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-md object-contain border border-slate-200 bg-white p-0.5 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-1 text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">FXIFY\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500\">4,400\u003C/span>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-3 px-5 py-2.5 hover:bg-teal-50/50 transition-colors\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-6 text-xs font-black text-slate-400\">5.\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/blueberry-funded-logo.png\" alt=\"Blueberry Funded\" class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-md object-contain border border-slate-200 bg-white p-0.5 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-1 text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Blueberry Funded\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500\">3,600\u003C/span>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-3 px-5 py-2.5 hover:bg-teal-50/50 transition-colors\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-6 text-xs font-black text-slate-400\">6.\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/ic-funded-logo.png\" alt=\"IC Funded\" class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-md object-contain border border-slate-200 bg-white p-0.5 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-1 text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">IC Funded\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500\">720\u003C/span>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-3 px-5 py-2.5 hover:bg-teal-50/50 transition-colors\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-6 text-xs font-black text-slate-400\">7.\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/thinkcapital-icon.png\" alt=\"ThinkCapital\" class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-md object-contain border border-slate-200 bg-white p-0.5 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-1 text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">ThinkCapital\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500\">390\u003C/span>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-3 px-5 py-2.5 hover:bg-teal-50/50 transition-colors\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-6 text-xs font-black text-slate-400\">8.\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/brightfunded-logo.png\" alt=\"BrightFunded\" class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-md object-contain border border-slate-200 bg-white p-0.5 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-1 text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">BrightFunded\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500\">320\u003C/span>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-3 px-5 py-2.5 hover:bg-teal-50/50 transition-colors\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-6 text-xs font-black text-slate-400\">9.\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/dna-funded-logo.png\" alt=\"DNA Funded\" class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-md object-contain border border-slate-200 bg-white p-0.5 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"flex-1 text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">DNA Funded\u003C/span>\n      \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500\">150\u003C/span>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"how-to-choose-the-right-indian-prop-trading-firm\">How To Choose The Right Indian Prop Trading Firm\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>We have provided our list (in order) of the top proprietary trading firms for Indian traders but the final choice could come down to a few factors.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"1-reputation-and-track-record\">1. Reputation and Track Record\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>The most important factor for traders in India is trust, leading to firms being researched based on their standing in the trading community. The history of the company is often also researched including how long they have been offering prop trading (or CFD trading), how reliable their payouts are and their overall stability. Forums and review sites (such as Trustpilot) are often the primary sources to get this information.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"2-regulatory-compliance\">2. Regulatory Compliance\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Prop firms don’t require regulation including being setup under the Securities and Exchange Board of India (SEBI). That said, broker-backed firms that also offer forex trading or share trading require regulation by default and must adhere to industry standards.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"3-capital-and-funding-process\">3. Capital and Funding Process\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Understand the prop trading firm’s funding process and the capital requirements. This includes the evaluation phases at each stage and the funding required at each stage to match your capital expectations.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"4-fees\">4. Fees\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Understanding all the prop trading fees of a firm is a must. There can be hidden fees that require additional funding or fees that impact the chances of passing a stage such as spreads, commissions or even trading platform fees.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"5-profit-payout-policies\">5. Profit Payout Policies\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>If you pass the evaluation stages it’s important to understand what profit-share is available and when the firm will payout. How much capital they will make available is also important as it will dictate the potential profit a trader may make.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"6-trading-platforms\">6. Trading Platforms\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Most individuals that have traded before have a preference when it comes to the trading software they use such as MetaTrader 4 (MT4), MetaTrader 5 (MT5), cTrader or TradingView. These traders should shortlist the prop firms that offer the trading software that they are familiar with.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"7-risk-management\">7. Risk Management\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>All prop firms have inbuilt risk management tools (e.g. margin requirements) which exist to protect traders when their account balances run low or limit leverage. This can impact trading styles and lead to the early exits of evaluation stages so understanding the firm’s in-built systems is a must.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"8-community-and-customer-support\">8. Community and Customer Support\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Prop traders require more support than general forex traders. This is because many individuals are new to trading, have questions about evaluation stages, and require additional onboarding. For this reason, traders should look at the types and quality of the customer service available and if a wider community can support them, such as Discord, to help them during the onboarding and evaluation period.\u003C/p>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"faqs\">FAQs\u003C/h2>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"what-is-the-best-prop-firm-in-india\">What is the best prop firm in India?\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>FundedNext is the best prop firm in India, offering flexible challenges, high profit splits up to 95%, and fast bi-weekly payouts. You can choose between one-step or two-step models, trade on MT4, MT5, or cTrader, and access forex, indices, commodities, and crypto. With low fees starting from $32 and a strong Indian user base, it’s the top prop firm for traders seeking capital and consistent funding options.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"is-prop-fund-trading-legal-in-india\">Is prop fund trading legal in India?\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Yes, prop fund trading is legal in India. Traders can access capital through top prop trading firms like FXIFY or DNA Funded, among others. These prop firms offer a variety of challenges, flexible profit splits, and advanced trading platforms like MT4 and MT5. With options tailored to different styles and experience levels, Indian traders can benefit from scalable funding opportunities and competitive profit-sharing arrangements through these proprietary trading firms.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"are-there-any-prop-trading-firms-in-india\">Are there any prop trading firms in India?\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Yes, Indian traders can choose from a number of top prop firms, including FXIFY, popular for its flexible challenges and profit splits up to 90%, and DNA Funded, who we consider to be the best broker-backed prop firm with low fees and access to over 800 markets. BrightFunded is another strong option, with its Trade2Earn Rewards Program allowing traders to earn tokens for upgrades or free challenges.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"is-forex-prop-trading-a-good-idea-in-india\">Is Forex prop trading a good idea in India?\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Yes, forex prop trading can be a good idea in India, as it provides traders with access to significant capital without risking their own funds. It’s ideal for disciplined traders who can meet profit targets and manage drawdowns effectively. By trading on advanced platforms like MT4 and MT5, you can access global forex markets with competitive spreads. For a detailed guide, visit our list of the \u003Ca href=\"/prop-firms\">top forex prop firms\u003C/a>.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"what-is-the-most-trusted-prop-firm\">What is the most trusted prop firm?\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>The most trusted prop firms are broker-backed firms, as they operate in partnership with regulated brokers, ensuring secure trading conditions and transparent policies. These firms offer access to reliable trading platforms and low-cost trading environments. DNA Funded is a prime example, known for its partnership with a regulated broker. To learn more about the most trusted firms, read about the \u003Ca href=\"/prop-firms\">best prop trading firms\u003C/a>.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"what-is-a-prop-trading-firm\">What is a prop trading firm?\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Prop trading firms provide traders with capital to trade financial markets, earning a share of profits in return. Traders undergo evaluations or access instant funding to trade larger amounts without risking personal money. These prop firms generate revenue through fees, profit splits, and additional services, making them a popular choice for skilled traders looking to scale.\u003C/p>",{"headings":6078,"localImagePaths":6195,"remoteImagePaths":6196,"frontmatter":6197,"imagePaths":6209},[6079,6082,6085,6088,6089,6092,6093,6096,6097,6100,6101,6102,6103,6104,6107,6108,6110,6111,6112,6113,6114,6117,6118,6120,6121,6122,6123,6124,6127,6128,6130,6131,6132,6133,6134,6137,6138,6140,6141,6142,6143,6144,6147,6150,6153,6156,6159,6162,6165,6168,6171,6174,6177,6178,6181,6184,6187,6190,6193],{"depth":879,"slug":6080,"text":6081},"which-prop-firm-is-the-best-in-india","Which Prop Firm Is The Best In India?",{"depth":879,"slug":6083,"text":6084},"what-to-look-for-as-an-indian-trader","What to Look for as an Indian Trader",{"depth":158,"slug":6086,"text":6087},"sebi-regulation-vs-offshore-operations","SEBI Regulation vs Offshore Operations",{"depth":158,"slug":5024,"text":5025},{"depth":158,"slug":6090,"text":6091},"inr-payment-options","INR Payment Options",{"depth":158,"slug":5030,"text":5031},{"depth":879,"slug":6094,"text":6095},"1-fundednext--best-prop-firm-in-india","1. FundedNext — Best Prop Firm in India",{"depth":158,"slug":5221,"text":5222},{"depth":158,"slug":6098,"text":6099},"fees-and-profit-payouts","Fees and Profit Payouts",{"depth":158,"slug":4841,"text":4842},{"depth":158,"slug":4844,"text":4845},{"depth":158,"slug":5048,"text":5049},{"depth":158,"slug":5051,"text":5052},{"depth":879,"slug":6105,"text":6106},"2-fxify--best-instant-funding-prop-firm","2. FXIFY — Best Instant Funding Prop Firm",{"depth":158,"slug":5237,"text":5222},{"depth":158,"slug":6109,"text":6099},"fees-and-profit-payouts-1",{"depth":158,"slug":4862,"text":4842},{"depth":158,"slug":4864,"text":4845},{"depth":158,"slug":5066,"text":5049},{"depth":158,"slug":5068,"text":5052},{"depth":879,"slug":6115,"text":6116},"3-dna-funded--top-broker-backed-prop-firm","3. DNA Funded — Top Broker Backed Prop Firm",{"depth":158,"slug":5250,"text":5222},{"depth":158,"slug":6119,"text":6099},"fees-and-profit-payouts-2",{"depth":158,"slug":4882,"text":4842},{"depth":158,"slug":4884,"text":4845},{"depth":158,"slug":5081,"text":5049},{"depth":158,"slug":5083,"text":5052},{"depth":879,"slug":6125,"text":6126},"4-brightfunded--best-prop-trader-rewards-program","4. BrightFunded — Best Prop Trader Rewards Program",{"depth":158,"slug":5263,"text":5222},{"depth":158,"slug":6129,"text":6099},"fees-and-profit-payouts-3",{"depth":158,"slug":4899,"text":4842},{"depth":158,"slug":4916,"text":4845},{"depth":158,"slug":5096,"text":5049},{"depth":158,"slug":5098,"text":5052},{"depth":879,"slug":6135,"text":6136},"5-blueberry-funded--good-stock-and-crypto-prop-firm","5. Blueberry Funded — Good Stock and Crypto Prop Firm",{"depth":158,"slug":5276,"text":5222},{"depth":158,"slug":6139,"text":6099},"fees-and-profit-payouts-4",{"depth":158,"slug":4914,"text":4842},{"depth":158,"slug":5280,"text":4845},{"depth":158,"slug":5111,"text":5049},{"depth":158,"slug":5113,"text":5052},{"depth":879,"slug":6145,"text":6146},"how-we-rank-the-best-prop-firms","How We Rank the Best Prop Firms",{"depth":879,"slug":6148,"text":6149},"most-popular-prop-firms-in-india","Most Popular Prop Firms In India",{"depth":879,"slug":6151,"text":6152},"how-to-choose-the-right-indian-prop-trading-firm","How To Choose The Right Indian Prop Trading Firm",{"depth":158,"slug":6154,"text":6155},"1-reputation-and-track-record","1. Reputation and Track Record",{"depth":158,"slug":6157,"text":6158},"2-regulatory-compliance","2. Regulatory Compliance",{"depth":158,"slug":6160,"text":6161},"3-capital-and-funding-process","3. Capital and Funding Process",{"depth":158,"slug":6163,"text":6164},"4-fees","4. Fees",{"depth":158,"slug":6166,"text":6167},"5-profit-payout-policies","5. Profit Payout Policies",{"depth":158,"slug":6169,"text":6170},"6-trading-platforms","6. Trading Platforms",{"depth":158,"slug":6172,"text":6173},"7-risk-management","7. Risk Management",{"depth":158,"slug":6175,"text":6176},"8-community-and-customer-support","8. Community and Customer Support",{"depth":879,"slug":4935,"text":4936},{"depth":158,"slug":6179,"text":6180},"what-is-the-best-prop-firm-in-india","What is the best prop firm in India?",{"depth":158,"slug":6182,"text":6183},"is-prop-fund-trading-legal-in-india","Is prop fund trading legal in India?",{"depth":158,"slug":6185,"text":6186},"are-there-any-prop-trading-firms-in-india","Are there any prop trading firms in India?",{"depth":158,"slug":6188,"text":6189},"is-forex-prop-trading-a-good-idea-in-india","Is Forex prop trading a good idea in India?",{"depth":158,"slug":6191,"text":6192},"what-is-the-most-trusted-prop-firm","What is the most trusted prop firm?",{"depth":158,"slug":6194,"text":3528},"what-is-a-prop-trading-firm",[],[],{"title":6047,"excerpt":6048,"category":4792,"tags":6198,"author":4798,"authorImage":4799,"publishedAt":1273,"featured":110,"coverImage":6051,"readingTimeMinutes":104,"youtubeVideoId":6052,"featuredFirms":6199},[6050,4795,4796],[6200,6201,6202,6203,6204,6205,6206,6207,6208],{"slug":1392,"descriptor":6055},{"slug":1599,"descriptor":6057},{"slug":728,"descriptor":6059},{"slug":584,"descriptor":6061},{"slug":332,"descriptor":6063},{"slug":1241,"descriptor":6065},{"slug":4813,"descriptor":6067},{"slug":1002,"descriptor":6069},{"slug":2380,"descriptor":6071},[],"india.md",{"id":1975,"data":6212,"body":6236,"filePath":6237,"digest":6238,"rendered":6239,"legacyId":6392},{"title":6213,"excerpt":6214,"category":5171,"tags":6215,"coverImage":6217,"author":4798,"authorImage":4799,"publishedAt":1273,"featured":110,"readingTimeMinutes":5176,"youtubeVideoId":4800,"featuredFirms":6218},"Best Instant Funding Prop Firms (Verified Testing 2026)","Find the best instant funding prop firms offering immediate access to trading accounts and capital. This guide breaks down true instant funding account options only, along with their platforms, fees, profit payouts and more, to help you choose the ideal funded account and prop firm.",[6216,4796,5173],"instant funding","/images/guides/instant.png",[6219,6221,6222,6224,6226,6228,6230,6232,6234],{"slug":332,"descriptor":6220},"Best Instant Funding Prop Firm Overall",{"slug":1599,"descriptor":5800},{"slug":728,"descriptor":6223},"Good for Crypto Instant Funding",{"slug":2747,"descriptor":6225},"Instant Funding for Futures Trading",{"slug":1278,"descriptor":6227},"$100K Instant Funding Account",{"slug":1843,"descriptor":6229},"Broker Backed Prop Firm with Instant Funding",{"slug":1682,"descriptor":6231},"Futures Instant Prop Account",{"slug":1459,"descriptor":6233},"Low Fee Instant Funding",{"slug":1975,"descriptor":6235},"Micro Instant Funding Accounts","## How Did We Test Instant Funding Prop Firms?\n\nUnlike sites that give you the same info as a prop firms FAQ, we audit every instant funding prop firm by buying accounts with our own money and running them through a rigorous signup-to-payout lifecycle test. We execute identical trades across multiple firms simultaneously in our tests, to capture hard data on execution speeds, spread variance, and slippage, ensuring direct apples-to-apples comparisons. We meticulously log every friction point, from platform outages and lag, to unhelpful customer support teams, and delayed rule enforcement.\n\n---\n\n## The 10 Best Instant Funding Accounts We Tested in 2026\n\n---\n\n## 1. Blueberry Funded — Best Instant Funding Prop Firm Overall\n\nBlueberry Funded ranks 1st on our shortlist because it offers two different types of instant funding accounts, unlike most firms that only offer one. Instant Lite keeps risk tighter with a daily loss cap, while Instant Elite removes that limit for more breathing room.\n\nIt's also backed by Blueberry Markets, an ASIC regulated forex broker, meaning transparent pricing, stable execution, and strong oversight. Combined with competitive fees and payouts every 14 days, Blueberry's setup covers both security and performance.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/blueberry-funded-logo.png\" alt=\"Blueberry Funded logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\" />\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">Blueberry Funded\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">Best Instant Funding Prop Firm Overall\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">90%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Max DD\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">10%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Trustpilot\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">3.8 \u003Cspan class=\"text-amber-500\">★\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Ca href=\"/reviews/blueberry-funded\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-lg bg-teal-500 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-white hover:bg-teal-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n        Full Review →\n      \u003C/a>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose -mt-3 mb-6 rounded-xl border border-emerald-200 bg-emerald-50/80 px-5 py-3 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-3\">\n  \u003Ca href=\"https://blueberryfunded.com/?utm_source=affiliate&ref=1457\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-emerald-500 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-emerald-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14\" />\u003C/svg>\n    Visit Blueberry Funded\n  \u003C/a>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2.5\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4 text-emerald-600 flex-shrink-0\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M7 7h.01M7 3h5c.512 0 1.024.195 1.414.586l7 7a2 2 0 010 2.828l-7 7a2 2 0 01-2.828 0l-7-7A1.994 1.994 0 013 12V7a4 4 0 014-4z\" />\u003C/svg>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm text-emerald-700 font-semibold\">20% Off — Code:\u003C/span>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"font-mono font-bold text-xs bg-white border border-dashed border-emerald-300 px-3 py-1.5 rounded text-emerald-700 tracking-wide select-all\">PROPFIRMS20\u003C/span>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Pros & Cons\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Pros\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Two instant funding account types\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Backed by regulated forex broker\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Low fees, raw pricing\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Scaling up to $2 million\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Huge range of instruments\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Instant Lite has tighter limits\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Limited educational content\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Payments only by card or crypto\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Instant not available on MT4\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>No swap free account option\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n### Full Details\n\nBlueberry Funded offers two instant funding accounts that start with a 80% profit share, giving you immediate access to funded capital without any need to work through an evaluation process. Both instant options use a trailing drawdown that moves up as your equity grows, locking in profits while protecting the account.\n\nThe key difference between the two instant funding accounts is how risk is managed. The Instant Lite has stricter daily and overall loss limits, while Instant Elite removes the daily loss cap and has a more relaxed overall drawdown, but the initial fees are higher.\n\n### Instant Lite\n\nInstant Lite gives you instant access to funded capital with tighter drawdown limits. You'll work under a 2% daily loss and a 4% total trailing drawdown, which moves up as your balance grows. The setup rewards consistency and helps control exposure from day one.\n\nIt's a solid option if you trade shorter timeframes, manage smaller positions, or prefer steady growth with less volatility. The structure keeps risk defined and lets you build results without large balance swings.\n\n| Account Size | One-Off Fee | Profit Target | Max Total Loss (10%) | Max Daily Loss |\n|-------------|------------|--------------|---------------------|---------------|\n| $1,250 | $37.04 | None | $125 | None |\n| $2,500 | $55.56 | None | $250 | None |\n| $5,000 | $83.33 | None | $500 | None |\n| $10,000 | $125.00 | None | $1,000 | None |\n| $25,000 | $187.50 | None | $2,500 | None |\n| $50,000 | $375.00 | None | $5,000 | None |\n| $100,000 | $750.00 | None | $10,000 | None |\n\n### Instant Elite\n\nInstant Elite offers the same direct funding but removes the daily loss limit, giving you a wider 10% total trailing drawdown. You have more room to manage open positions, scale in, or hold trades overnight.\n\nIt fits better if you're experienced with self-managed risk or trade swing and multi-day setups that need space to play out. The flexibility makes Instant Elite the more open version of Blueberry's instant accounts, while keeping the same payout and scaling rules.\n\n| Account Size | One-Off Fee | Profit Target | Max Total Loss (10%) | Max Daily Loss (2%) |\n|-------------|------------|--------------|---------------------|-------------------|\n| $2,500 | $100 | None | $250 | $50 |\n| $5,000 | $300 | None | $500 | $100 |\n| $10,000 | $400 | None | $1,000 | $200 |\n| $25,000 | $800 | None | $2,500 | $500 |\n| $50,000 | $1,500 | None | $5,000 | $1,000 |\n\n### Other Challenges\n\nIf you prefer an evaluation route, Blueberry has four additional challenges. Rapid runs a single 7 day challenge and will suit if you prefer short, high feedback setups. One Step keeps things simple with a static drawdown, while Two Step and Prime offer more structure.\n\n### Trading Fees\n\nBlueberry Funded's trading costs come directly from its broker, Blueberry Markets, using a raw pricing model with fixed commissions.\n\n- **Spreads:** Starting from 0.1 pips on major forex pairs during peak trading hours. Spreads can widen slightly in low-liquidity periods but remain competitive compared to other instant funding firms.\n- **Commissions:** $3.50 per side for forex and gold. Indices, commodities, and crypto are commission free. US stock CFDs have a $2 round-turn fee.\n\nThis setup provides stable execution costs for both discretionary and automated traders. All pricing is identical across platforms, so conditions stay consistent whether you trade on MT4, MT5, DXTrade, or TradeLocker.\n\n### Markets and Leverage\n\nBlueberry Funded's instant funding accounts offer access to over 1,100 instruments across six asset classes: forex, indices, commodities, cryptocurrencies, stocks, and synthetics.\n\n| Asset Class | Details | Leverage |\n|------------|---------|---------|\n| Forex | 45 pairs including majors, minors, and exotics | Up to 50:1 (Elite) / 30:1 (Lite) |\n| Indices | 14 global indices (NASDAQ 100, S&P 500, GER30) | Up to 10:1 |\n| Commodities | 17 instruments (gold, silver, crude oil, natural gas) | Up to 10:1 |\n| Crypto | 52 pairs (BTC/USD, ETH/USD, SOL/USD) | Up to 2:1 |\n| Stocks | 1,000+ US stock CFDs via MT5 and TradeLocker | Up to 10:1 |\n| Synthetics | 12 volatility based indices unique to Blueberry | Up to 30:1 |\n\nThe range is one of the broadest available from any prop firm, allowing both short-term and multi-asset strategies without switching platforms or accounts.\n\n### Trading Platforms\n\nBlueberry Funded supports four of the most popular trading platforms worldwide with MetaTrader 4 (MT4), MetaTrader 5 (MT5), DXTrade, and TradeLocker available.\n\n- **MT4:** Available on evaluation and challenge accounts but not Instant Funding. Designed for manual and EA trading with familiar charting tools and order management.\n- **MT5:** Available across all account types including Instant Funding. Supports advanced order types, Depth of Market data, and multi-asset trading such as stocks and crypto.\n- **DXTrade:** Web-based platform with TradingView-style charting, ideal for quick execution and clean layout.\n- **TradeLocker:** Browser and mobile-based interface focused on fast execution and modern usability.\n\nInstant Funding traders can choose between MT5, DXTrade, or TradeLocker. EA use and weekend trading are permitted, but strategies like latency arbitrage, grid systems, and news scalping remain restricted under standard prop rules.\n\n### Payouts and Scaling\n\nProfit payouts are available every 14 days through RiseWorks, with a $100 minimum. You keep 80% by default and 90% after consistent results. Accounts that meet performance and withdrawal milestones every three months can scale by 25%, up to a simulated balance of $2 million.\n\nThe payout process is fast and predictable, which is a strong point for instant funding traders who rely on frequent withdrawals.\n\n### Trust and Community\n\nBlueberry Funded operates under the same umbrella as Blueberry Markets, an ASIC regulated broker based out of Australia. That backing gives the firm genuine oversight and transparency on pricing and execution. It's also a founding member of The Prop Association, which aims to set industry wide standards on fairness and dispute resolution.\n\nThe firm's Discord community has over 30,000 traders and remains active with shared trade setups, payouts, and platform feedback.\n\n### Verdict on Blueberry Funded\n\nBlueberry Funded ranks first because it delivers genuine instant access through two account types that serve different trading styles. With strong regulation behind it, low costs, wide market access, and a clean payout structure, it's the most complete instant funding model available right now. The additional Rapid, One Step, and Two Step challenges round out a well-built program that suits both new and professional traders looking for direct capital access.\n\n---\n\n## 2. FXIFY — High Profit Split\n\nFXIFY is the 2nd on our shortlist of the best instant funding prop firms, offering immediate access to capital with account sizes starting at $1,000 and profit shares up to 90%. Backed by FXPIG, it provides low spreads and access to MT4, MT5, DXTrade, and TradingView. With a scaling plan up to $4 million, FXIFY combines flexibility, reliability, and growth potential for all traders.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/fxify-1-1-1-1.png\" alt=\"FXIFY logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\" />\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">FXIFY\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">High Profit Split\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">90%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Max DD\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">10%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Trustpilot\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">4.4 \u003Cspan class=\"text-amber-500\">★\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Ca href=\"/reviews/fxify\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-lg bg-teal-500 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-white hover:bg-teal-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n        Full Review →\n      \u003C/a>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose -mt-3 mb-6 rounded-xl border border-emerald-200 bg-emerald-50/80 px-5 py-3 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-3\">\n  \u003Ca href=\"https://trader.fxify.com/purchasechallenge?affiliateId=5837\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-emerald-500 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-emerald-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14\" />\u003C/svg>\n    Visit FXIFY\n  \u003C/a>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2.5\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4 text-emerald-600 flex-shrink-0\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M7 7h.01M7 3h5c.512 0 1.024.195 1.414.586l7 7a2 2 0 010 2.828l-7 7a2 2 0 01-2.828 0l-7-7A1.994 1.994 0 013 12V7a4 4 0 014-4z\" />\u003C/svg>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm text-emerald-700 font-semibold\">15% Off — Code:\u003C/span>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"font-mono font-bold text-xs bg-white border border-dashed border-emerald-300 px-3 py-1.5 rounded text-emerald-700 tracking-wide select-all\">PROPFIRMS15\u003C/span>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Pros & Cons\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Pros\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Instant funding accounts from $1K\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Low fees and spreads from 0 pips\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>News trading allowed\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Broker backed proprietary trading firm\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Trailing drawdown may not suit all\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Max trading account 50K for instant\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Stocks only on MetaTrader 5\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Minimal educational materials\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n### Account Options\n\nFXIFY's Instant Funding Accounts let you start trading immediately with account sizes from $1,000 to $50,000, no evaluations required. Backed by FXPIG, a trusted forex broker, you can benefit from reliable trade execution and access to tight spreads on forex, indices, commodities, and cryptocurrencies.\n\nThe instant funding accounts include simple, trader-friendly rules, like an 8% daily loss limit, designed to support disciplined trading without overwhelming beginner traders. Advanced traders will appreciate the flexibility to use MT4, MT5, or DXTrade platforms, accommodating both manual and automated strategies.\n\nFXIFY also offers a scaling plan where you can grow your trading account up to $4 million, with consistent performers increasing their account size by 25% every three months. Combined with profit shares up to 90%, it's a strong option for traders focused on capital growth and earning potential.\n\n| Account Size | Fee | Daily Loss Limit (8%) | Max Trailing Drawdown (8%) |\n|-------------|-----|----------------------|--------------------------|\n| $1,000 | $69 | $80 | $80 |\n| $2,500 | $119 | $200 | $200 |\n| $5,000 | $229 | $400 | $400 |\n| $10,000 | $449 | $800 | $800 |\n| $25,000 | $899 | $2,000 | $2,000 |\n| $50,000 | $1,749 | $4,000 | $4,000 |\n\nThis structure is perfect for traders who want a clear and simple path to funding. Newer traders will appreciate the smaller account sizes and straightforward rules, while experienced traders can benefit from the ability to trade immediately without the need for lengthy evaluations. However, because FXIFY uses a trailing drawdown, traders with aggressive or highly volatile strategies may find it less flexible than static drawdown models.\n\n### Trading Fees\n\nFXIFY's fee structure combines competitive spreads with low commission costs:\n\n- **Spreads:** Starting from 0.0 pips on Forex pairs during peak trading times, though spreads can widen in low-liquidity periods.\n- **Commissions:** $3 per lot on Forex trades, which is lower than many competitors offering similar instant funding options.\n\nThis setup is ideal for traders prioritising cost-effective trading, particularly during high-liquidity market hours.\n\n### Markets and Leverage\n\nFXIFY's instant funding accounts grant access to a range of financial instruments:\n\n| Asset Class | Details | Leverage |\n|------------|---------|---------|\n| Forex | 42 currency pairs (majors, minors, exotics) | Up to 30:1 |\n| Indices | 13 global indices (S&P 500, NASDAQ 100) | Up to 10:1 |\n| Commodities | Gold, silver, and oil (MT4/MT5) | Up to 10:1 |\n| Crypto | Bitcoin, Ethereum, Ripple (MT4/MT5 only) | Up to 2:1 |\n\nThe default leverage for instant funding is capped at 30:1 for forex and gold.\n\n### Platforms\n\nFXIFY supports three trading platforms: MetaTrader 4 (MT4), MetaTrader 5 (MT5), and DXTrade with TradingView integration. Platform access depends on the account type.\n\n- **MT4** is available on One, Two, and Three Step accounts only.\n- **MT5** is available on all accounts, including Instant Funding and Lightning Challenge.\n- **DXTrade** is available on all accounts except Lightning.\n\nEach platform caters to different trading styles. MT4 is suited to traders who rely on EAs or fast manual execution, MT5 includes more order types and stock/crypto access, and DXTrade offers browser-based charting powered by TradingView.\n\nInstant Funding accounts do not support MT4. If you're planning to use Expert Advisors or need low-latency execution via MT4, you'll need to choose an evaluation challenge instead.\n\n### Payouts\n\nFXIFY allows traders to request their first payout immediately after a profitable live trade. Instant Funding accounts follow a 14-day cycle, while other account types can request withdrawals on demand.\n\nThe default schedule is monthly, but you can upgrade to bi-weekly payouts by selecting an add-on at checkout. Instant accounts have a $50 minimum withdrawal; evaluation accounts have no minimum.\n\nWithdrawals are processed via crypto, bank transfer, or Deel, and typically take 24 to 48 hours. FXIFY also refunds your challenge fee with your first funded payout and regularly shares top withdrawal amounts publicly, adding trust and transparency.\n\n### Trust\n\nFXIFY is backed by FXPIG, a broker licensed by the Vanuatu Financial Services Commission. While this isn't a top-tier regulatory licence like ASIC or FCA, it still adds a layer of oversight missing from many prop firms.\n\nFXIFY scores well on Trustpilot, with a rating of 4.2/5 from over 3,000 reviews. Traders regularly mention fast payouts, simple trading rules, and helpful community support. That said, some users have flagged minor delays in payout or activation on higher-tier accounts.\n\nThe FXIFY Discord community is also active, with verified trader channels and weekly payout posts. It's one of the better firm communities if you're looking for peer support and updates.\n\n### Verdict on FXIFY Instant Funding Accounts\n\nWith account sizes from $1,000 to $50,000, profit splits up to 90%, and the backing of forex broker FXPIG, FXIFY takes 2nd place on our instant funding rankings. You can access top tier platforms like MT5 and DXTrade, get profit splits up to 90%, and withdraw profits every 14 days. While the trailing drawdown and limited MT4 access on Instant Funding accounts may not suit everyone, FXIFY remains one of the strongest options if you want to skip the challenge and get funded straight away.\n\n---\n\n## 3. DNA Funded — Good for Crypto Instant Funding\n\nDNA Funded ranked 3rd on our instant funding shortlist due to its simple instant funding structure and relatively low friction between account purchase and live trading. The firm offers true instant access with no evaluation phase, allowing you to begin trading funded capital immediately under predefined risk limits.\n\nDuring early testing, account activation was fast and we didn't experience any delays signing up. Trading platform access was available immediately which keeps the onboarding process clean compared to instant models that introduce manual approval steps.\n\nBased on our analysis of the top prop firms worldwide, we found DNA Funded to be the best prop firm overall with a score of 97/100. The Australian-based prop firm is backed by regulated broker DNA Markets (ASIC AFSL 514425), offering traders access to institutional-grade conditions like tight spreads, fast execution, and low trading costs.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/dna-funded-logo.png\" alt=\"DNA Funded logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\" />\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">DNA Funded\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">Good for Crypto Instant Funding\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-sl