th stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M7 7h.01M7 3h5c.512 0 1.024.195 1.414.586l7 7a2 2 0 010 2.828l-7 7a2 2 0 01-2.828 0l-7-7A1.994 1.994 0 013 12V7a4 4 0 014-4z\" />\u003C/svg>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm text-emerald-700 font-semibold\">25% Off — Code:\u003C/span>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"font-mono font-bold text-xs bg-white border border-dashed border-emerald-300 px-3 py-1.5 rounded text-emerald-700 tracking-wide select-all\">PROPFIRMS25\u003C/span>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Pros & Cons\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Pros\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>ASIC regulated broker-backed\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>800+ instruments including crypto\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Three flexible challenge types\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Low fees starting from $49\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>On-demand payouts in 24 hours\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>TradeLocker only (no MT4/MT5)\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>No EA or automated trading\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>40% daily profit cap applies\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Still a newer firm with limited track record\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n### Prop Challenges and Accounts\n\nDNA Funded offers three challenge types, catering to various trading styles:\n\n- **Single Helix (1-step challenge):** Account sizes from $5,000 to $200,000. Fees start at $59, with a 10% profit target and no time limits, making it ideal for swing traders and those focused on longer-term strategies.\n- **Double Helix (2-step challenge):** Account sizes also range from $5,000 to $200,000, with fees starting at $49. Phase 1 requires a 10% profit target, while Phase 2 lowers it to 5%, with flexible trading days.\n- **Rapid Challenge (1-step challenge):** Designed for more experienced traders with account sizes ranging from $10,000 to $100,000, and fees from $99. This challenge requires a 5% profit target to be met within 10 days, with a stricter drawdown limit, making it suitable for scalpers or high-frequency traders.\n\n| DNA Funded Account Type | Challenge Fees | Account Sizes | Early Payout (14→7 Days) Add-on | Profit Split Increase (80%→90%) Add-on |\n|------------------------|---------------|--------------|--------------------------------|---------------------------------------|\n| Single Helix (1 Step) | $59 – $1,451 | 5K – 200K | Yes | No |\n| Double Helix (2 Step) | $49 – $1,295 | 5K – 200K | No | Yes |\n| Pro Challenge | $99 – $714 | 10K – 100K | Yes | Yes |\n\n### Markets and Leverage\n\nDNA Funded provides access to over 800 forex, commodities, indices, stocks, and crypto markets (with restrictions on crypto in the Pro Challenge).\n\nLeverage varies by challenge type and asset. Forex is capped at 1:50 on Double Helix and 1:30 on Single Helix and Pro Challenge. Commodities and indices are fixed at 1:10, stocks at 1:5 following a recent reduction from 1:10, and crypto is 1:2 but only available on Single and Double Helix.\n\n| Asset Class | Single Helix | Double Helix | Pro Challenge |\n|------------|-------------|-------------|--------------|\n| Forex | 1:30 | 1:50 | 1:30 |\n| Commodities | 1:10 | 1:10 | 1:10 |\n| Indices | 1:10 | 1:10 | 1:10 |\n| Stocks | 1:5 | 1:5 | 1:5 |\n| Crypto | 1:2 | 1:2 | Not Allowed |\n\n### Trading Platforms\n\nAll trading is done through **TradeLocker**, which comes fully integrated with TradingView. This setup is ideal for manual traders who want advanced charting, one-click execution, and a clean web-based interface. However, automated trading and EAs are not supported.\n\nDNA Funded keeps its trading rules simple and in line with broker-backed standards. All accounts follow daily and overall drawdown limits based on the challenge type, and a daily profit cap of 40% now applies. This means you can only count up to 40% of your payout target in one trading day, which helps support steady, consistent trading.\n\nAutomated trading and expert advisors (EAs) are not allowed. You can copy trades between your own accounts, but not from others. News trading is allowed, but you'll need to avoid opening or closing positions within 10 minutes of high-impact news. Weekend trading is also permitted.\n\n### Trust and Community\n\nDNA Funded is backed by DNA Markets, a well-known ASIC-regulated broker (AFSL 514425), ensuring tight spreads and reliable execution. While DNA Funded is still new, its connection to DNA Markets boosts its credibility hugely.\n\nThe prop firm is also developing an active trading community through its Discord channel, offering a space for traders to connect and share insights. DNA Funded holds a **4.9/5 on Trustpilot** from over 3,200 verified reviews.\n\n### Verdict on DNA Funded\n\nDNA Funded is the best prop trading firm for 2026 even in the early stages of launch thanks to its flexible challenges, low fees, and an 80%–90% profit share. Backed by DNA Markets, it provides reliable market access across forex, commodities, indices, stocks, and crypto. You can read our full evaluation on our [DNA Funded review page](/reviews/dna-funded).\n\nWith a user-friendly platform like TradeLocker and growing community support, DNA Funded is the best prop firm for both new and experienced traders looking for a new challenge to become a funded trader.\n\n---\n\n## 4. Tradeify — Instant Funding for Futures Trading\n\nTradeify is the only dedicated futures prop firm on our instant funding shortlist. Its Lightning model gives you immediate access to funded futures capital through real US exchange markets — CME, CBOT, COMEX, and NYMEX — with no evaluation required. If you trade futures and want to skip the challenge phase entirely, this is the most direct route available.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/tradeify-logo.png\" alt=\"Tradeify logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\" />\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">Tradeify\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">Instant Funding for Futures Trading\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">90%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Max DD\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">4%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Trustpilot\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">4.7 \u003Cspan class=\"text-amber-500\">★\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Ca href=\"/reviews/tradeify\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-lg bg-teal-500 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-white hover:bg-teal-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n        Full Review →\n      \u003C/a>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose -mt-3 mb-6 flex justify-center\">\n  \u003Ca href=\"https://tradeify.co/?ref=bestpropfirms\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-emerald-500 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-emerald-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14\" />\u003C/svg>\n    Visit Tradeify\n  \u003C/a>\n\u003C/div>\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Pros & Cons\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Pros\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Instant futures funding (Lightning)\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Real exchange access (CME, CBOT, COMEX, NYMEX)\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>90% profit split with fast payouts\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Tradovate, TradingView, and NinjaTrader\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>No weekend trading on any model\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Strict consistency rules (20% daily cap)\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Email-only support, no phone or live chat\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>No EAs or copy trading allowed\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n### Lightning Instant Funding\n\nTradeify's **Lightning** model is the instant funding option. It's a one-time fee with no monthly subscription, no evaluation, and no profit target — you're trading funded capital from day one. Account sizes range from $25,000 to $150,000 with an EOD trailing drawdown.\n\n| Account Size | One-Time Fee | Max Drawdown | Daily Profit Cap |\n|-------------|-------------|-------------|-----------------|\n| $25,000 | $349 | EOD Trailing | 20% |\n| $50,000 | $509 | EOD Trailing | 20% |\n| $100,000 | $629 | EOD Trailing | 20% |\n| $150,000 | $729 | EOD Trailing | 20% |\n\nTo request your first payout, you need 10 trading days and 5 profitable days with at least $200 profit each. The minimum withdrawal on Lightning is $1,000.\n\nTradeify also offers two evaluation models — **Advanced** (intraday trailing drawdown, monthly from $69) and **Growth** (EOD trailing drawdown, monthly from $139) — if you'd prefer a challenge-based route into funding.\n\n### Markets and Platforms\n\nAll Tradeify accounts trade regulated US futures on CME, CBOT, COMEX, and NYMEX. That includes equity indices (ES, NQ, YM), metals (gold, silver), energies (crude oil, natural gas), currencies, agriculturals, and crypto futures (Micro Bitcoin, Micro Ether).\n\nTrading is done through **Tradovate** (web and mobile), **TradingView** (via Tradovate backend), or **NinjaTrader** (desktop). All execution routes through Tradovate with a flat commission of $1.29 per side.\n\n### Payouts and Trust\n\nTradeify pays a 90% profit split with payouts processed in 24–72 hours via Rise Pay and Plane Payouts. The firm holds a **4.7/5 on Trustpilot** from 1,800+ reviews and has an active Discord community of around 30,000 members.\n\n### Verdict on Tradeify\n\nTradeify earns 4th place as the best instant funding option for futures traders. The Lightning model gives you direct, no-evaluation access to real US exchange markets with a clean fee structure and strong platform support. The main trade-offs are strict consistency rules, no weekend trading, and limited support channels — but if you're an experienced futures trader who knows what you're doing, it's one of the most direct routes to funded capital available.\n\n---\n\n## 5. Funded Trading Plus — $100K Instant Funding Account\n\nFunded Trading Plus (FTP) ranked 5th on our instant funding shortlist scoring 77/100 overall, largely due to its Master Trader Program which skips the evaluation process altogether.\n\nDuring our assessment, FTP grabbed our attention thanks to its account customisation features like adjustable payout intervals and upgradeable profit shares to 90%. This makes it ideal for experienced traders looking for a $100K instant funding account and the option to personalise their account terms.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/funded-trading-plus.png\" alt=\"Funded Trading Plus logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\" />\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">Funded Trading Plus\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">$100K Instant Funding Account\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">90%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Max DD\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">10%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Trustpilot\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">4.5 \u003Cspan class=\"text-amber-500\">★\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Ca href=\"/reviews/funded-trading-plus\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-lg bg-teal-500 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-white hover:bg-teal-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n        Full Review →\n      \u003C/a>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose -mt-3 mb-6 flex justify-center\">\n  \u003Ca href=\"https://www.fundedtradingplus.com/?ref=2020\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-emerald-500 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-emerald-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14\" />\u003C/svg>\n    Visit Funded Trading Plus\n  \u003C/a>\n\u003C/div>\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Pros & Cons\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Pros\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Instant funding with no evaluation\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Upgradable profit splits up to 90%\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Payouts every 3, 5, or 7 days\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>$25 fee for cTrader access\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Higher fees for instant funding\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Initial support bot can be limited\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n### Master Trader Program\n\nThe Master Trader Program at FTP is a straightforward instant funding option ideal if you want to start with live capital immediately. There is no evaluation or multi-step process — just direct access to capital, allowing more experienced traders to bypass testing phases and focus solely on achieving profitability.\n\nThe program's profit share starts at 80%, but you can upgrade this to 90% based on performance milestones, offering higher earnings potential as your trading results improve. Account sizes range from $5,000 to $100,000, with the flexibility to scale up to $5 million over time.\n\n| Account Size | One-Time Fee | Starting Profit Split | Max Drawdown | Daily Drawdown |\n|-------------|-------------|----------------------|-------------|---------------|\n| $5,000 | $225 | 80% (upgradable to 90%) | 6% | 3% |\n| $10,000 | $450 | 80% (upgradable to 90%) | 6% | 3% |\n| $25,000 | $1,125 | 80% (upgradable to 90%) | 6% | 3% |\n| $50,000 | $2,250 | 80% (upgradable to 90%) | 6% | 3% |\n| $100,000 | $4,500 | 80% (upgradable to 90%) | 6% | 3% |\n\n### Other Challenges\n\nWhile the Master Trader Program is FTP's instant funding option, they also offer structured evaluation challenges:\n\n- **One-Phase Challenge:** A single-step evaluation requiring a 10% profit target, suitable for confident traders ready to meet profitability criteria in one go. Fees start at $119.\n- **Two-Phase Challenge:** A structured assessment over two stages, with a lower profit target in the second phase to reduce pressure. Fees range from $199 to $1,097, depending on the account size.\n\n### Trading Fees\n\nFTP's fee structure varies based on the account type and size. The Master Trader Program fees start at $225 and go up to $4,500, depending on the account size. Fees for the one-phase and two-phase challenges are lower, with the smallest one-phase account starting at $119 and the largest two-phase account at $1,097.\n\n### Financial Markets\n\nOur analysis of FTP's market options revealed a decent selection across four main asset classes with access to 53 markets total.\n\n| Asset Class | Details | Leverage |\n|------------|---------|---------|\n| Forex | 37 currency pairs (majors, minors, exotics) | Up to 30:1 |\n| Commodities | Gold, Silver, and Oil | Up to 10:1 |\n| Indices | 8 major global indices | Up to 20:1 (10:1 on cTrader) |\n| Crypto | 4 crypto pairs | Up to 2:1 |\n\n### Platforms\n\nFTP scored well in platform variety, with five options that accommodate different trading preferences:\n\n- **MT4 and MT5:** Widely used platforms supporting automated trading with Expert Advisors (EAs) and a solid range of charting and analytical tools.\n- **Match-Trader:** Integrated with TradingView, especially effective for traders who rely heavily on technical analysis.\n- **cTrader:** Advanced tools and Level II pricing for deep market insights, but comes with a $25 access fee.\n- **DXTrade:** FTP's default platform, generally functional though it experienced minor delays in high-traffic times.\n\n### Payouts\n\nFTP offers flexible payout schedules — profit payouts can be made every 3, 5, or 7 days, giving traders more control over their earnings.\n\nThe initial profit split is 80%, and traders can upgrade this to 85% or 90% if they prefer a higher share. The minimum withdrawal amount is set at $50. Payouts are processed via bank transfer or crypto.\n\n### Support\n\nCustomer support at FTP is available 24/7 through email and live chat. Although the chat initially connects with a bot, you're quickly transferred to a live representative for further assistance. Support is limited to English.\n\n### Trust\n\nFunded Trading Plus has earned a high reputation, backed by a TrustPilot rating of 4.7/5. FTP's online community presence includes active groups on Facebook and Discord with over 40,000 members, providing a space for traders to connect, share insights, and gain support.\n\n### Verdict on Funded Trading Plus\n\nBased on our testing, FTP is one of the top prop firms for instant funding with its Master Trader Program, coming in 5th place in our shortlist. With good trading platforms, competitive payout schedules, and a supportive global community, Funded Trading Plus provides a solid offering for traders seeking fast access to trading accounts without lengthy evaluations.\n\n---\n\n## Instant Funding Accounts and Profit Splits\n\nInstant funding accounts skip the evaluation process entirely, providing you with immediate access to trading capital after a one-time fee. You can begin live trading directly with a funded account, usually under a profit split agreement ranging from 70% to 90%.\n\n---\n\n## How We Ranked Instant Funding Programs\n\nWe ranked the best instant funding prop firms using a structured methodology focused on key factors that impact trader success.\n\nUnlike traditional prop firms that require an evaluation phase, instant funding programs allow traders to access capital immediately, so we prioritised firms that offer fair trading conditions, transparent fees, and reliable payouts.\n\nHere's our methodology when ranking the top instant funding prop firms:\n\n- **Instant Access to Capital:** We included firms that offer true instant funding or extremely fast evaluation options (such as 7-day challenges).\n- **Profit Splits & Fees:** A strong instant funding prop firm should provide fair profit splits (typically 70-90%) while keeping fees reasonable and transparent.\n- **Payout Speed & Reliability:** Since instant funding traders often rely on frequent withdrawals, firms with fast, consistent payouts scored higher.\n- **Trading Rules & Risk Limits:** We assessed drawdown limits, leverage rules, and other risk management policies to ensure traders have flexibility while maintaining account security.\n- **Trading Platform Availability:** Firms that support popular trading platforms like MT4, MT5, and cTrader ranked higher, as they provide better tools and execution options.\n- **Reputation & Transparency:** Trust is key in prop trading, so we factored in trader reviews, customer support quality, and clarity around fees, payouts, and trading conditions.\n\n---\n\n## How Prop Trading Firm Challenges Work\n\nProp firm challenges are designed to assess traders' skills and commitment by requiring them to achieve set profit targets under strict risk management rules.\n\nThese challenges often involve one or two evaluation phases where traders must meet profit objectives, such as 8-10% within a set period while respecting daily and overall drawdown limits. Successfully passing these challenges leads to a funded account, granting traders access to capital while adhering to ongoing risk parameters.\n\nIf you aren't familiar with the prop industry, we recommend you learn more about [prop trading firms](/guides/what-is-a-prop-firm) and how challenges work before you buy an instant funding account.\n\n---\n\n## FAQs\n\n### What is the best instant funded prop firm?\n\nBlueberry Funded is the best instant funding prop firm, offering two true instant funding accounts that let you start trading funded capital immediately with no evaluation or time limit. You can choose between Instant Lite, with a 2% daily and 4% total drawdown, or Instant Elite, which removes the daily cap and sets a 10% trailing limit.\n\nYou can trade on MT5, DXTrade, or TradeLocker, earn up to a 90% profit split, and scale your account up to $2 million.\n\n### Are instant funding prop firms legit?\n\nYes, instant funding prop firms are legitimate, but their reliability depends on their trading conditions, payout history, and transparency. Reputable instant funding firms like FXIFY and Funded Trading Plus provide real capital, fair profit share agreements, and clear rules. However, some other prop firms have hidden fees, unclear trading terms, or delayed payouts, making due diligence essential.\n\n### Which prop firm payout the fastest?\n\nFunded Trading Plus (FTP) is the prop firm with one of the fastest payout systems, allowing withdrawals every 3, 5, or 7 days. This flexible schedule gives traders more frequent access to profits than most firms, which typically offer biweekly or monthly payouts. However, instant funding accounts do not guarantee instant payouts.\n\n### Which prop firm gives the most money?\n\nBlueberry Funded offers one of the highest earning potentials through its instant funding programs, with profit splits up to 90% and a scaling plan that goes up to $2 million. Both Instant Lite and Instant Elite accounts give you direct access to funded capital from day one.\n\nFXIFY also provides strong earning potential, matching 90% profit splits and offering a larger scaling plan up to $4 million. Both prop trading firms are broker backed and give you immediate access to capital and regular payouts, but Blueberry Funded's regulatory backing and two instant funding models make it the stronger overall choice for consistent long term returns.\n\n### Does instant funding actually pay out?\n\nYes, instant funding accounts do offer profit payouts, typically based on a profit share arrangement. You get to keep a percentage of the profits you generate, often between 80% to 100%, depending on the prop firm and account performance. Some prop firms have minimum withdrawal amounts, and others offer fast payouts, such as weekly or biweekly.\n\n### What are the benefits of funded forex accounts?\n\nThere are many perks to funded forex accounts as you gain access to trading capital without risking your own money. Unlike self-funded CFD trading, proprietary trading firms allow traders to take larger positions with firm capital, enhancing profit potential while limiting personal financial exposure.\n\nView our top 10 [best prop firms](/prop-firms) list for a comparison of the top funded forex accounts.\n\n### How do prop traders manage their risk?\n\nProp traders use risk management techniques so they can follow the strict guidelines set by prop firms, such as daily and max drawdown limits and required stop-loss orders. These techniques and trading rules help control losses and prevent excessive risk-taking on any single trade. Many firms also enforce position size limits and leverage restrictions to maintain a balanced risk profile and help traders pass prop challenges.","src/content/blog/instant-funding.md","31884a032b527596",{"html":6240,"metadata":6241},"\u003Ch2 id=\"how-did-we-test-instant-funding-prop-firms\">How Did We Test Instant Funding Prop Firms?\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>Unlike sites that give you the same info as a prop firms FAQ, we audit every instant funding prop firm by buying accounts with our own money and running them through a rigorous signup-to-payout lifecycle test. We execute identical trades across multiple firms simultaneously in our tests, to capture hard data on execution speeds, spread variance, and slippage, ensuring direct apples-to-apples comparisons. We meticulously log every friction point, from platform outages and lag, to unhelpful customer support teams, and delayed rule enforcement.\u003C/p>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"the-10-best-instant-funding-accounts-we-tested-in-2026\">The 10 Best Instant Funding Accounts We Tested in 2026\u003C/h2>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"1-blueberry-funded--best-instant-funding-prop-firm-overall\">1. Blueberry Funded — Best Instant Funding Prop Firm Overall\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>Blueberry Funded ranks 1st on our shortlist because it offers two different types of instant funding accounts, unlike most firms that only offer one. Instant Lite keeps risk tighter with a daily loss cap, while Instant Elite removes that limit for more breathing room.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>It’s also backed by Blueberry Markets, an ASIC regulated forex broker, meaning transparent pricing, stable execution, and strong oversight. Combined with competitive fees and payouts every 14 days, Blueberry’s setup covers both security and performance.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/blueberry-funded-logo.png\" alt=\"Blueberry Funded logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">Blueberry Funded\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">Best Instant Funding Prop Firm Overall\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">90%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Max DD\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">10%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Trustpilot\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">3.8 \u003Cspan class=\"text-amber-500\">★\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Ca href=\"/reviews/blueberry-funded\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-lg bg-teal-500 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-white hover:bg-teal-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n        Full Review →\n      \u003C/a>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose -mt-3 mb-6 rounded-xl border border-emerald-200 bg-emerald-50/80 px-5 py-3 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-3\">\n  \u003Ca href=\"https://blueberryfunded.com/?utm_source=affiliate&#x26;ref=1457\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-emerald-500 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-emerald-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n    Visit Blueberry Funded\n  \u003C/a>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2.5\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4 text-emerald-600 flex-shrink-0\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M7 7h.01M7 3h5c.512 0 1.024.195 1.414.586l7 7a2 2 0 010 2.828l-7 7a2 2 0 01-2.828 0l-7-7A1.994 1.994 0 013 12V7a4 4 0 014-4z\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm text-emerald-700 font-semibold\">20% Off — Code:\u003C/span>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"font-mono font-bold text-xs bg-white border border-dashed border-emerald-300 px-3 py-1.5 rounded text-emerald-700 tracking-wide select-all\">PROPFIRMS20\u003C/span>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Pros &#x26; Cons\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Pros\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Two instant funding account types\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Backed by regulated forex broker\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Low fees, raw pricing\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Scaling up to $2 million\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Huge range of instruments\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Instant Lite has tighter limits\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Limited educational content\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Payments only by card or crypto\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Instant not available on MT4\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>No swap free account option\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"full-details\">Full Details\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Blueberry Funded offers two instant funding accounts that start with a 80% profit share, giving you immediate access to funded capital without any need to work through an evaluation process. Both instant options use a trailing drawdown that moves up as your equity grows, locking in profits while protecting the account.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>The key difference between the two instant funding accounts is how risk is managed. The Instant Lite has stricter daily and overall loss limits, while Instant Elite removes the daily loss cap and has a more relaxed overall drawdown, but the initial fees are higher.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"instant-lite\">Instant Lite\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Instant Lite gives you instant access to funded capital with tighter drawdown limits. You’ll work under a 2% daily loss and a 4% total trailing drawdown, which moves up as your balance grows. The setup rewards consistency and helps control exposure from day one.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>It’s a solid option if you trade shorter timeframes, manage smaller positions, or prefer steady growth with less volatility. The structure keeps risk defined and lets you build results without large balance swings.\u003C/p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003Ctable>\u003Cthead>\u003Ctr>\u003Cth>Account Size\u003C/th>\u003Cth>One-Off Fee\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Profit Target\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Max Total Loss (10%)\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Max Daily Loss\u003C/th>\u003C/tr>\u003C/thead>\u003Ctbody>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>$1,250\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$37.04\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>None\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$125\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>None\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>$2,500\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$55.56\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>None\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$250\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>None\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>$5,000\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$83.33\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>None\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$500\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>None\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>$10,000\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$125.00\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>None\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$1,000\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>None\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>$25,000\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$187.50\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>None\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$2,500\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>None\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>$50,000\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$375.00\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>None\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$5,000\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>None\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>$100,000\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$750.00\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>None\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$10,000\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>None\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003C/tbody>\u003C/table>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"instant-elite\">Instant Elite\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Instant Elite offers the same direct funding but removes the daily loss limit, giving you a wider 10% total trailing drawdown. You have more room to manage open positions, scale in, or hold trades overnight.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>It fits better if you’re experienced with self-managed risk or trade swing and multi-day setups that need space to play out. The flexibility makes Instant Elite the more open version of Blueberry’s instant accounts, while keeping the same payout and scaling rules.\u003C/p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003Ctable>\u003Cthead>\u003Ctr>\u003Cth>Account Size\u003C/th>\u003Cth>One-Off Fee\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Profit Target\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Max Total Loss (10%)\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Max Daily Loss (2%)\u003C/th>\u003C/tr>\u003C/thead>\u003Ctbody>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>$2,500\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$100\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>None\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$250\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$50\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>$5,000\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$300\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>None\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$500\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$100\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>$10,000\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$400\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>None\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$1,000\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$200\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>$25,000\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$800\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>None\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$2,500\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$500\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>$50,000\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$1,500\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>None\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$5,000\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$1,000\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003C/tbody>\u003C/table>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"other-challenges\">Other Challenges\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>If you prefer an evaluation route, Blueberry has four additional challenges. Rapid runs a single 7 day challenge and will suit if you prefer short, high feedback setups. One Step keeps things simple with a static drawdown, while Two Step and Prime offer more structure.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"trading-fees\">Trading Fees\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Blueberry Funded’s trading costs come directly from its broker, Blueberry Markets, using a raw pricing model with fixed commissions.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Spreads:\u003C/strong> Starting from 0.1 pips on major forex pairs during peak trading hours. Spreads can widen slightly in low-liquidity periods but remain competitive compared to other instant funding firms.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Commissions:\u003C/strong> $3.50 per side for forex and gold. Indices, commodities, and crypto are commission free. US stock CFDs have a $2 round-turn fee.\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Cp>This setup provides stable execution costs for both discretionary and automated traders. All pricing is identical across platforms, so conditions stay consistent whether you trade on MT4, MT5, DXTrade, or TradeLocker.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"markets-and-leverage\">Markets and Leverage\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Blueberry Funded’s instant funding accounts offer access to over 1,100 instruments across six asset classes: forex, indices, commodities, cryptocurrencies, stocks, and synthetics.\u003C/p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003Ctable>\u003Cthead>\u003Ctr>\u003Cth>Asset Class\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Details\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Leverage\u003C/th>\u003C/tr>\u003C/thead>\u003Ctbody>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Forex\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>45 pairs including majors, minors, and exotics\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Up to 50:1 (Elite) / 30:1 (Lite)\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Indices\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>14 global indices (NASDAQ 100, S&#x26;P 500, GER30)\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Up to 10:1\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Commodities\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>17 instruments (gold, silver, crude oil, natural gas)\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Up to 10:1\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Crypto\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>52 pairs (BTC/USD, ETH/USD, SOL/USD)\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Up to 2:1\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Stocks\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1,000+ US stock CFDs via MT5 and TradeLocker\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Up to 10:1\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Synthetics\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>12 volatility based indices unique to Blueberry\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Up to 30:1\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003C/tbody>\u003C/table>\n\u003Cp>The range is one of the broadest available from any prop firm, allowing both short-term and multi-asset strategies without switching platforms or accounts.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"trading-platforms\">Trading Platforms\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Blueberry Funded supports four of the most popular trading platforms worldwide with MetaTrader 4 (MT4), MetaTrader 5 (MT5), DXTrade, and TradeLocker available.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>MT4:\u003C/strong> Available on evaluation and challenge accounts but not Instant Funding. Designed for manual and EA trading with familiar charting tools and order management.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>MT5:\u003C/strong> Available across all account types including Instant Funding. Supports advanced order types, Depth of Market data, and multi-asset trading such as stocks and crypto.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>DXTrade:\u003C/strong> Web-based platform with TradingView-style charting, ideal for quick execution and clean layout.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>TradeLocker:\u003C/strong> Browser and mobile-based interface focused on fast execution and modern usability.\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Cp>Instant Funding traders can choose between MT5, DXTrade, or TradeLocker. EA use and weekend trading are permitted, but strategies like latency arbitrage, grid systems, and news scalping remain restricted under standard prop rules.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"payouts-and-scaling\">Payouts and Scaling\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Profit payouts are available every 14 days through RiseWorks, with a $100 minimum. You keep 80% by default and 90% after consistent results. Accounts that meet performance and withdrawal milestones every three months can scale by 25%, up to a simulated balance of $2 million.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>The payout process is fast and predictable, which is a strong point for instant funding traders who rely on frequent withdrawals.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"trust-and-community\">Trust and Community\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Blueberry Funded operates under the same umbrella as Blueberry Markets, an ASIC regulated broker based out of Australia. That backing gives the firm genuine oversight and transparency on pricing and execution. It’s also a founding member of The Prop Association, which aims to set industry wide standards on fairness and dispute resolution.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>The firm’s Discord community has over 30,000 traders and remains active with shared trade setups, payouts, and platform feedback.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"verdict-on-blueberry-funded\">Verdict on Blueberry Funded\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Blueberry Funded ranks first because it delivers genuine instant access through two account types that serve different trading styles. With strong regulation behind it, low costs, wide market access, and a clean payout structure, it’s the most complete instant funding model available right now. The additional Rapid, One Step, and Two Step challenges round out a well-built program that suits both new and professional traders looking for direct capital access.\u003C/p>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"2-fxify--high-profit-split\">2. FXIFY — High Profit Split\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>FXIFY is the 2nd on our shortlist of the best instant funding prop firms, offering immediate access to capital with account sizes starting at $1,000 and profit shares up to 90%. Backed by FXPIG, it provides low spreads and access to MT4, MT5, DXTrade, and TradingView. With a scaling plan up to $4 million, FXIFY combines flexibility, reliability, and growth potential for all traders.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/fxify-1-1-1-1.png\" alt=\"FXIFY logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">FXIFY\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">High Profit Split\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">90%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Max DD\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">10%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Trustpilot\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">4.4 \u003Cspan class=\"text-amber-500\">★\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Ca href=\"/reviews/fxify\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-lg bg-teal-500 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-white hover:bg-teal-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n        Full Review →\n      \u003C/a>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose -mt-3 mb-6 rounded-xl border border-emerald-200 bg-emerald-50/80 px-5 py-3 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-3\">\n  \u003Ca href=\"https://trader.fxify.com/purchasechallenge?affiliateId=5837\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-emerald-500 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-emerald-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n    Visit FXIFY\n  \u003C/a>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2.5\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4 text-emerald-600 flex-shrink-0\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M7 7h.01M7 3h5c.512 0 1.024.195 1.414.586l7 7a2 2 0 010 2.828l-7 7a2 2 0 01-2.828 0l-7-7A1.994 1.994 0 013 12V7a4 4 0 014-4z\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm text-emerald-700 font-semibold\">15% Off — Code:\u003C/span>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"font-mono font-bold text-xs bg-white border border-dashed border-emerald-300 px-3 py-1.5 rounded text-emerald-700 tracking-wide select-all\">PROPFIRMS15\u003C/span>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Pros &#x26; Cons\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Pros\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Instant funding accounts from $1K\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Low fees and spreads from 0 pips\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>News trading allowed\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Broker backed proprietary trading firm\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Trailing drawdown may not suit all\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Max trading account 50K for instant\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Stocks only on MetaTrader 5\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Minimal educational materials\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"account-options\">Account Options\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>FXIFY’s Instant Funding Accounts let you start trading immediately with account sizes from $1,000 to $50,000, no evaluations required. Backed by FXPIG, a trusted forex broker, you can benefit from reliable trade execution and access to tight spreads on forex, indices, commodities, and cryptocurrencies.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>The instant funding accounts include simple, trader-friendly rules, like an 8% daily loss limit, designed to support disciplined trading without overwhelming beginner traders. Advanced traders will appreciate the flexibility to use MT4, MT5, or DXTrade platforms, accommodating both manual and automated strategies.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>FXIFY also offers a scaling plan where you can grow your trading account up to $4 million, with consistent performers increasing their account size by 25% every three months. Combined with profit shares up to 90%, it’s a strong option for traders focused on capital growth and earning potential.\u003C/p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003Ctable>\u003Cthead>\u003Ctr>\u003Cth>Account Size\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Fee\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Daily Loss Limit (8%)\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Max Trailing Drawdown (8%)\u003C/th>\u003C/tr>\u003C/thead>\u003Ctbody>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>$1,000\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$69\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$80\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$80\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>$2,500\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$119\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$200\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$200\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>$5,000\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$229\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$400\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$400\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>$10,000\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$449\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$800\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$800\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>$25,000\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$899\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$2,000\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$2,000\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>$50,000\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$1,749\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$4,000\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$4,000\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003C/tbody>\u003C/table>\n\u003Cp>This structure is perfect for traders who want a clear and simple path to funding. Newer traders will appreciate the smaller account sizes and straightforward rules, while experienced traders can benefit from the ability to trade immediately without the need for lengthy evaluations. However, because FXIFY uses a trailing drawdown, traders with aggressive or highly volatile strategies may find it less flexible than static drawdown models.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"trading-fees-1\">Trading Fees\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>FXIFY’s fee structure combines competitive spreads with low commission costs:\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Spreads:\u003C/strong> Starting from 0.0 pips on Forex pairs during peak trading times, though spreads can widen in low-liquidity periods.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Commissions:\u003C/strong> $3 per lot on Forex trades, which is lower than many competitors offering similar instant funding options.\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Cp>This setup is ideal for traders prioritising cost-effective trading, particularly during high-liquidity market hours.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"markets-and-leverage-1\">Markets and Leverage\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>FXIFY’s instant funding accounts grant access to a range of financial instruments:\u003C/p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003Ctable>\u003Cthead>\u003Ctr>\u003Cth>Asset Class\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Details\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Leverage\u003C/th>\u003C/tr>\u003C/thead>\u003Ctbody>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Forex\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>42 currency pairs (majors, minors, exotics)\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Up to 30:1\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Indices\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>13 global indices (S&#x26;P 500, NASDAQ 100)\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Up to 10:1\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Commodities\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Gold, silver, and oil (MT4/MT5)\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Up to 10:1\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Crypto\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Bitcoin, Ethereum, Ripple (MT4/MT5 only)\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Up to 2:1\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003C/tbody>\u003C/table>\n\u003Cp>The default leverage for instant funding is capped at 30:1 for forex and gold.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"platforms\">Platforms\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>FXIFY supports three trading platforms: MetaTrader 4 (MT4), MetaTrader 5 (MT5), and DXTrade with TradingView integration. Platform access depends on the account type.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>MT4\u003C/strong> is available on One, Two, and Three Step accounts only.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>MT5\u003C/strong> is available on all accounts, including Instant Funding and Lightning Challenge.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>DXTrade\u003C/strong> is available on all accounts except Lightning.\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Cp>Each platform caters to different trading styles. MT4 is suited to traders who rely on EAs or fast manual execution, MT5 includes more order types and stock/crypto access, and DXTrade offers browser-based charting powered by TradingView.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Instant Funding accounts do not support MT4. If you’re planning to use Expert Advisors or need low-latency execution via MT4, you’ll need to choose an evaluation challenge instead.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"payouts\">Payouts\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>FXIFY allows traders to request their first payout immediately after a profitable live trade. Instant Funding accounts follow a 14-day cycle, while other account types can request withdrawals on demand.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>The default schedule is monthly, but you can upgrade to bi-weekly payouts by selecting an add-on at checkout. Instant accounts have a $50 minimum withdrawal; evaluation accounts have no minimum.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Withdrawals are processed via crypto, bank transfer, or Deel, and typically take 24 to 48 hours. FXIFY also refunds your challenge fee with your first funded payout and regularly shares top withdrawal amounts publicly, adding trust and transparency.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"trust\">Trust\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>FXIFY is backed by FXPIG, a broker licensed by the Vanuatu Financial Services Commission. While this isn’t a top-tier regulatory licence like ASIC or FCA, it still adds a layer of oversight missing from many prop firms.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>FXIFY scores well on Trustpilot, with a rating of 4.2/5 from over 3,000 reviews. Traders regularly mention fast payouts, simple trading rules, and helpful community support. That said, some users have flagged minor delays in payout or activation on higher-tier accounts.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>The FXIFY Discord community is also active, with verified trader channels and weekly payout posts. It’s one of the better firm communities if you’re looking for peer support and updates.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"verdict-on-fxify-instant-funding-accounts\">Verdict on FXIFY Instant Funding Accounts\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>With account sizes from $1,000 to $50,000, profit splits up to 90%, and the backing of forex broker FXPIG, FXIFY takes 2nd place on our instant funding rankings. You can access top tier platforms like MT5 and DXTrade, get profit splits up to 90%, and withdraw profits every 14 days. While the trailing drawdown and limited MT4 access on Instant Funding accounts may not suit everyone, FXIFY remains one of the strongest options if you want to skip the challenge and get funded straight away.\u003C/p>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"3-dna-funded--good-for-crypto-instant-funding\">3. DNA Funded — Good for Crypto Instant Funding\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>DNA Funded ranked 3rd on our instant funding shortlist due to its simple instant funding structure and relatively low friction between account purchase and live trading. The firm offers true instant access with no evaluation phase, allowing you to begin trading funded capital immediately under predefined risk limits.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>During early testing, account activation was fast and we didn’t experience any delays signing up. Trading platform access was available immediately which keeps the onboarding process clean compared to instant models that introduce manual approval steps.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Based on our analysis of the top prop firms worldwide, we found DNA Funded to be the best prop firm overall with a score of 97/100. The Australian-based prop firm is backed by regulated broker DNA Markets (ASIC AFSL 514425), offering traders access to institutional-grade conditions like tight spreads, fast execution, and low trading costs.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/dna-funded-logo.png\" alt=\"DNA Funded logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">DNA Funded\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">Good for Crypto Instant Funding\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">90%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Max DD\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">10%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Trustpilot\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">4.9 \u003Cspan class=\"text-amber-500\">★\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Ca href=\"/reviews/dna-funded\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-lg bg-teal-500 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-white hover:bg-teal-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n        Full Review →\n      \u003C/a>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose -mt-3 mb-6 rounded-xl border border-emerald-200 bg-emerald-50/80 px-5 py-3 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-3\">\n  \u003Ca href=\"https://partners.dnafunded.com/click?campaign_id=1&#x26;ref_id=30\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-emerald-500 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-emerald-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n    Visit DNA Funded\n  \u003C/a>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2.5\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4 text-emerald-600 flex-shrink-0\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M7 7h.01M7 3h5c.512 0 1.024.195 1.414.586l7 7a2 2 0 010 2.828l-7 7a2 2 0 01-2.828 0l-7-7A1.994 1.994 0 013 12V7a4 4 0 014-4z\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm text-emerald-700 font-semibold\">25% Off — Code:\u003C/span>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"font-mono font-bold text-xs bg-white border border-dashed border-emerald-300 px-3 py-1.5 rounded text-emerald-700 tracking-wide select-all\">PROPFIRMS25\u003C/span>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Pros &#x26; Cons\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Pros\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>ASIC regulated broker-backed\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>800+ instruments including crypto\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Three flexible challenge types\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Low fees starting from $49\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>On-demand payouts in 24 hours\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>TradeLocker only (no MT4/MT5)\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>No EA or automated trading\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>40% daily profit cap applies\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Still a newer firm with limited track record\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"prop-challenges-and-accounts\">Prop Challenges and Accounts\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>DNA Funded offers three challenge types, catering to various trading styles:\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Single Helix (1-step challenge):\u003C/strong> Account sizes from $5,000 to $200,000. Fees start at $59, with a 10% profit target and no time limits, making it ideal for swing traders and those focused on longer-term strategies.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Double Helix (2-step challenge):\u003C/strong> Account sizes also range from $5,000 to $200,000, with fees starting at $49. Phase 1 requires a 10% profit target, while Phase 2 lowers it to 5%, with flexible trading days.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Rapid Challenge (1-step challenge):\u003C/strong> Designed for more experienced traders with account sizes ranging from $10,000 to $100,000, and fees from $99. This challenge requires a 5% profit target to be met within 10 days, with a stricter drawdown limit, making it suitable for scalpers or high-frequency traders.\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003Ctable>\u003Cthead>\u003Ctr>\u003Cth>DNA Funded Account Type\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Challenge Fees\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Account Sizes\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Early Payout (14→7 Days) Add-on\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Profit Split Increase (80%→90%) Add-on\u003C/th>\u003C/tr>\u003C/thead>\u003Ctbody>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Single Helix (1 Step)\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$59 – $1,451\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>5K – 200K\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Yes\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>No\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Double Helix (2 Step)\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$49 – $1,295\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>5K – 200K\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>No\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Yes\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Pro Challenge\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$99 – $714\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>10K – 100K\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Yes\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Yes\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003C/tbody>\u003C/table>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"markets-and-leverage-2\">Markets and Leverage\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>DNA Funded provides access to over 800 forex, commodities, indices, stocks, and crypto markets (with restrictions on crypto in the Pro Challenge).\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Leverage varies by challenge type and asset. Forex is capped at 1:50 on Double Helix and 1:30 on Single Helix and Pro Challenge. Commodities and indices are fixed at 1:10, stocks at 1:5 following a recent reduction from 1:10, and crypto is 1:2 but only available on Single and Double Helix.\u003C/p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003Ctable>\u003Cthead>\u003Ctr>\u003Cth>Asset Class\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Single Helix\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Double Helix\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Pro Challenge\u003C/th>\u003C/tr>\u003C/thead>\u003Ctbody>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Forex\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1:30\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1:50\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1:30\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Commodities\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1:10\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1:10\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1:10\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Indices\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1:10\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1:10\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1:10\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Stocks\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1:5\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1:5\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1:5\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Crypto\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1:2\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1:2\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Not Allowed\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003C/tbody>\u003C/table>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"trading-platforms-1\">Trading Platforms\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>All trading is done through \u003Cstrong>TradeLocker\u003C/strong>, which comes fully integrated with TradingView. This setup is ideal for manual traders who want advanced charting, one-click execution, and a clean web-based interface. However, automated trading and EAs are not supported.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>DNA Funded keeps its trading rules simple and in line with broker-backed standards. All accounts follow daily and overall drawdown limits based on the challenge type, and a daily profit cap of 40% now applies. This means you can only count up to 40% of your payout target in one trading day, which helps support steady, consistent trading.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Automated trading and expert advisors (EAs) are not allowed. You can copy trades between your own accounts, but not from others. News trading is allowed, but you’ll need to avoid opening or closing positions within 10 minutes of high-impact news. Weekend trading is also permitted.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"trust-and-community-1\">Trust and Community\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>DNA Funded is backed by DNA Markets, a well-known ASIC-regulated broker (AFSL 514425), ensuring tight spreads and reliable execution. While DNA Funded is still new, its connection to DNA Markets boosts its credibility hugely.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>The prop firm is also developing an active trading community through its Discord channel, offering a space for traders to connect and share insights. DNA Funded holds a \u003Cstrong>4.9/5 on Trustpilot\u003C/strong> from over 3,200 verified reviews.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"verdict-on-dna-funded\">Verdict on DNA Funded\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>DNA Funded is the best prop trading firm for 2026 even in the early stages of launch thanks to its flexible challenges, low fees, and an 80%–90% profit share. Backed by DNA Markets, it provides reliable market access across forex, commodities, indices, stocks, and crypto. You can read our full evaluation on our \u003Ca href=\"/reviews/dna-funded\">DNA Funded review page\u003C/a>.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>With a user-friendly platform like TradeLocker and growing community support, DNA Funded is the best prop firm for both new and experienced traders looking for a new challenge to become a funded trader.\u003C/p>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"4-tradeify--instant-funding-for-futures-trading\">4. Tradeify — Instant Funding for Futures Trading\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>Tradeify is the only dedicated futures prop firm on our instant funding shortlist. Its Lightning model gives you immediate access to funded futures capital through real US exchange markets — CME, CBOT, COMEX, and NYMEX — with no evaluation required. If you trade futures and want to skip the challenge phase entirely, this is the most direct route available.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/tradeify-logo.png\" alt=\"Tradeify logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">Tradeify\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">Instant Funding for Futures Trading\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">90%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Max DD\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">4%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Trustpilot\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">4.7 \u003Cspan class=\"text-amber-500\">★\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Ca href=\"/reviews/tradeify\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-lg bg-teal-500 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-white hover:bg-teal-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n        Full Review →\n      \u003C/a>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose -mt-3 mb-6 flex justify-center\">\n  \u003Ca href=\"https://tradeify.co/?ref=bestpropfirms\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-emerald-500 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-emerald-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n    Visit Tradeify\n  \u003C/a>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Pros &#x26; Cons\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Pros\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Instant futures funding (Lightning)\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Real exchange access (CME, CBOT, COMEX, NYMEX)\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>90% profit split with fast payouts\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Tradovate, TradingView, and NinjaTrader\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>No weekend trading on any model\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Strict consistency rules (20% daily cap)\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Email-only support, no phone or live chat\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>No EAs or copy trading allowed\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"lightning-instant-funding\">Lightning Instant Funding\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Tradeify’s \u003Cstrong>Lightning\u003C/strong> model is the instant funding option. It’s a one-time fee with no monthly subscription, no evaluation, and no profit target — you’re trading funded capital from day one. Account sizes range from $25,000 to $150,000 with an EOD trailing drawdown.\u003C/p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003Ctable>\u003Cthead>\u003Ctr>\u003Cth>Account Size\u003C/th>\u003Cth>One-Time Fee\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Max Drawdown\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Daily Profit Cap\u003C/th>\u003C/tr>\u003C/thead>\u003Ctbody>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>$25,000\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$349\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>EOD Trailing\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>20%\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>$50,000\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$509\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>EOD Trailing\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>20%\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>$100,000\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$629\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>EOD Trailing\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>20%\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>$150,000\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$729\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>EOD Trailing\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>20%\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003C/tbody>\u003C/table>\n\u003Cp>To request your first payout, you need 10 trading days and 5 profitable days with at least $200 profit each. The minimum withdrawal on Lightning is $1,000.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Tradeify also offers two evaluation models — \u003Cstrong>Advanced\u003C/strong> (intraday trailing drawdown, monthly from $69) and \u003Cstrong>Growth\u003C/strong> (EOD trailing drawdown, monthly from $139) — if you’d prefer a challenge-based route into funding.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"markets-and-platforms\">Markets and Platforms\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>All Tradeify accounts trade regulated US futures on CME, CBOT, COMEX, and NYMEX. That includes equity indices (ES, NQ, YM), metals (gold, silver), energies (crude oil, natural gas), currencies, agriculturals, and crypto futures (Micro Bitcoin, Micro Ether).\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Trading is done through \u003Cstrong>Tradovate\u003C/strong> (web and mobile), \u003Cstrong>TradingView\u003C/strong> (via Tradovate backend), or \u003Cstrong>NinjaTrader\u003C/strong> (desktop). All execution routes through Tradovate with a flat commission of $1.29 per side.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"payouts-and-trust\">Payouts and Trust\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Tradeify pays a 90% profit split with payouts processed in 24–72 hours via Rise Pay and Plane Payouts. The firm holds a \u003Cstrong>4.7/5 on Trustpilot\u003C/strong> from 1,800+ reviews and has an active Discord community of around 30,000 members.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"verdict-on-tradeify\">Verdict on Tradeify\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Tradeify earns 4th place as the best instant funding option for futures traders. The Lightning model gives you direct, no-evaluation access to real US exchange markets with a clean fee structure and strong platform support. The main trade-offs are strict consistency rules, no weekend trading, and limited support channels — but if you’re an experienced futures trader who knows what you’re doing, it’s one of the most direct routes to funded capital available.\u003C/p>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"5-funded-trading-plus--100k-instant-funding-account\">5. Funded Trading Plus — $100K Instant Funding Account\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>Funded Trading Plus (FTP) ranked 5th on our instant funding shortlist scoring 77/100 overall, largely due to its Master Trader Program which skips the evaluation process altogether.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>During our assessment, FTP grabbed our attention thanks to its account customisation features like adjustable payout intervals and upgradeable profit shares to 90%. This makes it ideal for experienced traders looking for a $100K instant funding account and the option to personalise their account terms.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/funded-trading-plus.png\" alt=\"Funded Trading Plus logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">Funded Trading Plus\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">$100K Instant Funding Account\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">90%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Max DD\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">10%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Trustpilot\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">4.5 \u003Cspan class=\"text-amber-500\">★\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Ca href=\"/reviews/funded-trading-plus\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-lg bg-teal-500 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-white hover:bg-teal-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n        Full Review →\n      \u003C/a>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose -mt-3 mb-6 flex justify-center\">\n  \u003Ca href=\"https://www.fundedtradingplus.com/?ref=2020\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-emerald-500 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-emerald-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n    Visit Funded Trading Plus\n  \u003C/a>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Pros &#x26; Cons\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Pros\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Instant funding with no evaluation\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Upgradable profit splits up to 90%\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Payouts every 3, 5, or 7 days\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>$25 fee for cTrader access\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Higher fees for instant funding\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Initial support bot can be limited\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"master-trader-program\">Master Trader Program\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>The Master Trader Program at FTP is a straightforward instant funding option ideal if you want to start with live capital immediately. There is no evaluation or multi-step process — just direct access to capital, allowing more experienced traders to bypass testing phases and focus solely on achieving profitability.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>The program’s profit share starts at 80%, but you can upgrade this to 90% based on performance milestones, offering higher earnings potential as your trading results improve. Account sizes range from $5,000 to $100,000, with the flexibility to scale up to $5 million over time.\u003C/p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003Ctable>\u003Cthead>\u003Ctr>\u003Cth>Account Size\u003C/th>\u003Cth>One-Time Fee\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Starting Profit Split\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Max Drawdown\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Daily Drawdown\u003C/th>\u003C/tr>\u003C/thead>\u003Ctbody>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>$5,000\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$225\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>80% (upgradable to 90%)\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>6%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>3%\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>$10,000\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$450\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>80% (upgradable to 90%)\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>6%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>3%\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>$25,000\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$1,125\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>80% (upgradable to 90%)\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>6%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>3%\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>$50,000\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$2,250\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>80% (upgradable to 90%)\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>6%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>3%\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>$100,000\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$4,500\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>80% (upgradable to 90%)\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>6%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>3%\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003C/tbody>\u003C/table>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"other-challenges-1\">Other Challenges\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>While the Master Trader Program is FTP’s instant funding option, they also offer structured evaluation challenges:\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>One-Phase Challenge:\u003C/strong> A single-step evaluation requiring a 10% profit target, suitable for confident traders ready to meet profitability criteria in one go. Fees start at $119.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Two-Phase Challenge:\u003C/strong> A structured assessment over two stages, with a lower profit target in the second phase to reduce pressure. Fees range from $199 to $1,097, depending on the account size.\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"trading-fees-2\">Trading Fees\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>FTP’s fee structure varies based on the account type and size. The Master Trader Program fees start at $225 and go up to $4,500, depending on the account size. Fees for the one-phase and two-phase challenges are lower, with the smallest one-phase account starting at $119 and the largest two-phase account at $1,097.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"financial-markets\">Financial Markets\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Our analysis of FTP’s market options revealed a decent selection across four main asset classes with access to 53 markets total.\u003C/p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003Ctable>\u003Cthead>\u003Ctr>\u003Cth>Asset Class\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Details\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Leverage\u003C/th>\u003C/tr>\u003C/thead>\u003Ctbody>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Forex\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>37 currency pairs (majors, minors, exotics)\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Up to 30:1\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Commodities\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Gold, Silver, and Oil\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Up to 10:1\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Indices\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>8 major global indices\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Up to 20:1 (10:1 on cTrader)\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Crypto\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>4 crypto pairs\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Up to 2:1\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003C/tbody>\u003C/table>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"platforms-1\">Platforms\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>FTP scored well in platform variety, with five options that accommodate different trading preferences:\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>MT4 and MT5:\u003C/strong> Widely used platforms supporting automated trading with Expert Advisors (EAs) and a solid range of charting and analytical tools.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Match-Trader:\u003C/strong> Integrated with TradingView, especially effective for traders who rely heavily on technical analysis.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>cTrader:\u003C/strong> Advanced tools and Level II pricing for deep market insights, but comes with a $25 access fee.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>DXTrade:\u003C/strong> FTP’s default platform, generally functional though it experienced minor delays in high-traffic times.\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"payouts-1\">Payouts\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>FTP offers flexible payout schedules — profit payouts can be made every 3, 5, or 7 days, giving traders more control over their earnings.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>The initial profit split is 80%, and traders can upgrade this to 85% or 90% if they prefer a higher share. The minimum withdrawal amount is set at $50. Payouts are processed via bank transfer or crypto.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"support\">Support\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Customer support at FTP is available 24/7 through email and live chat. Although the chat initially connects with a bot, you’re quickly transferred to a live representative for further assistance. Support is limited to English.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"trust-1\">Trust\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Funded Trading Plus has earned a high reputation, backed by a TrustPilot rating of 4.7/5. FTP’s online community presence includes active groups on Facebook and Discord with over 40,000 members, providing a space for traders to connect, share insights, and gain support.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"verdict-on-funded-trading-plus\">Verdict on Funded Trading Plus\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Based on our testing, FTP is one of the top prop firms for instant funding with its Master Trader Program, coming in 5th place in our shortlist. With good trading platforms, competitive payout schedules, and a supportive global community, Funded Trading Plus provides a solid offering for traders seeking fast access to trading accounts without lengthy evaluations.\u003C/p>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"instant-funding-accounts-and-profit-splits\">Instant Funding Accounts and Profit Splits\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>Instant funding accounts skip the evaluation process entirely, providing you with immediate access to trading capital after a one-time fee. You can begin live trading directly with a funded account, usually under a profit split agreement ranging from 70% to 90%.\u003C/p>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"how-we-ranked-instant-funding-programs\">How We Ranked Instant Funding Programs\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>We ranked the best instant funding prop firms using a structured methodology focused on key factors that impact trader success.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Unlike traditional prop firms that require an evaluation phase, instant funding programs allow traders to access capital immediately, so we prioritised firms that offer fair trading conditions, transparent fees, and reliable payouts.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Here’s our methodology when ranking the top instant funding prop firms:\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Instant Access to Capital:\u003C/strong> We included firms that offer true instant funding or extremely fast evaluation options (such as 7-day challenges).\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Profit Splits &#x26; Fees:\u003C/strong> A strong instant funding prop firm should provide fair profit splits (typically 70-90%) while keeping fees reasonable and transparent.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Payout Speed &#x26; Reliability:\u003C/strong> Since instant funding traders often rely on frequent withdrawals, firms with fast, consistent payouts scored higher.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Trading Rules &#x26; Risk Limits:\u003C/strong> We assessed drawdown limits, leverage rules, and other risk management policies to ensure traders have flexibility while maintaining account security.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Trading Platform Availability:\u003C/strong> Firms that support popular trading platforms like MT4, MT5, and cTrader ranked higher, as they provide better tools and execution options.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Reputation &#x26; Transparency:\u003C/strong> Trust is key in prop trading, so we factored in trader reviews, customer support quality, and clarity around fees, payouts, and trading conditions.\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"how-prop-trading-firm-challenges-work\">How Prop Trading Firm Challenges Work\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>Prop firm challenges are designed to assess traders’ skills and commitment by requiring them to achieve set profit targets under strict risk management rules.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>These challenges often involve one or two evaluation phases where traders must meet profit objectives, such as 8-10% within a set period while respecting daily and overall drawdown limits. Successfully passing these challenges leads to a funded account, granting traders access to capital while adhering to ongoing risk parameters.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>If you aren’t familiar with the prop industry, we recommend you learn more about \u003Ca href=\"/guides/what-is-a-prop-firm\">prop trading firms\u003C/a> and how challenges work before you buy an instant funding account.\u003C/p>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"faqs\">FAQs\u003C/h2>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"what-is-the-best-instant-funded-prop-firm\">What is the best instant funded prop firm?\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Blueberry Funded is the best instant funding prop firm, offering two true instant funding accounts that let you start trading funded capital immediately with no evaluation or time limit. You can choose between Instant Lite, with a 2% daily and 4% total drawdown, or Instant Elite, which removes the daily cap and sets a 10% trailing limit.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>You can trade on MT5, DXTrade, or TradeLocker, earn up to a 90% profit split, and scale your account up to $2 million.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"are-instant-funding-prop-firms-legit\">Are instant funding prop firms legit?\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Yes, instant funding prop firms are legitimate, but their reliability depends on their trading conditions, payout history, and transparency. Reputable instant funding firms like FXIFY and Funded Trading Plus provide real capital, fair profit share agreements, and clear rules. However, some other prop firms have hidden fees, unclear trading terms, or delayed payouts, making due diligence essential.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"which-prop-firm-payout-the-fastest\">Which prop firm payout the fastest?\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Funded Trading Plus (FTP) is the prop firm with one of the fastest payout systems, allowing withdrawals every 3, 5, or 7 days. This flexible schedule gives traders more frequent access to profits than most firms, which typically offer biweekly or monthly payouts. However, instant funding accounts do not guarantee instant payouts.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"which-prop-firm-gives-the-most-money\">Which prop firm gives the most money?\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Blueberry Funded offers one of the highest earning potentials through its instant funding programs, with profit splits up to 90% and a scaling plan that goes up to $2 million. Both Instant Lite and Instant Elite accounts give you direct access to funded capital from day one.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>FXIFY also provides strong earning potential, matching 90% profit splits and offering a larger scaling plan up to $4 million. Both prop trading firms are broker backed and give you immediate access to capital and regular payouts, but Blueberry Funded’s regulatory backing and two instant funding models make it the stronger overall choice for consistent long term returns.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"does-instant-funding-actually-pay-out\">Does instant funding actually pay out?\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Yes, instant funding accounts do offer profit payouts, typically based on a profit share arrangement. You get to keep a percentage of the profits you generate, often between 80% to 100%, depending on the prop firm and account performance. Some prop firms have minimum withdrawal amounts, and others offer fast payouts, such as weekly or biweekly.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"what-are-the-benefits-of-funded-forex-accounts\">What are the benefits of funded forex accounts?\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>There are many perks to funded forex accounts as you gain access to trading capital without risking your own money. Unlike self-funded CFD trading, proprietary trading firms allow traders to take larger positions with firm capital, enhancing profit potential while limiting personal financial exposure.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>View our top 10 \u003Ca href=\"/prop-firms\">best prop firms\u003C/a> list for a comparison of the top funded forex accounts.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"how-do-prop-traders-manage-their-risk\">How do prop traders manage their risk?\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Prop traders use risk management techniques so they can follow the strict guidelines set by prop firms, such as daily and max drawdown limits and required stop-loss orders. These techniques and trading rules help control losses and prevent excessive risk-taking on any single trade. Many firms also enforce position size limits and leverage restrictions to maintain a balanced risk profile and help traders pass prop challenges.\u003C/p>",{"headings":6242,"localImagePaths":6377,"remoteImagePaths":6378,"frontmatter":6379,"imagePaths":6391},[6243,6246,6249,6252,6255,6258,6261,6264,6267,6268,6269,6272,6273,6276,6279,6282,6284,6285,6288,6290,6293,6296,6299,6300,6301,6302,6303,6306,6309,6312,6315,6318,6321,6324,6327,6329,6331,6334,6336,6338,6341,6343,6346,6349,6352,6355,6356,6359,6362,6365,6368,6371,6374],{"depth":879,"slug":6244,"text":6245},"how-did-we-test-instant-funding-prop-firms","How Did We Test Instant Funding Prop Firms?",{"depth":879,"slug":6247,"text":6248},"the-10-best-instant-funding-accounts-we-tested-in-2026","The 10 Best Instant Funding Accounts We Tested in 2026",{"depth":879,"slug":6250,"text":6251},"1-blueberry-funded--best-instant-funding-prop-firm-overall","1. Blueberry Funded — Best Instant Funding Prop Firm Overall",{"depth":158,"slug":6253,"text":6254},"full-details","Full Details",{"depth":158,"slug":6256,"text":6257},"instant-lite","Instant Lite",{"depth":158,"slug":6259,"text":6260},"instant-elite","Instant Elite",{"depth":158,"slug":6262,"text":6263},"other-challenges","Other Challenges",{"depth":158,"slug":6265,"text":6266},"trading-fees","Trading Fees",{"depth":158,"slug":4841,"text":4842},{"depth":158,"slug":4844,"text":4845},{"depth":158,"slug":6270,"text":6271},"payouts-and-scaling","Payouts and Scaling",{"depth":158,"slug":4847,"text":4848},{"depth":158,"slug":6274,"text":6275},"verdict-on-blueberry-funded","Verdict on Blueberry Funded",{"depth":879,"slug":6277,"text":6278},"2-fxify--high-profit-split","2. FXIFY — High Profit Split",{"depth":158,"slug":6280,"text":6281},"account-options","Account Options",{"depth":158,"slug":6283,"text":6266},"trading-fees-1",{"depth":158,"slug":4862,"text":4842},{"depth":158,"slug":6286,"text":6287},"platforms","Platforms",{"depth":158,"slug":5957,"text":6289},"Payouts",{"depth":158,"slug":6291,"text":6292},"trust","Trust",{"depth":158,"slug":6294,"text":6295},"verdict-on-fxify-instant-funding-accounts","Verdict on FXIFY Instant Funding Accounts",{"depth":879,"slug":6297,"text":6298},"3-dna-funded--good-for-crypto-instant-funding","3. DNA Funded — Good for Crypto Instant Funding",{"depth":158,"slug":4838,"text":4839},{"depth":158,"slug":4882,"text":4842},{"depth":158,"slug":4864,"text":4845},{"depth":158,"slug":4869,"text":4848},{"depth":158,"slug":6304,"text":6305},"verdict-on-dna-funded","Verdict on DNA Funded",{"depth":879,"slug":6307,"text":6308},"4-tradeify--instant-funding-for-futures-trading","4. Tradeify — Instant Funding for Futures Trading",{"depth":158,"slug":6310,"text":6311},"lightning-instant-funding","Lightning Instant Funding",{"depth":158,"slug":6313,"text":6314},"markets-and-platforms","Markets and Platforms",{"depth":158,"slug":6316,"text":6317},"payouts-and-trust","Payouts and Trust",{"depth":158,"slug":6319,"text":6320},"verdict-on-tradeify","Verdict on Tradeify",{"depth":879,"slug":6322,"text":6323},"5-funded-trading-plus--100k-instant-funding-account","5. Funded Trading Plus — $100K Instant Funding Account",{"depth":158,"slug":6325,"text":6326},"master-trader-program","Master Trader Program",{"depth":158,"slug":6328,"text":6263},"other-challenges-1",{"depth":158,"slug":6330,"text":6266},"trading-fees-2",{"depth":158,"slug":6332,"text":6333},"financial-markets","Financial Markets",{"depth":158,"slug":6335,"text":6287},"platforms-1",{"depth":158,"slug":6337,"text":6289},"payouts-1",{"depth":158,"slug":6339,"text":6340},"support","Support",{"depth":158,"slug":6342,"text":6292},"trust-1",{"depth":158,"slug":6344,"text":6345},"verdict-on-funded-trading-plus","Verdict on Funded Trading Plus",{"depth":879,"slug":6347,"text":6348},"instant-funding-accounts-and-profit-splits","Instant Funding Accounts and Profit Splits",{"depth":879,"slug":6350,"text":6351},"how-we-ranked-instant-funding-programs","How We Ranked Instant Funding Programs",{"depth":879,"slug":6353,"text":6354},"how-prop-trading-firm-challenges-work","How Prop Trading Firm Challenges Work",{"depth":879,"slug":4935,"text":4936},{"depth":158,"slug":6357,"text":6358},"what-is-the-best-instant-funded-prop-firm","What is the best instant funded prop firm?",{"depth":158,"slug":6360,"text":6361},"are-instant-funding-prop-firms-legit","Are instant funding prop firms legit?",{"depth":158,"slug":6363,"text":6364},"which-prop-firm-payout-the-fastest","Which prop firm payout the fastest?",{"depth":158,"slug":6366,"text":6367},"which-prop-firm-gives-the-most-money","Which prop firm gives the most money?",{"depth":158,"slug":6369,"text":6370},"does-instant-funding-actually-pay-out","Does instant funding actually pay out?",{"depth":158,"slug":6372,"text":6373},"what-are-the-benefits-of-funded-forex-accounts","What are the benefits of funded forex accounts?",{"depth":158,"slug":6375,"text":6376},"how-do-prop-traders-manage-their-risk","How do prop traders manage their risk?",[],[],{"title":6213,"excerpt":6214,"category":5171,"tags":6380,"author":4798,"authorImage":4799,"publishedAt":1273,"featured":110,"coverImage":6217,"readingTimeMinutes":5176,"youtubeVideoId":4800,"featuredFirms":6381},[6216,4796,5173],[6382,6383,6384,6385,6386,6387,6388,6389,6390],{"slug":332,"descriptor":6220},{"slug":1599,"descriptor":5800},{"slug":728,"descriptor":6223},{"slug":2747,"descriptor":6225},{"slug":1278,"descriptor":6227},{"slug":1843,"descriptor":6229},{"slug":1682,"descriptor":6231},{"slug":1459,"descriptor":6233},{"slug":1975,"descriptor":6235},[],"instant-funding.md","prop-trading-account-types",{"id":6393,"data":6395,"body":6401,"filePath":6402,"digest":6403,"rendered":6404,"legacyId":6500},{"title":6396,"excerpt":6397,"category":5955,"tags":6398,"author":4798,"authorImage":5960,"publishedAt":240,"featured":110,"readingTimeMinutes":405},"Prop Trading Account Types: One-Step, Two-Step, Instant Funding & More","Prop trading firms give traders access to capital without risking personal funds. Account types vary from quick one-step challenges to multi-step evaluations and instant funding options.",[5609,6399,6400,6216,4796],"account types","evaluations","Prop trading firms give traders access to capital without risking personal funds. Account types vary, from quick one-step challenges to multi-step evaluations and instant funding options. This guide covers each type, helping you find the right pathway to a funded account.\n\nProp trading firms let traders access more capital through structured accounts and evaluations, using the firm's funds instead of their own, so they don't take on financial risk.\n\nTo get a funded account, you need to complete an evaluation or challenge, which involves hitting specific profit targets within risk limits. After passing the challenge, you can start trading with the prop firm's capital instead of your own money.\n\nSome trading firms also offer instant funding accounts, which skip the evaluation for a higher fee. To keep your funded account, you must follow the prop firm's trading rules, like risk and drawdown limits.\n\n## Account Types at a Glance\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-8\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"overflow-x-auto\">\n      \u003Ctable class=\"w-full text-sm\">\n        \u003Cthead>\n          \u003Ctr class=\"bg-[#0d1b2a]\">\n            \u003Cth class=\"px-5 py-3.5 text-left text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-300 uppercase tracking-widest\">Account Type\u003C/th>\n            \u003Cth class=\"px-4 py-3.5 text-center text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-300 uppercase tracking-widest\">Phases\u003C/th>\n            \u003Cth class=\"px-4 py-3.5 text-center text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-300 uppercase tracking-widest\">Time to Fund\u003C/th>\n            \u003Cth class=\"px-4 py-3.5 text-center text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-300 uppercase tracking-widest\">Typical Cost\u003C/th>\n            \u003Cth class=\"px-4 py-3.5 text-left text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-300 uppercase tracking-widest\">Best For\u003C/th>\n          \u003C/tr>\n        \u003C/thead>\n        \u003Ctbody class=\"divide-y divide-slate-100\">\n          \u003Ctr class=\"hover:bg-teal-50/30 transition-colors\">\n            \u003Ctd class=\"px-5 py-3.5 font-bold text-slate-900\">One-Step\u003C/td>\n            \u003Ctd class=\"px-4 py-3.5 text-center\">\u003Cspan class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-teal-50 text-teal-700 text-xs font-bold\">1\u003C/span>\u003C/td>\n            \u003Ctd class=\"px-4 py-3.5 text-center text-slate-600\">Fast\u003C/td>\n            \u003Ctd class=\"px-4 py-3.5 text-center\">\u003Cspan class=\"rounded-full bg-teal-50 text-teal-700 px-2.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-semibold\">$\u003C/span>\u003C/td>\n            \u003Ctd class=\"px-4 py-3.5 text-slate-600\">Confident, experienced traders\u003C/td>\n          \u003C/tr>\n          \u003Ctr class=\"hover:bg-teal-50/30 transition-colors bg-slate-50/40\">\n            \u003Ctd class=\"px-5 py-3.5 font-bold text-slate-900\">Two-Step\u003C/td>\n            \u003Ctd class=\"px-4 py-3.5 text-center\">\u003Cspan class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-teal-50 text-teal-700 text-xs font-bold\">2\u003C/span>\u003C/td>\n            \u003Ctd class=\"px-4 py-3.5 text-center text-slate-600\">Moderate\u003C/td>\n            \u003Ctd class=\"px-4 py-3.5 text-center\">\u003Cspan class=\"rounded-full bg-teal-50 text-teal-700 px-2.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-semibold\">$$\u003C/span>\u003C/td>\n            \u003Ctd class=\"px-4 py-3.5 text-slate-600\">Structured progression for beginners\u003C/td>\n          \u003C/tr>\n          \u003Ctr class=\"hover:bg-teal-50/30 transition-colors\">\n            \u003Ctd class=\"px-5 py-3.5 font-bold text-slate-900\">Three-Step\u003C/td>\n            \u003Ctd class=\"px-4 py-3.5 text-center\">\u003Cspan class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-teal-50 text-teal-700 text-xs font-bold\">3\u003C/span>\u003C/td>\n            \u003Ctd class=\"px-4 py-3.5 text-center text-slate-600\">Slow\u003C/td>\n            \u003Ctd class=\"px-4 py-3.5 text-center\">\u003Cspan class=\"rounded-full bg-teal-50 text-teal-700 px-2.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-semibold\">$$\u003C/span>\u003C/td>\n            \u003Ctd class=\"px-4 py-3.5 text-slate-600\">Skill-building & long-term consistency\u003C/td>\n          \u003C/tr>\n          \u003Ctr class=\"hover:bg-teal-50/30 transition-colors bg-slate-50/40\">\n            \u003Ctd class=\"px-5 py-3.5 font-bold text-slate-900\">Instant Funding\u003C/td>\n            \u003Ctd class=\"px-4 py-3.5 text-center\">\u003Cspan class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-slate-100 text-slate-500 text-xs font-bold\">0\u003C/span>\u003C/td>\n            \u003Ctd class=\"px-4 py-3.5 text-center\">\u003Cspan class=\"text-teal-600 font-bold\">Immediate\u003C/span>\u003C/td>\n            \u003Ctd class=\"px-4 py-3.5 text-center\">\u003Cspan class=\"rounded-full bg-amber-50 text-amber-700 px-2.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-semibold\">$$$\u003C/span>\u003C/td>\n            \u003Ctd class=\"px-4 py-3.5 text-slate-600\">Experienced traders wanting fast access\u003C/td>\n          \u003C/tr>\n        \u003C/tbody>\n      \u003C/table>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"px-5 py-3 border-t border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 leading-relaxed\">Cost ranges vary by firm and account size. See individual \u003Ca href=\"/reviews\" class=\"text-teal-600 font-semibold hover:underline\">firm reviews\u003C/a> for exact pricing.\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n## One-Step Evaluations\n\nOne-step evaluations are straightforward, single-phase challenges that let you demonstrate your trading skills by meeting a single profit target within defined risk limits.\n\nUnlike multi-step evaluations, this model fast-tracks you to funding with just one successful performance check. You'll pay a one-off fee to access the challenge, and if you meet the profit and drawdown requirements, you'll be eligible for a funded account.\n\nOne-step evaluations suit confident traders with a solid trading background who want a quicker route to a funded account but still value some level of performance assessment.\n\nIf you're comfortable managing risk and hitting targets without needing an extensive evaluation period, a one-step challenge may be a good fit.\n\nFor beginner traders, however, it may lack the structured progression that multi-step models offer.\n\n### Pros and Cons of One-Step Evaluations\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-8\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-2xl border border-teal-200 bg-teal-50/50 p-5\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-teal-600 mb-4\">Pros\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-3\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2.5\">\n          \u003Cspan class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-teal-500 flex items-center justify-center\">\n            \u003Csvg class=\"h-3 w-3 text-white\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M5 13l4 4L19 7\"/>\u003C/svg>\n          \u003C/span>\n          \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm text-slate-700\">Faster path to funding\u003C/span>\n        \u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2.5\">\n          \u003Cspan class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-teal-500 flex items-center justify-center\">\n            \u003Csvg class=\"h-3 w-3 text-white\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M5 13l4 4L19 7\"/>\u003C/svg>\n          \u003C/span>\n          \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm text-slate-700\">Lower evaluation fees\u003C/span>\n        \u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2.5\">\n          \u003Cspan class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-teal-500 flex items-center justify-center\">\n            \u003Csvg class=\"h-3 w-3 text-white\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M5 13l4 4L19 7\"/>\u003C/svg>\n          \u003C/span>\n          \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm text-slate-700\">Ideal for confident traders\u003C/span>\n        \u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-2xl border border-red-200 bg-red-50/50 p-5\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-red-500 mb-4\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-3\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2.5\">\n          \u003Cspan class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-red-400 flex items-center justify-center\">\n            \u003Csvg class=\"h-3 w-3 text-white\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>\n          \u003C/span>\n          \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm text-slate-700\">Less structured for skill-building\u003C/span>\n        \u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2.5\">\n          \u003Cspan class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-red-400 flex items-center justify-center\">\n            \u003Csvg class=\"h-3 w-3 text-white\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>\n          \u003C/span>\n          \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm text-slate-700\">Higher pressure to meet targets\u003C/span>\n        \u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2.5\">\n          \u003Cspan class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-red-400 flex items-center justify-center\">\n            \u003Csvg class=\"h-3 w-3 text-white\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>\n          \u003C/span>\n          \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm text-slate-700\">Higher risk for beginner traders\u003C/span>\n        \u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n### Best Prop Firms for One-Step Challenges\n\nProp firms such as DNA Funded and FundedNext provide streamlined one-step evaluation challenges, allowing traders a quicker path to securing funded accounts. These challenges offer a simplified evaluation process with straightforward profit targets, appealing to traders seeking fast-track funding without multi-phase evaluations.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-8 space-y-4\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"relative group bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-md hover:border-teal-200 transition-all duration-200 overflow-hidden\">\n    \u003Cspan class=\"absolute left-0 top-4 bottom-4 w-1 rounded-r-full bg-gradient-to-b from-teal-400 to-teal-600 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-200\">\u003C/span>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"p-5 sm:p-6\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4\">\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-white border border-slate-200 flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden shadow-sm\">\n          \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/dna-funded-logo.png\" alt=\"DNA Funded logo\" class=\"w-full h-full object-contain p-1.5\" loading=\"lazy\"/>\n        \u003C/div>\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\">\n          \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap\">\n            \u003Ca href=\"/reviews/dna-funded\" class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 hover:text-teal-600 transition-colors\">DNA Funded\u003C/a>\n          \u003C/div>\n          \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">One-step, two-step, and instant funding options with up to 90% profit split\u003C/p>\n        \u003C/div>\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 rounded-xl bg-teal-500 w-14 h-14 flex flex-col items-center justify-center\">\n          \u003Cspan class=\"text-xl font-black text-white leading-none\">97\u003C/span>\n          \u003Cspan class=\"text-[8px] text-teal-100 font-medium\">/100\u003C/span>\n        \u003C/div>\n      \u003C/d