lass=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Strict drawdown rules\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Limited payment options\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Minimal educational resources\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n### Prop Firm Details\n\nBlueberry Funded scored 93/100 during testing, and ranked in 4th place on our list of the best crypto prop firms. You can trade 52 crypto pairs, one of the best selections available, including BTC/USD, ETH/USD, SOL/USD, and XRP/USD. Leverage is capped at 1:2 for all challenge types. Crypto is commission-free, and spreads are competitive — EUR/USD averages 0.2 pips and BTC/USD remains tightly priced.\n\nYou can use Expert Advisors (EAs) on MT4 and MT5, which is ideal for crypto algo traders. TradeLocker is also available for browser-based access, with stocks and crypto supported natively.\n\nTheir scaling model increases capital by 25% every 3 months, with a maximum simulated allocation of $2 million.\n\n### Evaluation Process\n\nBlueberry Funded offers four challenge types suited to different strategies:\n\n**One Step Challenge:** 10% profit target, 6% drawdown, no time limit.\n\n**Two Step Challenge:** 10% and 5% targets across two phases, with 10% drawdown and 1:50 leverage.\n\n**Rapid Challenge:** 5% target within 7 days, 3% daily and 4% total trailing drawdown.\n\n**Stock Challenge:** 10% and 6% targets with stricter drawdown and trading hour limits (crypto not included here).\n\nAll challenges provide 80% profit splits initially, upgradeable to 90%.\n\n### Payments and Payouts\n\nYou can pay for challenges via credit card or cryptocurrency, with fees ranging from $32.50 to $1,100 depending on account size and model.\n\nProfit payouts are processed every 14 days via RiseWorks, with a minimum withdrawal of $100. Payouts are available in USDC or USDT, and crypto accounts are treated the same as forex in terms of rules and withdrawal eligibility.\n\n### Trading Platforms\n\nBlueberry Funded supports four platforms:\n\n- **MetaTrader 4 (MT4):** EA support, advanced charting, great for scalping bots.\n- **MetaTrader 5 (MT5):** Access to stocks + crypto, DOM, more indicators.\n- **DXTrade:** Basic, browser-based, fewer tools.\n- **TradeLocker:** Clean UI, mobile support, stocks and crypto enabled.\n\nFor crypto traders, MT5 and TradeLocker offer the best blend of automation, usability, and market access.\n\n### Support and Trust\n\nSupport is available 24/5 via live chat and email, with a helpful Discord community of over 27,000 members. Blueberry Funded is backed by Blueberry Markets, an ASIC-regulated broker, and became a founding member of The Prop Association in 2025.\n\nThe firm currently holds a TrustPilot rating of 4.1/5, and offers consistent payouts and transparent rules, though some traders cite strict news trading restrictions as a downside.\n\n### Final Verdict\n\nBlueberry Funded is one of the top crypto prop firms for EA users, offering commission-free access to 50+ pairs and 24/7 trading. With four challenge types, low fees, platform variety, and strong scaling potential, it's a well-rounded choice for both manual and automated crypto traders.\n\n---\n\n## 4. FundedNext — Consistent Trading Rules\n\nFundedNext is a great option if you want zero-commission crypto trading, profit splits up to 95%, and access to multiple trading platforms like MT4, MT5, and cTrader. Payouts are processed every two weeks, keeping withdrawals consistent.\n\nUse promo code PROPFIRMS to get 120% of your challenge fee refunded — that's your entire fee back plus an extra 20% as a bonus.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/fundednext.png\" alt=\"FundedNext logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\" />\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">FundedNext\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">Consistent Trading Rules\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">95%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Max DD\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">10%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Trustpilot\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">4.5 \u003Cspan class=\"text-amber-500\">★\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Ca href=\"/reviews/fundednext\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-lg bg-teal-500 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-white hover:bg-teal-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n        Full Review →\n      \u003C/a>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose -mt-3 mb-6 rounded-xl border border-emerald-200 bg-emerald-50/80 px-5 py-3 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-3\">\n  \u003Ca href=\"https://fundednext.com/?fpr=noam82\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-emerald-500 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-emerald-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14\" />\u003C/svg>\n    Visit FundedNext\n  \u003C/a>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2.5\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4 text-emerald-600 flex-shrink-0\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M7 7h.01M7 3h5c.512 0 1.024.195 1.414.586l7 7a2 2 0 010 2.828l-7 7a2 2 0 01-2.828 0l-7-7A1.994 1.994 0 013 12V7a4 4 0 014-4z\" />\u003C/svg>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm text-emerald-700 font-semibold\">120% Refund — Code:\u003C/span>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"font-mono font-bold text-xs bg-white border border-dashed border-emerald-300 px-3 py-1.5 rounded text-emerald-700 tracking-wide select-all\">PROPFIRMS\u003C/span>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Pros & Cons\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Pros\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Commission-free crypto trading\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Allows Expert Advisors (EAs)\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Up to 95% profit split\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Strict daily loss limits\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Only 10 crypto markets\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>cTrader/Match-Trader cost $25\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n### Prop Firm Details\n\nFundedNext provides access to 10 crypto markets including BTC/USD, ETH/USD, and XRP/USD. All crypto trades are commission-free with a fixed 2:1 leverage cap.\n\nTraders can use EAs on MT4 and MT5, but automation is not supported on cTrader. This makes FundedNext a strong choice for crypto scalpers and algo traders using MetaTrader.\n\n### Evaluation Process\n\nFundedNext offers three crypto-compatible challenges:\n\n**Stellar One Step:** 10% profit target, 3% daily / 6% overall loss. 15% profit share during the challenge, 95% when funded.\n\n**Stellar Two Step:** Two-phase model with 8% and 5% targets. Includes 15% profit share during the challenge and 95% when funded.\n\n**Stellar Lite:** Two-step option with lower entry fees and tighter rules. No profit share during the challenge, but 95% once funded.\n\nAll models are time-unlimited and allow for challenge add-ons like no minimum trading days or extended loss limits.\n\n| Feature | Stellar (1-Step) | Stellar (2-Step) | Stellar Lite |\n|---------|-----------------|-----------------|-------------|\n| Challenge Phases | 1 Phase | 2 Phases | 2 Phases |\n| Account Sizes | 6K - 200K | 6K - 200K | 5K - 100K |\n| Audition Fees | $65 - $1,099 | $59 - $999 | $32 - $399 |\n| Leverage | 30:1 | 100:1 | 100:1 |\n| Commission | $5 | $5 | $7 |\n| Profit Target | 10% | 8%, 5% | 8%, 4% |\n| Maximum Daily Loss | 3% | 5% | 4% |\n| Maximum Overall Loss | 6% | 10% | 8% |\n| Time Limit | No Time Limit | No Time Limit | No Time Limit |\n| Challenge Phase Profit Share | 15% | 15% | N/A |\n| Funded Profit Split | 95% | 95% | 95% |\n| Minimum Trading Days | 2 | 5 | 5 |\n\n### Payments and Payouts\n\nWithdrawals are available every 14 days for most models, and every 21 days for Stellar Lite. You can withdraw via crypto, Deel, or bank transfer.\n\n- **Minimum Payout:** $20\n- **Crypto Payouts:** Only option if under $50\n- **Evaluation Fee:** Fully refunded after your first funded withdrawal, with an added 20% bonus using the PROPFIRMS code\n\n### Trading Platforms\n\nYou can trade crypto on FundedNext using:\n\n- **MT4 & MT5:** EA support, free access\n- **cTrader:** Manual trading only, $25 platform fee, not available for accounts above $100K\n- **Match-Trader:** Web-based with mobile access, $25 fee, also unavailable above $100K\n\nTradingView is available via MT5 for advanced charting.\n\n### Support and Trust\n\nWith a Trustpilot rating of 4.6/5 stars and an active community across Telegram and Discord, FundedNext maintains a strong reputation.\n\nThe prop firm's strong educational resources, including webinars and a detailed dashboard, ensure traders have the support needed to succeed.\n\n### Final Verdict\n\nFundedNext is a top choice for crypto traders seeking high profit splits, commission-free trading, and strong platform variety. With three challenge types, bi-weekly payouts, and a large active community, it strikes a great balance for both manual and algorithmic crypto trading.\n\n---\n\n## 5. FXIFY Futures — CME Futures Trading\n\nFXIFY Futures is the best futures prop firm we reviewed with an overall score of 88/100. You go through a one step evaluation process to receive a funded account with up to 100% profit split. You also get access to real-time CME data with TradingView charts.\n\nYou can also save 15% on all futures challenge fees by using the promo code PROPFIRMS15 at checkout.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/fxify-futures.png\" alt=\"FXIFY Futures logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\" />\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">FXIFY Futures\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">CME Futures Trading\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">100%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Max DD\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">5%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Trustpilot\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">3.9 \u003Cspan class=\"text-amber-500\">★\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Ca href=\"/reviews/fxify-futures\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-lg bg-teal-500 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-white hover:bg-teal-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n        Full Review →\n      \u003C/a>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose -mt-3 mb-6 rounded-xl border border-emerald-200 bg-emerald-50/80 px-5 py-3 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-3\">\n  \u003Ca href=\"https://app.fxifyfutures.com?ref=VNPb7mgMLt63\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-emerald-500 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-emerald-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14\" />\u003C/svg>\n    Visit FXIFY Futures\n  \u003C/a>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2.5\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4 text-emerald-600 flex-shrink-0\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M7 7h.01M7 3h5c.512 0 1.024.195 1.414.586l7 7a2 2 0 010 2.828l-7 7a2 2 0 01-2.828 0l-7-7A1.994 1.994 0 013 12V7a4 4 0 014-4z\" />\u003C/svg>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm text-emerald-700 font-semibold\">15% Off — Code:\u003C/span>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"font-mono font-bold text-xs bg-white border border-dashed border-emerald-300 px-3 py-1.5 rounded text-emerald-700 tracking-wide select-all\">PROPFIRMS15\u003C/span>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Pros & Cons\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Pros\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Profit splits up to 100%\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>No time limits on evaluation\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>TradingView charts\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Payouts follow a tiered system\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>No NinjaTrader or Rithmic integration\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Buffer zone required before withdrawals\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n### Prop Firm Details\n\nFXIFY Futures is the top-rated futures prop firm if you are looking for a funded account with high profit splits and no time limits. With a one-step evaluation and scalable profit-sharing up to 100%, you get an accessible pathway to a professional style trading environment.\n\nYou can choose from two challenge types being Starter and Expert. In terms of trading platforms, the FFX Platform doesn't have any third-party integrations but does give you TradingView charts and real-time CME data.\n\nFXIFY Futures straight up pricing structure means you don't need to worry about hidden fees, with your monthly challenge payments covering all trading costs. Profit payouts are tiered, starting at 80% and going all the way up to 100%.\n\n**Key Features**\n\n- **Evaluation Process:** One-step challenge with no time limits, allowing you to hit profit targets at your own pace.\n- **Platform Options:** The FFX Platform with TradingView charts and real-time CME data.\n- **Futures Market Access:** Includes forex, equities, commodities, and bonds.\n- **Profit Split:** Tiered payout system, starting at 80% and scaling to 100% based on withdrawal milestones.\n\n### Trading Costs and Fees\n\nFXIFY Futures' pricing structure is clear and straightforward, with monthly fees for the evaluation phase and no recurring costs after funding. Unlike other futures prop firms, FXIFY does not charge platform fees, data fees, or per-trade commissions, making it a cost-effective choice for funded trading.\n\nChallenge Fees depend on the account size and plan:\n\n- **Starter Plan:** $89/month for a $50K account, scaling up to $225/month for $150K.\n- **Expert Plan:** $149/month for a $50K account, increasing to $349/month for $150K.\n\nOnce funded, Starter accounts require a one-time activation fee of $125, while Expert accounts have no activation fee, allowing immediate access to withdrawals.\n\nProfit payouts follow a tiered structure, starting at 60% on the first withdrawal, increasing to 100% after the fifth payout. Before withdrawing, traders must maintain a buffer zone, ensuring account stability. For example, a $50,000 funded account requires at least $500 in profits above the buffer before requesting a payout.\n\nUnlike many futures prop firms that require monthly exchange data fees, FXIFY provides real-time CME data for free. All trading commissions are covered in the evaluation fee, meaning no additional per-trade costs.\n\nTraders can upgrade their profit split by 10% at checkout, increasing the Starter payout from 80% to 90% and Expert from 90% to 100%. Expert traders can also remove daily drawdown limits, providing more flexibility in risk management.\n\nWith no hidden fees, no platform costs, and a structured withdrawal model, FXIFY Futures ensures traders keep more of their profits while maintaining a disciplined trading approach.\n\n### Support and Community\n\nFXIFY Futures provides customer support via live chat, email, and Discord, allowing traders to access real-time assistance. While educational resources are limited, the firm offers platform guides and payout proof channels in its community.\n\n- **Live Chat & Email Support:** Available during trading hours.\n- **Discord Community:** Traders can engage with peers, discuss strategies, and verify payouts.\n- **Help Center:** Provides detailed guides on rules, funding, and withdrawal policies.\n\nFXIFY Futures has a growing trader base, but its Trustpilot rating is still developing. While traders report smooth withdrawals and platform stability, some note delays in customer service response times.\n\n### Final Verdict on FXIFY Futures\n\nFXIFY Futures is the best futures prop firm with high profit splits, no time limits, and no hidden fees. The one-step evaluation offers scalable payouts up to 100%, and while the FFX Platform lacks third-party integrations, it provides TradingView charts and real-time CME data.\n\n---\n\n## Firms 6–10\n\n**6. FundedNext Futures** — Fast and Reliable Payouts. FundedNext Futures offers 100% profit splits, a one-step challenge with no time limit, and a $1,000 payout guarantee if they miss their 24-hour withdrawal promise. [Read our full review →](/reviews/fundednext-futures)\n\n**7. FXIFY** — Flexibility and Customisation. FXIFY gives traders multiple challenge types with customisable add-ons, including the ability to remove news trading restrictions or increase profit splits. [Read our full review →](/reviews/fxify)\n\n**8. Tradeify** — Instant Futures Funded Accounts. Tradeify offers instant funding for futures traders, letting you skip the evaluation entirely and start trading CME markets with a funded account from day one. [Read our full review →](/reviews/tradeify)\n\n**9. Funded Prime** — Meme Challenges. Funded Prime stands out with its unique Meme Coin Challenge, offering 10:1 leverage on tokens like PEPE and WIF alongside standard one and two step evaluations. [Read our full review →](/reviews/funded-prime)\n\n**10. Topstep** — Traditional Futures Prop Firm. Topstep is one of the most established names in futures prop trading, with a straightforward evaluation process and a large community of funded traders. [Read our full review →](/reviews/topstep)\n\n---\n\n## Frequently Asked Questions\n\n### Which is the best prop firm?\n\nTo determine the best prop firms, we tested the most popular challenges to see which actually followed through on their claims, overall we found DNA Funded, BrightFunded, FundedNext, and Blueberry Funded to be the most reliable and consistent.\n\n### Which prop firms allow crypto trading?\n\nThere's a huge number of prop firms that offer crypto CFD trading now, but many only offer one or two cryptocurrencies, usually the major markets like Bitcoin and Ethereum, with wider spreads. Crypto prop firms that offer a bigger selection of digital assets including altcoins, but also scored highly during 2026 testing, include BrightFunded, DNA Funded, and FundedNext.\n\n### What is the best futures prop firm?\n\nA few of the top prop firms recently opened futures trading branches, like FundedNext Futures and FXIFY Futures. Both are broker backed and offer profit splits up to 100%, which is much higher than the better known futures prop firms like Earn2Trade and The Trading Pit.\n\n### What's the best forex prop firms?\n\nTop forex prop firms serve different types of traders so the best completely depends on your trading strategy. If you want a day trading challenge, Eightcap Challenges now offers 1, 2, 4, and 8 hour programs. If you want a funded account where you can scale up into the millions, try FundedNext or BrightFunded. If your priority is ultra low spreads and fees, DNA Funded or Blueberry Funded might suit.\n\n### What prop firms offer instant funding?\n\nMore and more prop firms are offering instant funding accounts, where you skip the challenge entirely. They are usually more expensive than one or two step evaluations and come with much stricter risk management requirements, but suit more experienced traders who have solid track records passing challenges. If you want instant funding but with a reputable brand, have a look at broker backed prop firms like Blueberry Funded, DNA Funded, and FXIFY.\n\n### What is the best prop firm for US traders?\n\nUS traders are more limited than traders in most other countries, as many prop firms restrict access due to the regulatory environment. For US traders who want to trade CFDs, prop firms are often the only practical option. During testing, BrightFunded and Blueberry Funded were two of the more reliable firms still accessible to our US-based team. Both offer stable platforms, clear rules, and consistent payouts. Availability can change quickly, so it's important to check eligibility before buying a challenge.\n\n### Is prop trading legal in India?\n\nYes prop trading is actually legal in India, because you are using simulated accounts provided by overseas prop firms rather than trading Indian regulated markets directly. You can sign up to international prop firms like FundedNext or FXIFY which will give you access to CFDs or futures without breaching local regulations. As with any prop firm, you should still check local tax obligations and withdrawal methods.","src/content/blog/prop-firms.md","5ded2e81f4f0aced",{"html":7195,"metadata":7196},"\u003Cp>Best Prop Firms tests and shortlists proprietary trading firms, using our own money to buy challenges and instant accounts, then trade them ourselves. This lets us test what actually matters to prop traders like sign up speed, platform stability, slippage, spreads, rule enforcement, and how prop firms handle payouts and disputes.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"how-did-we-test-prop-firms\">How Did We Test Prop Firms?\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>Most rankings rely on marketing claims, but ours focus on real performance data. We buy challenges with our own money, allowing us to test the infrastructure behind the promises. From investigating hidden fees and rules, to monitoring platform stability during volatility, we track the metrics that actually impact your profitability. Our rankings reflect the reality of prop trading in 2026 by verifying who pays out efficiently, who offers stable servers, and who is simply good at advertising.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"what-are-the-top-10-prop-firms-in-the-world\">What Are the Top 10 Prop Firms in the World?\u003C/h2>\n\u003Col>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>DNA Funded\u003C/strong> — Highest Scoring Prop Firm\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>BrightFunded\u003C/strong> — Funded Account Scaling and Rewards\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Blueberry Funded\u003C/strong> — Most Stable Trading Platforms\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>FundedNext\u003C/strong> — Consistent Trading Rules\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>FXIFY Futures\u003C/strong> — CME Futures Trading\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>FundedNext Futures\u003C/strong> — Fast and Reliable Payouts\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>FXIFY\u003C/strong> — Flexibility and Customisation\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Tradeify\u003C/strong> — Instant Futures Funded Accounts\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Funded Prime\u003C/strong> — Meme Challenges\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Topstep\u003C/strong> — Traditional Futures Prop Firm\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ol>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"the-top-5-best-prop-firms-we-tested-in-2026\">The Top 5 Best Prop Firms We Tested in 2026\u003C/h2>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"1-dna-funded--highest-scoring-prop-firm\">1. DNA Funded — Highest Scoring Prop Firm\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>DNA Funded is a broker-backed prop firm offering low-cost crypto trading, high payout flexibility, and access to over 120 crypto pairs during evaluation. You can trade major coins like BTC and ETH in both the Single Helix and Double Helix challenges, with spreads starting from 0 pips and fees as low as $49.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>You can also deposit and withdraw using crypto, and select optional add-ons to reduce payout cycles or boost your profit share to 90%.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Use promo code PROPFIRMS25 to get 25% off your challenge fee, making it even cheaper to trade digital assets.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/dna-funded-logo.png\" alt=\"DNA Funded logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">DNA Funded\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">Highest Scoring Prop Firm\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">90%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Max DD\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">10%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Trustpilot\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">4.9 \u003Cspan class=\"text-amber-500\">★\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Ca href=\"/reviews/dna-funded\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-lg bg-teal-500 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-white hover:bg-teal-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n        Full Review →\n      \u003C/a>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose -mt-3 mb-6 rounded-xl border border-emerald-200 bg-emerald-50/80 px-5 py-3 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-3\">\n  \u003Ca href=\"https://partners.dnafunded.com/click?campaign_id=1&#x26;ref_id=30\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-emerald-500 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-emerald-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n    Visit DNA Funded\n  \u003C/a>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2.5\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4 text-emerald-600 flex-shrink-0\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M7 7h.01M7 3h5c.512 0 1.024.195 1.414.586l7 7a2 2 0 010 2.828l-7 7a2 2 0 01-2.828 0l-7-7A1.994 1.994 0 013 12V7a4 4 0 014-4z\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm text-emerald-700 font-semibold\">25% Off — Code:\u003C/span>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"font-mono font-bold text-xs bg-white border border-dashed border-emerald-300 px-3 py-1.5 rounded text-emerald-700 tracking-wide select-all\">PROPFIRMS25\u003C/span>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Pros &#x26; Cons\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Pros\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Competitive pricing for crypto trading\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Crypto payments accepted for fees and payouts\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Low challenge fees starting at $49\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Limited customer support\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>No crypto in Pro Challenge\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>No EAs or automated trading\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"prop-firm-details\">Prop Firm Details\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Crypto trading is available in the Single Helix and Double Helix challenges. You can’t trade crypto in the Rapid Challenge, which is focused on faster evaluation and traditional assets.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>DNA Funded offers access to 120+ crypto pairs with a 2:1 leverage cap, which applies to both evaluation and funded accounts. This provides controlled exposure given crypto’s volatility and aligns with their broker-backed compliance model.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"evaluation-process\">Evaluation Process\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>DNA Funded offers three types of challenges:\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>Single Helix (1-step):\u003C/strong> A simple evaluation requiring a 10% profit target with no time limit. This option is ideal for traders focusing on consistency rather than speed.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>Double Helix (2-step):\u003C/strong> A more structured process with a 10% profit target in Phase 1 and 5% in Phase 2. Like the Single Helix, this challenge has no time restrictions.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>Rapid Challenge (1-step):\u003C/strong> Designed for experienced traders, the Rapid Challenge requires hitting a 5% profit target within 10 calendar days. However, crypto trading is not allowed in this challenge.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>DNA Funded also offers optional add-ons to customize your experience. You can upgrade to a 90% profit split or reduce the payout period to 7 days, making it easier to access your earnings quickly.\u003C/p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003Ctable>\u003Cthead>\u003Ctr>\u003Cth>Attribute\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Single Helix\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Double Helix\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Rapid Challenge\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Instant Funding\u003C/th>\u003C/tr>\u003C/thead>\u003Ctbody>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Evaluation Process\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1 Step\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>2 Step\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1 Step\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>None (Instant Access)\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>One-Off Fee\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$59 - $1,209\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$49 – $1,079\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$99 – $549\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$199 – $979\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Account Sizes\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$5,000 - $200,000\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$5,000 – $200,000\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$10,000 – $100,000\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$5,000 – $50,000\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Fee for Add-Ons\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>20%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>20%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>30%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>NA\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Profit Share\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>80%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>80%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>80%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>80%\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Profit Target\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>10%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>10%, then 5%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>5%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>NA\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Max Daily Drawdown\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>5%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>6%, then 5%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>4%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>4% (Trailing)\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Max Total Drawdown\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>10%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>10%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>5%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>4% (Trailing)\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Max Active Trading Days\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Unlimited\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Unlimited\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>10 Calendar Days\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>NA\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Crypto Trading Allowed\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Yes\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Yes\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>No\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>Yes\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003C/tbody>\u003C/table>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"payments-and-payouts\">Payments and Payouts\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Profit payouts follow a standard 14-day cycle, with the option to reduce this to weekly payouts using the add-on. The profit split starts at 80% for successful traders, which can also be increased to 90% for a fee.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Recently, DNA Funded has introduced a 40% daily profit cap. This rule limits the maximum amount you can contribute toward your payout target in a single day to 40%. Any profits above that threshold won’t count until the next trading day. This policy supports consistent trading behaviour and aligns with their risk management framework.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>You can pay for challenges and receive withdrawals in crypto, with a 1% transaction fee for digital currency transfers.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"trading-platforms\">Trading Platforms\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>DNA Funded provides access to one trading platform, TradeLocker integrated with TradingView. Currently, there are no EAs available, creating a barrier for automated trading.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>The prop trading platform supports crypto trading, and is known for its advanced charting and ease of use. Its seamless integration with TradingView gives you access to custom indicators, on-chart trading, and risk management tools, making it ideal for manual crypto traders.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"support-and-trust\">Support and Trust\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>As a new firm, DNA Funded currently offers email support but is expected to expand its customer service options. It is backed by DNA Markets, a regulated forex broker with a strong track record for low spreads and reliable execution.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>While DNA Funded is still building its community, its active Discord server provides a space for prop traders to connect and share strategies.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"final-verdict\">Final Verdict\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>DNA Funded is the best crypto prop firm for manual traders who want a balance of tight spreads, low fees, and solid platform tools. With payouts available in crypto, 2:1 leverage on over 120 pairs, and broker-grade execution via DNA Markets, DNA Funded stands out for serious crypto traders. Just note that crypto is not tradable in the Pro Challenge, and the 40% daily cap rule encourages consistent strategy execution.\u003C/p>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"2-brightfunded--funded-account-scaling-and-rewards\">2. BrightFunded — Funded Account Scaling and Rewards\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>We’ve ranked BrightFunded as the best crypto prop firm thanks to a 95/100 overall score, dozens of cryptocurrency pairs with 5:1 leverage, and a load of addons to tailor your funded account. You get more than just the major cryptos like Bitcoin and Ethereum and can trade altcoins and meme coins as well. One of the major perks is that every time you trade, regardless of whether it’s successful or not, you earn tokens through their loyalty program that you can redeem for free challenges, better trading conditions, and various other benefits.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>You can use the promo code PROPFIRMS20 for 20% off your evaluation fee.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/brightfunded-logo.png\" alt=\"BrightFunded logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">BrightFunded\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">Funded Account Scaling and Rewards\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">100%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Max DD\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">10%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Trustpilot\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">4.4 \u003Cspan class=\"text-amber-500\">★\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Ca href=\"/reviews/brightfunded\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-lg bg-teal-500 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-white hover:bg-teal-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n        Full Review →\n      \u003C/a>\n    \u0