 border-emerald-300 px-3 py-1.5 rounded text-emerald-700 tracking-wide select-all\">PROPFIRMS20\u003C/span>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Pros &#x26; Cons\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Pros\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>52 cryptocurrency markets\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Commission free crypto trading\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Scaling up to $2 million\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Strict drawdown rules\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Limited payment options\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Minimal educational resources\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"prop-firm-details-2\">Prop Firm Details\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Blueberry Funded scored 93/100 during testing, and ranked in 4th place on our list of the best crypto prop firms. You can trade 52 crypto pairs, one of the best selections available, including BTC/USD, ETH/USD, SOL/USD, and XRP/USD. Leverage is capped at 1:2 for all challenge types. Crypto is commission-free, and spreads are competitive — EUR/USD averages 0.2 pips and BTC/USD remains tightly priced.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>You can use Expert Advisors (EAs) on MT4 and MT5, which is ideal for crypto algo traders. TradeLocker is also available for browser-based access, with stocks and crypto supported natively.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Their scaling model increases capital by 25% every 3 months, with a maximum simulated allocation of $2 million.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"evaluation-process-2\">Evaluation Process\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Blueberry Funded offers four challenge types suited to different strategies:\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>One Step Challenge:\u003C/strong> 10% profit target, 6% drawdown, no time limit.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>Two Step Challenge:\u003C/strong> 10% and 5% targets across two phases, with 10% drawdown and 1:50 leverage.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>Rapid Challenge:\u003C/strong> 5% target within 7 days, 3% daily and 4% total trailing drawdown.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>Stock Challenge:\u003C/strong> 10% and 6% targets with stricter drawdown and trading hour limits (crypto not included here).\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>All challenges provide 80% profit splits initially, upgradeable to 90%.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"payments-and-payouts-2\">Payments and Payouts\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>You can pay for challenges via credit card or cryptocurrency, with fees ranging from $32.50 to $1,100 depending on account size and model.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Profit payouts are processed every 14 days via RiseWorks, with a minimum withdrawal of $100. Payouts are available in USDC or USDT, and crypto accounts are treated the same as forex in terms of rules and withdrawal eligibility.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"trading-platforms-2\">Trading Platforms\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Blueberry Funded supports four platforms:\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>MetaTrader 4 (MT4):\u003C/strong> EA support, advanced charting, great for scalping bots.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>MetaTrader 5 (MT5):\u003C/strong> Access to stocks + crypto, DOM, more indicators.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>DXTrade:\u003C/strong> Basic, browser-based, fewer tools.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>TradeLocker:\u003C/strong> Clean UI, mobile support, stocks and crypto enabled.\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Cp>For crypto traders, MT5 and TradeLocker offer the best blend of automation, usability, and market access.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"support-and-trust-2\">Support and Trust\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Support is available 24/5 via live chat and email, with a helpful Discord community of over 27,000 members. Blueberry Funded is backed by Blueberry Markets, an ASIC-regulated broker, and became a founding member of The Prop Association in 2025.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>The firm currently holds a TrustPilot rating of 4.1/5, and offers consistent payouts and transparent rules, though some traders cite strict news trading restrictions as a downside.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"final-verdict-2\">Final Verdict\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Blueberry Funded is one of the top crypto prop firms for EA users, offering commission-free access to 50+ pairs and 24/7 trading. With four challenge types, low fees, platform variety, and strong scaling potential, it’s a well-rounded choice for both manual and automated crypto traders.\u003C/p>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"4-fundednext--consistent-trading-rules\">4. FundedNext — Consistent Trading Rules\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>FundedNext is a great option if you want zero-commission crypto trading, profit splits up to 95%, and access to multiple trading platforms like MT4, MT5, and cTrader. Payouts are processed every two weeks, keeping withdrawals consistent.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Use promo code PROPFIRMS to get 120% of your challenge fee refunded — that’s your entire fee back plus an extra 20% as a bonus.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/fundednext.png\" alt=\"FundedNext logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">FundedNext\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">Consistent Trading Rules\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">95%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Max DD\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">10%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Trustpilot\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">4.5 \u003Cspan class=\"text-amber-500\">★\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Ca href=\"/reviews/fundednext\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-lg bg-teal-500 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-white hover:bg-teal-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n        Full Review →\n      \u003C/a>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose -mt-3 mb-6 rounded-xl border border-emerald-200 bg-emerald-50/80 px-5 py-3 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-3\">\n  \u003Ca href=\"https://fundednext.com/?fpr=noam82\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-emerald-500 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-emerald-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n    Visit FundedNext\n  \u003C/a>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2.5\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4 text-emerald-600 flex-shrink-0\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M7 7h.01M7 3h5c.512 0 1.024.195 1.414.586l7 7a2 2 0 010 2.828l-7 7a2 2 0 01-2.828 0l-7-7A1.994 1.994 0 013 12V7a4 4 0 014-4z\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm text-emerald-700 font-semibold\">120% Refund — Code:\u003C/span>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"font-mono font-bold text-xs bg-white border border-dashed border-emerald-300 px-3 py-1.5 rounded text-emerald-700 tracking-wide select-all\">PROPFIRMS\u003C/span>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Pros &#x26; Cons\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Pros\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Commission-free crypto trading\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Allows Expert Advisors (EAs)\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Up to 95% profit split\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Strict daily loss limits\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Only 10 crypto markets\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>cTrader/Match-Trader cost $25\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"prop-firm-details-3\">Prop Firm Details\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>FundedNext provides access to 10 crypto markets including BTC/USD, ETH/USD, and XRP/USD. All crypto trades are commission-free with a fixed 2:1 leverage cap.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Traders can use EAs on MT4 and MT5, but automation is not supported on cTrader. This makes FundedNext a strong choice for crypto scalpers and algo traders using MetaTrader.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"evaluation-process-3\">Evaluation Process\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>FundedNext offers three crypto-compatible challenges:\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>Stellar One Step:\u003C/strong> 10% profit target, 3% daily / 6% overall loss. 15% profit share during the challenge, 95% when funded.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>Stellar Two Step:\u003C/strong> Two-phase model with 8% and 5% targets. Includes 15% profit share during the challenge and 95% when funded.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>Stellar Lite:\u003C/strong> Two-step option with lower entry fees and tighter rules. No profit share during the challenge, but 95% once funded.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>All models are time-unlimited and allow for challenge add-ons like no minimum trading days or extended loss limits.\u003C/p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003Ctable>\u003Cthead>\u003Ctr>\u003Cth>Feature\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Stellar (1-Step)\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Stellar (2-Step)\u003C/th>\u003Cth>Stellar Lite\u003C/th>\u003C/tr>\u003C/thead>\u003Ctbody>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Challenge Phases\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>1 Phase\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>2 Phases\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>2 Phases\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Account Sizes\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>6K - 200K\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>6K - 200K\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>5K - 100K\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Audition Fees\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$65 - $1,099\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$59 - $999\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$32 - $399\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Leverage\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>30:1\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>100:1\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>100:1\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Commission\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$5\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$5\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>$7\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Profit Target\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>10%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>8%, 5%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>8%, 4%\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Maximum Daily Loss\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>3%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>5%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>4%\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Maximum Overall Loss\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>6%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>10%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>8%\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Time Limit\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>No Time Limit\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>No Time Limit\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>No Time Limit\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Challenge Phase Profit Share\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>15%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>15%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>N/A\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Funded Profit Split\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>95%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>95%\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>95%\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003Ctr>\u003Ctd>Minimum Trading Days\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>2\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>5\u003C/td>\u003Ctd>5\u003C/td>\u003C/tr>\u003C/tbody>\u003C/table>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"payments-and-payouts-3\">Payments and Payouts\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Withdrawals are available every 14 days for most models, and every 21 days for Stellar Lite. You can withdraw via crypto, Deel, or bank transfer.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Minimum Payout:\u003C/strong> $20\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Crypto Payouts:\u003C/strong> Only option if under $50\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Evaluation Fee:\u003C/strong> Fully refunded after your first funded withdrawal, with an added 20% bonus using the PROPFIRMS code\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"trading-platforms-3\">Trading Platforms\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>You can trade crypto on FundedNext using:\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>MT4 &#x26; MT5:\u003C/strong> EA support, free access\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>cTrader:\u003C/strong> Manual trading only, $25 platform fee, not available for accounts above $100K\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Match-Trader:\u003C/strong> Web-based with mobile access, $25 fee, also unavailable above $100K\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Cp>TradingView is available via MT5 for advanced charting.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"support-and-trust-3\">Support and Trust\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>With a Trustpilot rating of 4.6/5 stars and an active community across Telegram and Discord, FundedNext maintains a strong reputation.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>The prop firm’s strong educational resources, including webinars and a detailed dashboard, ensure traders have the support needed to succeed.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"final-verdict-3\">Final Verdict\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>FundedNext is a top choice for crypto traders seeking high profit splits, commission-free trading, and strong platform variety. With three challenge types, bi-weekly payouts, and a large active community, it strikes a great balance for both manual and algorithmic crypto trading.\u003C/p>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"5-fxify-futures--cme-futures-trading\">5. FXIFY Futures — CME Futures Trading\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>FXIFY Futures is the best futures prop firm we reviewed with an overall score of 88/100. You go through a one step evaluation process to receive a funded account with up to 100% profit split. You also get access to real-time CME data with TradingView charts.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>You can also save 15% on all futures challenge fees by using the promo code PROPFIRMS15 at checkout.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/fxify-futures.png\" alt=\"FXIFY Futures logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">FXIFY Futures\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">CME Futures Trading\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">100%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Max DD\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">5%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Trustpilot\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">3.9 \u003Cspan class=\"text-amber-500\">★\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Ca href=\"/reviews/fxify-futures\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-lg bg-teal-500 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-white hover:bg-teal-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n        Full Review →\n      \u003C/a>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose -mt-3 mb-6 rounded-xl border border-emerald-200 bg-emerald-50/80 px-5 py-3 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-3\">\n  \u003Ca href=\"https://app.fxifyfutures.com?ref=VNPb7mgMLt63\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-emerald-500 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-emerald-600 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n    Visit FXIFY Futures\n  \u003C/a>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2.5\">\n    \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4 text-emerald-600 flex-shrink-0\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M7 7h.01M7 3h5c.512 0 1.024.195 1.414.586l7 7a2 2 0 010 2.828l-7 7a2 2 0 01-2.828 0l-7-7A1.994 1.994 0 013 12V7a4 4 0 014-4z\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm text-emerald-700 font-semibold\">15% Off — Code:\u003C/span>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"font-mono font-bold text-xs bg-white border border-dashed border-emerald-300 px-3 py-1.5 rounded text-emerald-700 tracking-wide select-all\">PROPFIRMS15\u003C/span>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Pros &#x26; Cons\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-emerald-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Pros\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Profit splits up to 100%\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>No time limits on evaluation\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>TradingView charts\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Payouts follow a tiered system\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>No NinjaTrader or Rithmic integration\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Buffer zone required before withdrawals\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"prop-firm-details-4\">Prop Firm Details\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>FXIFY Futures is the top-rated futures prop firm if you are looking for a funded account with high profit splits and no time limits. With a one-step evaluation and scalable profit-sharing up to 100%, you get an accessible pathway to a professional style trading environment.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>You can choose from two challenge types being Starter and Expert. In terms of trading platforms, the FFX Platform doesn’t have any third-party integrations but does give you TradingView charts and real-time CME data.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>FXIFY Futures straight up pricing structure means you don’t need to worry about hidden fees, with your monthly challenge payments covering all trading costs. Profit payouts are tiered, starting at 80% and going all the way up to 100%.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>Key Features\u003C/strong>\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Evaluation Process:\u003C/strong> One-step challenge with no time limits, allowing you to hit profit targets at your own pace.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Platform Options:\u003C/strong> The FFX Platform with TradingView charts and real-time CME data.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Futures Market Access:\u003C/strong> Includes forex, equities, commodities, and bonds.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Profit Split:\u003C/strong> Tiered payout system, starting at 80% and scaling to 100% based on withdrawal milestones.\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"trading-costs-and-fees\">Trading Costs and Fees\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>FXIFY Futures’ pricing structure is clear and straightforward, with monthly fees for the evaluation phase and no recurring costs after funding. Unlike other futures prop firms, FXIFY does not charge platform fees, data fees, or per-trade commissions, making it a cost-effective choice for funded trading.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Challenge Fees depend on the account size and plan:\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Starter Plan:\u003C/strong> $89/month for a $50K account, scaling up to $225/month for $150K.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Expert Plan:\u003C/strong> $149/month for a $50K account, increasing to $349/month for $150K.\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Cp>Once funded, Starter accounts require a one-time activation fee of $125, while Expert accounts have no activation fee, allowing immediate access to withdrawals.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Profit payouts follow a tiered structure, starting at 60% on the first withdrawal, increasing to 100% after the fifth payout. Before withdrawing, traders must maintain a buffer zone, ensuring account stability. For example, a $50,000 funded account requires at least $500 in profits above the buffer before requesting a payout.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Unlike many futures prop firms that require monthly exchange data fees, FXIFY provides real-time CME data for free. All trading commissions are covered in the evaluation fee, meaning no additional per-trade costs.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Traders can upgrade their profit split by 10% at checkout, increasing the Starter payout from 80% to 90% and Expert from 90% to 100%. Expert traders can also remove daily drawdown limits, providing more flexibility in risk management.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>With no hidden fees, no platform costs, and a structured withdrawal model, FXIFY Futures ensures traders keep more of their profits while maintaining a disciplined trading approach.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"support-and-community\">Support and Community\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>FXIFY Futures provides customer support via live chat, email, and Discord, allowing traders to access real-time assistance. While educational resources are limited, the firm offers platform guides and payout proof channels in its community.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Live Chat &#x26; Email Support:\u003C/strong> Available during trading hours.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Discord Community:\u003C/strong> Traders can engage with peers, discuss strategies, and verify payouts.\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Help Center:\u003C/strong> Provides detailed guides on rules, funding, and withdrawal policies.\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Cp>FXIFY Futures has a growing trader base, but its Trustpilot rating is still developing. While traders report smooth withdrawals and platform stability, some note delays in customer service response times.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"final-verdict-on-fxify-futures\">Final Verdict on FXIFY Futures\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>FXIFY Futures is the best futures prop firm with high profit splits, no time limits, and no hidden fees. The one-step evaluation offers scalable payouts up to 100%, and while the FFX Platform lacks third-party integrations, it provides TradingView charts and real-time CME data.\u003C/p>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"firms-610\">Firms 6–10\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>6. FundedNext Futures\u003C/strong> — Fast and Reliable Payouts. FundedNext Futures offers 100% profit splits, a one-step challenge with no time limit, and a $1,000 payout guarantee if they miss their 24-hour withdrawal promise. \u003Ca href=\"/reviews/fundednext-futures\">Read our full review →\u003C/a>\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>7. FXIFY\u003C/strong> — Flexibility and Customisation. FXIFY gives traders multiple challenge types with customisable add-ons, including the ability to remove news trading restrictions or increase profit splits. \u003Ca href=\"/reviews/fxify\">Read our full review →\u003C/a>\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>8. Tradeify\u003C/strong> — Instant Futures Funded Accounts. Tradeify offers instant funding for futures traders, letting you skip the evaluation entirely and start trading CME markets with a funded account from day one. \u003Ca href=\"/reviews/tradeify\">Read our full review →\u003C/a>\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>9. Funded Prime\u003C/strong> — Meme Challenges. Funded Prime stands out with its unique Meme Coin Challenge, offering 10:1 leverage on tokens like PEPE and WIF alongside standard one and two step evaluations. \u003Ca href=\"/reviews/funded-prime\">Read our full review →\u003C/a>\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>10. Topstep\u003C/strong> — Traditional Futures Prop Firm. Topstep is one of the most established names in futures prop trading, with a straightforward evaluation process and a large community of funded traders. \u003Ca href=\"/reviews/topstep\">Read our full review →\u003C/a>\u003C/p>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"frequently-asked-questions\">Frequently Asked Questions\u003C/h2>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"which-is-the-best-prop-firm\">Which is the best prop firm?\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>To determine the best prop firms, we tested the most popular challenges to see which actually followed through on their claims, overall we found DNA Funded, BrightFunded, FundedNext, and Blueberry Funded to be the most reliable and consistent.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"which-prop-firms-allow-crypto-trading\">Which prop firms allow crypto trading?\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>There’s a huge number of prop firms that offer crypto CFD trading now, but many only offer one or two cryptocurrencies, usually the major markets like Bitcoin and Ethereum, with wider spreads. Crypto prop firms that offer a bigger selection of digital assets including altcoins, but also scored highly during 2026 testing, include BrightFunded, DNA Funded, and FundedNext.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"what-is-the-best-futures-prop-firm\">What is the best futures prop firm?\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>A few of the top prop firms recently opened futures trading branches, like FundedNext Futures and FXIFY Futures. Both are broker backed and offer profit splits up to 100%, which is much higher than the better known futures prop firms like Earn2Trade and The Trading Pit.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"whats-the-best-forex-prop-firms\">What’s the best forex prop firms?\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Top forex prop firms serve different types of traders so the best completely depends on your trading strategy. If you want a day trading challenge, Eightcap Challenges now offers 1, 2, 4, and 8 hour programs. If you want a funded account where you can scale up into the millions, try FundedNext or BrightFunded. If your priority is ultra low spreads and fees, DNA Funded or Blueberry Funded might suit.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"what-prop-firms-offer-instant-funding\">What prop firms offer instant funding?\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>More and more prop firms are offering instant funding accounts, where you skip the challenge entirely. They are usually more expensive than one or two step evaluations and come with much stricter risk management requirements, but suit more experienced traders who have solid track records passing challenges. If you want instant funding but with a reputable brand, have a look at broker backed prop firms like Blueberry Funded, DNA Funded, and FXIFY.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"what-is-the-best-prop-firm-for-us-traders\">What is the best prop firm for US traders?\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>US traders are more limited than traders in most other countries, as many prop firms restrict access due to the regulatory environment. For US traders who want to trade CFDs, prop firms are often the only practical option. During testing, BrightFunded and Blueberry Funded were two of the more reliable firms still accessible to our US-based team. Both offer stable platforms, clear rules, and consistent payouts. Availability can change quickly, so it’s important to check eligibility before buying a challenge.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"is-prop-trading-legal-in-india\">Is prop trading legal in India?\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Yes prop trading is actually legal in India, because you are using simulated accounts provided by overseas prop firms rather than trading Indian regulated markets directly. You can sign up to international prop firms like FundedNext or FXIFY which will give you access to CFDs or futures without breaching local regulations. As with any prop firm, you should still check local tax obligations and withdrawal methods.\u003C/p>",{"headings":7197,"localImagePaths":7274,"remoteImagePaths":7275,"frontmatter":7276,"imagePaths":7289},[7198,7201,7204,7207,7210,7211,7212,7213,7214,7215,7216,7219,7220,7221,7222,7223,7224,7225,7228,7229,7230,7231,7232,7233,7234,7237,7238,7239,7240,7241,7242,7243,7246,7247,7248,7249,7250,7253,7256,7259,7260,7262,7265,7268,7271],{"depth":879,"slug":7199,"text":7200},"how-did-we-test-prop-firms","How Did We Test Prop Firms?",{"depth":879,"slug":7202,"text":7203},"what-are-the-top-10-prop-firms-in-the-world","What Are the Top 10 Prop Firms in the World?",{"depth":879,"slug":7205,"text":7206},"the-top-5-best-prop-firms-we-tested-in-2026","The Top 5 Best Prop Firms We Tested in 2026",{"depth":879,"slug":7208,"text":7209},"1-dna-funded--highest-scoring-prop-firm","1. DNA Funded — Highest Scoring Prop Firm",{"depth":158,"slug":5218,"text":5219},{"depth":158,"slug":5221,"text":5222},{"depth":158,"slug":5224,"text":5225},{"depth":158,"slug":4844,"text":4845},{"depth":158,"slug":5228,"text":5229},{"depth":158,"slug":5051,"text":5052},{"depth":879,"slug":7217,"text":7218},"2-brightfunded--funded-account-scaling-and-rewards","2. BrightFunded — Funded Account Scaling and Rewards",{"depth":158,"slug":5235,"text":5219},{"depth":158,"slug":5237,"text":5222},{"depth":158,"slug":5239,"text":5225},{"depth":158,"slug":4864,"text":4845},{"depth":158,"slug":5242,"text":5229},{"depth":158,"slug":5068,"text":5052},{"depth":879,"slug":7226,"text":7227},"3-blueberry-funded--most-stable-trading-platforms","3. Blueberry Funded — Most Stable Trading Platforms",{"depth":158,"slug":5248,"text":5219},{"depth":158,"slug":5250,"text":5222},{"depth":158,"slug":5252,"text":5225},{"depth":158,"slug":4884,"text":4845},{"depth":158,"slug":5255,"text":5229},{"depth":158,"slug":5083,"text":5052},{"depth":879,"slug":7235,"text":7236},"4-fundednext--consistent-trading-rules","4. FundedNext — Consistent Trading Rules",{"depth":158,"slug":5261,"text":5219},{"depth":158,"slug":5263,"text":5222},{"depth":158,"slug":5265,"text":5225},{"depth":158,"slug":4916,"text":4845},{"depth":158,"slug":5268,"text":5229},{"depth":158,"slug":5098,"text":5052},{"depth":879,"slug":7244,"text":7245},"5-fxify-futures--cme-futures-trading","5. FXIFY Futures — CME Futures Trading",{"depth":158,"slug":5274,"text":5219},{"depth":158,"slug":5827,"text":5828},{"depth":158,"slug":5830,"text":5831},{"depth":158,"slug":5833,"text":4084},{"depth":879,"slug":7251,"text":7252},"firms-610","Firms 6–10",{"depth":879,"slug":7254,"text":7255},"frequently-asked-questions","Frequently Asked Questions",{"depth":158,"slug":7257,"text":7258},"which-is-the-best-prop-firm","Which is the best prop firm?",{"depth":158,"slug":5298,"text":5299},{"depth":158,"slug":7261,"text":4406},"what-is-the-best-futures-prop-firm",{"depth":158,"slug":7263,"text":7264},"whats-the-best-forex-prop-firms","What’s the best forex prop firms?",{"depth":158,"slug":7266,"text":7267},"what-prop-firms-offer-instant-funding","What prop firms offer instant funding?",{"depth":158,"slug":7269,"text":7270},"what-is-the-best-prop-firm-for-us-traders","What is the best prop firm for US traders?",{"depth":158,"slug":7272,"text":7273},"is-prop-trading-legal-in-india","Is prop trading legal in India?",[],[],{"title":7165,"excerpt":7166,"category":5171,"tags":7277,"author":4798,"authorImage":4799,"publishedAt":240,"featured":26,"coverImage":7169,"readingTimeMinutes":405,"youtubeVideoId":4800,"featuredFirms":7278},[5173,7168,4796,5609],[7279,7280,7281,7282,7283,7284,7285,7286,7287,7288],{"slug":728,"descriptor":7172},{"slug":584,"descriptor":7174},{"slug":332,"descriptor":7176},{"slug":1392,"descriptor":7178},{"slug":1550,"descriptor":7180},{"slug":1341,"descriptor":7182},{"slug":1599,"descriptor":7184},{"slug":2747,"descriptor":7186},{"slug":1241,"descriptor":7188},{"slug":2621,"descriptor":7190},[],"prop-firms.md","crypto-trading",{"id":7291,"data":7293,"body":7308,"filePath":7309,"digest":7310,"rendered":7311,"legacyId":7375},{"title":7294,"excerpt":7295,"category":5171,"tags":7296,"author":4798,"authorImage":4799,"publishedAt":7298,"featured":110,"readingTimeMinutes":7299,"featuredFirms":7300},"What Is Crypto Prop Trading? A Complete Guide","Crypto prop trading gives skilled traders access to firm-funded capital to trade digital assets like Bitcoin, Ethereum, and altcoins. Learn how it works, what to look for, and which firms offer the best crypto trading conditions.",[207,5609,4796,7297],"cryptocurrency","2026-03-10",16,[7301,7303,7304,7306],{"slug":584,"descriptor":7302},"Best Crypto Prop Firm Overall",{"slug":728,"descriptor":5181},{"slug":1392,"descriptor":7305},"High Profit Split Crypto Prop Firm",{"slug":332,"descriptor":7307},"Widest Range of Crypto Markets","## How Does Crypto Prop Trading Work?\n\nWhen you trade with a crypto prop firm, you go through an evaluation process to prove you can hit profit targets while managing risk. Once you pass, you are awarded a funded account, typically starting from $10,000 and scaling up to $100,000, $500,000, or even millions.\n\nUnlike hedge funds or banks, prop firms do not manage client capital. They take on the risk themselves, earning from challenge fees and a share of trader profits. If you consistently perform well, your account may be scaled up for larger trades and higher earnings.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">How It Works at a Glance\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-4 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 text-center\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-2xl font-black text-teal-600 mb-1\">1\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-semibold text-slate-700\">Pay a challenge fee and enter an evaluation\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 text-center\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-2xl font-black text-teal-600 mb-1\">2\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-semibold text-slate-700\">Hit profit targets while staying within risk limits\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 text-center\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-2xl font-black text-teal-600 mb-1\">3\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-semibold text-slate-700\">Pass evaluation and receive a funded account\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 text-center\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-2xl font-black text-teal-600 mb-1\">4\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-semibold text-slate-700\">Trade crypto and keep up to 90-100% of profits\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n---\n\n## Inside the Evaluation Process\n\nGetting funded starts with a trading challenge. You pay an upfront fee, trade in a simulated environment, and aim to meet profit goals (usually between 8% and 15%) without breaking drawdown or risk limits. There are various models, but one-step or two-step evaluation processes are the most common, with instant funding accounts becoming more and more popular too.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"bg-[#0d1b2a] px-5 py-4\">\n    \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-black text-white uppercase tracking-wide\">Example: Two-Step Challenge\u003C/p>\n  \u003C/div>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"p-5\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"space-y-4\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-teal-500 flex items-center justify-center\">\n          \u003Cspan class=\"text-xs font-black text-white\">1\u003C/span>\n        \u003C/div>\n        \u003Cdiv>\n          \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Challenge Phase\u003C/p>\n          \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-600\">Hit profit targets while staying within daily and overall drawdown limits.\u003C/p>\n        \u003C/div>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-teal-500 flex items-center justify-center\">\n          \u003Cspan class=\"text-xs font-black text-white\">2\u003C/span>\n        \u003C/div>\n        \u003Cdiv>\n          \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Verification Phase\u003C/p>\n          \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-600\">Prove your performance was not a fluke by maintaining similar results under potentially stricter conditions.\u003C/p>\n        \u003C/div>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 flex items-center justify-center\">\n          \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4 text-white\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>\n        \u003C/div>\n        \u003Cdiv>\n          \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Funded Account\u003C/p>\n          \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-600\">Only traders who pass both stages receive a funded account. This system filters out reckless or lucky traders and helps firms find those with real skill.\u003C/p>\n        \u003C/div>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n---\n\n## How Prop Firms Choose Traders\n\nProp firms are selective. Their business model relies on finding consistent, low-risk performers, not gamblers. Most use a structured boot-camp-style evaluation to separate skilled traders from the rest. Challenge fees (often starting at $50 for small accounts) serve a dual purpose: generating revenue and discouraging uncommitted applicants.\n\nFirms raise capital internally or through investors and reinvest it into funded accounts. They also build advanced trading tools and algorithms tailored to crypto volatility, giving traders the edge they need to profit in fast-moving markets.\n\n---\n\n## Crypto-Only vs Multi-Asset Prop Firms\n\nChoosing between a crypto-only and a multi-asset prop firm depends on what you want from your trading experience: depth in one market or the ability to move across multiple.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"p-5 border-b sm:border-b-0 sm:border-r border-slate-200\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-3\">\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-amber-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n          \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4 text-amber-600\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z\"/>\u003C/svg>\n        \u003C/div>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-extrabold text-slate-900\">Crypto-Only Firms\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Broader range of pairs (40+ coins)\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Platforms optimized for crypto volatility\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Higher crypto leverage (up to 1:10)\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>24/7 trading support\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Limited to crypto markets only\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"p-5\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-3\">\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-blue-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n          \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4 text-blue-600\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z\"/>\u003C/svg>\n        \u003C/div>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-extrabold text-slate-900\">Multi-Asset Firms\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Forex, commodities, indices, stocks + crypto\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Longer track records in traditional finance\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>More established risk management systems\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Diverse payout options and scaling structures\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Fewer crypto pairs and lower crypto leverage\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\nCrypto-only prop firms are fully focused on digital assets. They tend to offer a broader range of cryptocurrency pairs, often supporting 40 or more coins, including lesser-known altcoins. Their platforms and tools are usually optimized for crypto's unique characteristics, like high volatility and 24/7 trading. These firms may offer higher leverage on crypto positions, sometimes up to 1:10, and their support teams are typically more familiar with blockchain-specific issues.\n\nIn contrast, multi-asset prop firms offer access to a broader range of markets, including forex, commodities, indices, and stocks alongside crypto. This setup allows traders to switch between asset classes based on market conditions or personal preference. These firms often have longer track records in traditional finance, with more established risk management systems and educational resources. Their larger funding pools can also mean different scaling structures and potentially more diverse payout options.\n\n---\n\n## Prop Trading Rules to Know\n\nEvery crypto prop firm has its own trading rules to protect capital, and breaking them can get your challenge or funded account revoked.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Common Restrictions\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"space-y-3\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-red-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Csvg class=\"h-3 w-3 text-red-500\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">News trading bans\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500\">Some firms restrict trading during major events like halving cycles, regulation changes, or network forks.\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-red-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Csvg class=\"h-3 w-3 text-red-500\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Overnight holds\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500\">Due to high volatility, many firms disallow holding crypto positions overnight.\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-red-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Csvg class=\"h-3 w-3 text-red-500\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">High-risk strategy bans\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500\">Martingale and other aggressive strategies are often prohibited, especially when combined with leverage.\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-red-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Csvg class=\"h-3 w-3 text-red-500\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Time-window limits\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500\">A few firms may restrict trading to certain hours or require activity during specific sessions.\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-red-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Csvg class=\"h-3 w-3 text-red-500\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Instrument restrictions\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500\">Most support BTC and ETH, but availability of niche altcoins varies by firm.\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n---\n\n## Best Crypto Proprietary Trading Firms\n\nEach crypto prop trading firm offers its unique advantages to traders looking to dabble with or have expertise with digital assets, from bigger leverage options to firms offering a bigger selection of coins to trade. Below are the top ranked options from our list of the best cryptocurrency prop firms.\n\n### 1. BrightFunded -- Best Crypto Prop Firm Overall\n\nBrightFunded is the leading crypto prop firm, offering high leverage, over 40 crypto pairs, and scalable funded accounts. With profit splits reaching up to 100%, it provides a strong option for traders aiming to grow their accounts and maximize returns.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/brightfunded-logo.png\" alt=\"BrightFunded logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\" />\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">BrightFunded\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">Best Crypto Prop Firm Overall\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">100%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>