f -- Code:\u003C/span>\n    \u003Cspan class=\"font-mono font-bold text-xs bg-white border border-dashed border-emerald-300 px-3 py-1.5 rounded text-emerald-700 tracking-wide select-all\">PROPFIRMS20\u003C/span>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Key Crypto Features\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n    \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>52 cryptocurrency markets (class-leading range)\u003C/li>\n    \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>25% scaling every 3 months (up to $2M)\u003C/li>\n    \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>80 to 90% profit splits (same rules as you scale)\u003C/li>\n    \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>24/7 commission-free crypto trading\u003C/li>\n    \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>EA support on MT4 and MT5 platforms\u003C/li>\n  \u003C/ul>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cp>Algorithm-focused traders who look for bigger crypto trading options will like Blueberry Funded. They also offer a 7-day challenge, with fixed 1:2 leverage to balance risk control with trading power.\u003C/p>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"risk-management-in-crypto-prop-trading\">Risk Management in Crypto Prop Trading\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>While it is the exciting part, crypto prop trading is not all about chasing those big profits. Risk management is what keeps a successful prop trader in the game in the long term.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"market-volatility\">Market Volatility\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Crypto trading is known to be very volatile, where one random tweet from some tech billionaire can send prices surging or plunging within minutes, making volatility both a blessing and a curse for crypto traders. As a result, prop trading firms have developed strategies to contain the wild price swings that often come with cryptocurrencies.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>These crypto-focused firms are especially strict with position sizing. Placing a big chunk of your trading account into a single trade, regardless of how sure you are of a “pump”, is not possible. Individual positions are usually capped at around 1% to 2%, so you will not be wiped out even if the trade goes against your plan. In extreme times of market volatility, these firms may temporarily reduce available leverage or even restrict it altogether.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"leverage-and-risk-appetite\">Leverage and Risk Appetite\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Leverage in crypto proprietary trading firms could be extremely useful, but if misused, it can also be extremely dangerous. Trading firms can offer leverage starting from 1:5 to 1:10, with some offering even higher levels, allowing you to trade positions much larger than your funded account.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border-l-4 border-amber-400 bg-amber-50/60 px-5 py-4\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-amber-800 mb-1\">Leverage example\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-700 leading-relaxed\">With a $10,000 account and 1:10 leverage, you can control a $100,000 position. This magnifies potential gains by ten times, but also losses by ten times.\u003C/p>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cp>Various guardrails are being implemented to keep traders from taking full-on risks with leveraged trading. Cryptocurrency prop trading generally has drawdown limits of 5% to 10%, and risk-per-trade limits are also capped at around 1% to 2% per position to help in this.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Prop traders generally have a higher risk appetite than the average retail trader, but trading with the firm’s capital, these risk guidelines can help improve trading performance in the long term by enforcing trading discipline, which is hard to develop when trading alone.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"trading-restrictions\">Trading Restrictions\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Part of the broader risk management strategy, and depending on the trading firm, trading restrictions are in place to prevent catastrophic losses when markets go on wild swings. Many firms restrict news trading, scaling, and high-frequency trading, with some outright banning them. These are some of the most unpredictable and riskiest strategies, making these rules non-negotiable, making it crucial for you to double-check what strategies are allowed and not allowed.\u003C/p>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"is-prop-crypto-trading-right-for-you\">Is Prop Crypto Trading Right for You?\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>Is crypto prop trading for you? The answer to that question depends on your trading goals, experience level, and your ability to manage risk properly.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"who-benefits-from-crypto-prop-trading\">Who Benefits From Crypto Prop Trading?\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Prop trading in general is beneficial for experienced traders who have already developed working trading strategies, but do not have the trading capital necessary to have a significant impact on their desired profit levels.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Trader Profiles Likely to Succeed\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"space-y-3\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-5 w-5 flex-shrink-0 text-teal-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Skilled Traders Lacking Capital\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500\">Traders who have the skills but not a substantial trading account will benefit from the capital a prop firm can provide.\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-5 w-5 flex-shrink-0 text-teal-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Risk-Averse Experienced Traders\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500\">With strict risk management protocols to follow and no personal funds at risk, these traders gain a psychological edge.\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-5 w-5 flex-shrink-0 text-teal-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Disciplined Traders\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500\">If you manage risks carefully, stick to the rules, and do not let emotions get the better of you, these restrictions will not feel like hindrances.\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-5 w-5 flex-shrink-0 text-teal-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Technical Analyst Traders\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500\">Technical chart setups usually work better with cryptocurrencies compared to other instruments like forex, providing more trading opportunities.\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"signing-up-to-a-crypto-prop-firm\">Signing Up to a Crypto Prop Firm\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Before you start prop trading and purchase a challenge, it is vital to evaluate the evaluation process, or you are risking wasting time and money.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Pre-Signup Checklist\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"space-y-3\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-teal-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Cspan class=\"text-xs font-black text-teal-600\">1\u003C/span>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Evaluation Requirements\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500\">What are the profit targets? Is it a reasonable 8%, or a very ambitious 25%? What about drawdown limits? Will they close your account with a tight 5%, or do they have a lenient 10% drawdown limit?\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-teal-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Cspan class=\"text-xs font-black text-teal-600\">2\u003C/span>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Fee Structure\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500\">How much are the upfront fees compared to the potential funded account you can get? Will they have hidden subscription fees after getting the funded account?\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-teal-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Cspan class=\"text-xs font-black text-teal-600\">3\u003C/span>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Profit Splits and Payout Rules\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500\">The usual profit-sharing agreement is at 70/30, with you getting the larger share. Will you get paid weekly, monthly, or is open withdrawal allowed? Minimum amounts for withdrawal also need to be considered.\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-teal-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Cspan class=\"text-xs font-black text-teal-600\">4\u003C/span>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Trading Restrictions\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500\">Depending on the company, trading restrictions vary. Make sure these guidelines and rules align with your favourite trading strategy and style.\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-teal-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Cspan class=\"text-xs font-black text-teal-600\">5\u003C/span>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Scaling Opportunities\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500\">Do they have a system in place to upgrade your account bigger and bigger? What are the required performance metrics to level up? The top crypto prop trading firms will have a clear and transparent mechanism to reward successful traders with larger trading accounts.\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"faqs\">FAQs\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 space-y-4\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5\">\n    \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2\">How does prop trading work?\u003C/p>\n    \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed\">Prop trading lets you trade with a firm's capital instead of your own. To qualify, you must pass an evaluation challenge that tests your ability to hit profit targets and follow risk rules. If successful, you are awarded a funded account and keep a portion of the profits, often up to 90%. The firm absorbs the risk, but you must follow strict trading rules to maintain the account and qualify for scaling opportunities.\u003C/p>\n  \u003C/div>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5\">\n    \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2\">Is prop trading illegal?\u003C/p>\n    \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed\">No, prop trading is legal. Many financial firms, including independent crypto prop firms, operate within regulatory boundaries. However, not all firms are created equal. Traders should choose firms with clear terms, transparent policies, and a strong reputation (broker backed firms are considered the most trustworthy). Always review the firm's rules, compliance practices, and trader reviews to avoid scams or misleading promises.\u003C/p>\n  \u003C/div>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5\">\n    \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2\">What is an example of proprietary trading?\u003C/p>\n    \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed\">A trader passes a $50,000 challenge and gets a funded $50,000 account. They spot a trade, risk $500 (1%), and make $1,000 in profit. With an 80% profit split, they keep $800 and the firm keeps $200. The trader did not risk personal capital, and consistent performance could lead to account scaling. This model rewards disciplined risk management while giving traders access to larger capital than they would typically have on their own.\u003C/p>\n  \u003C/div>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5\">\n    \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2\">Can you make money as a prop trader?\u003C/p>\n    \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed\">Yes, prop traders can earn steady income if they are consistently profitable and follow the firm's rules. Success depends on your trading strategy, discipline, and ability to manage risk, not luck. Many traders turn prop trading into a full-time career, especially with firms that offer high profit splits, low fees, and scaling opportunities. However, it is not a shortcut to wealth. Long-term results require experience, emotional control, and commitment to continuous improvement.\u003C/p>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>",{"headings":7314,"localImagePaths":7365,"remoteImagePaths":7366,"frontmatter":7367,"imagePaths":7374},[7315,7318,7321,7324,7327,7330,7333,7336,7337,7340,7343,7346,7349,7352,7355,7358,7361,7364],{"depth":879,"slug":7316,"text":7317},"how-does-crypto-prop-trading-work","How Does Crypto Prop Trading Work?",{"depth":879,"slug":7319,"text":7320},"inside-the-evaluation-process","Inside the Evaluation Process",{"depth":879,"slug":7322,"text":7323},"how-prop-firms-choose-traders","How Prop Firms Choose Traders",{"depth":879,"slug":7325,"text":7326},"crypto-only-vs-multi-asset-prop-firms","Crypto-Only vs Multi-Asset Prop Firms",{"depth":879,"slug":7328,"text":7329},"prop-trading-rules-to-know","Prop Trading Rules to Know",{"depth":879,"slug":7331,"text":7332},"best-crypto-proprietary-trading-firms","Best Crypto Proprietary Trading Firms",{"depth":158,"slug":7334,"text":7335},"1-brightfunded--best-crypto-prop-firm-overall","1. BrightFunded — Best Crypto Prop Firm Overall",{"depth":158,"slug":5232,"text":5233},{"depth":158,"slug":7338,"text":7339},"3-fundednext--high-profit-split-crypto-prop-firm","3. FundedNext — High Profit Split Crypto Prop Firm",{"depth":158,"slug":7341,"text":7342},"4-blueberry-funded--widest-range-of-crypto-markets","4. Blueberry Funded — Widest Range of Crypto Markets",{"depth":879,"slug":7344,"text":7345},"risk-management-in-crypto-prop-trading","Risk Management in Crypto Prop Trading",{"depth":158,"slug":7347,"text":7348},"market-volatility","Market Volatility",{"depth":158,"slug":7350,"text":7351},"leverage-and-risk-appetite","Leverage and Risk Appetite",{"depth":158,"slug":7353,"text":7354},"trading-restrictions","Trading Restrictions",{"depth":879,"slug":7356,"text":7357},"is-prop-crypto-trading-right-for-you","Is Prop Crypto Trading Right for You?",{"depth":158,"slug":7359,"text":7360},"who-benefits-from-crypto-prop-trading","Who Benefits From Crypto Prop Trading?",{"depth":158,"slug":7362,"text":7363},"signing-up-to-a-crypto-prop-firm","Signing Up to a Crypto Prop Firm",{"depth":879,"slug":4935,"text":4936},[],[],{"title":7294,"excerpt":7295,"category":5171,"tags":7368,"author":4798,"authorImage":4799,"publishedAt":7298,"featured":110,"readingTimeMinutes":7299,"featuredFirms":7369},[207,5609,4796,7297],[7370,7371,7372,7373],{"slug":584,"descriptor":7302},{"slug":728,"descriptor":5181},{"slug":1392,"descriptor":7305},{"slug":332,"descriptor":7307},[],"crypto-trading.md","forex-trading",{"id":7376,"data":7378,"body":7391,"filePath":7392,"digest":7393,"rendered":7394,"legacyId":7500},{"title":7379,"excerpt":7380,"category":5171,"tags":7381,"author":4798,"authorImage":4799,"publishedAt":7298,"featured":110,"readingTimeMinutes":5176,"featuredFirms":7383},"Forex Prop Trading Explained: A Complete Guide","Forex prop trading lets you access larger trading accounts, keep a big chunk of the profits, and trade without risking personal funds. Our guide breaks down how it works, the benefits, and what to expect.",[4795,5609,4796,7382],"leverage",[7384,7386,7388,7390],{"slug":1002,"descriptor":7385},"Most Established Forex Prop Firm",{"slug":1392,"descriptor":7387},"High Profit Split Forex Prop Firm",{"slug":2507,"descriptor":7389},"Best for Scaling Forex Traders",{"slug":1459,"descriptor":5631},"## What Is Prop Forex Trading?\n\nForex prop trading is when you use a firm's capital rather than your own to execute trades in the foreign exchange market. Traders who are confident in their trading skills but lack the trading funds can look at the best forex prop firms, which offer ways to provide significantly more capital and generate potentially more profits shared between both parties.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Forex Prop Trading at a Glance\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-4 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 text-center\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-2xl font-black text-teal-600 mb-1\">1\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-semibold text-slate-700\">Pay a challenge fee and enter an evaluation\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 text-center\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-2xl font-black text-teal-600 mb-1\">2\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-semibold text-slate-700\">Prove your skills by hitting profit targets within risk limits\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 text-center\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-2xl font-black text-teal-600 mb-1\">3\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-semibold text-slate-700\">Pass evaluation and receive a funded trading account\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 text-center\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-2xl font-black text-teal-600 mb-1\">4\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-semibold text-slate-700\">Trade forex and keep up to 90-100% of profits\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n---\n\n## How Do Prop Trading Firms Work?\n\nThe basic principle of proprietary trading firms is that they allocate their own capital to skilled traders whom they have deemed capable of trading profitably and responsibly. They use internally raised capital in their trading activities, unlike traditional institutions like banks and hedge funds that primarily deal with client funds.\n\nThese firms actively look for talented traders who may lack the capital to trade big, but have all the qualities necessary to succeed in this industry. They also operate through various financial instruments, including the forex market, where there are plenty of opportunities for fast-moving trades, perfect for prop traders. Other markets in which these firms operate include the stock market, futures markets, and more.\n\nProp firms usually run challenge programs where forex traders show their trading skills and risk discipline in a controlled trading environment, starting with demo accounts. After passing the challenge, you will be awarded a funded account and share the profits generated with the trading firm. Some prop firms will allow you to start trading right away, but this usually comes with a steeper challenge fee and stricter rules on risk management.\n\n---\n\n## Profit-Sharing Model and Risk Management\n\nHaving access to the firm's capital will naturally come with some guidelines on how you are going to split the profits while handling the firm's money responsibly.\n\nIf you become one of the firm's prop traders, you and the prop firm share the profits generated on a pre-agreed percentage, with you getting the bigger share, usually starting at 70% and up to 90%, and the remaining going to the firm.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-8 rounded-xl border-l-4 border-teal-500 bg-teal-50/60 px-5 py-4\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1\">Risk management is the cornerstone of most prop trading firms.\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-700\">These firms need to put systems in place to protect the trading money they are providing their traders. As a prop trader, you will have to operate within risk management guidelines.\u003C/p>\n\u003C/div>\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Common Risk Management Rules\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"space-y-3\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-red-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Csvg class=\"h-3 w-3 text-red-500\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Maximum Drawdown Limits\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500\">The maximum level your portfolio value is allowed to drop from its highest level.\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-red-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Csvg class=\"h-3 w-3 text-red-500\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Daily Loss Limits\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500\">The limit you are allowed to lose in a single trading day.\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-red-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Csvg class=\"h-3 w-3 text-red-500\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Position Sizing Rules\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500\">Rules dictating how much trading position you can take relative to your account size.\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-red-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Csvg class=\"h-3 w-3 text-red-500\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Trading Restrictions\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500\">Some firms regulate strategies like news trading, high-frequency trading, etc. Before joining a prop firm, ensure your preferred strategy is allowed.\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n---\n\n## Types of Forex Prop Trading Firms\n\nDepending on your skill level and how quickly you want to get the capital to trade, there are many prop trading firms available that fit your needs. The two main models are challenges and instant funding, though hybrid models exist too.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"p-5 border-b sm:border-b-0 sm:border-r border-slate-200\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-3\">\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-teal-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n          \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4 text-teal-600\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z\"/>\u003C/svg>\n        \u003C/div>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-extrabold text-slate-900\">Challenge-Based\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Lower entry fees\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>More flexible strategies allowed\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>More lenient risk management\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Must pass evaluation first\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"p-5 border-b sm:border-b-0 sm:border-r border-slate-200\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-3\">\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-amber-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n          \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4 text-amber-600\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z\"/>\u003C/svg>\n        \u003C/div>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-extrabold text-slate-900\">Instant Funding\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Immediate access to capital\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>No evaluation waiting period\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Higher upfront fees\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Stricter trading rules and drawdowns\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"p-5\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-3\">\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-blue-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n          \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4 text-blue-600\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M8 7h12m0 0l-4-4m4 4l-4 4m0 6H4m0 0l4 4m-4-4l4-4\"/>\u003C/svg>\n        \u003C/div>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-extrabold text-slate-900\">Hybrid Models\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Choose challenge or instant funding\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Switch models based on performance\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Best of both worlds flexibility\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>May involve switching fees\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n### Challenge-Based Prop Firms\n\nThis is probably the most popular type of proprietary trading firm in the forex market. Before you can trade using the firm's capital, you need to prove yourself first with an evaluation or challenge round.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"bg-[#0d1b2a] px-5 py-4\">\n    \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-black text-white uppercase tracking-wide\">How a Challenge Works\u003C/p>\n  \u003C/div>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"p-5\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"space-y-4\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-teal-500 flex items-center justify-center\">\n          \u003Cspan class=\"text-xs font-black text-white\">1\u003C/span>\n        \u003C/div>\n        \u003Cdiv>\n          \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Start with a Demo Account\u003C/p>\n          \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-600\">Trade in a controlled simulated environment using the firm's trading platforms.\u003C/p>\n        \u003C/div>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-teal-500 flex items-center justify-center\">\n          \u003Cspan class=\"text-xs font-black text-white\">2\u003C/span>\n        \u003C/div>\n        \u003Cdiv>\n          \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Hit Profit Targets\u003C/p>\n          \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-600\">Reach the profit target (usually around 8-10%) while following the firm's risk management protocols within a set period.\u003C/p>\n        \u003C/div>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 flex items-center justify-center\">\n          \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4 text-white\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>\n        \u003C/div>\n        \u003Cdiv>\n          \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Receive a Funded Account\u003C/p>\n          \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-600\">Successful traders receive a funded account with real capital and begin sharing profits with the firm.\u003C/p>\n        \u003C/div>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\nWith entry fees usually lower compared to instant funding options, challenge-based models appeal to many traders because they are also more flexible, with more trading strategies allowed and more lenient risk management parameters.\n\n### Instant Funding Prop Firms\n\nFor those wanting to start trading immediately, instant funding prop firms offer immediate access to the firm's capital, but with a higher upfront fee. Paying a bigger entry fee may seem easy enough, but this comes with significantly stricter trading rules. You are expected to trade at a high level from the start with stricter risk management rules and tighter drawdown limits.\n\nThis is not for everyone, and is usually reserved only for seasoned traders who may have a deeper understanding of the financial markets. But with the right person, this is a quick way to get funded and potentially generate profits as early as possible.\n\n### Hybrid Models\n\nThe middle ground between the earlier models is the hybrid one, perfect for traders wanting to get funded quickly but not fully confident in their trading skills. Prop firms with this hybrid setup will let you choose between a challenge or instant funding at the beginning, or come with an option to switch between these models on the fly with a fee, or based on your performance.\n\nBefore jumping into a prop firm, make sure that you understand which model works best for you based on your current skill and preferences, as these can dictate your success or failure as a prop trader.\n\n---\n\n## How Prop Traders Get Paid\n\nOne of the biggest reasons why most forex traders join prop firms is to get that trading payout. If you have what it takes and get a funded account, this is a great way to potentially earn more profits that are otherwise not accessible to you without risking your own money.\n\n### Profit-Sharing\n\nHow traders get paid is a straightforward process: make a profit, and get your share. The profit split structure is where you split the profits you made as a prop trader, with the larger piece of the pie going to the trader.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Profit Split Example\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 text-center\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium mb-1\">Trading Profit\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xl font-black text-slate-900\">$1,000\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-teal-50 px-4 py-3 text-center\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-teal-600 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium mb-1\">Your Share (80%)\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xl font-black text-teal-600\">$800\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 text-center\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium mb-1\">Firm Share (20%)\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xl font-black text-slate-900\">$200\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-3 text-center\">Typical splits range from 70/30 to 90/10 in favor of the trader. Some firms offer up to 100% on early payouts.\u003C/p>\n\u003C/div>\n\nThe best forex prop firms work to keep their traders happy by offering the best profit splits, and it is not unusual for proven and profitable traders to receive favorable trading terms and better profit splits from prop firms.\n\n### Withdrawal and Payment Policies\n\nAfter doing the hard part of making profits, the next part is getting your share of the profits into your bank account. Trading firms have varying policies on how and when you can get your share of the profits.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"p-5 border-b sm:border-b-0 sm:border-r border-slate-200\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-extrabold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Payment Schedules\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"space-y-2\">\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n          \u003Cdiv class=\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-teal-500\">\u003C/div>\n          \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-700\">\u003Cstrong>Bi-Weekly Payouts\u003C/strong> - Gaining traction\u003C/p>\n        \u003C/div>\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n          \u003Cdiv class=\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-teal-500\">\u003C/div>\n          \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-700\">\u003Cstrong>Monthly Withdrawals\u003C/strong> - Most common\u003C/p>\n        \u003C/div>\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n          \u003Cdiv class=\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-slate-300\">\u003C/div>\n          \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-700\">\u003Cstrong>Quarterly Withdrawals\u003C/strong> - Less common\u003C/p>\n        \u003C/div>\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n          \u003Cdiv class=\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-teal-500\">\u003C/div>\n          \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-700\">\u003Cstrong>On-Demand\u003C/strong> - Growing in popularity\u003C/p>\n        \u003C/div>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"p-5\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-extrabold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Payment Methods\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"space-y-2\">\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n          \u003Cdiv class=\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-teal-500\">\u003C/div>\n          \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-700\">Traditional bank transfers\u003C/p>\n        \u003C/div>\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n          \u003Cdiv class=\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-teal-500\">\u003C/div>\n          \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-700\">Cryptocurrency (BTC, ETH, etc)\u003C/p>\n        \u003C/div>\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n          \u003Cdiv class=\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-teal-500\">\u003C/div>\n          \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-700\">E-wallets (PayPal, Wise, Skrill)\u003C/p>\n        \u003C/div>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\nFirms may also require you to keep a certain equity value before allowing you to proceed with the withdrawal, making sure that you still have adequate trading capital to continue trading properly.\n\n### Scaling Plans\n\nFor professional traders, scaling plans are what they look for, as most prop firms provide opportunities to trade increasingly bigger trading accounts as you prove consistent profitability and trading discipline. This is a great way to grow your capital allocation and greatly impact your earning potential without any additional investment.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">How Scaling Plans Work\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"space-y-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-teal-500 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Cspan class=\"text-xs font-black text-white\">1\u003C/span>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Percentage-Based Increases\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-600\">Hit a 10% profit target, get 25% more trading capital.\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-teal-500 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Cspan class=\"text-xs font-black text-white\">2\u003C/span>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Milestone Achievements\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-600\">Unlock access to bigger accounts after reaching specific trading targets.\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-teal-500 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Cspan class=\"text-xs font-black text-white\">3\u003C/span>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Time-Based Evaluations\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-600\">The firm increases your trading allocation after showing consistent profitability over a set time period.\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-4\">For forex traders, scaling a $50,000 funded account all the way to $500,000 or even $1 million will significantly increase income potential in proportion to your original account size.\u003C/p>\n\u003C/div>\n\n---\n\n## Forex Prop Trading vs Regular Forex Trading\n\nThe basic difference between regular forex trading and forex prop trading is all about whose money the trader is using. However, there is more to it than prop traders having access to significant capital otherwise unavailable if they trade as a retail forex trader.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"p-5 border-b sm:border-b-0 sm:border-r border-slate-200 bg-teal-50/30\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-3\">\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-teal-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n          \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4 text-teal-600\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4\"/>\u003C/svg>\n        \u003C/div>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-extrabold text-slate-900\">Prop Forex Trading\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Firm's capital, not yours at risk\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Access to substantial capital ($10K-$1M+)\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Professional-grade tools included\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Scaling plans to grow account size\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Profit shared with the firm\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Must follow strict trading rules\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"p-5\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-3\">\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-blue-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n          \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4 text-blue-600\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z\"/>\u003C/svg>\n        \u003C/div>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-extrabold text-slate-900\">Regular Forex Trading\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Full control over strategies\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Keep 100% of all profits\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>No evaluation required\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Trade any way you want\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Your own capital at risk\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Limited by personal funds\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n### Risk Management Rules\n\nAs a retail forex trader, nobody will stop you from using whatever trading strategies you want. With proprietary trading firms, before entrusting you with their money, they have to put strict risk management protocols in place to prevent you from quickly burning through their trading capital.\n\nSome of the common rules include daily loss limits, total drawdown limits, and mandatory stop-loss orders, among others. Compared to regular forex trading, these may feel restrictive, but this is really designed to protect both the trader and the trading company from unnecessary trading risks. Adjusting to these restrictions may take some time, especially if you are coming from the freedom of trading your own funds. But for many individual traders, the potential profit opportunities are worth it.\n\n### Profit Splits Instead of Full Ownership\n\nTrading solo, all profits you make are yours. On the other hand, using the prop trading firm's resources, while you get access to significant capital, profits made will be split between you and the firm on a pre-agreed percentage, typically at 80/20 or even 90/10 splits in favor of the trader.\n\nThis sounds fair since the firm provided the capital for you to trade, so you are not risking your own money. You also gain more capital to trade, plus access to cutting-edge technology to help you perform better with your trading activities.\n\n### Trading Restrictions\n\nTrading as a self-funded forex trader will allow you to use any strategy that you may think of. Scalping, news trading, holding periods, etc. However, a shotgun approach to your trading strategy may not be a good idea in the long run.\n\nTrading restrictions employed by prop trading firms will impose limitations on some or all of these strategies, enabling them to manage risks and prevent traders from exploiting the system with overly aggressive and risky strategies. Being forced to adopt more conservative and predictable strategies will promote discipline, prevent gambling-style trading, and likely improve long-term trading performance.\n\n---\n\n## Benefits of Forex Prop Trading\n\nIf you are a skilled forex trader but do not have much capital, prop trading can be a game-changer. It gives you access to serious trading funds without risking your own money, while also opening the door to bigger profits, scaling opportunities, and professional-grade tools.\n\n### More Capital, Less Risk\n\nProp firms provide traders with more capital to trade, amplifying opportunities to make profits in the fast-moving forex market by being able to take larger positions, as compared to relying on personal funds. Plus, the financial risks are significantly lower since you are not putting your own funds on the line.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Capital Advantage Benefits\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\n      \u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-700\">Implement proper position sizing\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\n      \u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-700\">Diversify across multiple forex pairs\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\n      \u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-700\">Survive normal market fluctuations\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\n      \u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-700\">Make clearer, objective trading decisions\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\nWhen not emotionally attached to your trades, you can make clearer and more objective trading decisions, improving your performance in the long term.\n\n### Profit Potential and Scaling Plans\n\nProp trading firms are always looking for successful traders with a proven trading history, and if you are one of them, you can stand to benefit from performance-based scaling plans that many firms offer, potentially allowing you to have access to even bigger trading accounts.\n\nFor example, starting from a $25,000 funded account, and you check all the boxes like consistently hitting your profit targets while adhering to the risk protocols, your trading can be upgraded to the next account size like $50,000, $100,000, or even a $1 million account.\n\n### Professional Trading Environment\n\nProp trading will allow forex traders to access advanced trading tools like low-latency trading execution, premium charting systems, market data and other cutting-edge technology. Traders serious about establishing a career in prop trading will find this a good place to start establishing a trading history.\n\nTaking advantage of these perks can help your trading performance, without having the need to pay for the market data and other trading tools. Aside from these, many firms also offer educational materials, trader mentorship, and even access to an online community of fellow traders.\n\n### Flexibility and Remote Trading\n\nModern prop firms are now starting to fully adopt remote work, and be able to trade and generate profits anywhere as long as you have a decent internet connection.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Lifestyle Benefits of Prop Trading\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\n      \u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-700\">Choose your preferred market sessions\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\n      \u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-700\">Set up your own ideal trading environment\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\n      \u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-700\">Eliminate commute time, avoid office politics\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\n      \u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-700\">Travel anywhere without neglecting your career\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\nThe flexibility offered by prop trading firms makes them really appealing to part-time employees, freelancers, or anyone who wants to do a bunch of stuff simultaneously.\n\n---\n\n## How Does Leverage Work in Forex Prop Trading?\n\nIn a prop trader's arsenal, leverage is one of the most potent tools that can boost a trader's profits. However, if not properly used, it can send your trading career into a screeching halt.\n\n### How Prop Firms Provide Leverage to Traders\n\nJoining a prop firm and getting a funded trading account not only gives you access to the firm's capital resources, but you will also be getting access to trading leverage. Through this, you can significantly trade larger positions in the foreign exchange market, boosting your buying power.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Common Leverage Ratios in Forex Prop Trading\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 text-center\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium mb-1\">Conservative\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xl font-black text-slate-900\">1:10 - 1:30\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1\">$10K controls $100K-$300K\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-teal-50 px-4 py-3 text-center\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-teal-600 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium mb-1\">Standard\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xl font-black text-teal-600\">1:50 - 1:100\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1\">$10K controls $500K-$1M\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-amber-50 px-4 py-3 text-center\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-amber-600 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium mb-1\">Aggressive\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xl font-black text-amber-600\">1:200 - 1:500\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1\">$10K controls $2M-$5M\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n### Risk and Reward: Managing Leverage Effectively\n\nIn theory, leverage sounds excellent as it allows you to supercharge your trading size and your profit potential. However, bigger leverage comes with equally bigger financial risks. If a trade did not go according to plan, if you did not exercise proper risk management, you can wipe out your account with a single trade. Leverage trading is inherently risky, so pairing it with strict risk management safeguards is necessary.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-8 rounded-xl border-l-4 border-amber-500 bg-amber-50/60 px-5 py-4\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1\">Leverage Warning\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-700\">Bigger leverage comes with equally bigger financial risks. If a trade goes against you and you have not exercised proper risk management, you can wipe out your account with a single trade. Always pair leverage with strict risk management safeguards.\u003C/p>\n\u003C/div>\n\n### Leverage Limits\n\nNot all forex traders can properly handle leverage without blowing out their account. Prop firms have come up with tiered systems where they assign leverage limits based on your trading history, experience and performance.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"bg-[#0d1b2a] px-5 py-4\">\n    \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-black text-white uppercase tracking-wide\">Leverage Tier System\u003C/p>\n  \u003C/div>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"p-5\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"space-y-4\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-slate-400 flex items-center justify-center\">\n          \u003Cspan class=\"text-xs font-black text-white\">1\u003C/span>\n        \u003C/div>\n        \u003Cdiv>\n          \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">New Prop Traders\u003C/p>\n          \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-600\">Usually capped at 1:10 or 1:20. Must prove they can trade profitably while managing risks properly.\u003C/p>\n        \u003C/div>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-teal-500 flex items-center justify-center\">\n          \u003Cspan class=\"text-xs font-black text-white\">2\u003C/span>\n        \u003C/div>\n        \u003Cdiv>\n          \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Experienced Traders\u003C/p>\n          \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-600\">Demonstrated consistency in the past. Granted access to higher leverage exceeding 1:50.\u003C/p>\n        \u003C/div>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-amber-500 flex items-center justify-center\">\n          \u003Cspan class=\"text-xs font-black text-white\">3\u003C/span>\n        \u003C/div>\n        \u003Cdiv>\n          \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Established Traders\u003C/p>\n          \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-600\">Proven track record of success. May be granted access to leverage ratios of 1:100 and higher.\u003C/p>\n        \u003C/div>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\nThis is a sensible way to gradually reward skilled traders and level them up with continued success.\n\n---\n\n## Best Forex Prop Trading Firms\n\nEach forex prop trading firm offers its unique advantages to traders, from higher leverage options to better profit splits to more flexible trading rules. Below are some of the top-ranked options from our list of the best forex prop firms.\n\n### 1. FTMO -- Most Established Forex Prop Firm\n\nFTMO is one of the most well-known and established prop firms in the forex space, with a 4.8 Trustpilot rating and a strong reputation for reliable payouts. With profit splits up to 90%, multiple platform options, and a proven track record, FTMO remains a top choice for serious forex traders.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/ftmo-logo-2-2-1-1-1.png\" alt=\"FTMO logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\" />\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">FTMO\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">Most Established Forex Prop Firm\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">90%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Max DD\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">10%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Trustpilot\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">4.8/5\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Ca href=\"https://trader.ftmo.com/?affiliates=oMPqzmmKTKnnWsrmRgXc\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"flex items-center justify-center px-5 py-3 sm:py-0 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-teal-600 hover:bg-teal-700 text-white text-sm font-bold transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n      Visit FTMO &rarr;\n    \u003C/a>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n**Key Features:**\n- **Platforms:** MT4, MT5, cTrader, DXtrade\n- **Instruments:** Forex, Indices, Commodities, Crypto, Stocks, Bonds\n- **Account Sizes:** Up to $200,000\n- **Profit Split:** Up to 90%\n- **Challenge:** Two-step evaluation (FTMO Challenge + Verification)\n\nFTMO has been operating since 2015 and is widely regarded as the gold standard of forex prop firms. Their two-step evaluation is transparent and well-documented, with clearly defined profit targets and drawdown limits. The firm supports a wide variety of trading platforms and instruments, making it ideal for traders who want flexibility and reliability.\n\n### 2. FundedNext -- High Profit Split Forex Prop Firm\n\nFundedNext stands out for offering one of the highest profit splits in the industry at up to 95%. With multiple challenge types including their Express model, FundedNext provides flexible paths to funding for forex traders of all experience levels.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/fundednext.png\" alt=\"FundedNext logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\" />\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">FundedNext\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">High Profit Split Forex Prop Firm\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">95%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Max DD\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">10%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Trustpilot\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">4.5/5\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Ca href=\"https://fundednext.com/?fpr=noam82\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"flex items-center justify-center px-5 py-3 sm:py-0 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-teal-600 hover:bg-teal-700 text-white text-sm font-bold transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n      Visit FundedNext &rarr;\n    \u003C/a>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n**Key Features:**\n- **Platforms:** MT4, MT5, cTrader, Match-Trader\n- **Instruments:** Forex, Indices, Commodities, Crypto\n- **Account Sizes:** Up to $200,000\n- **Profit Split:** Up to 95%\n- **Challenge:** Multiple models (Evaluation, Express, Stellar)\n\nFundedNext has quickly grown into one of the most popular prop firms, thanks to its generous profit split and variety of challenge paths. The Express model is particularly appealing for traders who want to get funded faster, while the Evaluation model offers a more traditional two-step process with relaxed conditions.\n\n### 3. The5%ers -- Best for Scaling Forex Traders\n\nThe5%ers is a veteran forex prop firm known for its generous scaling plan and up to 100% profit splits. With a focus on forex and metals, The5%ers offers both evaluation and instant funding options, making it a strong choice for traders looking to build a long-term funded trading career.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/the5ers-logo-2-2-1-1-1.png\" alt=\"The5%ers logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\" />\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">The5%ers\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">Best for Scaling Forex Traders\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">100%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Max DD\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">10%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Trustpilot\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">4.9/5\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Ca href=\"https://the5ers.com/?ref=79424\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"flex items-center justify-center px-5 py-3 sm:py-0 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-teal-600 hover:bg-teal-700 text-white text-sm font-bold transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n      Visit The5%ers &rarr;\n    \u003C/a>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n**Key Features:**\n- **Platforms:** MT5, MatchTrader\n- **Instruments:** FX, Metals, Indices, Crypto, Commodities\n- **Account Sizes:** Up to $250,000\n- **Profit Split:** Up to 100%\n- **Challenge:** Evaluation and instant funding options\n\nThe5%ers has earned a stellar 4.9 Trustpilot rating, which speaks volumes about their reliability and trader satisfaction. Their scaling plan is one of the best in the industry, allowing traders to grow their accounts significantly over time. The option for 100% profit splits on certain programs makes them exceptionally competitive.\n\n### 4. Funding Pips -- Up to 100% Profit Split\n\nFunding Pips offers a straightforward path to funded trading with profit splits that can reach 100%. Supporting MT5, cTrader, and Match-Trader, the firm provides flexible challenge options and a strong payout structure for forex traders.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/funding-pips-1.png\" alt=\"Funding Pips logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\" />\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">Funding Pips\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">Up to 100% Profit Split\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">100%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Max DD\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">10%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Trustpilot\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">4.5/5\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Ca href=\"https://app.fundingpips.com/register?ref=53fd8c2c\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"flex items-center justify-center px-5 py-3 sm:py-0 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-teal-600 hover:bg-teal-700 text-white text-sm font-bold transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n      Visit Funding Pips &rarr;\n    \u003C/a>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n**Key Features:**\n- **Platforms:** MetaTrader 5, cTrader, Match-Trader\n- **Instruments:** Forex, Indices, Commodities, Oil, Crypto\n- **Account Sizes:** Up to $100,000\n- **Profit Split:** Up to 100%\n- **Challenge:** Multiple evaluation models available\n\nFunding Pips has gained a strong following for its competitive pricing and flexible payout options. The firm's straightforward challenge structure and the potential for 100% profit splits make it an attractive option, particularly for traders who prioritize maximizing their earnings on each payout cycle.\n\n---\n\n## Is Prop Forex Trading Right for You?\n\nProp trading, especially for forex traders, can be a huge boon for traders with a proven and working trading strategy who lack the funds to make an impact. At the same time, you will not be risking your own money, but the firm's capital, making it very compelling.\n\nHowever, since you will be trading the firm's money, there are strict risk management rules. If you are disciplined and adaptable, this will be in your favor. But for those who like total control or do not like the profit-sharing models, you may have to look elsewhere.\n\n### Who Benefits the Most From Forex Prop Trading?\n\nAdmittedly, prop trading is not for everyone, especially for new traders who may struggle initially with the strict trading rules during the evaluation phase. Proprietary trading rewards consistency, not luck.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4\">Ideal Trader Profiles\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600 mb-1\">Experienced Traders with Limited Funds\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-600\">Traders who have developed a working and consistently profitable strategy will find that prop trading can take their profit potential to a whole new level.\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600 mb-1\">Disciplined and Risk-Averse Traders\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-600\">If you are disciplined in taking care of capital, you will feel at home, since risk management is very important in this industry.\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600 mb-1\">Strategic Traders\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-600\">Those using scalable strategies like day or swing trading can benefit from the extra liquidity and advanced trading tools the firm provides.\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600 mb-1\">Learners\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-600\">Many proprietary trading firms offer learning opportunities through free reading materials, community support, and even mentorship from experienced traders.\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n### Key Considerations Before Joining a Prop Firm\n\nBefore signing up, consider these key considerations, as jumping in blindfolded will only lead to failure.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Pre-Signup Checklist\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"space-y-3\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-teal-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Csvg class=\"h-3 w-3 text-teal-600\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Evaluation Process\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500\">What kind of challenge do they have? Is it a one-stage challenge or multiple phases? Are the profit targets and drawdown limits realistic and achievable?\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-teal-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Csvg class=\"h-3 w-3 text-teal-600\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Profit Splits and Entry Fees\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500\">Profit splits vary from 50% to as high as 90-100%, with varying rules. Entry fees also differ between firms.\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-teal-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Csvg class=\"h-3 w-3 text-teal-600\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Trading Rules\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500\">Some firms have overly tight drawdown limits, restricted strategies, and even limited trading hours.\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-teal-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Csvg class=\"h-3 w-3 text-teal-600\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Firm's Reputation\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500\">Read reviews on sites like Trustpilot, and look for trader feedback from Reddit, Twitter, etc. Avoid firms with payout issues or unrealistic trading goals.\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-teal-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Csvg class=\"h-3 w-3 text-teal-600\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Support and Resources\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500\">How responsive is the firm's customer support? Do they have free education resources? Positive answers add strong value.\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\nForex prop trading can unlock opportunities, but your success depends on matching your trading skills and discipline with the right prop firm. If you find the right firm with trading rules that align with your skill set and experience, this is a low-risk way to level up your trading. But if you are still unsure, many firms offer free trials or demo accounts, or an affordable challenge for a starter trading account, so you can get an actual feel before fully committing.\n\n---\n\n## FAQs\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 space-y-4\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5\">\n    \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2\">Is Prop Trading Allowed in the US?\u003C/p>\n    \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-600\">Yes, prop trading is legal in the US. Independent proprietary trading firms that use their own capital are not restricted, as long as they comply with relevant regulations. If you are based in the US, check that the firm accepts US traders and operates transparently.\u003C/p>\n  \u003C/div>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5\">\n    \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2\">Do Prop Traders Make Money?\u003C/p>\n    \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-600\">Yes, but it requires discipline and risk management skills, aside from your trading skillset. While a bigger percentage fail to overcome the evaluation or challenge phases, through practice and discipline, you can still get funded. Once you receive a funded account, earnings vary based on the account size, risk management, and overall market conditions.\u003C/p>\n  \u003C/div>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5\">\n    \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2\">What Is a Prop Trading Example?\u003C/p>\n    \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-600\">If you pass a firm's $50,000 evaluation, you will receive a funded $50,000 account. From there, you trade using the firm's capital. For example, if you risk 1% ($500) and make a $1,000 profit, and your profit split is 80/20, you would keep $800 and the firm keeps $200. If you trade consistently, they may increase your account size through a scaling plan.\u003C/p>\n  \u003C/div>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5\">\n    \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2\">Why Is Prop Trading Illegal?\u003C/p>\n    \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-600\">Prop trading is not illegal. The confusion usually comes from its high-profit potential and the use of a firm's capital, which can seem too good to be true. In reality, most countries allow proprietary trading, including the USA, UK, India, and Canada. Always check that the firm you are trading with is transparent, properly registered, and accepts traders from your country.\u003C/p>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>","src/content/blog/forex-trading.md","56c16fb4c6811d50",{"html":7395,"metadata":7396},"\u003Ch2 id=\"what-is-prop-forex-trading\">What Is Prop Forex Trading?\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>Forex prop trading is when you use a firm’s capital rather than your own to execute trades in the foreign exchange market. Traders who are confident in their trading skills but lack the trading funds can look at the best forex prop firms, which offer ways to provide significantly more capital and generate potentially more profits shared between both parties.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Forex Prop Trading at a Glance\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-4 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 text-center\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-2xl font-black text-teal-600 mb-1\">1\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-semibold text-slate-700\">Pay a challenge fee and enter an evaluation\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 text-center\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-2xl font-black text-teal-600 mb-1\">2\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-semibold text-slate-700\">Prove your skills by hitting profit targets within risk limits\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 text-center\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-2xl font-black text-teal-600 mb-1\">3\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-semibold text-slate-700\">Pass evaluation and receive a funded trading account\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 text-center\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-2xl font-black text-teal-600 mb-1\">4\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-semibold text-slate-700\">Trade forex and keep up to 90-100% of profits\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"how-do-prop-trading-firms-work\">How Do Prop Trading Firms Work?\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>The basic principle of proprietary trading firms is that they allocate their own capital to skilled traders whom they have deemed capable of trading profitably and responsibly. They use internally raised capital in their trading activities, unlike traditional institutions like banks and hedge funds that primarily deal with client funds.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>These firms actively look for talented traders who may lack the capital to trade big, but have all the qualities necessary to succeed in this industry. They also operate through various financial instruments, including the forex market, where there are plenty of opportunities for fast-moving trades, perfect for prop traders. Other markets in which these firms operate include the stock market, futures markets, and more.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Prop firms usually run challenge programs where forex traders show their trading skills and risk discipline in a controlled trading environment, starting with demo accounts. After passing the challenge, you will be awarded a funded account and share the profits generated with the trading firm. Some prop firms will allow you to start trading right away, but this usually comes with a steeper challenge fee and stricter rules on risk management.\u003C/p>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"profit-sharing-model-and-risk-management\">Profit-Sharing Model and Risk Management\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>Having access to the firm’s capital will naturally come with some guidelines on how you are going to split the profits while handling the firm’s money responsibly.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>If you become one of the firm’s prop traders, you and the prop firm share the profits generated on a pre-agreed percentage, with you getting the bigger share, usually starting at 70% and up to 90%, and the remaining going to the firm.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-8 rounded-xl border-l-4 border-teal-500 bg-teal-50/60 px-5 py-4\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1\">Risk management is the cornerstone of most prop trading firms.\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-700\">These firms need to put systems in place to protect the trading money they are providing their traders. As a prop trader, you will have to operate within risk management guidelines.\u003C/p>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Common Risk Management Rules\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"space-y-3\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-red-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Csvg class=\"h-3 w-3 text-red-500\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Maximum Drawdown Limits\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500\">The maximum level your portfolio value is allowed to drop from its highest level.\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-red-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Csvg class=\"h-3 w-3 text-red-500\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Daily Loss Limits\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500\">The limit you are allowed to lose in a single trading day.\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-red-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Csvg class=\"h-3 w-3 text-red-500\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Position Sizing Rules\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500\">Rules dictating how much trading position you can take relative to your account size.\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-red-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Csvg class=\"h-3 w-3 text-red-500\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Trading Restrictions\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500\">Some firms regulate strategies like news trading, high-frequency trading, etc. Before joining a prop firm, ensure your preferred strategy is allowed.\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"types-of-forex-prop-trading-firms\">Types of Forex Prop Trading Firms\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>Depending on your skill level and how quickly you want to get the capital to trade, there are many prop trading firms available that fit your needs. The two main models are challenges and instant funding, though hybrid models exist too.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"p-5 border-b sm:border-b-0 sm:border-r border-slate-200\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-3\">\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-teal-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n          \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4 text-teal-600\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n        \u003C/div>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-extrabold text-slate-900\">Challenge-Based\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Lower entry fees\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>More flexible strategies allowed\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>More lenient risk management\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Must pass evaluation first\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"p-5 border-b sm:border-b-0 sm:border-r border-slate-200\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-3\">\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-amber-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n          \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4 text-amber-600\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n        \u003C/div>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-extrabold text-slate-900\">Instant Funding\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Immediate access to capital\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>No evaluation waiting period\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Higher upfront fees\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Stricter trading rules and drawdowns\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"p-5\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-3\">\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-blue-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n          \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4 text-blue-600\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M8 7h12m0 0l-4-4m4 4l-4 4m0 6H4m0 0l4 4m-4-4l4-4\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n        \u003C/div>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-extrabold text-slate-900\">Hybrid Models\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Choose challenge or instant funding\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Switch models based on performance\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Best of both worlds flexibility\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>May involve switching fees\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"challenge-based-prop-firms\">Challenge-Based Prop Firms\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>This is probably the most popular type of proprietary trading firm in the forex market. Before you can trade using the firm’s capital, you need to prove yourself first with an evaluation or challenge round.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"bg-[#0d1b2a] px-5 py-4\">\n    \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-black text-white uppercase tracking-wide\">How a Challenge Works\u003C/p>\n  \u003C/div>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"p-5\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"space-y-4\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-teal-500 flex items-center justify-center\">\n          \u003Cspan class=\"text-xs font-black text-white\">1\u003C/span>\n        \u003C/div>\n        \u003Cdiv>\n          \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Start with a Demo Account\u003C/p>\n          \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-600\">Trade in a controlled simulated environment using the firm's trading platforms.\u003C/p>\n        \u003C/div>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-teal-500 flex items-center justify-center\">\n          \u003Cspan class=\"text-xs font-black text-white\">2\u003C/span>\n        \u003C/div>\n        \u003Cdiv>\n          \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Hit Profit Targets\u003C/p>\n          \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-600\">Reach the profit target (usually around 8-10%) while following the firm's risk management protocols within a set period.\u003C/p>\n        \u003C/div>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 flex items-center justify-center\">\n          \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4 text-white\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n        \u003C/div>\n        \u003Cdiv>\n          \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Receive a Funded Account\u003C/p>\n          \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-600\">Successful traders receive a funded account with real capital and begin sharing profits with the firm.\u003C/p>\n        \u003C/div>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cp>With entry fees usually lower compared to instant funding options, challenge-based models appeal to many traders because they are also more flexible, with more trading strategies allowed and more lenient risk management parameters.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"instant-funding-prop-firms\">Instant Funding Prop Firms\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>For those wanting to start trading immediately, instant funding prop firms offer immediate access to the firm’s capital, but with a higher upfront fee. Paying a bigger entry fee may seem easy enough, but this comes with significantly stricter trading rules. You are expected to trade at a high level from the start with stricter risk management rules and tighter drawdown limits.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>This is not for everyone, and is usually reserved only for seasoned traders who may have a deeper understanding of the financial markets. But with the right person, this is a quick way to get funded and potentially generate profits as early as possible.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"hybrid-models\">Hybrid Models\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>The middle ground between the earlier models is the hybrid one, perfect for traders wanting to get funded quickly but not fully confident in their trading skills. Prop firms with this hybrid setup will let you choose between a challenge or instant funding at the beginning, or come with an option to switch between these models on the fly with a fee, or based on your performance.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Before jumping into a prop firm, make sure that you understand which model works best for you based on your current skill and preferences, as these can dictate your success or failure as a prop trader.\u003C/p>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"how-prop-traders-get-paid\">How Prop Traders Get Paid\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>One of the biggest reasons why most forex traders join prop firms is to get that trading payout. If you have what it takes and get a funded account, this is a great way to potentially earn more profits that are otherwise not accessible to you without risking your own money.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"profit-sharing\">Profit-Sharing\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>How traders get paid is a straightforward process: make a profit, and get your share. The profit split structure is where you split the profits you made as a prop trader, with the larger piece of the pie going to the trader.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Profit Split Example\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 text-center\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium mb-1\">Trading Profit\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xl font-black text-slate-900\">$1,000\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-teal-50 px-4 py-3 text-center\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-teal-600 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium mb-1\">Your Share (80%)\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xl font-black text-teal-600\">$800\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 text-center\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium mb-1\">Firm Share (20%)\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xl font-black text-slate-900\">$200\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-3 text-center\">Typical splits range from 70/30 to 90/10 in favor of the trader. Some firms offer up to 100% on early payouts.\u003C/p>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cp>The best forex prop firms work to keep their traders happy by offering the best profit splits, and it is not unusual for proven and profitable traders to receive favorable trading terms and better profit splits from prop firms.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"withdrawal-and-payment-policies\">Withdrawal and Payment Policies\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>After doing the hard part of making profits, the next part is getting your share of the profits into your bank account. Trading firms have varying policies on how and when you can get your share of the profits.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"p-5 border-b sm:border-b-0 sm:border-r border-slate-200\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-extrabold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Payment Schedules\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"space-y-2\">\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n          \u003Cdiv class=\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-teal-500\">\u003C/div>\n          \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-700\">\u003Cstrong>Bi-Weekly Payouts\u003C/strong> - Gaining traction\u003C/p>\n        \u003C/div>\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n          \u003Cdiv class=\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-teal-500\">\u003C/div>\n          \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-700\">\u003Cstrong>Monthly Withdrawals\u003C/strong> - Most common\u003C/p>\n        \u003C/div>\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n          \u003Cdiv class=\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-slate-300\">\u003C/div>\n          \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-700\">\u003Cstrong>Quarterly Withdrawals\u003C/strong> - Less common\u003C/p>\n        \u003C/div>\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n          \u003Cdiv class=\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-teal-500\">\u003C/div>\n          \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-700\">\u003Cstrong>On-Demand\u003C/strong> - Growing in popularity\u003C/p>\n        \u003C/div>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"p-5\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-extrabold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Payment Methods\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"space-y-2\">\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n          \u003Cdiv class=\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-teal-500\">\u003C/div>\n          \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-700\">Traditional bank transfers\u003C/p>\n        \u003C/div>\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n          \u003Cdiv class=\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-teal-500\">\u003C/div>\n          \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-700\">Cryptocurrency (BTC, ETH, etc)\u003C/p>\n        \u003C/div>\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n          \u003Cdiv class=\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-teal-500\">\u003C/div>\n          \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-700\">E-wallets (PayPal, Wise, Skrill)\u003C/p>\n        \u003C/div>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cp>Firms may also require you to keep a certain equity value before allowing you to proceed with the withdrawal, making sure that you still have adequate trading capital to continue trading properly.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"scaling-plans\">Scaling Plans\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>For professional traders, scaling plans are what they look for, as most prop firms provide opportunities to trade increasingly bigger trading accounts as you prove consistent profitability and trading discipline. This is a great way to grow your capital allocation and greatly impact your earning potential without any additional investment.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">How Scaling Plans Work\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"space-y-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-teal-500 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Cspan class=\"text-xs font-black text-white\">1\u003C/span>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Percentage-Based Increases\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-600\">Hit a 10% profit target, get 25% more trading capital.\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-teal-500 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Cspan class=\"text-xs font-black text-white\">2\u003C/span>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Milestone Achievements\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-600\">Unlock access to bigger accounts after reaching specific trading targets.\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-teal-500 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Cspan class=\"text-xs font-black text-white\">3\u003C/span>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Time-Based Evaluations\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-600\">The firm increases your trading allocation after showing consistent profitability over a set time period.\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-4\">For forex traders, scaling a $50,000 funded account all the way to $500,000 or even $1 million will significantly increase income potential in proportion to your original account size.\u003C/p>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"forex-prop-trading-vs-regular-forex-trading\">Forex Prop Trading vs Regular Forex Trading\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>The basic difference between regular forex trading and forex prop trading is all about whose money the trader is using. However, there is more to it than prop traders having access to significant capital otherwise unavailable if they trade as a retail forex trader.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"p-5 border-b sm:border-b-0 sm:border-r border-slate-200 bg-teal-50/30\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-3\">\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-teal-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n          \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4 text-teal-600\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n        \u003C/div>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-extrabold text-slate-900\">Prop Forex Trading\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Firm's capital, not yours at risk\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Access to substantial capital ($10K-$1M+)\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Professional-grade tools included\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Scaling plans to grow account size\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Profit shared with the firm\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Must follow strict trading rules\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"p-5\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-3\">\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-blue-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n          \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4 text-blue-600\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n        \u003C/div>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-extrabold text-slate-900\">Regular Forex Trading\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Full control over strategies\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Keep 100% of all profits\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>No evaluation required\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Trade any way you want\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Your own capital at risk\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Limited by personal funds\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"risk-management-rules\">Risk Management Rules\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>As a retail forex trader, nobody will stop you from using whatever trading strategies you want. With proprietary trading firms, before entrusting you with their money, they have to put strict risk management protocols in place to prevent you from quickly burning through their trading capital.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Some of the common rules include daily loss limits, total drawdown limits, and mandatory stop-loss orders, among others. Compared to regular forex trading, these may feel restrictive, but this is really designed to protect both the trader and the trading company from unnecessary trading risks. Adjusting to these restrictions may take some time, especially if you are coming from the freedom of trading your own funds. But for many individual traders, the potential profit opportunities are worth it.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"profit-splits-instead-of-full-ownership\">Profit Splits Instead of Full Ownership\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Trading solo, all profits you make are yours. On the other hand, using the prop trading firm’s resources, while you get access to significant capital, profits made will be split between you and the firm on a pre-agreed percentage, typically at 80/20 or even 90/10 splits in favor of the trader.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>This sounds fair since the firm provided the capital for you to trade, so you are not risking your own money. You also gain more capital to trade, plus access to cutting-edge technology to help you perform better with your trading activities.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"trading-restrictions\">Trading Restrictions\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Trading as a self-funded forex trader will allow you to use any strategy that you may think of. Scalping, news trading, holding periods, etc. However, a shotgun approach to your trading strategy may not be a good idea in the long run.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Trading restrictions employed by prop trading firms will impose limitations on some or all of these strategies, enabling them to manage risks and prevent traders from exploiting the system with overly aggressive and risky strategies. Being forced to adopt more conservative and predictable strategies will promote discipline, prevent gambling-style trading, and likely improve long-term trading performance.\u003C/p>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"benefits-of-forex-prop-trading\">Benefits of Forex Prop Trading\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>If you are a skilled forex trader but do not have much capital, prop trading can be a game-changer. It gives you access to serious trading funds without risking your own money, while also opening the door to bigger profits, scaling opportunities, and professional-grade tools.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"more-capital-less-risk\">More Capital, Less Risk\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Prop firms provide traders with more capital to trade, amplifying opportunities to make profits in the fast-moving forex market by being able to take larger positions, as compared to relying on personal funds. Plus, the financial risks are significantly lower since you are not putting your own funds on the line.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Capital Advantage Benefits\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\n      \u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-700\">Implement proper position sizing\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\n      \u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-700\">Diversify across multiple forex pairs\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\n      \u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-700\">Survive normal market fluctuations\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\n      \u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-700\">Make clearer, objective trading decisions\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cp>When not emotionally attached to your trades, you can make clearer and more objective trading decisions, improving your performance in the long term.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"profit-potential-and-scaling-plans\">Profit Potential and Scaling Plans\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Prop trading firms are always looking for successful traders with a proven trading history, and if you are one of them, you can stand to benefit from performance-based scaling plans that many firms offer, potentially allowing you to have access to even bigger trading accounts.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>For example, starting from a $25,000 funded account, and you check all the boxes like consistently hitting your profit targets while adhering to the risk protocols, your trading can be upgraded to the next account size like $50,000, $100,000, or even a $1 million account.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"professional-trading-environment\">Professional Trading Environment\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Prop trading will allow forex traders to access advanced trading tools like low-latency trading execution, premium charting systems, market data and other cutting-edge technology. Traders serious about establishing a career in prop trading will find this a good place to start establishing a trading history.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Taking advantage of these perks can help your trading performance, without having the need to pay for the market data and other trading tools. Aside from these, many firms also offer educational materials, trader mentorship, and even access to an online community of fellow traders.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"flexibility-and-remote-trading\">Flexibility and Remote Trading\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Modern prop firms are now starting to fully adopt remote work, and be able to trade and generate profits anywhere as long as you have a decent internet connection.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Lifestyle Benefits of Prop Trading\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\n      \u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-700\">Choose your preferred market sessions\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\n      \u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-700\">Set up your own ideal trading environment\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\n      \u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-700\">Eliminate commute time, avoid office politics\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\n      \u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-700\">Travel anywhere without neglecting your career\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cp>The flexibility offered by prop trading firms makes them really appealing to part-time employees, freelancers, or anyone who wants to do a bunch of stuff simultaneously.\u003C/p>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"how-does-leverage-work-in-forex-prop-trading\">How Does Leverage Work in Forex Prop Trading?\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>In a prop trader’s arsenal, leverage is one of the most potent tools that can boost a trader’s profits. However, if not properly used, it can send your trading career into a screeching halt.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"how-prop-firms-provide-leverage-to-traders\">How Prop Firms Provide Leverage to Traders\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Joining a prop firm and getting a funded trading account not only gives you access to the firm’s capital resources, but you will also be getting access to trading leverage. Through this, you can significantly trade larger positions in the foreign exchange market, boosting your buying power.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Common Leverage Ratios in Forex Prop Trading\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 text-center\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium mb-1\">Conservative\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xl font-black text-slate-900\">1:10 - 1:30\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1\">$10K controls $100K-$300K\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-teal-50 px-4 py-3 text-center\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-teal-600 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium mb-1\">Standard\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xl font-black text-teal-600\">1:50 - 1:100\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1\">$10K controls $500K-$1M\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-amber-50 px-4 py-3 text-center\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-amber-600 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium mb-1\">Aggressive\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xl font-black text-amber-600\">1:200 - 1:500\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1\">$10K controls $2M-$5M\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"risk-and-reward-managing-leverage-effectively\">Risk and Reward: Managing Leverage Effectively\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>In theory, leverage sounds excellent as it allows you to supercharge your trading size and your profit potential. However, bigger leverage comes with equally bigger financial risks. If a trade did not go according to plan, if you did not exercise proper risk management, you can wipe out your account with a single trade. Leverage trading is inherently risky, so pairing it with strict risk management safeguards is necessary.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-8 rounded-xl border-l-4 border-amber-500 bg-amber-50/60 px-5 py-4\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1\">Leverage Warning\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-700\">Bigger leverage comes with equally bigger financial risks. If a trade goes against you and you have not exercised proper risk management, you can wipe out your account with a single trade. Always pair leverage with strict risk management safeguards.\u003C/p>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"leverage-limits\">Leverage Limits\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Not all forex traders can properly handle leverage without blowing out their account. Prop firms have come up with tiered systems where they assign leverage limits based on your trading history, experience and performance.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"bg-[#0d1b2a] px-5 py-4\">\n    \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-black text-white uppercase tracking-wide\">Leverage Tier System\u003C/p>\n  \u003C/div>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"p-5\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"space-y-4\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-slate-400 flex items-center justify-center\">\n          \u003Cspan class=\"text-xs font-black text-white\">1\u003C/span>\n        \u003C/div>\n        \u003Cdiv>\n          \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">New Prop Traders\u003C/p>\n          \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-600\">Usually capped at 1:10 or 1:20. Must prove they can trade profitably while managing risks properly.\u003C/p>\n        \u003C/div>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-teal-500 flex items-center justify-center\">\n          \u003Cspan class=\"text-xs font-black text-white\">2\u003C/span>\n        \u003C/div>\n        \u003Cdiv>\n          \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Experienced Traders\u003C/p>\n          \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-600\">Demonstrated consistency in the past. Granted access to higher leverage exceeding 1:50.\u003C/p>\n        \u003C/div>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-amber-500 flex items-center justify-center\">\n          \u003Cspan class=\"text-xs font-black text-white\">3\u003C/span>\n        \u003C/div>\n        \u003Cdiv>\n          \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Established Traders\u003C/p>\n          \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-600\">Proven track record of success. May be granted access to leverage ratios of 1:100 and higher.\u003C/p>\n        \u003C/div>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cp>This is a sensible way to gradually reward skilled traders and level them up with continued success.\u003C/p>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"best-forex-prop-trading-firms\">Best Forex Prop Trading Firms\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>Each forex prop trading firm offers its unique advantages to traders, from higher leverage options to better profit splits to more flexible trading rules. Below are some of the top-ranked options from our list of the best forex prop firms.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"1-ftmo--most-established-forex-prop-firm\">1. FTMO — Most Established Forex Prop Firm\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>FTMO is one of the most well-known and established prop firms in the forex space, with a 4.8 Trustpilot rating and a strong reputation for reliable payouts. With profit splits up to 90%, multiple platform options, and a proven track record, FTMO remains a top choice for serious forex traders.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/ftmo-logo-2-2-1-1-1.png\" alt=\"FTMO logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">FTMO\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">Most Established Forex Prop Firm\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">90%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Max DD\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">10%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Trustpilot\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">4.8/5\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Ca href=\"https://trader.ftmo.com/?affiliates=oMPqzmmKTKnnWsrmRgXc\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"flex items-center justify-center px-5 py-3 sm:py-0 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-teal-600 hover:bg-teal-700 text-white text-sm font-bold transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n      Visit FTMO →\n    \u003C/a>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>Key Features:\u003C/strong>\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Platforms:\u003C/strong> MT4, MT5, cTrader, DXtrade\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Instruments:\u003C/strong> Forex, Indices, Commodities, Crypto, Stocks, Bonds\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Account Sizes:\u003C/strong> Up to $200,000\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Profit Split:\u003C/strong> Up to 90%\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Challenge:\u003C/strong> Two-step evaluation (FTMO Challenge + Verification)\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Cp>FTMO has been operating since 2015 and is widely regarded as the gold standard of forex prop firms. Their two-step evaluation is transparent and well-documented, with clearly defined profit targets and drawdown limits. The firm supports a wide variety of trading platforms and instruments, making it ideal for traders who want flexibility and reliability.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"2-fundednext--high-profit-split-forex-prop-firm\">2. FundedNext — High Profit Split Forex Prop Firm\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>FundedNext stands out for offering one of the highest profit splits in the industry at up to 95%. With multiple challenge types including their Express model, FundedNext provides flexible paths to funding for forex traders of all experience levels.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/fundednext.png\" alt=\"FundedNext logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">FundedNext\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">High Profit Split Forex Prop Firm\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">95%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Max DD\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">10%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Trustpilot\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">4.5/5\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Ca href=\"https://fundednext.com/?fpr=noam82\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"flex items-center justify-center px-5 py-3 sm:py-0 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-teal-600 hover:bg-teal-700 text-white text-sm font-bold transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n      Visit FundedNext →\n    \u003C/a>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>Key Features:\u003C/strong>\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Platforms:\u003C/strong> MT4, MT5, cTrader, Match-Trader\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Instruments:\u003C/strong> Forex, Indices, Commodities, Crypto\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Account Sizes:\u003C/strong> Up to $200,000\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Profit Split:\u003C/strong> Up to 95%\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Challenge:\u003C/strong> Multiple models (Evaluation, Express, Stellar)\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Cp>FundedNext has quickly grown into one of the most popular prop firms, thanks to its generous profit split and variety of challenge paths. The Express model is particularly appealing for traders who want to get funded faster, while the Evaluation model offers a more traditional two-step process with relaxed conditions.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"3-the5ers--best-for-scaling-forex-traders\">3. The5%ers — Best for Scaling Forex Traders\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>The5%ers is a veteran forex prop firm known for its generous scaling plan and up to 100% profit splits. With a focus on forex and metals, The5%ers offers both evaluation and instant funding options, making it a strong choice for traders looking to build a long-term funded trading career.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/the5ers-logo-2-2-1-1-1.png\" alt=\"The5%ers logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">The5%ers\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">Best for Scaling Forex Traders\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">100%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Max DD\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">10%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Trustpilot\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">4.9/5\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Ca href=\"https://the5ers.com/?ref=79424\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"flex items-center justify-center px-5 py-3 sm:py-0 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-teal-600 hover:bg-teal-700 text-white text-sm font-bold transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n      Visit The5%ers →\n    \u003C/a>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>Key Features:\u003C/strong>\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Platforms:\u003C/strong> MT5, MatchTrader\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Instruments:\u003C/strong> FX, Metals, Indices, Crypto, Commodities\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Account Sizes:\u003C/strong> Up to $250,000\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Profit Split:\u003C/strong> Up to 100%\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Challenge:\u003C/strong> Evaluation and instant funding options\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Cp>The5%ers has earned a stellar 4.9 Trustpilot rating, which speaks volumes about their reliability and trader satisfaction. Their scaling plan is one of the best in the industry, allowing traders to grow their accounts significantly over time. The option for 100% profit splits on certain programs makes them exceptionally competitive.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"4-funding-pips--up-to-100-profit-split\">4. Funding Pips — Up to 100% Profit Split\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Funding Pips offers a straightforward path to funded trading with profit splits that can reach 100%. Supporting MT5, cTrader, and Match-Trader, the firm provides flexible challenge options and a strong payout structure for forex traders.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/funding-pips-1.png\" alt=\"Funding Pips logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">Funding Pips\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">Up to 100% Profit Split\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">100%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Max DD\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">10%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Trustpilot\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">4.5/5\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Ca href=\"https://app.fundingpips.com/register?ref=53fd8c2c\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"flex items-center justify-center px-5 py-3 sm:py-0 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-teal-600 hover:bg-teal-700 text-white text-sm font-bold transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n      Visit Funding Pips →\n    \u003C/a>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>Key Features:\u003C/strong>\u003C/p>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Platforms:\u003C/strong> MetaTrader 5, cTrader, Match-Trader\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Instruments:\u003C/strong> Forex, Indices, Commodities, Oil, Crypto\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Account Sizes:\u003C/strong> Up to $100,000\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Profit Split:\u003C/strong> Up to 100%\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>Challenge:\u003C/strong> Multiple evaluation models available\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Cp>Funding Pips has gained a strong following for its competitive pricing and flexible payout options. The firm’s straightforward challenge structure and the potential for 100% profit splits make it an attractive option, particularly for traders who prioritize maximizing their earnings on each payout cycle.\u003C/p>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"is-prop-forex-trading-right-for-you\">Is Prop Forex Trading Right for You?\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>Prop trading, especially for forex traders, can be a huge boon for traders with a proven and working trading strategy who lack the funds to make an impact. At the same time, you will not be risking your own money, but the firm’s capital, making it very compelling.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>However, since you will be trading the firm’s money, there are strict risk management rules. If you are disciplined and adaptable, this will be in your favor. But for those who like total control or do not like the profit-sharing models, you may have to look elsewhere.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"who-benefits-the-most-from-forex-prop-trading\">Who Benefits the Most From Forex Prop Trading?\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Admittedly, prop trading is not for everyone, especially for new traders who may struggle initially with the strict trading rules during the evaluation phase. Proprietary trading rewards consistency, not luck.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4\">Ideal Trader Profiles\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600 mb-1\">Experienced Traders with Limited Funds\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-600\">Traders who have developed a working and consistently profitable strategy will find that prop trading can take their profit potential to a whole new level.\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600 mb-1\">Disciplined and Risk-Averse Traders\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-600\">If you are disciplined in taking care of capital, you will feel at home, since risk management is very important in this industry.\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600 mb-1\">Strategic Traders\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-600\">Those using scalable strategies like day or swing trading can benefit from the extra liquidity and advanced trading tools the firm provides.\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600 mb-1\">Learners\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-600\">Many proprietary trading firms offer learning opportunities through free reading materials, community support, and even mentorship from experienced traders.\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"key-considerations-before-joining-a-prop-firm\">Key Considerations Before Joining a Prop Firm\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Before signing up, consider these key considerations, as jumping in blindfolded will only lead to failure.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Pre-Signup Checklist\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"space-y-3\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-teal-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Csvg class=\"h-3 w-3 text-teal-600\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Evaluation Process\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500\">What kind of challenge do they have? Is it a one-stage challenge or multiple phases? Are the profit targets and drawdown limits realistic and achievable?\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-teal-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Csvg class=\"h-3 w-3 text-teal-600\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Profit Splits and Entry Fees\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500\">Profit splits vary from 50% to as high as 90-100%, with varying rules. Entry fees also differ between firms.\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-teal-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Csvg class=\"h-3 w-3 text-teal-600\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Trading Rules\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500\">Some firms have overly tight drawdown limits, restricted strategies, and even limited trading hours.\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-teal-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Csvg class=\"h-3 w-3 text-teal-600\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Firm's Reputation\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500\">Read reviews on sites like Trustpilot, and look for trader feedback from Reddit, Twitter, etc. Avoid firms with payout issues or unrealistic trading goals.\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-teal-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Csvg class=\"h-3 w-3 text-teal-600\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Support and Resources\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500\">How responsive is the firm's customer support? Do they have free education resources? Positive answers add strong value.\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cp>Forex prop trading can unlock opportunities, but your success depends on matching your trading skills and discipline with the right prop firm. If you find the right firm with trading rules that align with your skill set and experience, this is a low-risk way to level up your trading. But if you are still unsure, many firms offer free trials or demo accounts, or an affordable challenge for a starter trading account, so you can get an actual feel before fully committing.\u003C/p>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"faqs\">FAQs\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 space-y-4\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5\">\n    \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2\">Is Prop Trading Allowed in the US?\u003C/p>\n    \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-600\">Yes, prop trading is legal in the US. Independent proprietary trading firms that use their own capital are not restricted, as long as they comply with relevant regulations. If you are based in the US, check that the firm accepts US traders and operates transparently.\u003C/p>\n  \u003C/div>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5\">\n    \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2\">Do Prop Traders Make Money?\u003C/p>\n    \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-600\">Yes, but it requires discipline and risk management skills, aside from your trading skillset. While a bigger percentage fail to overcome the evaluation or challenge phases, through practice and discipline, you can still get funded. Once you receive a funded account, earnings vary based on the account size, risk management, and overall market conditions.\u003C/p>\n  \u003C/div>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5\">\n    \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2\">What Is a Prop Trading Example?\u003C/p>\n    \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-600\">If you pass a firm's $50,000 evaluation, you will receive a funded $50,000 account. From there, you trade using the firm's capital. For example, if you risk 1% ($500) and make a $1,000 profit, and your profit split is 80/20, you would keep $800 and the firm keeps $200. If you trade consistently, they may increase your account size through a scaling plan.\u003C/p>\n  \u003C/div>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5\">\n    \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2\">Why Is Prop Trading Illegal?\u003C/p>\n    \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-600\">Prop trading is not illegal. The confusion usually comes from its high-profit potential and the use of a firm's capital, which can seem too good to be true. In reality, most countries allow proprietary trading, including the USA, UK, India, and Canada. Always check that the firm you are trading with is transparent, properly registered, and accepts traders from your country.\u003C/p>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>",{"headings":7397,"localImagePaths":7490,"remoteImagePaths":7491,"frontmatter":7492,"imagePaths":7499},[7398,7401,7404,7407,7410,7413,7416,7419,7422,7424,7427,7428,7431,7434,7437,7438,7441,7444,7447,7450,7453,7456,7459,7462,7465,7468,7471,7474,7477,7480,7483,7486,7489],{"depth":879,"slug":7399,"text":7400},"what-is-prop-forex-trading","What Is Prop Forex Trading?",{"depth":879,"slug":7402,"text":7403},"how-do-prop-trading-firms-work","How Do Prop Trading Firms Work?",{"depth":879,"slug":7405,"text":7406},"profit-sharing-model-and-risk-management","Profit-Sharing Model and Risk Management",{"depth":879,"slug":7408,"text":7409},"types-of-forex-prop-trading-firms","Types of Forex Prop Trading Firms",{"depth":158,"slug":7411,"text":7412},"challenge-based-prop-firms","Challenge-Based Prop Firms",{"depth":158,"slug":7414,"text":7415},"instant-funding-prop-firms","Instant Funding Prop Firms",{"depth":158,"slug":7417,"text":7418},"hybrid-models","Hybrid Models",{"depth":879,"slug":7420,"text":7421},"how-prop-traders-get-paid","How Prop Traders Get Paid",{"depth":158,"slug":7094,"text":7423},"Profit-Sharing",{"depth":158,"slug":7425,"text":7426},"withdrawal-and-payment-policies","Withdrawal and Payment Policies",{"depth":158,"slug":6546,"text":6547},{"depth":879,"slug":7429,"text":7430},"forex-prop-trading-vs-regular-forex-trading","Forex Prop Trading vs Regular Forex Trading",{"depth":158,"slug":7432,"text":7433},"risk-management-rules","Risk Management Rules",{"depth":158,"slug":7435,"text":7436},"profit-splits-instead-of-full-ownership","Profit Splits Instead of Full Ownership",{"depth":158,"slug":7353,"text":7354},{"depth":879,"slug":7439,"text":7440},"benefits-of-forex-prop-trading","Benefits of Forex Prop Trading",{"depth":158,"slug":7442,"text":7443},"more-capital-less-risk","More Capital, Less Risk",{"depth":158,"slug":7445,"text":7446},"profit-potential-and-scaling-plans","Profit Potential and Scaling Plans",{"depth":158,"slug":7448,"text":7449},"professional-trading-environment","Professional Trading Environment",{"depth":158,"slug":7451,"text":7452},"flexibility-and-remote-trading","Flexibility and Remote Trading",{"depth":879,"slug":7454,"text":7455},"how-does-leverage-work-in-forex-prop-trading","How Does Leverage Work in Forex Prop Trading?",{"depth":158,"slug":7457,"text":7458},"how-prop-firms-provide-leverage-to-traders","How Prop Firms Provide Leverage to Traders",{"depth":158,"slug":7460,"text":7461},"risk-and-reward-managing-leverage-effectively","Risk and Reward: Managing Leverage Effectively",{"depth":158,"slug":7463,"text":7464},"leverage-limits","Leverage Limits",{"depth":879,"slug":7466,"text":7467},"best-forex-prop-trading-firms","Best Forex Prop Trading Firms",{"depth":158,"slug":7469,"text":7470},"1-ftmo--most-established-forex-prop-firm","1. FTMO — Most Established Forex Prop Firm",{"depth":158,"slug":7472,"text":7473},"2-fundednext--high-profit-split-forex-prop-firm","2. FundedNext — High Profit Split Forex Prop Firm",{"depth":158,"slug":7475,"text":7476},"3-the5ers--best-for-scaling-forex-traders","3. The5%ers — Best for Scaling Forex Traders",{"depth":158,"slug":7478,"text":7479},"4-funding-pips--up-to-100-profit-split","4. Funding Pips — Up to 100% Profit Split",{"depth":879,"slug":7481,"text":7482},"is-prop-forex-trading-right-for-you","Is Prop Forex Trading Right for You?",{"depth":158,"slug":7484,"text":7485},"who-benefits-the-most-from-forex-prop-trading","Who Benefits the Most From Forex Prop Trading?",{"depth":158,"slug":7487,"text":7488},"key-considerations-before-joining-a-prop-firm","Key Considerations Before Joining a Prop Firm",{"depth":879,"slug":4935,"text":4936},[],[],{"title":7379,"excerpt":7380,"category":5171,"tags":7493,"author":4798,"authorImage":4799,"publishedAt":7298,"featured":110,"readingTimeMinutes":5176,"featuredFirms":7494},[4795,5609,4796,7382],[7495,7496,7497,7498],{"slug":1002,"descriptor":7385},{"slug":1392,"descriptor":7387},{"slug":2507,"descriptor":7389},{"slug":1459,"descriptor":5631},[],"forex-trading.md",{"id":6546,"data":7502,"body":7515,"filePath":7516,"digest":7517,"rendered":7518,"legacyId":7583},{"title":7503,"excerpt":7504,"category":5171,"tags":7505,"author":4798,"authorImage":4799,"publishedAt":7298,"featured":110,"readingTimeMinutes":405,"featuredFirms":7508},"Prop Scaling Plans: How to Grow Your Funded Account","Scaling plans are a core feature of prop trading, rewarding consistent traders with more capital and better profit splits. Learn how they work, what firms offer the best programs, and how to scale up successfully.",[7506,5609,4796,7507],"scaling plans","capital growth",[7509,7511,7513],{"slug":584,"descriptor":7510},"Unlimited Scaling Potential",{"slug":1392,"descriptor":7512},"Scale Up to $4 Million",{"slug":332,"descriptor":7514},"Top Broker-Backed Scaling Plan","## What Are Prop Scaling Plans?\n\nScaling plans allow successful traders to grow the funds available exponentially and increase possible earnings, and are one of the main features of prop trading. As you demonstrate consistent trading performance and strong risk management skills, prop firms will reward you with more capital allocation.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">How Scaling Works at a Glance\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-4 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 text-center\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-2xl font-black text-teal-600 mb-1\">1\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-semibold text-slate-700\">Pass your challenge and receive a funded account\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 text-center\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-2xl font-black text-teal-600 mb-1\">2\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-semibold text-slate-700\">Trade consistently and hit profit targets within risk limits\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 text-center\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-2xl font-black text-teal-600 mb-1\">3\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-semibold text-slate-700\">Meet the scaling criteria over the review period\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 text-center\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-2xl font-black text-teal-600 mb-1\">4\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-semibold text-slate-700\">Receive a capital increase and repeat the cycle\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n---\n\n## Best Prop Firms with Scaling Plans\n\nBrightFunded, FundedNext, and Blueberry Funded offer three of the best scaling programs in the industry. Below is a quick comparison of how their plans stack up.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"bg-[#0d1b2a] px-5 py-4\">\n    \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-black text-white uppercase tracking-wide\">Scaling Plan Comparison\u003C/p>\n  \u003C/div>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"p-5\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"overflow-x-auto\">\n      \u003Ctable class=\"w-full text-sm text-left\">\n        \u003Cthead>\n          \u003Ctr class=\"border-b border-slate-200\">\n            \u003Cth class=\"py-2 pr-4 font-bold text-slate-900\">Firm\u003C/th>\n            \u003Cth class=\"py-2 pr-4 font-bold text-slate-900\">Score\u003C/th>\n            \u003Cth class=\"py-2 pr-4 font-bold text-slate-900\">Scale Increase\u003C/th>\n            \u003Cth class=\"py-2 pr-4 font-bold text-slate-900\">Frequency\u003C/th>\n            \u003Cth class=\"py-2 pr-4 font-bold text-slate-900\">Max Capital\u003C/th>\n            \u003Cth class=\"py-2 font-bold text-slate-900\">Max Split\u003C/th>\n          \u003C/tr>\n        \u003C/thead>\n        \u003Ctbody>\n          \u003Ctr class=\"border-b border-slate-100\">\n            \u003Ctd class=\"py-3 pr-4 font-bold text-slate-900\">BrightFunded\u003C/td>\n            \u003Ctd class=\"py-3 pr-4\">\u003Cspan class=\"inline-block rounded-full bg-teal-100 px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-bold text-teal-700\">95/100\u003C/span>\u003C/td>\n            \u003Ctd class=\"py-3 pr-4 text-slate-700\">30%\u003C/td>\n            \u003Ctd class=\"py-3 pr-4 text-slate-700\">Every 4 months\u003C/td>\n            \u003Ctd class=\"py-3 pr-4 font-bold text-teal-600\">Unlimited\u003C/td>\n            \u003Ctd class=\"py-3 text-slate-700\">100%\u003C/td>\n          \u003C/tr>\n          \u003Ctr class=\"border-b border-slate-100\">\n            \u003Ctd class=\"py-3 pr-4 font-bold text-slate-900\">Blueberry Funded\u003C/td>\n            \u003Ctd class=\"py-3 pr-4\">\u003Cspan class=\"inline-block rounded-full bg-teal-100 px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-bold text-teal-700\">93/100\u003C/span>\u003C/td>\n            \u003Ctd class=\"py-3 pr-4 text-slate-700\">25%\u003C/td>\n            \u003Ctd class=\"py-3 pr-4 text-slate-700\">Every 3 months\u003C/td>\n            \u003Ctd class=\"py-3 pr-4 font-bold text-slate-800\">$2 million\u003C/td>\n            \u003Ctd class=\"py-3 text-slate-700\">90%\u003C/td>\n          \u003C/tr>\n          \u003Ctr>\n            \u003Ctd class=\"py-3 pr-4 font-bold text-slate-900\">FundedNext\u003C/td>\n            \u003Ctd class=\"py-3 pr-4\">\u003Cspan class=\"inline-block rounded-full bg-teal-100 px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-bold text-teal-700\">92/100\u003C/span>\u003C/td>\n            \u003Ctd class=\"py-3 pr-4 text-slate-700\">40%\u003C/td>\n            \u003Ctd class=\"py-3 pr-4 text-slate-700\">Every 4 months\u003C/td>\n            \u003Ctd class=\"py-3 pr-4 font-bold text-slate-800\">$4 million\u003C/td>\n            \u003Ctd class=\"py-3 text-slate-700\">95%\u003C/td>\n          \u003C/tr>\n        \u003C/tbody>\n      \u003C/table>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n---\n\n### 1. BrightFunded Scaling Plan\n\nBrightFunded's unlimited scaling plan is designed for long-term traders who consistently hit performance targets. Once funded, traders can increase their account balance by 30% every 4 months, provided the following conditions are met.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/brightfunded-logo.png\" alt=\"BrightFunded logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\" />\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">BrightFunded\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">Unlimited Scaling Potential\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">100%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Score\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">95/100\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Trustpilot\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">4.4/5\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Ca href=\"https://brightfunded.com?affiliateId=rsBbtrzYQSyr3RcHYHQT5w\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"flex items-center justify-center px-5 py-3 sm:py-0 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-teal-600 hover:bg-teal-700 text-white text-sm font-bold transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n      Visit BrightFunded &rarr;\n    \u003C/a>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">BrightFunded Scaling Requirements\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"space-y-3\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-teal-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Csvg class=\"h-3 w-3 text-teal-600\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-700\">At least \u003Cstrong>2 profitable months\u003C/strong> within a 4-month cycle\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-teal-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Csvg class=\"h-3 w-3 text-teal-600\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-700\">A minimum total profit of \u003Cstrong>10% over 4 months\u003C/strong>\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-teal-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Csvg class=\"h-3 w-3 text-teal-600\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-700\">At least \u003Cstrong>2 payouts received\u003C/strong> during the review period\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-teal-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Csvg class=\"h-3 w-3 text-teal-600\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-700\">Ending balance must be \u003Cstrong>positive or breakeven\u003C/strong>\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\nScaling is ongoing with no upper cap, and from the third scale-up onward, traders receive a 100% profit split, meaning you keep all the profits. Combined with the Trade2Earn loyalty program, which rewards active trading with perks like free challenges and better payout terms, BrightFunded is ideal for traders who want both flexibility and longevity.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-4 gap-3\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 text-center\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium mb-1\">Scale Amount\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-black text-teal-600\">30%\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-500\">every 4 months\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 text-center\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium mb-1\">Max Split\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-black text-teal-600\">100%\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-500\">from 3rd scale-up\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 text-center\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium mb-1\">Max Capital\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-black text-teal-600\">Unlimited\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-500\">no upper cap\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 text-center\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium mb-1\">Bonus\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-black text-teal-600\">Trade2Earn\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-500\">loyalty perks\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n---\n\n### 2. FundedNext Scaling Plan\n\nFundedNext offers a clear and structured Scale-Up Plan with one of the largest potential account allocations in the industry, up to $4 million. Traders who maintain strong performance over a 4-month period can qualify for a 40% capital increase.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/fundednext.png\" alt=\"FundedNext logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\" />\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">FundedNext\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">Scale Up to $4 Million\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">95%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Score\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">92/100\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Trustpilot\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">4.5/5\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Ca href=\"https://fundednext.com/?fpr=noam82\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"flex items-center justify-center px-5 py-3 sm:py-0 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-teal-600 hover:bg-teal-700 text-white text-sm font-bold transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n      Visit FundedNext &rarr;\n    \u003C/a>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">FundedNext Scaling Requirements\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"space-y-3\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-teal-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Csvg class=\"h-3 w-3 text-teal-600\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-700\">Achieve \u003Cstrong>10% account growth\u003C/strong> over 4 consecutive months\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-teal-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Csvg class=\"h-3 w-3 text-teal-600\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-700\">Receive at least \u003Cstrong>2 payouts\u003C/strong> in that period\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-teal-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Csvg class=\"h-3 w-3 text-teal-600\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-700\">Have a \u003Cstrong>profitable last trading month\u003C/strong>\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\nIf you meet these milestones, your account size increases by 40%, and the profit split remains as high as 95% depending on your account model. The drawdown limits are also adjusted proportionally, giving you room to scale without tighter restrictions.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-4 gap-3\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 text-center\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium mb-1\">Scale Amount\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-black text-teal-600\">40%\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-500\">every 4 months\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 text-center\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium mb-1\">Max Split\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-black text-teal-600\">95%\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-500\">depending on model\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 text-center\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium mb-1\">Max Capital\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-black text-teal-600\">$4M\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-500\">maximum allocation\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 text-center\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium mb-1\">Rules\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-black text-teal-600\">Transparent\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-500\">across all models\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n---\n\n### 3. Blueberry Funded Scaling Plan\n\nBlueberry Funded rewards steady performance with a 25% account increase every 3 months, allowing growth up to $2 million in simulated capital.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/blueberry-funded-logo.png\" alt=\"Blueberry Funded logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\" />\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">Blueberry Funded\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">Top Broker-Backed Scaling Plan\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">90%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Score\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">93/100\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Trustpilot\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">3.8/5\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Ca href=\"https://blueberryfunded.com/?utm_source=affiliate&ref=1457\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"flex items-center justify-center px-5 py-3 sm:py-0 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-teal-600 hover:bg-teal-700 text-white text-sm font-bold transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n      Visit Blueberry Funded &rarr;\n    \u003C/a>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Blueberry Funded Scaling Requirements\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"space-y-3\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-teal-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Csvg class=\"h-3 w-3 text-teal-600\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-700\">Maintain a \u003Cstrong>10% net profit\u003C/strong> over 3 months\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-teal-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Csvg class=\"h-3 w-3 text-teal-600\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-700\">Complete \u003Cstrong>4 profit payouts\u003C/strong> during that period\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\nProfit splits start at 80%, but can increase to 90% for top performers. Trading conditions remain the same even as your account scales, so your strategy does not need to change, just your position sizing.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-4 gap-3\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 text-center\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium mb-1\">Scale Amount\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-black text-teal-600\">25%\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-500\">every 3 months\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 text-center\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium mb-1\">Max Split\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-black text-teal-600\">90%\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-500\">for top performers\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 text-center\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium mb-1\">Max Capital\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-black text-teal-600\">$2M\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-500\">simulated capital\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 text-center\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium mb-1\">Conditions\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-black text-teal-600\">Same\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-500\">no rule changes\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n---\n\n## How Prop Scaling Plans Work\n\nIf you have proven to the firm that you are a profitable trader and manage risk well, the prop firm will want you to handle more capital. As long as you meet all the scaling requirements, providing you with a bigger chunk of the firm's capital means bigger profit potential for everyone involved, with the prop firm literally investing in your talent and betting on your success.\n\nThis is your pathway to growth within a prop firm, allowing you access to a larger account size and more buying power than what you likely have with your personal funds, turning prop trading into a career path with strong earning potential. This mechanism is what allows many prop firms to attract and retain winning traders.\n\n### Requirements for Capital Increases\n\nOf course, prop firms will not simply hand out more capital to their prop traders. They need to earn it first before being granted capital increases. Rules differ between trading firms, but the main details that are common in the industry are detailed below.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4\">Core Scaling Requirements\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"space-y-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-teal-500 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Cspan class=\"text-xs font-black text-white\">1\u003C/span>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Consistent Profits\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-600\">This is the main requirement. You need to demonstrate that you have trading strategies that consistently yield results, not just relying solely on luck. Prop firms have defined profit targets for you to achieve, which is usually the main trigger for a scaling upgrade review.\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-teal-500 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Cspan class=\"text-xs font-black text-white\">2\u003C/span>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Risk Management\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-600\">This is a must. Failing to follow the prop firm's risk management rules, like daily loss limits or maximum drawdown limits, can get your account closed. Effective risk management shows you can handle larger trading account sizes responsibly.\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-teal-500 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Cspan class=\"text-xs font-black text-white\">3\u003C/span>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Other Trading Rules\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-600\">Besides risk management, other trading rules must be followed, including position sizing, minimum trading days, and any specific firm trading guidelines. Even if you are profitable, but are breaking some of these other rules, you will not get your account scaled up.\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n### Gradual vs Rapid Scaling Plans\n\nThis is where most trading prop firms differ, as not all prop firms provide scaling plans at the same speed. Depending on the firm, these plans can be gradual or rapid.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"p-5 border-b sm:border-b-0 sm:border-r border-slate-200 bg-teal-50/30\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-3\">\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-teal-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n          \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4 text-teal-600\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6\"/>\u003C/svg>\n        \u003C/div>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-extrabold text-slate-900\">Gradual Scaling\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Typically 25-50% capital increases\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Adapt comfortably to larger capital\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Ideal for steady, consistent growth\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Lower risk of overexposure\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"p-5\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-3\">\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-amber-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n          \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4 text-amber-600\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z\"/>\u003C/svg>\n        \u003C/div>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-extrabold text-slate-900\">Rapid Scaling\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Can double account size multiple times\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Shorter timeframes to reach max capital\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Requires ambitious profit targets\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Only for experienced, disciplined traders\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\nThe key here is to find the prop firm with a scaling plan that is in sync with your trading style and personality and how quickly you can adapt to the increasing risk exposure. Only then can you figure out which trading firm is better for you.\n\n### Performance Milestones and Scaling Increments\n\nOnce you get a funded account, your next target is to get more trading capital. But before you can unlock those scaling increments, you need to hit trading goals or performance milestones.\n\nTypically, prop firms set these targets in percentage terms rather than fixed dollar amounts, usually between 5-15%, before triggering the first capital increase.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Typical Profit Target Progression\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"space-y-3\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-20\">\n        \u003Cspan class=\"inline-block rounded-full bg-teal-100 px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-bold text-teal-700\">Beginner\u003C/span>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-1 bg-slate-100 rounded-full h-4 overflow-hidden\">\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"bg-teal-500 h-full rounded-full\" style=\"width: 40%\">\u003C/div>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-700 w-16 text-right\">5-8%\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-20\">\n        \u003Cspan class=\"inline-block rounded-full bg-amber-100 px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-bold text-amber-700\">Mid-Level\u003C/span>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-1 bg-slate-100 rounded-full h-4 overflow-hidden\">\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"bg-amber-500 h-full rounded-full\" style=\"width: 66%\">\u003C/div>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-700 w-16 text-right\">8-12%\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-20\">\n        \u003Cspan class=\"inline-block rounded-full bg-red-100 px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-bold text-red-700\">Advanced\u003C/span>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-1 bg-slate-100 rounded-full h-4 overflow-hidden\">\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"bg-red-500 h-full rounded-full\" style=\"width: 100%\">\u003C/div>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-700 w-16 text-right\">15%+\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-3\">Example: On a $50,000 account, a 5% target means $2,500 profit, while a 15% target means $7,500.\u003C/p>\n\u003C/div>\n\n---\n\n## Trading Styles and Scaling Up\n\nYour trading style plays a big factor in how fast you can level up through the scaling plans, with different styles having different scaling potential.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"p-5 border-b sm:border-b-0 sm:border-r border-slate-200\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-3\">\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-amber-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n          \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4 text-amber-600\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z\"/>\u003C/svg>\n        \u003C/div>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-extrabold text-slate-900\">Day Trading\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-600 mb-2\">Fastest way to scale. Frequent trades give more chances to lock in profits and hit targets quickly.\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-1 mt-3\">\n        \u003Cspan class=\"text-xs font-bold text-amber-600\">Speed:\u003C/span>\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"flex gap-0.5\">\n          \u003Cdiv class=\"w-3 h-3 rounded-sm bg-amber-500\">\u003C/div>\n          \u003Cdiv class=\"w-3 h-3 rounded-sm bg-amber-500\">\u003C/div>\n          \u003Cdiv class=\"w-3 h-3 rounded-sm bg-amber-500\">\u003C/div>\n        \u003C/div>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-1 mt-1\">\n        \u003Cspan class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500\">Risk:\u003C/span>\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"flex gap-0.5\">\n          \u003Cdiv class=\"w-3 h-3 rounded-sm bg-red-500\">\u003C/div>\n          \u003Cdiv class=\"w-3 h-3 rounded-sm bg-red-500\">\u003C/div>\n          \u003Cdiv class=\"w-3 h-3 rounded-sm bg-red-500\">\u003C/div>\n        \u003C/div>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"p-5 border-b sm:border-b-0 sm:border-r border-slate-200\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-3\">\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-teal-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n          \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4 text-teal-600\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M8 7h12m0 0l-4-4m4 4l-4 4m0 6H4m0 0l4 4m-4-4l4-4\"/>\u003C/svg>\n        \u003C/div>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-extrabold text-slate-900\">Swing Trading\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-600 mb-2\">Balanced approach. Less risk exposure with the ideal middle ground that works with most scaling plans.\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-1 mt-3\">\n        \u003Cspan class=\"text-xs font-bold text-teal-600\">Speed:\u003C/span>\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"flex gap-0.5\">\n          \u003Cdiv class=\"w-3 h-3 rounded-sm bg-teal-500\">\u003C/div>\n          \u003Cdiv class=\"w-3 h-3 rounded-sm bg-teal-500\">\u003C/div>\n          \u003Cdiv class=\"w-3 h-3 rounded-sm bg-slate-200\">\u003C/div>\n        \u003C/div>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-1 mt-1\">\n        \u003Cspan class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500\">Risk:\u003C/span>\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"flex gap-0.5\">\n          \u003Cdiv class=\"w-3 h-3 rounded-sm bg-red-500\">\u003C/div>\n          \u003Cdiv class=\"w-3 h-3 rounded-sm bg-red-500\">\u003C/div>\n          \u003Cdiv class=\"w-3 h-3 rounded-sm bg-slate-200\">\u003C/div>\n        \u003C/div>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"p-5\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-3\">\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-blue-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n          \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4 text-blue-600\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z\"/>\u003C/svg>\n        \u003C/div>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-extrabold text-slate-900\">Position Trading\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-600 mb-2\">Slower but safest. Provides the most sustainable long-term scaling approach with minimal drawdown risk.\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-1 mt-3\">\n        \u003Cspan class=\"text-xs font-bold text-blue-600\">Speed:\u003C/span>\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"flex gap-0.5\">\n          \u003Cdiv class=\"w-3 h-3 rounded-sm bg-blue-500\">\u003C/div>\n          \u003Cdiv class=\"w-3 h-3 rounded-sm bg-slate-200\">\u003C/div>\n          \u003Cdiv class=\"w-3 h-3 rounded-sm bg-slate-200\">\u003C/div>\n        \u003C/div>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-1 mt-1\">\n        \u003Cspan class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500\">Risk:\u003C/span>\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"flex gap-0.5\">\n          \u003Cdiv class=\"w-3 h-3 rounded-sm bg-red-500\">\u003C/div>\n          \u003Cdiv class=\"w-3 h-3 rounded-sm bg-slate-200\">\u003C/div>\n          \u003Cdiv class=\"w-3 h-3 rounded-sm bg-slate-200\">\u003C/div>\n        \u003C/div>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\nFinding a prop firm with a scaling structure that aligns with your trading approach is usually a good idea. Some firms will be a match for active traders, while more consistent and methodical traders may be at home with certain prop trading firms.\n\n---\n\n## Trading Performance and Capital Allocation\n\nBeyond hitting profit targets, prop firms examine how you achieve them, evaluating the quality of your trading and other performance criteria, which will dictate how they increase your funded trading account.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4\">What Prop Firms Evaluate\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600 mb-1\">Risk-Adjusted Returns\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-600\">Achieving consistent performance while staying within risk parameters can significantly help in securing favorable scaling terms.\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600 mb-1\">Drawdown Management\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-600\">Generating profits without your account fluctuating into big dips. Prop firms will be more willing to provide additional capital to steady performers.\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600 mb-1\">Consistency in Returns\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-600\">Trading firms value traders whose fund value moves steadily upwards, rather than one that swings wildly up and down. Predictable performance is better for them.\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600 mb-1\">Trade Management\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-600\">How traders size positions, as well as trade entry and exit timings, also factor into scaling decisions.\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-3\">Prop firms are now adopting algorithms to automatically analyze these metrics, customizing scaling plans according to each trader's style and strengths.\u003C/p>\n\u003C/div>\n\n---\n\n## Prop Firm Scaling Criteria\n\nHitting profit targets is great, but prop firms look beyond this before scaling your account to the next level. They have other key trading parameters you need to reach before you can get a bigger trading account.\n\n### Minimum Trading Days\n\nWhile it varies, many prop firms will want to see you trading actively with at least 10, 15, 30 days, etc, before they will consider upgrading your account size. You can hit your profit goals, but scaling will not automatically happen unless you reach the required trading days before getting a bump on your capital.\n\nSome of them will even look at how you spread your trades across the month, as they would rather see you make a few but consistent trades each day, than cramming your activities in a short period of time. This way, they can identify traders with sustainable trading strategies, rather than gamblers looking to make quick profits.\n\n### Trading Consistency\n\nBefore being trusted with more capital allocation, prop firms need to see that you can maintain consistent profitability. As your account size grows, you must demonstrate that you can handle the increased pressure and responsibility that comes with it.\n\nTrading dynamics differ significantly from the initial capital allocation of $25,000 to a scaled plan of $100,000, and prop firms know this. If the firms notice that your performance dips after scaling, they may hold off on upgrading your account, making it crucial to keep following risk management protocols to maintain consistent performance.\n\n### Common Trading Rules\n\nProp firms use guardrails to help their prop traders stay on the right path to success, especially as the trading account size increases, ensuring adherence to risk parameters.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Common Rules at Scaled Levels\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"space-y-3\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-red-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Csvg class=\"h-3 w-3 text-red-500\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Daily Drawdown Limits\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500\">Usually capped at under 5% of account value on any single day. Hit this and you risk getting your account shut down.\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-red-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Csvg class=\"h-3 w-3 text-red-500\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Maximum Drawdown Limits\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500\">Caps the allowable loss from a trader's peak account value. Breach this and you may face account termination.\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-red-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Csvg class=\"h-3 w-3 text-red-500\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Position Holding Periods\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500\">Usually restricts overnight or weekend positions. Some firms will relax holding restrictions for consistently profitable traders.\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-red-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Csvg class=\"h-3 w-3 text-red-500\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">News Trading Restrictions\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500\">Usually restricted to 2-10 minute high impact news windows, as price swings can be significant during these periods.\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-red-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Csvg class=\"h-3 w-3 text-red-500\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Instrument Restrictions\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500\">Commonly applied to volatile instruments like cryptocurrencies. These can loosen as traders progress to higher account levels.\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-3\">Some rules may be introduced or relaxed as you progress through the scaling levels.\u003C/p>\n\u003C/div>\n\n---\n\n## Trading Strategies for Scaling Success\n\nScaling plans allow for increased profit potential, but to keep winning and levelling up your account, you need to adjust trading strategies from when you started trading, as they may no longer apply to scaled-up accounts.\n\nSimply increasing your trade position sizing will not cut it. You need to change your mental approach, update your strategy or learn a few more skills. You do not have to overhaul your entire trading strategy as your account grows, but making it adaptable is a trait successful traders have in the prop trading industry.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4\">Key Areas to Adapt\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"space-y-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-slate-700 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4 text-white\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z\"/>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Mental State\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-600\">With bigger trading accounts come bigger gains or losses, which can mess with your head if you are not ready for it. Larger positions will require even stronger mental discipline for you to stick to your plan.\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-slate-700 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4 text-white\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M4 4v5h.582m15.356 2A8.001 8.001 0 004.582 9m0 0H9m11 11v-5h-.581m0 0a8.003 8.003 0 01-15.357-2m15.357 2H15\"/>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Update Trading Strategy\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-600\">Make sure that your favorite trading strategy remains effective at bigger trading accounts. Strategies may be effective at smaller accounts, but with larger accounts requiring more liquidity, closing positions can pose significant challenges.\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-slate-700 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4 text-white\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6\"/>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Refining Trading Skills\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-600\">Scaling up means your trading skills got you there. However, reaching the next scaling level may require further improvement in certain aspects, such as trade execution, analysis, or adopting a more rigid trading discipline and increased patience.\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n### Risk Management at Scale\n\nEffective risk management remains crucial, especially with scaled-up accounts. The temptation to take more risks with bigger accounts is strong, making risk management more critical at this point.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-8 rounded-xl border-l-4 border-amber-500 bg-amber-50/60 px-5 py-4\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1\">Scaling Warning\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-700\">As your account grows, the temptation to take more risks is strong. Risking 1% of a $100,000 account ($1,000) feels very different from 1% of a $25,000 account ($250). You need to be mentally ready for the increased risk exposure at each level.\u003C/p>\n\u003C/div>\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4\">Risk Discipline Tips for Scaling\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"space-y-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-teal-500 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Cspan class=\"text-xs font-black text-white\">1\u003C/span>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Keep Risk Proportional\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-600\">Underexposure may risk your account failing to meet increased profit targets, but overexposure may risk reaching drawdown limits faster if the trade goes against you.\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-teal-500 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Cspan class=\"text-xs font-black text-white\">2\u003C/span>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Spread Entries and Exits\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-600\">Compared to smaller accounts, instantly filling buy or sell orders may be dangerous on bigger accounts. Spreading out larger positions across a wider entry or exit plan helps reduce market impact.\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-teal-500 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Cspan class=\"text-xs font-black text-white\">3\u003C/span>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Be Wary of Trade Correlations\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-600\">With greater buying power, you may unintentionally open multiple positions that move in response to the same market catalyst, indirectly multiplying your risk exposure.\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-teal-500 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Cspan class=\"text-xs font-black text-white\">4\u003C/span>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Drawdown Planning\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-600\">Top traders implement a \"cooling off\" system: if they lose 3%, they automatically reduce their position sizes by 50% until they recover the lost ground.\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\nRisk management rules are set up to protect the firm's capital, but these rules also set up the prop traders for long-term success, while preventing disaster in the short term. Following these risk parameters, you demonstrate to the prop trading firm that you can be trusted, making it more likely for them to accelerate your scaling plan. It is not unusual for firms to be more lenient with traders with a track record of consistent performance and risk management.\n\n---\n\n## FAQs\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 space-y-4\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5\">\n    \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2\">Which prop firm has the best scaling plan?\u003C/p>\n    \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-600\">BrightFunded has one of the best scaling plans and funded accounts, offering unlimited 30% account growth every 4 months and 100% profit splits from the third scale-up onward. It is built for long-term growth and high-profit retention. FundedNext is another top prop firm, with capital scaling up to $4 million and 40% increases every 4 months. Blueberry Funded is a broker-backed option, scaling accounts by 25% every 3 months up to $2 million.\u003C/p>\n  \u003C/div>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5\">\n    \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2\">What is a scaling plan?\u003C/p>\n    \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-600\">Scaling plans are a structured system that a prop firm offers traders to increase trading capital, once they have proven consistent profitability. Once you hit certain performance criteria, the firm will increase the allocated capital to you, allowing you to trade larger positions and increasing your profit potential. This paves the way for you to grow without putting more capital yourself.\u003C/p>\n  \u003C/div>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5\">\n    \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2\">Does FundedNext have a scaling plan?\u003C/p>\n    \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-600\">Yes, FundedNext offers a scaling plan that allows their prop traders to increase their account size by up to 40%, and up to a maximum capital allocation of $4 million. Traders need to accumulate an account growth of 10% over four consecutive months and receive at least two payouts during the period.\u003C/p>\n  \u003C/div>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5\">\n    \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2\">How to scale up a prop firm account?\u003C/p>\n    \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-600\">Consistent performance is the best way to scale up your account. You need to master risk management, follow all trading rules by the prop firm, especially those related to risk management, and minimize drawdowns. Be consistently profitable, show the firm that you can keep it up in the long term, and hit specific profit targets in the scaling plan. Finally, all the criteria, like the minimum trading days or other specific performance metrics, must be met.\u003C/p>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>","src/content/blog/scaling-plans.md","e946861261517642",{"html":7519,"metadata":7520},"\u003Ch2 id=\"what-are-prop-scaling-plans\">What Are Prop Scaling Plans?\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>Scaling plans allow successful traders to grow the funds available exponentially and increase possible earnings, and are one of the main features of prop trading. As you demonstrate consistent trading performance and strong risk management skills, prop firms will reward you with more capital allocation.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">How Scaling Works at a Glance\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-4 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 text-center\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-2xl font-black text-teal-600 mb-1\">1\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-semibold text-slate-700\">Pass your challenge and receive a funded account\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 text-center\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-2xl font-black text-teal-600 mb-1\">2\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-semibold text-slate-700\">Trade consistently and hit profit targets within risk limits\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 text-center\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-2xl font-black text-teal-600 mb-1\">3\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-semibold text-slate-700\">Meet the scaling criteria over the review period\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 text-center\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-2xl font-black text-teal-600 mb-1\">4\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-semibold text-slate-700\">Receive a capital increase and repeat the cycle\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"best-prop-firms-with-scaling-plans\">Best Prop Firms with Scaling Plans\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>BrightFunded, FundedNext, and Blueberry Funded offer three of the best scaling programs in the industry. Below is a quick comparison of how their plans stack up.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"bg-[#0d1b2a] px-5 py-4\">\n    \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-black text-white uppercase tracking-wide\">Scaling Plan Comparison\u003C/p>\n  \u003C/div>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"p-5\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"overflow-x-auto\">\n      \u003Ctable class=\"w-full text-sm text-left\">\n        \u003Cthead>\n          \u003Ctr class=\"border-b border-slate-200\">\n            \u003Cth class=\"py-2 pr-4 font-bold text-slate-900\">Firm\u003C/th>\n            \u003Cth class=\"py-2 pr-4 font-bold text-slate-900\">Score\u003C/th>\n            \u003Cth class=\"py-2 pr-4 font-bold text-slate-900\">Scale Increase\u003C/th>\n            \u003Cth class=\"py-2 pr-4 font-bold text-slate-900\">Frequency\u003C/th>\n            \u003Cth class=\"py-2 pr-4 font-bold text-slate-900\">Max Capital\u003C/th>\n            \u003Cth class=\"py-2 font-bold text-slate-900\">Max Split\u003C/th>\n          \u003C/tr>\n        \u003C/thead>\n        \u003Ctbody>\n          \u003Ctr class=\"border-b border-slate-100\">\n            \u003Ctd class=\"py-3 pr-4 font-bold text-slate-900\">BrightFunded\u003C/td>\n            \u003Ctd class=\"py-3 pr-4\">\u003Cspan class=\"inline-block rounded-full bg-teal-100 px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-bold text-teal-700\">95/100\u003C/span>\u003C/td>\n            \u003Ctd class=\"py-3 pr-4 text-slate-700\">30%\u003C/td>\n            \u003Ctd class=\"py-3 pr-4 text-slate-700\">Every 4 months\u003C/td>\n            \u003Ctd class=\"py-3 pr-4 font-bold text-teal-600\">Unlimited\u003C/td>\n            \u003Ctd class=\"py-3 text-slate-700\">100%\u003C/td>\n          \u003C/tr>\n          \u003Ctr class=\"border-b border-slate-100\">\n            \u003Ctd class=\"py-3 pr-4 font-bold text-slate-900\">Blueberry Funded\u003C/td>\n            \u003Ctd class=\"py-3 pr-4\">\u003Cspan class=\"inline-block rounded-full bg-teal-100 px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-bold text-teal-700\">93/100\u003C/span>\u003C/td>\n            \u003Ctd class=\"py-3 pr-4 text-slate-700\">25%\u003C/td>\n            \u003Ctd class=\"py-3 pr-4 text-slate-700\">Every 3 months\u003C/td>\n            \u003Ctd class=\"py-3 pr-4 font-bold text-slate-800\">$2 million\u003C/td>\n            \u003Ctd class=\"py-3 text-slate-700\">90%\u003C/td>\n          \u003C/tr>\n          \u003Ctr>\n            \u003Ctd class=\"py-3 pr-4 font-bold text-slate-900\">FundedNext\u003C/td>\n            \u003Ctd class=\"py-3 pr-4\">\u003Cspan class=\"inline-block rounded-full bg-teal-100 px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-bold text-teal-700\">92/100\u003C/span>\u003C/td>\n            \u003Ctd class=\"py-3 pr-4 text-slate-700\">40%\u003C/td>\n            \u003Ctd class=\"py-3 pr-4 text-slate-700\">Every 4 months\u003C/td>\n            \u003Ctd class=\"py-3 pr-4 font-bold text-slate-800\">$4 million\u003C/td>\n            \u003Ctd class=\"py-3 text-slate-700\">95%\u003C/td>\n          \u003C/tr>\n        \u003C/tbody>\n      \u003C/table>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"1-brightfunded-scaling-plan\">1. BrightFunded Scaling Plan\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>BrightFunded’s unlimited scaling plan is designed for long-term traders who consistently hit performance targets. Once funded, traders can increase their account balance by 30% every 4 months, provided the following conditions are met.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/brightfunded-logo.png\" alt=\"BrightFunded logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">BrightFunded\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">Unlimited Scaling Potential\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">100%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Score\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">95/100\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Trustpilot\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">4.4/5\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Ca href=\"https://brightfunded.com?affiliateId=rsBbtrzYQSyr3RcHYHQT5w\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"flex items-center justify-center px-5 py-3 sm:py-0 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-teal-600 hover:bg-teal-700 text-white text-sm font-bold transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n      Visit BrightFunded →\n    \u003C/a>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">BrightFunded Scaling Requirements\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"space-y-3\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-teal-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Csvg class=\"h-3 w-3 text-teal-600\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-700\">At least \u003Cstrong>2 profitable months\u003C/strong> within a 4-month cycle\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-teal-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Csvg class=\"h-3 w-3 text-teal-600\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-700\">A minimum total profit of \u003Cstrong>10% over 4 months\u003C/strong>\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-teal-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Csvg class=\"h-3 w-3 text-teal-600\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-700\">At least \u003Cstrong>2 payouts received\u003C/strong> during the review period\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-teal-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Csvg class=\"h-3 w-3 text-teal-600\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-700\">Ending balance must be \u003Cstrong>positive or breakeven\u003C/strong>\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cp>Scaling is ongoing with no upper cap, and from the third scale-up onward, traders receive a 100% profit split, meaning you keep all the profits. Combined with the Trade2Earn loyalty program, which rewards active trading with perks like free challenges and better payout terms, BrightFunded is ideal for traders who want both flexibility and longevity.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-4 gap-3\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 text-center\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium mb-1\">Scale Amount\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-black text-teal-600\">30%\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-500\">every 4 months\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 text-center\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium mb-1\">Max Split\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-black text-teal-600\">100%\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-500\">from 3rd scale-up\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 text-center\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium mb-1\">Max Capital\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-black text-teal-600\">Unlimited\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-500\">no upper cap\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 text-center\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium mb-1\">Bonus\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-black text-teal-600\">Trade2Earn\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-500\">loyalty perks\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"2-fundednext-scaling-plan\">2. FundedNext Scaling Plan\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>FundedNext offers a clear and structured Scale-Up Plan with one of the largest potential account allocations in the industry, up to $4 million. Traders who maintain strong performance over a 4-month period can qualify for a 40% capital increase.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/fundednext.png\" alt=\"FundedNext logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">FundedNext\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">Scale Up to $4 Million\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">95%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Score\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">92/100\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Trustpilot\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">4.5/5\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Ca href=\"https://fundednext.com/?fpr=noam82\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"flex items-center justify-center px-5 py-3 sm:py-0 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-teal-600 hover:bg-teal-700 text-white text-sm font-bold transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n      Visit FundedNext →\n    \u003C/a>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">FundedNext Scaling Requirements\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"space-y-3\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-teal-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Csvg class=\"h-3 w-3 text-teal-600\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-700\">Achieve \u003Cstrong>10% account growth\u003C/strong> over 4 consecutive months\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-teal-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Csvg class=\"h-3 w-3 text-teal-600\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-700\">Receive at least \u003Cstrong>2 payouts\u003C/strong> in that period\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-teal-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Csvg class=\"h-3 w-3 text-teal-600\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-700\">Have a \u003Cstrong>profitable last trading month\u003C/strong>\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cp>If you meet these milestones, your account size increases by 40%, and the profit split remains as high as 95% depending on your account model. The drawdown limits are also adjusted proportionally, giving you room to scale without tighter restrictions.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-4 gap-3\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 text-center\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium mb-1\">Scale Amount\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-black text-teal-600\">40%\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-500\">every 4 months\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 text-center\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium mb-1\">Max Split\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-black text-teal-600\">95%\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-500\">depending on model\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 text-center\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium mb-1\">Max Capital\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-black text-teal-600\">$4M\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-500\">maximum allocation\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 text-center\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium mb-1\">Rules\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-black text-teal-600\">Transparent\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-500\">across all models\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"3-blueberry-funded-scaling-plan\">3. Blueberry Funded Scaling Plan\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Blueberry Funded rewards steady performance with a 25% account increase every 3 months, allowing growth up to $2 million in simulated capital.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-4 p-5 flex-1 min-w-0\">\n      \u003Cimg src=\"/images/logos/blueberry-funded-logo.png\" alt=\"Blueberry Funded logo\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 object-contain bg-white p-1 flex-shrink-0\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"min-w-0\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight\">Blueberry Funded\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5\">Top Broker-Backed Scaling Plan\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-6 px-5 py-3 sm:py-5 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/50 text-center\">\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Split\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600\">90%\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Score\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">93/100\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium\">Trustpilot\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800\">3.8/5\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Ca href=\"https://blueberryfunded.com/?utm_source=affiliate&#x26;ref=1457\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"flex items-center justify-center px-5 py-3 sm:py-0 border-t sm:border-t-0 sm:border-l border-slate-100 bg-teal-600 hover:bg-teal-700 text-white text-sm font-bold transition-colors whitespace-nowrap\">\n      Visit Blueberry Funded →\n    \u003C/a>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Blueberry Funded Scaling Requirements\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"space-y-3\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-teal-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Csvg class=\"h-3 w-3 text-teal-600\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-700\">Maintain a \u003Cstrong>10% net profit\u003C/strong> over 3 months\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-teal-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Csvg class=\"h-3 w-3 text-teal-600\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-700\">Complete \u003Cstrong>4 profit payouts\u003C/strong> during that period\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cp>Profit splits start at 80%, but can increase to 90% for top performers. Trading conditions remain the same even as your account scales, so your strategy does not need to change, just your position sizing.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-4 gap-3\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 text-center\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium mb-1\">Scale Amount\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-black text-teal-600\">25%\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-500\">every 3 months\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 text-center\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium mb-1\">Max Split\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-black text-teal-600\">90%\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-500\">for top performers\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 text-center\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium mb-1\">Max Capital\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-black text-teal-600\">$2M\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-500\">simulated capital\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 text-center\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium mb-1\">Conditions\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-black text-teal-600\">Same\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-[10px] text-slate-500\">no rule changes\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"how-prop-scaling-plans-work\">How Prop Scaling Plans Work\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>If you have proven to the firm that you are a profitable trader and manage risk well, the prop firm will want you to handle more capital. As long as you meet all the scaling requirements, providing you with a bigger chunk of the firm’s capital means bigger profit potential for everyone involved, with the prop firm literally investing in your talent and betting on your success.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>This is your pathway to growth within a prop firm, allowing you access to a larger account size and more buying power than what you likely have with your personal funds, turning prop trading into a career path with strong earning potential. This mechanism is what allows many prop firms to attract and retain winning traders.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"requirements-for-capital-increases\">Requirements for Capital Increases\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Of course, prop firms will not simply hand out more capital to their prop traders. They need to earn it first before being granted capital increases. Rules differ between trading firms, but the main details that are common in the industry are detailed below.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4\">Core Scaling Requirements\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"space-y-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-teal-500 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Cspan class=\"text-xs font-black text-white\">1\u003C/span>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Consistent Profits\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-600\">This is the main requirement. You need to demonstrate that you have trading strategies that consistently yield results, not just relying solely on luck. Prop firms have defined profit targets for you to achieve, which is usually the main trigger for a scaling upgrade review.\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-teal-500 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Cspan class=\"text-xs font-black text-white\">2\u003C/span>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Risk Management\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-600\">This is a must. Failing to follow the prop firm's risk management rules, like daily loss limits or maximum drawdown limits, can get your account closed. Effective risk management shows you can handle larger trading account sizes responsibly.\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-teal-500 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Cspan class=\"text-xs font-black text-white\">3\u003C/span>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Other Trading Rules\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-600\">Besides risk management, other trading rules must be followed, including position sizing, minimum trading days, and any specific firm trading guidelines. Even if you are profitable, but are breaking some of these other rules, you will not get your account scaled up.\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"gradual-vs-rapid-scaling-plans\">Gradual vs Rapid Scaling Plans\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>This is where most trading prop firms differ, as not all prop firms provide scaling plans at the same speed. Depending on the firm, these plans can be gradual or rapid.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"p-5 border-b sm:border-b-0 sm:border-r border-slate-200 bg-teal-50/30\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-3\">\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-teal-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n          \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4 text-teal-600\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n        \u003C/div>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-extrabold text-slate-900\">Gradual Scaling\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Typically 25-50% capital increases\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Adapt comfortably to larger capital\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Ideal for steady, consistent growth\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Lower risk of overexposure\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"p-5\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-3\">\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-amber-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n          \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4 text-amber-600\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n        \u003C/div>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-extrabold text-slate-900\">Rapid Scaling\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Can double account size multiple times\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Shorter timeframes to reach max capital\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Requires ambitious profit targets\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>Only for experienced, disciplined traders\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cp>The key here is to find the prop firm with a scaling plan that is in sync with your trading style and personality and how quickly you can adapt to the increasing risk exposure. Only then can you figure out which trading firm is better for you.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"performance-milestones-and-scaling-increments\">Performance Milestones and Scaling Increments\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Once you get a funded account, your next target is to get more trading capital. But before you can unlock those scaling increments, you need to hit trading goals or performance milestones.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Typically, prop firms set these targets in percentage terms rather than fixed dollar amounts, usually between 5-15%, before triggering the first capital increase.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Typical Profit Target Progression\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"space-y-3\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-20\">\n        \u003Cspan class=\"inline-block rounded-full bg-teal-100 px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-bold text-teal-700\">Beginner\u003C/span>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-1 bg-slate-100 rounded-full h-4 overflow-hidden\">\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"bg-teal-500 h-full rounded-full\" style=\"width: 40%\">\u003C/div>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-700 w-16 text-right\">5-8%\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-20\">\n        \u003Cspan class=\"inline-block rounded-full bg-amber-100 px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-bold text-amber-700\">Mid-Level\u003C/span>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-1 bg-slate-100 rounded-full h-4 overflow-hidden\">\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"bg-amber-500 h-full rounded-full\" style=\"width: 66%\">\u003C/div>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-700 w-16 text-right\">8-12%\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-20\">\n        \u003Cspan class=\"inline-block rounded-full bg-red-100 px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-bold text-red-700\">Advanced\u003C/span>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-1 bg-slate-100 rounded-full h-4 overflow-hidden\">\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"bg-red-500 h-full rounded-full\" style=\"width: 100%\">\u003C/div>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-700 w-16 text-right\">15%+\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-3\">Example: On a $50,000 account, a 5% target means $2,500 profit, while a 15% target means $7,500.\u003C/p>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"trading-styles-and-scaling-up\">Trading Styles and Scaling Up\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>Your trading style plays a big factor in how fast you can level up through the scaling plans, with different styles having different scaling potential.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"p-5 border-b sm:border-b-0 sm:border-r border-slate-200\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-3\">\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-amber-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n          \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4 text-amber-600\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n        \u003C/div>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-extrabold text-slate-900\">Day Trading\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-600 mb-2\">Fastest way to scale. Frequent trades give more chances to lock in profits and hit targets quickly.\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-1 mt-3\">\n        \u003Cspan class=\"text-xs font-bold text-amber-600\">Speed:\u003C/span>\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"flex gap-0.5\">\n          \u003Cdiv class=\"w-3 h-3 rounded-sm bg-amber-500\">\u003C/div>\n          \u003Cdiv class=\"w-3 h-3 rounded-sm bg-amber-500\">\u003C/div>\n          \u003Cdiv class=\"w-3 h-3 rounded-sm bg-amber-500\">\u003C/div>\n        \u003C/div>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-1 mt-1\">\n        \u003Cspan class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500\">Risk:\u003C/span>\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"flex gap-0.5\">\n          \u003Cdiv class=\"w-3 h-3 rounded-sm bg-red-500\">\u003C/div>\n          \u003Cdiv class=\"w-3 h-3 rounded-sm bg-red-500\">\u003C/div>\n          \u003Cdiv class=\"w-3 h-3 rounded-sm bg-red-500\">\u003C/div>\n        \u003C/div>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"p-5 border-b sm:border-b-0 sm:border-r border-slate-200\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-3\">\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-teal-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n          \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4 text-teal-600\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M8 7h12m0 0l-4-4m4 4l-4 4m0 6H4m0 0l4 4m-4-4l4-4\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n        \u003C/div>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-extrabold text-slate-900\">Swing Trading\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-600 mb-2\">Balanced approach. Less risk exposure with the ideal middle ground that works with most scaling plans.\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-1 mt-3\">\n        \u003Cspan class=\"text-xs font-bold text-teal-600\">Speed:\u003C/span>\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"flex gap-0.5\">\n          \u003Cdiv class=\"w-3 h-3 rounded-sm bg-teal-500\">\u003C/div>\n          \u003Cdiv class=\"w-3 h-3 rounded-sm bg-teal-500\">\u003C/div>\n          \u003Cdiv class=\"w-3 h-3 rounded-sm bg-slate-200\">\u003C/div>\n        \u003C/div>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-1 mt-1\">\n        \u003Cspan class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500\">Risk:\u003C/span>\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"flex gap-0.5\">\n          \u003Cdiv class=\"w-3 h-3 rounded-sm bg-red-500\">\u003C/div>\n          \u003Cdiv class=\"w-3 h-3 rounded-sm bg-red-500\">\u003C/div>\n          \u003Cdiv class=\"w-3 h-3 rounded-sm bg-slate-200\">\u003C/div>\n        \u003C/div>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"p-5\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-3\">\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-blue-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n          \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4 text-blue-600\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n        \u003C/div>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-extrabold text-slate-900\">Position Trading\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-600 mb-2\">Slower but safest. Provides the most sustainable long-term scaling approach with minimal drawdown risk.\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-1 mt-3\">\n        \u003Cspan class=\"text-xs font-bold text-blue-600\">Speed:\u003C/span>\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"flex gap-0.5\">\n          \u003Cdiv class=\"w-3 h-3 rounded-sm bg-blue-500\">\u003C/div>\n          \u003Cdiv class=\"w-3 h-3 rounded-sm bg-slate-200\">\u003C/div>\n          \u003Cdiv class=\"w-3 h-3 rounded-sm bg-slate-200\">\u003C/div>\n        \u003C/div>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center gap-1 mt-1\">\n        \u003Cspan class=\"text-xs font-bold text-red-500\">Risk:\u003C/span>\n        \u003Cdiv class=\"flex gap-0.5\">\n          \u003Cdiv class=\"w-3 h-3 rounded-sm bg-red-500\">\u003C/div>\n          \u003Cdiv class=\"w-3 h-3 rounded-sm bg-slate-200\">\u003C/div>\n          \u003Cdiv class=\"w-3 h-3 rounded-sm bg-slate-200\">\u003C/div>\n        \u003C/div>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cp>Finding a prop firm with a scaling structure that aligns with your trading approach is usually a good idea. Some firms will be a match for active traders, while more consistent and methodical traders may be at home with certain prop trading firms.\u003C/p>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"trading-performance-and-capital-allocation\">Trading Performance and Capital Allocation\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>Beyond hitting profit targets, prop firms examine how you achieve them, evaluating the quality of your trading and other performance criteria, which will dictate how they increase your funded trading account.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4\">What Prop Firms Evaluate\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600 mb-1\">Risk-Adjusted Returns\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-600\">Achieving consistent performance while staying within risk parameters can significantly help in securing favorable scaling terms.\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600 mb-1\">Drawdown Management\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-600\">Generating profits without your account fluctuating into big dips. Prop firms will be more willing to provide additional capital to steady performers.\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600 mb-1\">Consistency in Returns\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-600\">Trading firms value traders whose fund value moves steadily upwards, rather than one that swings wildly up and down. Predictable performance is better for them.\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-600 mb-1\">Trade Management\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-600\">How traders size positions, as well as trade entry and exit timings, also factor into scaling decisions.\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-3\">Prop firms are now adopting algorithms to automatically analyze these metrics, customizing scaling plans according to each trader's style and strengths.\u003C/p>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"prop-firm-scaling-criteria\">Prop Firm Scaling Criteria\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>Hitting profit targets is great, but prop firms look beyond this before scaling your account to the next level. They have other key trading parameters you need to reach before you can get a bigger trading account.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"minimum-trading-days\">Minimum Trading Days\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>While it varies, many prop firms will want to see you trading actively with at least 10, 15, 30 days, etc, before they will consider upgrading your account size. You can hit your profit goals, but scaling will not automatically happen unless you reach the required trading days before getting a bump on your capital.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Some of them will even look at how you spread your trades across the month, as they would rather see you make a few but consistent trades each day, than cramming your activities in a short period of time. This way, they can identify traders with sustainable trading strategies, rather than gamblers looking to make quick profits.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"trading-consistency\">Trading Consistency\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Before being trusted with more capital allocation, prop firms need to see that you can maintain consistent profitability. As your account size grows, you must demonstrate that you can handle the increased pressure and responsibility that comes with it.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Trading dynamics differ significantly from the initial capital allocation of $25,000 to a scaled plan of $100,000, and prop firms know this. If the firms notice that your performance dips after scaling, they may hold off on upgrading your account, making it crucial to keep following risk management protocols to maintain consistent performance.\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"common-trading-rules\">Common Trading Rules\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Prop firms use guardrails to help their prop traders stay on the right path to success, especially as the trading account size increases, ensuring adherence to risk parameters.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Common Rules at Scaled Levels\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"space-y-3\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-red-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Csvg class=\"h-3 w-3 text-red-500\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Daily Drawdown Limits\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500\">Usually capped at under 5% of account value on any single day. Hit this and you risk getting your account shut down.\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-red-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Csvg class=\"h-3 w-3 text-red-500\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Maximum Drawdown Limits\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500\">Caps the allowable loss from a trader's peak account value. Breach this and you may face account termination.\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-red-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Csvg class=\"h-3 w-3 text-red-500\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Position Holding Periods\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500\">Usually restricts overnight or weekend positions. Some firms will relax holding restrictions for consistently profitable traders.\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-red-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Csvg class=\"h-3 w-3 text-red-500\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">News Trading Restrictions\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500\">Usually restricted to 2-10 minute high impact news windows, as price swings can be significant during these periods.\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-red-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Csvg class=\"h-3 w-3 text-red-500\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Instrument Restrictions\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500\">Commonly applied to volatile instruments like cryptocurrencies. These can loosen as traders progress to higher account levels.\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500 mt-3\">Some rules may be introduced or relaxed as you progress through the scaling levels.\u003C/p>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"trading-strategies-for-scaling-success\">Trading Strategies for Scaling Success\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cp>Scaling plans allow for increased profit potential, but to keep winning and levelling up your account, you need to adjust trading strategies from when you started trading, as they may no longer apply to scaled-up accounts.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>Simply increasing your trade position sizing will not cut it. You need to change your mental approach, update your strategy or learn a few more skills. You do not have to overhaul your entire trading strategy as your account grows, but making it adaptable is a trait successful traders have in the prop trading industry.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4\">Key Areas to Adapt\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"space-y-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-slate-700 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4 text-white\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Mental State\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-600\">With bigger trading accounts come bigger gains or losses, which can mess with your head if you are not ready for it. Larger positions will require even stronger mental discipline for you to stick to your plan.\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-slate-700 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4 text-white\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M4 4v5h.582m15.356 2A8.001 8.001 0 004.582 9m0 0H9m11 11v-5h-.581m0 0a8.003 8.003 0 01-15.357-2m15.357 2H15\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Update Trading Strategy\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-600\">Make sure that your favorite trading strategy remains effective at bigger trading accounts. Strategies may be effective at smaller accounts, but with larger accounts requiring more liquidity, closing positions can pose significant challenges.\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-slate-700 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4 text-white\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Refining Trading Skills\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-600\">Scaling up means your trading skills got you there. However, reaching the next scaling level may require further improvement in certain aspects, such as trade execution, analysis, or adopting a more rigid trading discipline and increased patience.\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Ch3 id=\"risk-management-at-scale\">Risk Management at Scale\u003C/h3>\n\u003Cp>Effective risk management remains crucial, especially with scaled-up accounts. The temptation to take more risks with bigger accounts is strong, making risk management more critical at this point.\u003C/p>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-8 rounded-xl border-l-4 border-amber-500 bg-amber-50/60 px-5 py-4\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1\">Scaling Warning\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-700\">As your account grows, the temptation to take more risks is strong. Risking 1% of a $100,000 account ($1,000) feels very different from 1% of a $25,000 account ($250). You need to be mentally ready for the increased risk exposure at each level.\u003C/p>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4\">Risk Discipline Tips for Scaling\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"space-y-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-teal-500 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Cspan class=\"text-xs font-black text-white\">1\u003C/span>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Keep Risk Proportional\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-600\">Underexposure may risk your account failing to meet increased profit targets, but overexposure may risk reaching drawdown limits faster if the trade goes against you.\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-teal-500 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Cspan class=\"text-xs font-black text-white\">2\u003C/span>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Spread Entries and Exits\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-600\">Compared to smaller accounts, instantly filling buy or sell orders may be dangerous on bigger accounts. Spreading out larger positions across a wider entry or exit plan helps reduce market impact.\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-teal-500 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Cspan class=\"text-xs font-black text-white\">3\u003C/span>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Be Wary of Trade Correlations\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-600\">With greater buying power, you may unintentionally open multiple positions that move in response to the same market catalyst, indirectly multiplying your risk exposure.\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-teal-500 flex items-center justify-center\">\n        \u003Cspan class=\"text-xs font-black text-white\">4\u003C/span>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Drawdown Planning\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-600\">Top traders implement a \"cooling off\" system: if they lose 3%, they automatically reduce their position sizes by 50% until they recover the lost ground.\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\u003Cp>Risk management rules are set up to protect the firm’s capital, but these rules also set up the prop traders for long-term success, while preventing disaster in the short term. Following these risk parameters, you demonstrate to the prop trading firm that you can be trusted, making it more likely for them to accelerate your scaling plan. It is not unusual for firms to be more lenient with traders with a track record of consistent performance and risk management.\u003C/p>\n\u003Chr>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"faqs\">FAQs\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 space-y-4\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5\">\n    \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2\">Which prop firm has the best scaling plan?\u003C/p>\n    \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-600\">BrightFunded has one of the best scaling plans and funded accounts, offering unlimited 30% account growth every 4 months and 100% profit splits from the third scale-up onward. It is built for long-term growth and high-profit retention. FundedNext is another top prop firm, with capital scaling up to $4 million and 40% increases every 4 months. Blueberry Funded is a broker-backed option, scaling accounts by 25% every 3 months up to $2 million.\u003C/p>\n  \u003C/div>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5\">\n    \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2\">What is a scaling plan?\u003C/p>\n    \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-600\">Scaling plans are a structured system that a prop firm offers traders to increase trading capital, once they have proven consistent profitability. Once you hit certain performance criteria, the firm will increase the allocated capital to you, allowing you to trade larger positions and increasing your profit potential. This paves the way for you to grow without putting more capital yourself.\u003C/p>\n  \u003C/div>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5\">\n    \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2\">Does FundedNext have a scaling plan?\u003C/p>\n    \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-600\">Yes, FundedNext offers a scaling plan that allows their prop traders to increase their account size by up to 40%, and up to a maximum capital allocation of $4 million. Traders need to accumulate an account growth of 10% over four consecutive months and receive at least two payouts during the period.\u003C/p>\n  \u003C/div>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5\">\n    \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2\">How to scale up a prop firm account?\u003C/p>\n    \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-600\">Consistent performance is the best way to scale up your account. You need to master risk management, follow all trading rules by the prop firm, especially those related to risk management, and minimize drawdowns. Be consistently profitable, show the firm that you can keep it up in the long term, and hit specific profit targets in the scaling plan. Finally, all the criteria, like the minimum trading days or other specific performance metrics, must be met.\u003C/p>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>",{"headings":7521,"localImagePaths":7574,"remoteImagePaths":7575,"frontmatter":7576,"imagePaths":7582},[7522,7525,7528,7531,7534,7537,7540,7543,7546,7549,7552,7555,7558,7561,7564,7567,7570,7573],{"depth":879,"slug":7523,"text":7524},"what-are-prop-scaling-plans","What Are Prop Scaling Plans?",{"depth":879,"slug":7526,"text":7527},"best-prop-firms-with-scaling-plans","Best Prop Firms with Scaling Plans",{"depth":158,"slug":7529,"text":7530},"1-brightfunded-scaling-plan","1. BrightFunded Scaling Plan",{"depth":158,"slug":7532,"text":7533},"2-fundednext-scaling-plan","2. FundedNext Scaling Plan",{"depth":158,"slug":7535,"text":7536},"3-blueberry-funded-scaling-plan","3. Blueberry Funded Scaling Plan",{"depth":879,"slug":7538,"text":7539},"how-prop-scaling-plans-work","How Prop Scaling Plans Work",{"depth":158,"slug":7541,"text":7542},"requirements-for-capital-increases","Requirements for Capital Increases",{"depth":158,"slug":7544,"text":7545},"gradual-vs-rapid-scaling-plans","Gradual vs Rapid Scaling Plans",{"depth":158,"slug":7547,"text":7548},"performance-milestones-and-scaling-increments","Performance Milestones and Scaling Increments",{"depth":879,"slug":7550,"text":7551},"trading-styles-and-scaling-up","Trading Styles and Scaling Up",{"depth":879,"slug":7553,"text":7554},"trading-performance-and-capital-allocation","Trading Performance and Capital Allocation",{"depth":879,"slug":7556,"text":7557},"prop-firm-scaling-criteria","Prop Firm Scaling Criteria",{"depth":158,"slug":7559,"text":7560},"minimum-trading-days","Minimum Trading Days",{"depth":158,"slug":7562,"text":7563},"trading-consistency","Trading Consistency",{"depth":158,"slug":7565,"text":7566},"common-trading-rules","Common Trading Rules",{"depth":879,"slug":7568,"text":7569},"trading-strategies-for-scaling-success","Trading Strategies for Scaling Success",{"depth":158,"slug":7571,"text":7572},"risk-management-at-scale","Risk Management at Scale",{"depth":879,"slug":4935,"text":4936},[],[],{"title":7503,"excerpt":7504,"category":5171,"tags":7577,"author":4798,"authorImage":4799,"publishedAt":7298,"featured":110,"readingTimeMinutes":405,"featuredFirms":7578},[7506,5609,4796,7507],[7579,7580,7581],{"slug":584,"descriptor":7510},{"slug":1392,"descriptor":7512},{"slug":332,"descriptor":7514},[],"scaling-plans.md",{"id":6400,"data":7585,"body":7597,"filePath":7598,"digest":7599,"rendered":7600,"legacyId":7683},{"title":7586,"excerpt":7587,"category":5171,"tags":7588,"author":4798,"authorImage":4799,"publishedAt":7298,"featured":110,"readingTimeMinutes":5176,"featuredFirms":7590},"Prop Firm Evaluations: How to Pass and Get Funded","Prop firm evaluations test traders on profitability and risk management before granting access to firm capital. Learn how evaluations work, the different challenge types, common rules, and how to pass the evaluation process.",[6400,5609,4796,7589],"challenges",[7591,7593,7595],{"slug":584,"descriptor":7592},"Best Overall Prop Firm",{"slug":1392,"descriptor":7594},"High Profit Split Prop Firm",{"slug":1002,"descriptor":7596},"Most Established Prop Firm","## What Are Prop Firm Evaluations?\n\nProp firms test traders by having them go through an evaluation process to prove they can trade profitably while managing risk. This challenge is designed to filter out undisciplined traders. If you follow the rules and meet the profit target, you get access to a funded account, where you can trade with the firm's capital instead of your own money and keep the bulk of the profits, with the prop firm taking a cut.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">The Evaluation Process at a Glance\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-4 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 text-center\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-2xl font-black text-teal-600 mb-1\">1\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-semibold text-slate-700\">Pay a challenge fee and enter an evaluation\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 text-center\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-2xl font-black text-teal-600 mb-1\">2\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-semibold text-slate-700\">Hit profit targets while staying within drawdown limits\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 text-center\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-2xl font-black text-teal-600 mb-1\">3\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-semibold text-slate-700\">Prove consistency over the required trading period\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 text-center\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-2xl font-black text-teal-600 mb-1\">4\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-semibold text-slate-700\">Pass evaluation and receive a funded trading account\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n---\n\n## Understanding Prop Firm Evaluations\n\nProp firm evaluations are the pathway to trading with a firm's capital. Since prop firms do not fund just anyone, you must first prove you can trade profitably while managing risk. These evaluations act as a real-world trading test, filtering out reckless traders and ensuring only those who follow risk protocols and maintain consistency move forward to a funded account.\n\nA prop firm evaluation is a structured process where you prove your trading skills before gaining access to a funded account. These evaluations test your ability to meet profit targets while staying within strict risk management rules set by the firm.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-8 rounded-xl border-l-4 border-teal-500 bg-teal-50/60 px-5 py-4\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-teal-900 mb-1\">Why Do Prop Firms Use Evaluations?\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-teal-800\">Prop firms use these challenges to identify disciplined traders who can generate consistent profits without reckless risk-taking. The evaluation rules, such as drawdown limits, trading timeframes, and allowed strategies, vary by firm, but the goal remains the same: to ensure traders can handle capital responsibly. Passing means you get to trade with the firm's money instead of your own, keeping a share of the profits while the firm takes a cut.\u003C/p>\n\u003C/div>\n\n---\n\n## Types of Prop Firm Evaluation Processes\n\nProp firms use different evaluation models to assess traders before granting them access to a funded account. These range from rapid challenges (7-10 days) to multi-step evaluations that test long-term consistency.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"bg-[#0d1b2a] px-5 py-4\">\n    \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-black text-white uppercase tracking-wide\">Evaluation Types Overview\u003C/p>\n  \u003C/div>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"p-5\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-4\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 text-center\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-black text-teal-600 mb-1\">Rapid\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-600\">7-10 day fast-track challenges\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 text-center\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-black text-teal-600 mb-1\">1-Step\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-600\">Single-phase evaluation\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 text-center\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-black text-teal-600 mb-1\">2-Step\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-600\">Industry standard process\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 text-center\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-black text-teal-600 mb-1\">3-Step\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-600\">Extended verification process\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 text-center\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-lg font-black text-teal-600 mb-1\">Instant\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-600\">Skip evaluations entirely\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\nEach type suits different trader profiles. Beginners often perform best in multi-step evaluations, while experienced traders may prefer rapid challenges, one-step processes, or instant funding.\n\n### 1. Rapid Challenges\n\nSome prop firms offer rapid challenges, requiring traders to meet profit targets within a short timeframe, typically 7-10 days. These challenges test a trader's ability to perform under pressure while managing risk.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3 mb-3\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-teal-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n      \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4 text-teal-600\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z\"/>\u003C/svg>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Rapid Challenge\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500\">Fast-track to funding in 7-10 days\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n  \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n    \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Cspan class=\"font-semibold text-slate-900 min-w-[80px]\">Best For:\u003C/span> Skilled traders who can trade efficiently within strict time constraints\u003C/li>\n    \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Cspan class=\"font-semibold text-slate-900 min-w-[80px]\">Risk Level:\u003C/span> High - shorter timeframes often force more aggressive trading styles\u003C/li>\n  \u003C/ul>\n\u003C/div>\n\nRapid challenges provide a fast route to funding but leave little room for error. Traders who cannot handle pressure or prefer a structured approach may struggle with this format.\n\n### 2. One-Step Evaluation\n\nA one-step evaluation process requires traders to meet a profit target while following strict risk management rules. Unlike rapid challenges, this process focuses more on trading discipline than pure speed.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3 mb-3\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-teal-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n      \u003Cspan class=\"text-sm font-black text-teal-600\">1\u003C/span>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">One-Step Evaluation\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500\">Single phase, focused on discipline\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n  \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n    \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Cspan class=\"font-semibold text-slate-900 min-w-[80px]\">Best For:\u003C/span> Experienced traders comfortable with risk controls and confident in their strategy\u003C/li>\n    \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Cspan class=\"font-semibold text-slate-900 min-w-[80px]\">Risk Level:\u003C/span> Moderate - profit targets must be hit, but traders typically have more flexibility than in rapid challenges\u003C/li>\n  \u003C/ul>\n\u003C/div>\n\nThis model offers a faster path to funding than multi-step processes but demands strong risk management. One bad trade can mean failure.\n\n### 3. Two-Step Evaluation\n\nThe two-step evaluation process is the most common process used by prop firms. It allows traders to prove their skills over multiple phases, focusing on both profitability and risk control.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"bg-[#0d1b2a] px-5 py-4\">\n    \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-black text-white uppercase tracking-wide\">Two-Step Evaluation Process\u003C/p>\n  \u003C/div>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"p-5\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-4\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-teal-50 border border-teal-200 px-4 py-3\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-teal-700 uppercase tracking-wide mb-1\">Step 1\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-700\">Traders must reach a profit target while respecting drawdown limits\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-teal-50 border border-teal-200 px-4 py-3\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-teal-700 uppercase tracking-wide mb-1\">Step 2\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-700\">Tests consistency over a longer period, ensuring traders are not relying on short-term luck\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n      \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Cspan class=\"font-semibold text-slate-900 min-w-[80px]\">Best For:\u003C/span> Ideal for beginners and intermediate traders who want a structured approach\u003C/li>\n      \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Cspan class=\"font-semibold text-slate-900 min-w-[80px]\">Risk Level:\u003C/span> Lower than one-step challenges - more time allows for controlled, disciplined trading\u003C/li>\n    \u003C/ul>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\nTwo-step challenges give traders more room to adapt and prove they can trade responsibly over time.\n\n### 4. Three-Step Evaluation\n\nA three-step evaluation process is a less common but more rigorous assessment that extends the verification process further. This model ensures traders have a long-term, repeatable strategy before gaining access to a funded account.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"bg-[#0d1b2a] px-5 py-4\">\n    \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-black text-white uppercase tracking-wide\">Three-Step Evaluation Process\u003C/p>\n  \u003C/div>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"p-5\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-4\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-teal-50 border border-teal-200 px-4 py-3\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-teal-700 uppercase tracking-wide mb-1\">Step 1\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-700\">Profitability and risk management test\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-teal-50 border border-teal-200 px-4 py-3\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-teal-700 uppercase tracking-wide mb-1\">Step 2\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-700\">Emphasizes consistency over a longer trading period\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-teal-50 border border-teal-200 px-4 py-3\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-teal-700 uppercase tracking-wide mb-1\">Step 3\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-700\">Additional restrictions, often including profit consistency requirements or scaling rules\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n      \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Cspan class=\"font-semibold text-slate-900 min-w-[80px]\">Best For:\u003C/span> Traders looking to prove sustained performance and build a long-term relationship with a prop firm\u003C/li>\n      \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Cspan class=\"font-semibold text-slate-900 min-w-[80px]\">Risk Level:\u003C/span> Lower - firms provide more time to demonstrate steady growth\u003C/li>\n    \u003C/ul>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\nWhile this model takes longer, it helps prop firms identify traders who can consistently perform over extended periods.\n\n### 5. Instant Funding\n\nSome prop firms offer instant funding, allowing traders to start with firm capital immediately without passing an evaluation. Instead of completing a challenge, traders pay a one-time fee to access a funded account with profit splits.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3 mb-3\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-emerald-100 flex items-center justify-center\">\n      \u003Csvg class=\"h-4 w-4 text-emerald-600\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z\"/>\u003C/svg>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Instant Funding\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500\">Skip evaluations and start trading immediately\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n  \u003Cul class=\"space-y-1.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n    \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Cspan class=\"font-semibold text-slate-900 min-w-[80px]\">Best For:\u003C/span> Traders who want immediate access to capital without going through a multi-step evaluation\u003C/li>\n    \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Cspan class=\"font-semibold text-slate-900 min-w-[80px]\">Risk Level:\u003C/span> Moderate - no challenge required, but strict risk limits and profit withdrawal conditions often apply\u003C/li>\n  \u003C/ul>\n\u003C/div>\n\nInstant funding provides a faster route to trading firm capital, but traders should review fees, restrictions, and profit withdrawal policies before choosing a provider. You can read about the [best instant funding prop firms](/guides/instant-funding/) here.\n\n---\n\n## Common Rules and Requirements of Prop Evaluations\n\nPassing a prop firm evaluation is not just about hitting profit targets. It is about sticking to risk management rules, demonstrating consistency, and following the firm's trading guidelines. Prop firms use strict parameters to filter out high-risk traders and reward those who trade with discipline and control.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"bg-[#0d1b2a] px-5 py-4\">\n    \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-black text-white uppercase tracking-wide\">Key Evaluation Components\u003C/p>\n  \u003C/div>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"p-5\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-3\">\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-teal-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-1\">Profit Targets\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-600\">The minimum return traders must achieve\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-teal-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-1\">Drawdown Limits\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-600\">The maximum loss before failing\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-teal-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-1\">Trading Days\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-600\">Min and max time constraints\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-teal-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-1\">Consistency Rules\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-600\">No reliance on single big trades\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-teal-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-1\">Markets & Rules\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-600\">Limitations on assets and strategies\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n      \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3\">\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-bold text-teal-600 uppercase tracking-wide mb-1\">Leverage & Sizing\u003C/p>\n        \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-600\">Restrictions on trade size and margin\u003C/p>\n      \u003C/div>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\nUnderstanding these elements is essential for passing the evaluation process and securing a funded account.\n\n### Profit Targets\n\nProfit targets are the minimum percentage or dollar amount a trader must achieve during the challenge. Most firms set targets between 5% and 10% of the starting balance.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2\">Example\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-600\">A \u003Cspan class=\"font-semibold\">10% profit target\u003C/span> on a \u003Cspan class=\"font-semibold\">$100,000 account\u003C/span> means the trader must generate \u003Cspan class=\"font-semibold text-teal-600\">$10,000 in profit\u003C/span> within the evaluation process.\u003C/p>\n\u003C/div>\n\nHowever, reaching the target in a single trade is usually not allowed. Many firms require traders to show consistent performance over multiple trades, preventing them from passing the challenge with high-risk strategies. Some prop firms also cap maximum profit per trade to encourage stable growth rather than aggressive risk-taking.\n\n### Drawdown Limits\n\nDrawdown limits define the maximum amount a trader can lose before failing the evaluation. These limits ensure traders manage risk properly instead of chasing profits recklessly.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"bg-[#0d1b2a] px-5 py-4\">\n    \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-black text-white uppercase tracking-wide\">Types of Drawdown Limits\u003C/p>\n  \u003C/div>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"p-5 space-y-3\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1\">Daily Drawdown\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-600\">The most a trader can lose in a single day. Exceeding this limit results in instant failure.\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1\">Overall Drawdown\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-600\">The total loss limit over the evaluation process. If the balance drops below this level, the trader is disqualified.\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1\">Trailing Drawdown\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-600\">A dynamic loss limit that moves as the account balance grows. If a trader's peak profit level increases, the drawdown limit may adjust accordingly.\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Example Drawdown Rules\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium mb-1\">5% Daily Drawdown\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-700\">A trader with a $50,000 starting balance cannot lose more than \u003Cspan class=\"font-semibold text-red-600\">$2,500\u003C/span> in one day\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide font-medium mb-1\">10% Overall Drawdown\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm text-slate-700\">The trader must not let their balance drop below \u003Cspan class=\"font-semibold text-red-600\">$45,000\u003C/span> at any point\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\nMany traders fail not because they lack profitability, but because they ignore drawdown rules and overtrade. Managing drawdown is just as important as hitting profit targets.\n\n### Maximum and Minimum Trading Days\n\nProp firms set time constraints to balance risk and prevent traders from either rushing trades or dragging out the evaluation process indefinitely.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1\">Minimum Trading Days\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-600\">Some firms require traders to trade a minimum number of days (e.g., 5-10) to prove they are not passing with just a few lucky trades.\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1\">Maximum Trading Days\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-600\">Some firms impose deadlines (e.g., 30-90 days) to ensure traders complete the evaluation process within a set period.\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\nTraders need to plan their trades carefully. Rushing to meet deadlines can lead to poor decisions, while delaying trades too much can result in failing to meet the profit target in time.\n\n### Consistency Rules\n\nTo prevent traders from passing the evaluation with a single high-risk trade, many firms impose consistency requirements.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n    \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\n      \u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-amber-500\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z\"/>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003Cdiv>\u003Cspan class=\"font-semibold text-slate-900\">Profit Distribution Limits:\u003C/span> Some firms restrict how much of the total profit can come from one trade (e.g., no single trade can contribute more than 30-50% of total profits)\u003C/div>\n    \u003C/li>\n    \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\n      \u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-amber-500\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z\"/>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003Cdiv>\u003Cspan class=\"font-semibold text-slate-900\">Steady Position Sizing:\u003C/span> Some firms require traders to maintain consistent lot sizes to prevent them from making small trades early on and then betting big later\u003C/div>\n    \u003C/li>\n  \u003C/ul>\n\u003C/div>\n\nFor example, if a trader reaches a $10,000 profit target but $8,000 of that came from one trade, they may fail the challenge due to inconsistency. These rules ensure traders demonstrate stable, repeatable trading strategies rather than relying on a single lucky trade.\n\n### Markets and Trading Rules\n\nProprietary trading firms control which financial instruments you can trade and what trading strategies you can use to prevent excessive risk.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"bg-[#0d1b2a] px-5 py-4\">\n    \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-black text-white uppercase tracking-wide\">Common Trading Restrictions\u003C/p>\n  \u003C/div>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"p-5\">\n    \u003Cul class=\"space-y-2.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n      \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\n        \u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>\n        \u003Cdiv>\u003Cspan class=\"font-semibold text-slate-900\">Instrument Limitations:\u003C/span> Some firms limit trading to specific forex pairs, stocks, or commodities to control market exposure\u003C/div>\n      \u003C/li>\n      \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\n        \u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>\n        \u003Cdiv>\u003Cspan class=\"font-semibold text-slate-900\">Scalping Limits:\u003C/span> Some prop firms impose minimum trade durations (e.g., 1-3 minutes) to discourage ultra-fast scalping strategies\u003C/div>\n      \u003C/li>\n      \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\n        \u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>\n        \u003Cdiv>\u003Cspan class=\"font-semibold text-slate-900\">News Trading Rules:\u003C/span> Many prop firms restrict trading around high-impact economic events to prevent excessive volatility risks, typically a restricted window of 2-10 minutes before and after major news releases\u003C/div>\n      \u003C/li>\n      \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\n        \u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>\n        \u003Cdiv>\u003Cspan class=\"font-semibold text-slate-900\">HFT Limits:\u003C/span> Some firms ban algorithmic trading or rapid order execution to prevent market manipulation\u003C/div>\n      \u003C/li>\n      \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\n        \u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>\n        \u003Cdiv>\u003Cspan class=\"font-semibold text-slate-900\">Weekend & Overnight Holding:\u003C/span> Some firms require traders to close positions before market close to limit overnight risk\u003C/div>\n      \u003C/li>\n    \u003C/ul>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\nA trader using a news-based strategy might reach the profit target but fail the challenge if the firm explicitly bans trading during major economic announcements. Checking a firm's rulebook in advance is crucial.\n\n### Leverage and Position Sizing\n\nProp trading firms often limit leverage and trade size to prevent traders from taking excessive risks.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1\">Leverage Restrictions\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-600\">Some firms cap leverage at 1:10 or 1:30, especially for forex trading\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1\">Max Position Size\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-600\">Firms may limit the number of lots per trade, ensuring traders manage risk rather than placing oversized bets\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1\">Scaling Rules\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-600\">Some firms gradually increase lot size limits as traders demonstrate consistency\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\nFor example, a firm may allow a $100,000 account to trade a maximum of 5 lots at a time, preventing traders from placing massive positions that could violate drawdown rules. These restrictions force traders to prioritize risk management rather than using aggressive trade sizes to hit profit targets quickly.\n\n---\n\n## How to Pass a Prop Firm Evaluation\n\nTo pass a prop firm evaluation, traders must meet profit targets while staying within risk limits. Success depends on risk management, consistency, and discipline, not just profitability.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"bg-[#0d1b2a] px-5 py-4\">\n    \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-black text-white uppercase tracking-wide\">Keys to Passing Your Evaluation\u003C/p>\n  \u003C/div>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"p-5\">\n    \u003Cul class=\"space-y-2.5 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n      \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\n        \u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>\n        \u003Cdiv>\u003Cspan class=\"font-semibold text-slate-900\">Start with a clear trading plan\u003C/span> that includes entry/exit strategies, stop-loss levels, and position sizing rules\u003C/div>\n      \u003C/li>\n      \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\n        \u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>\n        \u003Cdiv>\u003Cspan class=\"font-semibold text-slate-900\">Follow strict drawdown limits\u003C/span> and avoid overleveraging your positions\u003C/div>\n      \u003C/li>\n      \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\n        \u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>\n        \u003Cdiv>\u003Cspan class=\"font-semibold text-slate-900\">Be consistent\u003C/span> - prop firms favour traders who show steady performance over time rather than relying on a few big trades\u003C/div>\n      \u003C/li>\n      \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\n        \u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>\n        \u003Cdiv>\u003Cspan class=\"font-semibold text-slate-900\">Use a trading journal\u003C/span> to track performance, refine strategies, and eliminate weak points\u003C/div>\n      \u003C/li>\n      \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\n        \u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>\n        \u003Cdiv>\u003Cspan class=\"font-semibold text-slate-900\">Avoid emotional trading\u003C/span> - chasing losses or overtrading often leads to failure\u003C/div>\n      \u003C/li>\n    \u003C/ul>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\nThe best approach is controlled, strategic execution with a focus on risk-adjusted profitability.\n\n---\n\n## Benefits of Passing a Prop Trading Firm Evaluation\n\nPassing the evaluation gives you access to larger trading capital without risking personal funds. Instead of growing a small account, you can manage funded accounts ranging from thousands to seven figures, significantly increasing profit potential.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Key Benefits of Getting Funded\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 text-center\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-2xl font-black text-teal-600 mb-1\">$200K+\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-semibold text-slate-700\">Access to large trading capital\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 text-center\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-2xl font-black text-teal-600 mb-1\">90%+\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-semibold text-slate-700\">Profit split in your favour\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 text-center\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-2xl font-black text-teal-600 mb-1\">$0\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs font-semibold text-slate-700\">Personal capital at risk\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\nMost prop trading firms offer profit splits up to 90%, allowing traders to keep the majority of their earnings. Beyond profits, prop trading provides professional growth opportunities, including access to advanced trading tools, mentorship, and analytics to refine trading strategies. Since you risk the firm's capital and not your own money, you can focus on strategy and execution without the emotional pressure of losing personal funds.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"p-5 border-b sm:border-b-0 sm:border-r border-slate-100\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-emerald-600 mb-3\">Pros\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Access to large capital\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Limited personal financial risk\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Improves risk management\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>No long-term commitment\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\">\u003Cpath fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"/>\u003C/svg>Builds trading discipline\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"p-5\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-red-500 mb-3\">Cons\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-700\">\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Strict drawdown limits\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Trading strategy restrictions\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Tough profit targets\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>Requires consistent gains\u003C/li>\n        \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-red-400\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\"/>\u003C/svg>No guaranteed success\u003C/li>\n      \u003C/ul>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\nProp trading is a gateway to higher-level trading opportunities while minimizing financial risk.\n\n---\n\n## Common Mistakes to Avoid in Prop Firm Evaluations\n\nProp firm challenges are worth it for traders with strong risk management skills, well-defined strategies, and consistent trading performance. Passing an evaluation grants access to larger trading capital with profit splits ranging from 70% to 90%.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-8 rounded-xl border-l-4 border-amber-400 bg-amber-50/60 px-5 py-4\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-amber-900 mb-2\">Avoid These Common Mistakes\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm text-amber-800\">\n    \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\n      \u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-amber-500\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z\"/>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003Cspan>Overleveraging positions to hit profit targets quickly\u003C/span>\n    \u003C/li>\n    \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\n      \u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-amber-500\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z\"/>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003Cspan>Ignoring drawdown limits and overtrading after losses\u003C/span>\n    \u003C/li>\n    \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\n      \u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-amber-500\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z\"/>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003Cspan>Relying on a single trade to pass the challenge\u003C/span>\n    \u003C/li>\n    \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\n      \u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-amber-500\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z\"/>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003Cspan>Trading during restricted news events without checking the firm's rules\u003C/span>\n    \u003C/li>\n    \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\n      \u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-amber-500\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z\"/>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003Cspan>Emotional trading and chasing losses after a bad day\u003C/span>\n    \u003C/li>\n    \u003Cli class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\n      \u003Csvg class=\"mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-amber-500\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\">\u003Cpath stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z\"/>\u003C/svg>\n      \u003Cspan>Not reading the firm's full rulebook before starting the challenge\u003C/span>\n    \u003C/li>\n  \u003C/ul>\n\u003C/div>\n\nTraders who lack disciplined risk management or struggle with drawdown limits may find it difficult to pass. Success depends on trading with control, following a structured plan, and managing risk effectively.\n\n---\n\n## Selecting the Best Prop Firm\n\nChoosing one of the best prop trading firms with competitive pricing and conditions is key to securing funding and avoiding unreliable firms. We outline which firms to avoid, along with leading broker-backed prop firms on our [broker reviews](/prop-firms/) page.\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"not-prose my-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm\">\n  \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Best Prop Firms by Region\u003C/p>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-4 gap-3\">\n    \u003Ca href=\"/best/usa/\" class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 text-center hover:bg-teal-50 hover:border-teal-200 border border-transparent transition-colors\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">USA\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500\">Top US firms\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/a>\n    \u003Ca href=\"/best/canada/\" class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 text-center hover:bg-teal-50 hover:border-teal-200 border border-transparent transition-colors\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">Canada\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500\">Top CA firms\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/a>\n    \u003Ca href=\"/best/uk/\" class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 text-center hover:bg-teal-50 hover:border-teal-200 border border-transparent transition-colors\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">UK\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500\">Top UK firms\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/a>\n    \u003Ca href=\"/best/india/\" class=\"rounded-lg bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 text-center hover:bg-teal-50 hover:border-teal-200 border border-transparent transition-colors\">\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900\">India\u003C/p>\n      \u003Cp class=\"text-xs text-slate-500\">Top IN firms\u003C/p>\n    \u003C/a>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/div>\n\nLook for transparent risk parameters, fair profit splits, good trading platforms, and verified trader reviews. Ensure the firm's profit targets, drawdown limits, and trading restrictions align with your strategy.\n\nA reputable prop firm provides educational resources, trader support, and clear payout policies. Always review fees and hidden costs to protect your profits. A well-structured firm increases your chances of passing and getting funded.\n\n---\n\n## Our Top Picks\n\n### 1. BrightFunded -- Best Overall Prop Firm\n\nBrightFunded stands out with its unlimited scal